NK120(e)001:1: // sdom gsum rnam par nges pa'i bstan bcos kyi 'bru
NK120(e)001:2: 'grel blo gros gsar bu'i yid kyi gdung sel legs
NK120(e)001:3: bshad bdud rtsi'i za ma tog ces bya ba bzhugs
NK120(e)001:5: rnam 'dren stong rtsa'i dbus na pad dkar bzhin //
NK120(e)001:6: rab basngagasa rtsod ldan gdul bya'i dpal shar ba //
NK120(e)001:7: ngo mtshar ston pa mtshungs med sh+aakya'i rgyal //
NK120(e)001:8: khyod zhabs spyi bo'i rgyan du thog mar bsnyen //
NK120(e)001:9: 'od snang mtha' yas mgon po'i zlos gar ni //
NK120(e)001:10: sin+d+hu'i pad mtshor bsgyur las mtshan sku'i dpal //
NK120(e)001:11: 'chi med rig 'dzin gzhon nu'i rnam 'gyur gyis //
NK120(e)001:12: snang srid zil gnon mdzad der snying nas gus //
NK120(e)001:13: gangs can skye 'gro thog ma'i 'dren pa ru //
NK120(e)001:14: bsam bzhin byon pa mkhan chen zhi ba 'tsho //
NK120(e)001:15: gangs ljongs smag rum khrod na rgyal bstan gyi //
NK120(e)001:16: snang byed thog mar 'dren bzod khri srong rje //
NK120(e)001:17: rnam gsum bod la lhag par rjes brtse'i stobs //
NK120(e)001:18: ngo mtshar rnam thar da lta'i bar du yang //
NK120(e)001:19: mngon sum tshad grub bka' drin phung po'i tshul //
NK120(e)001:20: rjes su mi dran byol song las gzhan su //
NK120(e)001:21: tha ma'i dus 'dir slar yang chos rgyal nyid //
NK120(e)001:22: sdom brtson pan+di ta yi tshul bzung nas //
NK120(e)001:23: rgyal ba'i gsung rab dgongs don gnad dril te //
NK120(e)001:24: sdom gsum rnam nges bdud rtsi'i bgo skal stsal //
NK120(e)001:25: tshul 'dir shes bya kun gzigs lo chen rje //
NK120(e)001:26: d+harma sh+r+ai sogs sngon byon mkhas rnams kyis //
NK120(e)001:27: dgongs 'grel legs bshad ci dgar spros las 'dir //
NK120(e)001:28: rgyal bstan mi nyams dar mdzad bka' drin dran //
NK120(e)001:29: slar yang rang 'dra thos chung gsar bu'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:30: rjod byed tshig nyung brjod bya'i don ma nor //
NK120(e)001:31: don gnad rjen phyungs rgyas bshad spros pa bskyungs //
NK120(e)001:32: blta bde go sla thog ma'i 'jug sgo ru //
NK120(e)001:34: don gnyer can 'gar tshegs chung don che'i skyes //
NK120(e)001:35: de phyir lhag bsam dag pa'i brtson pa 'di //
NK120(e)001:36: don ldan nyid du 'gyur bar byin brlabs gsol //
NK120(e)001:37: de'ang bdag cag gi ston pa thabs mkhas la thugs
NK120(e)001:38: rje tshad med pa dang ldan pa 'di nyid kyis
NK120(e)001:39: zhing 'di'i gdul bya rnams thar pa bla na med
NK120(e)001:40: pa'i lam du dkri ba'i phyir chos kyi phung po
NK120(e)001:41: brgyad khri bzhi stong ji snyed cig gsungs pa thams
NK120(e)001:42: cad bsdu na sde snod bzhir 'du zhing /
NK120(e)001:43: de dag gis bstan bya ma lus pa'ang sdom pa
NK120(e)001:44: gsum gyi nyams len gyi khongs su 'du ba'i phyir
NK120(e)001:45: / de nyid mdo sngags kyi bstan pa mtha' dag gi snying po'i bcud du yongs su gzigs nas /
NK120(e)001:46: 'jam dpal dbyangs dngos chos rgyal tshangs pa lha'i me
NK120(e)001:47: tog gi gsang ba gsum gyi rnam par rol pa
NK120(e)001:48: yul mnga' ris kyi pan+di ta chen po pad+ma dbang
NK120(e)001:49: rgyal rdo rje grags pa rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po
NK120(e)001:50: zhes mkhas pa'i phul du phyin cing grub pa'i sa
NK120(e)001:51: mthor gshegs pa de nyid kyis /
NK120(e)001:52: rang re rjes 'jug gi gdul bya rnams la brtse
NK120(e)001:53: ba chen pos lhag par rab tu dgongs te sdom
NK120(e)001:54: pa gsum gyi nyams len gnad du dril bar mdzad
NK120(e)001:55: pa'i legs bshad rmad du byung ba 'di nyid 'chad
NK120(e)001:56: par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK120(e)001:57: thog mar dge ba klad kyi don /
NK120(e)001:58: bar du dge ba gzhung gi don /
NK120(e)001:59: tha mar dge ba mjug gi don no //
NK120(e)001:60: dang po thog mar dge ba klad kyi don la'ang gsum /
NK120(e)001:64: dang po mtshan smos pa ni /
NK120(e)001:65: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lam gyi cha lag
NK120(e)001:66: sdom pa gsum rnam par nges pa zhes bya ba'i
NK120(e)001:69: 'di ltar sems kyi ranga bzhina ma bcos pa'i gnas
NK120(e)001:70: lugs zab mo'i klong na gzhi lam 'bras bu'i chos
NK120(e)001:71: thams cad ma btsal ye rdzogsa su lhun gyis grub
NK120(e)001:72: pa ni bla na medapa'i chena po ste /
NK120(e)001:73: de'i tshul ma nor bar dngos su gtan la 'bebs
NK120(e)001:74: par byed pas na lam kun gyi mthar thug pa
NK120(e)001:75: ni a ti yo ga yin cing /
NK120(e)001:76: a nu man chad mdo sngags kyi chos tshul thams
NK120(e)001:77: cad kyang 'di nyid rtogs par byed pa'i lam gyi
NK120(e)001:78: cha lag tu grub pa dang /
NK120(e)001:79: de thams cad kyi brjod bya nyams len gyi snying po ni sdom pa gsuma yin la /
NK120(e)001:80: de'i don dpyad pa gsum gyi sgo nas sgro skur
NK120(e)001:81: dang bral bar gtan la phab pas na rnam para
NK120(e)001:82: ngesa pa zhes bya ba ste /
NK120(e)001:83: bstan bcos zhes pa'i sgra don 'chos skyob la 'jug
NK120(e)001:84: pas na rgyu nyon mongs pa las 'chos te 'bras
NK120(e)001:85: bu ngan 'gro'i srid pa las skyob pa'i yon tan
NK120(e)001:86: dang ldan pas na bstan bcosa te /
NK120(e)001:88: nyon mongs dgra rnams ma lus 'chos pa dang //
NK120(e)001:89: ngan 'gro'i srid las skyob pa gang yin pa //
NK120(e)001:90: 'chos skyob yon tan phyir na bstan bcos te //
NK120(e)001:91: gnyis po 'di dag gzhan gyi lugs la med //
NK120(e)001:93: bzhugs so ni 'dir yod do zhes pa'o //
NK120(e)001:94: de ltar mtshan smoos pa'i dgos pa'am /
NK120(e)001:95: dbang rab rnams mtshan gyi nang du gzhung don tshang
NK120(e)001:96: bas de tsam gyis dbu zhabs kyi don thams cad
NK120(e)001:97: bde blag tu rtogs par 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:98: 'bring rnams kyis gzhung gi bzhugs tshul don spyi la nges pa rnyed par 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:99: tha mas kyang mtshan don de ldan gyi gzhung nyid
NK120(e)001:100: la myur du 'jug par spro zhing glegs bam yang
NK120(e)001:101: ngo shes pa'i dgos pa yod do //
NK120(e)001:102: gnyis pa mchod par brjod pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:103: spyir bka' drin can gyi bla ma la phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK120(e)001:104: khyad par slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas la phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK120(e)001:105: dang po spyir bka' drin can gyi bla ma la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK120(e)001:107: zhes legs sbyar gyi skad de nyid bod skad du bsgyur na /
NK120(e)001:108: na mo zhes pa phyag 'tshal ba'i don dang /
NK120(e)001:110: gu ra we zhes pa bla ma la'o //
NK120(e)001:111: de'ang gu ru'i sgra lci ba la 'jug pas lung
NK120(e)001:112: rtogs yon tan rgya che ba'i khur gyis lci ba'i
NK120(e)001:113: mkhyen pa bla na med cing thugs rje brtse ba
NK120(e)001:114: chen po ma dang mtshungs pa'i bka' drin che ba
NK120(e)001:115: de la sgo gsum gus pa chen pos 'dud pa'i
NK120(e)001:116: don no // de ltar bla ma la dang po
NK120(e)001:117: nyid du phyag 'tshal dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan gang zhe
NK120(e)001:118: don no // na / slob dpon b+ha bi lhas /
NK120(e)001:119: dbang bskur mchog thob rdo rje yi //
NK120(e)001:120: slob dpon la ni de bzhin gshegs //
NK120(e)001:121: phyogs bcu'i sems can khams bzhugs pa'i //
NK120(e)001:122: dus gsum du ni mngon phyag 'tshal //
NK120(e)001:124: gnyis pa khyad par slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas la phyag 'tshal ba ni /
NK120(e)001:125: dpal ldan tshogs gnyis chu gter bsrubs pa las //
NK120(e)001:126: mkhyen brtse'i 'od dkar nges gsang gru char 'bebs //
NK120(e)001:127: gangs can mkhas grub yongs kyi gtsug rgyan mchog /
NK120(e)001:128: mtsho skyes rdo rje 'gro ba'i bla mar 'dud //
NK120(e)001:130: 'di ni rig byed pas rgya mtsho bsrubs pa las
NK120(e)001:131: zla ba thon par 'dod pa'i gtam dang chos mtshungs
NK120(e)001:132: sbyar nas gzugs can gyi rgyan du mdzad pa ste
NK120(e)001:133: / de'ang rgyu bsod nams dang 'bras bu ye shes
NK120(e)001:134: kyi dapala phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan pa'i tshoogas
NK120(e)001:135: gnyisa chu gter zab mo'am rgya mtsho chen po bsrubsa
NK120(e)001:137: shes bya thams cad la chags thogs med pa'i mkhyen rab dang /
NK120(e)001:138: dmigs pa med pa'i brtse ba'i thugs rje chen po
NK120(e)001:139: zung du 'jug pa 'oda dakara can te zla ba'i
NK120(e)001:140: dkyil 'khor cha shas yongs su rdzogs pa lta bu
NK120(e)001:141: las / gdul bya rnams la ngesa sanga bla na
NK120(e)001:142: med pa rdo rje theg pa'i lam 'bras bur bcas
NK120(e)001:143: pa ston pa'i phrin las lhun gyis grub pa'i gru
NK120(e)001:144: chara 'bebas pa ni zla ba'i bsil zer dang chos
NK120(e)001:145: las / mtshungs sbyar la / de lta bu'i mkhyen
NK120(e)001:146: brtse nus pa'i yon tan phun sum tshogs pa dang
NK120(e)001:147: ldan pa de nyid gdul bya khyad par ba gangsa
NK120(e)001:148: cana gyi ljongs 'dis mtshon pa'i sa gsum la gnas
NK120(e)001:149: pa'i makhasa pa dang grub pa yongsa kyi gtsuga gi
NK120(e)001:150: rgyan mchoga tu bsten par 'os pa mdangs ldan dri
NK120(e)001:151: med rgya mtsho'i gling gi me tog pad+ma'i sbubs su
NK120(e)001:152: pha yi rgyu dang ma yi rkyen la ma brten
NK120(e)001:153: par rig pa thol skyes kyi tshul du sku 'khrungs
NK120(e)001:154: shing skye 'chi'i gzhom gzhig bgres rgud dang bral ba
NK120(e)001:155: mi 'gyur rdo rjee'i skus gdul bya rnams rang rang
NK120(e)001:156: gi skal ba bzhin phan bde'i dpal bzang po la
NK120(e)001:157: 'god par mdzad pa'i 'gro ba'i bla ma de la
NK120(e)001:158: rtsom pa po mchog tu gus pa chen pos 'duda
NK120(e)001:159: do zhes phyag mdzad pa ni kun rdzob brda'i phyag
NK120(e)001:160: las / mtshungs sbyar la / dang / yul dang
NK120(e)001:161: yul can gnyis med du rtogs pa don dam lta
NK120(e)001:163: de ltar mchod par brjod pa'i dgos pa'ang mgon po klus /
NK120(e)001:164: bstan bcom byed pos ston pa la /
NK120(e)001:165: mchod par brjod pa 'bras med min //
NK120(e)001:166: ston pa dang ni bstan bcos la //
NK120(e)001:167: dad 'dun bskyed par bya phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:168: zhes gsungs pa ltar rtsom pa po rang gi tshogs rdzogs nas brtsams pa mthar phyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:169: rjes mjug rnams kyis bstan bcos mchog tu rig nas gus pas 'jug pa'i dgos pa yod pas so //
NK120(e)001:170: gsum pa brtsam par dam bca' ba ni /
NK120(e)001:171: 'gro blo'i dri ma 'khrud mkhas drang srong gis //
NK120(e)001:172: blo gros bee d+aur bum bzang rab thogs nas //
NK120(e)001:173: legs bshad sdom gsum bdud rtsi'i chu sbyin gyi //
NK120(e)001:174: don gnyer skye bo'i tshogs rnams 'dir 'dus shig /
NK120(e)001:176: 'gro ba thams cad kyi blo'i mi shes rmongs pa'i
NK120(e)001:177: dri ma rnams 'khrud pa la makhasa pa'i rtsom pa
NK120(e)001:178: po rang nyid 'jig rten na che ba'i yon tan
NK120(e)001:179: dang ldan par grags pa'i dranga sronga gi gzugs su
NK120(e)001:180: bkod nas mnga' ris pa bdag gis gsung rab dgongs
NK120(e)001:181: 'grel dang bcas pa'i tshig don phyin ci ma log
NK120(e)001:182: par rtogs pa'i blo grosa phun sum tshogs pa ni
NK120(e)001:183: bee d+aur+ya'i bum pa bazanga po raba tu dag pa
NK120(e)001:184: drang srong gi lag tu thogs pa dang chos mtshungs
NK120(e)001:185: sbyar nas / ma rtogs log rtogs sogs kyi skyon
NK120(e)001:186: med pas legas bashada sdom pa gsuma gyi bstan bcos
NK120(e)001:187: gang zhig bum pa de'i nang du yod pa grib
NK120(e)001:188: sogs nad kun sel ba'i bduda rtsi'i chu rgyun dang
NK120(e)001:189: 'dra ba 'di nyid sbyin par bya ba yin gyi
NK120(e)001:190: sbyar nas / / thar pa mchog gi go 'phang
NK120(e)001:191: thob pa'i lam tshang la ma nor bar sdom pa
NK120(e)001:192: gsum gyi nyams len dona du gnyer ba'i skal bzang
NK120(e)001:194: thos bsam la sogs pas gtan la phab nas don gyi bcud myong bar gyis shiga ces bskul ba'o //
NK120(e)001:195: 'dis bstan bcos kyi dgos sogs chos bzhi yang legs par bstan pa yin te /
NK120(e)001:196: sdom pa gsum ni brjod bya /
NK120(e)001:197: rjod byed kyi legs bshad 'di las brjod bya'i don
NK120(e)001:198: legs par rtogs te thar pa'i lam la zhugs pa
NK120(e)001:199: ni dgos pa / zhugs pa mthar phyin nas byang chub thob pa ni nying dgos /
NK120(e)001:200: de dag kyang gcig la brten nas gcig 'byung bas 'brel ba can du grub pa ni 'brel ba'o //
NK120(e)001:201: gnyis pa bar du dge ba gzhung gi don la /
NK120(e)001:202: bshad gzhi rim par phye ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan /
NK120(e)001:203: sdom gsum so so'i rang bzhin dang bslab bya zhib tu ston pa'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad /
NK120(e)001:204: de gsum gang zag gcig gi rgyud la 'gal med
NK120(e)001:205: du nyams su len tshul gyis mtha' dpyad pa'i sgo
NK120(e)001:207: spyi'i sa bcad gsum la nang gses le'u lnga ru yod pa las /
NK120(e)001:208: le'u dang po bshad gzhi rim par phye ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:209: sbyang gzhi khams dang bral 'bras mthar thug gi 'bras bu ngos bzung ba /
NK120(e)001:210: thob byed lam gyi dbye ba spyir bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:211: theg pa thams cad kyi lam gyi gnad sdom pa
NK120(e)001:212: gsum gyi nyams len du 'dus pa'i 'brel gyis khog
NK120(e)001:213: dbub pa'o // dang po sbyang gzhi khams dang bral
NK120(e)001:214: 'bras mthar thug gi 'bras bu ngos bzung ba ni
NK120(e)001:215: dbub pa'o // / rdzogs pa chen po ye shes spyi yi gzugs //
NK120(e)001:216: yongs su dag sku rdo rje 'chang chen po //
NK120(e)001:217: 'bras bu'i mthar thug sangs rgyas nyag gcig de //
NK120(e)001:219: spyi rdzogs pa chen po la gsum du dbye na /
NK120(e)001:220: gzhi rdzogs pa chen po ni sems can gyi khams
NK120(e)001:221: na bde gshegs snying po'i ngo bor bzhugs pa de
NK120(e)001:222: yin la / lam rdzogs pa chen po ni de'i
NK120(e)001:223: steng gi glo bur sgrib gnyis kyi bag chags sbyong
NK120(e)001:224: byed kyi lam theg pa thams cad kyi mthar thug
NK120(e)001:225: yin la / pa de yin / 'bras bu rdzogs
NK120(e)001:226: pa chen po ni sgrib pa thams cad dang bral
NK120(e)001:227: ba nang gsal gzhon nu bum pa'i sku'i bdag nyid
NK120(e)001:228: sku dang ye shes bla na med pa de yin
NK120(e)001:229: yin la / pa de yin / no // de'ang
NK120(e)001:230: sbyang gzhi ni bde gshegs snying po yin cing de
NK120(e)001:231: la bstan bcos rnams su rigs zhes grags pa la
NK120(e)001:232: grub matha'i dbang gis 'dod tshul mi 'dra ba yod
NK120(e)001:233: yin la / pa de yin / no // de
NK120(e)001:234: / nyan thos bye brag smra bas srid pa dang
NK120(e)001:235: srid pa'i yo byad la ma chags pa'i sems byung
NK120(e)001:236: chog shes pa la 'phags pa'i rigs su 'dod de
NK120(e)001:237: yin la / pa de yin / no // de
NK120(e)001:238: / / ma chags pa de las zag med kyi
NK120(e)001:240: de'i don yang srid pa ni phung po lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:241: srid pa'i yo byad ni chos gos sogs te /
NK120(e)001:245: gnas mal ngan ngon tsam gyis chog shes pa 'phags pa'i rigs dang /
NK120(e)001:246: spong ba dang sgom pa la dga' ba 'phags pa'i
NK120(e)001:247: rigs te bzhir gsungs pa'i de'i dang po gsum ni
NK120(e)001:248: srid pa'i yo byad kyi gnyen po dang /
NK120(e)001:249: phyi ma ni srid pa'i gnyen pa'o //
NK120(e)001:250: de la spong ba ni 'gog bden dang /
NK120(e)001:251: sgom pa ni lam bden no //
NK120(e)001:252: mdo sde pas sems kyi sa bon zag med kyi
NK120(e)001:253: ye shes 'byung rung gi nus pa la 'dod cing
NK120(e)001:254: / sems tsam pas thog med nas sems rgyud la
NK120(e)001:255: gnas pa'i zag med kyi chos bskyed par byed pa'i
NK120(e)001:256: nus pa chos nyid kyis thob pa la 'dod de
NK120(e)001:258: de la rang bzhin gyi gnas pa'i rigs ni skye mched drug gis khyad par du byed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:259: de ni gcig nas gcig tu brgyud de 'ong la
NK120(e)001:260: thog ma med pa'i dus can chos nyid kyis thob
NK120(e)001:262: de thams cad 'dus byas te dngos por smra ba'i lugs so //
NK120(e)001:264: dri bcas de bzhin nyid la 'dod pa phal cher
NK120(e)001:265: mthun kyang ngos 'dzin tshul cung zad mi 'dra ba
NK120(e)001:266: mang mod / 'dir theg chen thun mong ma yin pa'i lugs ltar na /
NK120(e)001:267: sems nyid ye nas rnam par dag pa 'dus ma
NK120(e)001:268: byas pa'i ye shes stong gsal 'pho 'gyur med par
NK120(e)001:269: gnas pa ni bde gshegs snying po ste /
NK120(e)001:271: dag pa dwangs pa 'od gsal ba //
NK120(e)001:273: bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po ste //
NK120(e)001:274: ye nas gnas pa'i chos nyid do //
NK120(e)001:276: sems can rnams la bde gshegs snying po de tshul ji ltar yod ce na /
NK120(e)001:277: stong gsal 'gag med 'dus ma byas pa'i rang bzhin du gnas te /
NK120(e)001:278: dpe na 'o ma la mar gyis khyab pa'am /
NK120(e)001:279: til la snum gyis khyab pa ltar gnas pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:281: rdzogs sangs sku ni 'phro phyir dang //
NK120(e)001:282: de bzhin nyid dbyer med phyir dang //
NK120(e)001:283: rigs yod phyir na lus can kun //
NK120(e)001:284: rtag tu sangs rgyas snying po can //
NK120(e)001:285: zhes rgyu mtshan gsum gyis sems can thams cad bde gshegs snying po can du bstan nas /
NK120(e)001:286: ngo bo rgyu 'bras las ldan 'jug pa dang //
NK120(e)001:287: gnas skabs de bzhin kun tu 'gro ba dang //
NK120(e)001:288: rtag tu mi 'gyur yon tan dbyer med pa'i //
NK120(e)001:289: don dam dbyings kyi dgongs don yin zhes bya //
NK120(e)001:290: zhes rnam gzhag rnam pa bcus de'i don gtan la phab cing /
NK120(e)001:291: sangs rgyas pad ngan sbrang rtsi sbrang ma la //
NK120(e)001:292: sbun la snying po mi gtsang nang na gser //
NK120(e)001:293: sa la gter dang smyug sogs 'bras chung dang //
NK120(e)001:294: gos hrul nang na rgyal ba'i sku dang ni //
NK120(e)001:295: bud med ngan ma'i lto na mi bdag dang //
NK120(e)001:296: sa la rin chen gser yod ji lta bar //
NK120(e)001:297: glo bur nyon mongs dri mas bsgribs pa yi //
NK120(e)001:298: de bzhin sems can rnams la khams 'di gnas //
NK120(e)001:299: zhes dri mas bsgribs tshul dpe dgu'i sgo nas khyad par bstan pa ltar la /
NK120(e)001:300: de nyid gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i skabs su
NK120(e)001:301: gzhi rgyud rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor
NK120(e)001:302: zhes grags te / mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen
NK120(e)001:303: po dang rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong pa nyid
NK120(e)001:304: dbyer mi phyed pa'i sems kyi chos nyid la bshad
NK120(e)001:305: zhes grags te / cing / khyad par du a
NK120(e)001:306: ti yo gas sems kyi chos nyid rig pa stong
NK120(e)001:307: gsal gyi ngo bo la sku dang ye shes kyi
NK120(e)001:308: chos thams cad nyi ma dang 'od zer bzhin 'du
NK120(e)001:309: 'bral med par yongs su rdzogs pas na rdzogas pa
NK120(e)001:310: chen po zhes gsungs pa ste /
NK120(e)001:312: gzhir gnas rig pa ngo bo rang bzhin dang //
NK120(e)001:313: thugs rje gsum ldan rgyal ba'i snying po la //
NK120(e)001:314: sku gsum rang chas bzhugs par bshad pa yin //
NK120(e)001:317: lus can snying la gang gnas pa //
NK120(e)001:318: rang byung zag med ye shes gzugs //
NK120(e)001:321: lus la ye shes chen po gnas //
NK120(e)001:324: rgyal ba'i 'khor lo bar par rnam thar gsum //
NK120(e)001:325: bstan bya'i ngo bo so sor rang rig nyid //
NK120(e)001:326: sems can khams la bde gshegs snying po ru //
NK120(e)001:327: rang bzhin bzhugs la rdzogs pa chen por grags //
NK120(e)001:329: ye shes de nyid kyang ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje ste gzhir gnas kyi ye shes gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:330: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes sogs mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:331: ji lta ji snyed mkhyen pa zhes yul la 'jug pa'i ye shes gnyis te /
NK120(e)001:332: gzhi 'bras kyi ye shes thams cad gzhan ma yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:333: 'khor ba'i chos rnams thams cad kyang med snang glo bur ba yin la /
NK120(e)001:334: chos nyid de las gzhan brjod du med pas na
NK120(e)001:335: srid zhi kun la khyab pa'i phyir ye shesa spyi
NK120(e)001:337: de lta bu sbyang gzhi chos nyid bde gshegs snying po de nyid /
NK120(e)001:338: sbyang bya glo bur gyi dri ma 'khor ba'i chos su snang ba thams cad /
NK120(e)001:339: sbyong byed sdom pa gsum gyi lam gyi snying po rig pa 'dzin pa sngags kyi lam zab mos /
NK120(e)001:340: med snang glo bur ba'i dri ma sgrib gnyis bag
NK120(e)001:341: chags dang bcas pa yongas su sbyangs shing dag ste
NK120(e)001:342: / sbyang 'bras don gnyis lhun gyis grub pa sku
NK120(e)001:343: lnga ye shes lnga'i ngo bor 'tshang rgya bas na
NK120(e)001:344: kun tu bzang po'am rdo rje 'achanga chena po zhes
NK120(e)001:345: sogs su grags te theg pa thams cad kyi 'brasa
NK120(e)001:346: bu'i mathara thug pa sangsa rgyas nyag ma gciga pu
NK120(e)001:347: / de yin no // de la sku lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:348: dbyings spros bral gyi klong du rig pa'i ye shes rang grol ba zung 'jug chos kyi sku /
NK120(e)001:349: de las ma g.yos bzhin du sa bcu'i sems dpa'
NK120(e)001:350: la mtshan dpe'i gzugs brnyan rnam par snang ba longs
NK120(e)001:352: so skyes rnams la mos pa dang mthun par sangs
NK120(e)001:353: rgyas kyi gzugs brnyan ci rigs su snang ba sprul
NK120(e)001:354: pa'i sku dang / sku gsum gyi snang cha ma
NK120(e)001:355: 'dres pa'i cha nas mngon par byang chub pa'i sku
NK120(e)001:356: pa'i sku dang / / sku gsum dbyer mi phyed pa'i cha nas rdo rje'i sku ste sku lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:357: de la brten pa'i ye shes lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:358: chos thams cad ci yang mi dmigs pa chos dbyings ye shes /
NK120(e)001:359: gsal la rtog pa med pa me long ye shes /
NK120(e)001:360: 'khor 'das kyi mtha' la mi gnas pa mnyam nyid ye shes /
NK120(e)001:361: chos thams cad ma 'dres mngon sum sa ler mkhyen pa sor rtog ye shes /
NK120(e)001:362: 'gro don thogs pa med pa'i phrin las la 'jug pa bya grub ye shes so //
NK120(e)001:363: chos dbyings ye shes ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes dang /
NK120(e)001:364: phyi ma bzhi ji snyed pa gzigs pa'i ye shes su 'du bas gnyis so //
NK120(e)001:365: de thams cad kyang spangs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:367: sems te chen po gsum gyi rang bzhin can te /
NK120(e)001:369: sems can kun mchog nyid sems dang //
NK120(e)001:370: spongs dang rtogs dang gsum po la //
NK120(e)001:371: chen po gsum gyi rang byung gi //
NK120(e)001:372: ched du bya ba 'di shes bya //
NK120(e)001:374: des na bla med byang chub don du gnyer ba
NK120(e)001:375: rnams kyi bsam pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i 'bras bu'i
NK120(e)001:376: mthar thug tu nges pa ni sangs rgyas nyag gcig
NK120(e)001:377: pu yin la / de ni 'chad par 'gyur ba
NK120(e)001:378: gsang sngags bla med kyi lam kho nas thob dgos
NK120(e)001:379: pu yin la / pa yin no // gnyis pa
NK120(e)001:380: thob byed lam gyi dbye ba spyir bshad pa la
NK120(e)001:381: pu yin la / pa yin no // gsum / bgrod pa gcig pu'i lam mdor bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:382: lam stegs kyi theg pa'i dbye bsdu bye brag tu bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:383: so byang gnyis sngags sdom gyi yan lag tu 'gyur tshul bstan pas gnad bsdu ba'o //
NK120(e)001:384: dang po bgrod pa gcig pu'i lam mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:385: zab rgyas chos kyi sgo 'phar bgrang yas kyang //
NK120(e)001:386: gsang chen smin grol lam mchog ma bsten par //
NK120(e)001:387: thob pa min zhes rdzogs sangs rgyas des gsungs //
NK120(e)001:389: zaba pa ji lta ba don dam stong pa nyid ston pa dang /
NK120(e)001:390: rgyas pa ji snyed pa kun rdzob kyi phyogs rnams
NK120(e)001:391: ston pa'i chosa kyi sgo 'aphara bgranga mtha' yasa pa
NK120(e)001:392: zhig gsungs yod kyang gasnga chen rdo rje theg pa'i
NK120(e)001:394: grola byed bskyed rdzogs kyi lam mchoga gnyis la ma
NK120(e)001:395: brten para lam 'og ma rnams kyis nam yang thob
NK120(e)001:396: pa mina te / ci'i phyir na 'khor bar 'ching
NK120(e)001:397: byed kyi bag chags shin tu phra ba dkar dmar
NK120(e)001:398: rlung gsum gyis bskyed pa'i snang gsum 'pho ba'i sgrib
NK120(e)001:399: pa de nyid sbyong byed kyi thabs dngos ni lam
NK120(e)001:400: de dag tu ma bstan pa'i phyir te /
NK120(e)001:401: klu byang gi las mtha' rnam 'byed las /
NK120(e)001:402: mgo dang rkang lag sogs byin kyang //
NK120(e)001:403: snang ba rnam par ma dag phyir //
NK120(e)001:406: sngags bla med la brten nas 'thob pa'i tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:408: bskal pa zhing gi rdul snyed du //
NK120(e)001:409: shin tu sbyangs la rab gnas shing //
NK120(e)001:410: dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK120(e)001:412: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu na //
NK120(e)001:413: 'das dang da ltar byung ba yi //
NK120(e)001:414: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NK120(e)001:415: bsten nas sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs //
NK120(e)001:416: zhesa shes bya thams cad la chags thogs med pa'i
NK120(e)001:417: ye shes mnga' zhing bden pa nyag gcig tu smra
NK120(e)001:418: ba rdzogas pa'i sangsa rgyas desa legs par yongs su
NK120(e)001:419: gsungas so // gnyis pa lam stegs kyi theg pa'i dbye bsdu bye brag tu bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:420: dbye gzhi theg pa'i mtshan nyid spyir bshad //
NK120(e)001:421: dbye chos rnam grol gyi lam thams cad theg dgur 'du tshul bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:422: dang po dbye gzhi theg pa'i mtshan nyid spyir bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:423: ji srid sems kyi 'jug pa ma zad bar //
NK120(e)001:424: bsam yas theg pa'i bgrang mthar thug pa med //
NK120(e)001:425: bgrod gcig lam la dkri ba'i ngal stegs te //
NK120(e)001:426: rang rang rjes mthun 'bras bu bla dang bcas //
NK120(e)001:427: thob kyang theg pa so so'i nges 'byung las //
NK120(e)001:428: theg gcig lam la ma zhugs 'bras thob ci //
NK120(e)001:430: ji srid gdul bya'i sems dang semas byung phra rags
NK120(e)001:431: kyi rgyun gcig nas gcig tu 'juga pa chos kyi
NK120(e)001:432: dbyings su ma zada kyi bar du de 'dul byed
NK120(e)001:433: kyi gnyen po bsam gyis mi khyab cing mtha' yasa
NK120(e)001:434: pa theg pa'i rnam grangas 'di tsam mo zhes brjod
NK120(e)001:435: pa'i mathara thuga pa med la /
NK120(e)001:436: gang tshe sems kyi 'jug pa zad pa'i dus na 'gro ba'ang med la /
NK120(e)001:439: ji srid sems ni 'jug pa'i bar //
NK120(e)001:440: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK120(e)001:441: sems ni nam zhig gyur pa na //
NK120(e)001:442: theg pa med cing 'gro ba'ang med //
NK120(e)001:444: de lta na theg pa'i rnam grangs 'og ma rnams
NK120(e)001:445: ni re zhig de dang de'i gdul bya rnams drang
NK120(e)001:446: ba'i thabs su bstan pa yin la /
NK120(e)001:447: mthar de dag thams cad kyang sangs rgyas rnams kyi
NK120(e)001:448: bgroda pa gciga pu'i lam gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK120(e)001:449: pa bla na med pa la dkri ba'i ngala stegsa
NK120(e)001:450: tsam yin te / ci'i phyir na lam stegs kyi
NK120(e)001:451: theg pa de rnams kyis ranga ranga gi lugs dang
NK120(e)001:452: rjesa su mthuna pa'i 'brasa bu re thob mod kyi
NK120(e)001:453: tsam yin te / / da dung bla ste gong du bgrod bya dang bacasa pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:455: sa rnams khyad par bkod pa yang //
NK120(e)001:456: gsang ba snying por 'gro ba'i lam //
NK120(e)001:458: des na mtshan nyid sde gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:459: phyi rgyud sde gsum gyi theg pa rnams kyis rang
NK120(e)001:460: rang gi lam gyi mi mthun phyogs 'khor dang bcas
NK120(e)001:461: pa spangs pa'i 'bras bu re thob kyang thega pa
NK120(e)001:462: so so'i ngesa par 'byung ba'i myang 'das tsam lasa
NK120(e)001:463: / bla na med pa'i thega pa gciga pu gsang
NK120(e)001:464: sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lam la ma zhugsa par
NK120(e)001:465: mthar thug gi 'brasa bu byang chub chen po thoba
NK120(e)001:466: pa ci zhig yod de med do //
NK120(e)001:467: de ltar yang mtshan brjod las /
NK120(e)001:468: theg pa gsum gyi nges 'byung la //
NK120(e)001:469: theg pa gcig gi 'bras bur gnas //
NK120(e)001:471: gnyis pa dbye chos rnam grol gyi lam thams cad
NK120(e)001:472: theg dgur 'du tshul bye brag tu bshad pa ni
NK120(e)001:473: / 'dir ni rdzogs pa chen po'i ring lugs ltar //
NK120(e)001:474: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' la //
NK120(e)001:475: mtshan nyid rgyu yi theg pa gsum zhes gsungs //
NK120(e)001:476: kri ya u pa yo ga phyi rgyud gsum //
NK120(e)001:477: bla med pha rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang //
NK120(e)001:478: ma rgyud a nu yo gar grags pa dang //
NK120(e)001:479: gnyis med rgyud sde a ti yo ga la //
NK120(e)001:480: nang rgyud gsum zhes theg pa rim dgur bsdu //
NK120(e)001:482: bstan bcos 'dira ni thun mong ma yin pa gsang
NK120(e)001:483: sngags snga 'gyur rdzogas pa chena po'i ringa lugas ltar
NK120(e)001:484: theg pa rim dgur rnam par bzhag pa yin te
NK120(e)001:486: don dam nges pa'i theg pa ni //
NK120(e)001:487: gsum du nges par snang ba ste //
NK120(e)001:489: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa'o //
NK120(e)001:491: de'ang rang gis yongs 'dzin las nyan cing thos pa'i don gzhan la sgrogs pas na nyan thosa dang /
NK120(e)001:492: srid pa tha ma pa'i ched gzhan la ma bsten
NK120(e)001:493: par rang nyid srid pa las rgyal ba'i 'bras bu
NK120(e)001:494: mngon du byed pas na ranga rgyal dang /
NK120(e)001:495: rdzogs pa'i byang chub bsgrub pa'i ched du gzhan don
NK120(e)001:496: spyod pa la sems mi zhum par dpa' bas na
NK120(e)001:498: de dag gi nyams su blang bya'i theg pa gsum
NK120(e)001:499: la 'bras bur sbyor pa'i lam mtshon pas matshana nyid
NK120(e)001:500: dang / rang 'bras thob pa'i dngos rgyu dang /
NK120(e)001:501: mthar 'bras byang chub chen po thob pa'i brgyud rgyu
NK120(e)001:502: tsam las 'bras bu lam du byed pa ma yin
NK120(e)001:503: pas na rgyu yi thega pa gsuma zhesa gsungas la
NK120(e)001:504: / kri ya ste phyi'i bya ba gtso bor ston pas na bya ba'i rgyud dang /
NK120(e)001:505: u pa ste lta spyod cha mnyam par spyod pas na spyod pa'i rgyud dang /
NK120(e)001:506: yo ga ste nang gi sgom pa gtso bor ston pas na rnal 'byor gyi rgyud de /
NK120(e)001:507: de gsum po mtshan nyid theg pa dang tshul 'dra
NK120(e)001:508: zhing dngos grub gzhan nas 'tshol bas phyi rgyud gsuma
NK120(e)001:509: zhes grags / phyi rgyud las khyad par 'phags tshul
NK120(e)001:510: du ma yod kyang mdor bsdu na lta sgom spyod
NK120(e)001:511: gsum thun mong ma yin pa'i dbang gis bla na
NK120(e)001:513: dbye na thabs bskyed pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston
NK120(e)001:514: pa pha rgyud la ma h+aa yo ga ste rnal
NK120(e)001:515: 'byor chen po zhes bshad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:516: shes rab rdzogs pa'i rim pa gtso bor ston pa
NK120(e)001:517: ma rgyud la a nu yo ga ste rjes su
NK120(e)001:518: rnal 'byor zhes bya bar gragas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:519: zung 'jug 'od gsal gyi rim pa gtso bor ston
NK120(e)001:520: pa gnyis su med pa'i rgyud sde la a ti
NK120(e)001:521: yo ga ste thig le'i rnal 'byor zhes gsungs te
NK120(e)001:522: / de gsum la 'khor 'das dag mnyam du rtogs
NK120(e)001:523: shing dngos grub gzhan nas mi 'tshol bas na nanga
NK120(e)001:525: des na rnam grol gyi lam thams cad thega pa rima pa dgura bsdu ba yin no //
NK120(e)001:526: 'di'i zhar la theg pa rim dgu so so'i rnam
NK120(e)001:527: gzhag go don cung zad tsam spros te 'chad na
NK120(e)001:530: thog mar mtshan nyid rgyu'i theg pa'am kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa la gsum las /
NK120(e)001:532: theg pa'i 'jug sgo so thar rigs bdun gang rung gi sdom pa blangs nas ma nyams par bsrung /
NK120(e)001:534: gang zag gi bdag rang bzhin med par rtogs kyang
NK120(e)001:535: chos bdag gzung ba rdul phran cha med dang shes
NK120(e)001:536: pa skad cig cha med don dam bden par lta
NK120(e)001:537: ba ste / sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK120(e)001:538: gnyis med ma rtogs thams cad la //
NK120(e)001:539: bden bzhi dngos por yod lta zhing //
NK120(e)001:540: spangs dang mi spangs byed gyur na //
NK120(e)001:541: 'di ni nyan thos pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:543: de la'ang bye mdo gnyis te /
NK120(e)001:544: ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim las /
NK120(e)001:545: chos tsam lta ba'i nyan thos pa //
NK120(e)001:546: mdo sde pa dang bye brag gnyis //
NK120(e)001:547: phyi rol rdul la rtsod byed cing //
NK120(e)001:548: shes pa skad cig snang byed mthun //
NK120(e)001:550: bye brag smra bas rags pa kun rdzob kyi bden
NK120(e)001:551: pa 'di ne'u sing ltar tshogs pa gcig tu snang
NK120(e)001:552: yang / don dam par rdul phra rab bar dang bcas pa cha ldan sil bur 'dod /
NK120(e)001:553: mdo sde pas rdul phra rab 'byar yang ma 'byar /
NK120(e)001:554: bar yang med par 'bru'i phung po ltar 'dod pa nyid do //
NK120(e)001:556: 'dod chags kyi gnyen por mi sdug pa sgom pa
NK120(e)001:557: sogs zhi gnas kyi sems las rung du bsgrubs nas
NK120(e)001:558: / lhag mthong bden bzhi mi rtag bcu drug sgom pa ste /
NK120(e)001:559: de yang sdug bsngal gyi bden pa nad lta bu /
NK120(e)001:560: kun 'byung nad de'i rgyu lta bu /
NK120(e)001:561: lam bden nad kyi gnyen po sman lta bu /
NK120(e)001:562: 'gog bden nad las grol ba lta bur rtogs pas /
NK120(e)001:563: des na sdug bsngal shes bya /
NK120(e)001:566: 'gog pa mngon du thob bya dang /
NK120(e)001:567: de re re la'ang bzhi bzhir phye bas bden 'byung bcu drug rnams sgom /
NK120(e)001:569: rang nyid zhi bde'i bsam pas so sor thar pa
NK120(e)001:570: rigs bdun gang la zhugs pa'i bslab bya lam du
NK120(e)001:571: khyer zhing / sbyangs pa'i yon tan la gnas /
NK120(e)001:572: nyon mongs pa dgra dang tsher ma ltar spang /
NK120(e)001:573: dge bcu sman dang zas ltar len cing /
NK120(e)001:575: de yang srog gcod pa la btsan dug /
NK120(e)001:578: gos la rma dkris lta bu'i chos gos gsum dang mi 'bral ba /
NK120(e)001:580: nyon mongs pa la dug sbrul reg pas phung ba /
NK120(e)001:582: kha zas la bu sha za ba sred pa mi bya /
NK120(e)001:584: rnyed pa kur la rgya dang rnyi 'ching bar dogs te byol /
NK120(e)001:586: bla ma dkon mchog la nor bu rin po che mchod cing gus pas bsten /
NK120(e)001:588: chos la lam bzang po lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK120(e)001:590: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gser lta bu'i 'du shes /
NK120(e)001:591: dkon zhing bzang la rnyed pa don ldan /
NK120(e)001:592: tshul khrims la rgyan lta bu'i gces spras kyis bsrung bar bya /
NK120(e)001:594: chos nyid mngon du gyur pa la mun khung du
NK120(e)001:595: sgron me ting nge 'dzin la brtson pa mi 'dor
NK120(e)001:596: / btegs pa lta bu'i 'du shes dang mi 'bral bar byed pa'o //
NK120(e)001:600: phyir mi 'ong ba ste gnas skabs kyi 'bras bu gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:601: mthar thug gi 'bras bu lhag bcas lhag med kyi dgra bcom pa thob /
NK120(e)001:602: 'bras bu bzhi po re re la'ang bzhugs gnas gnyis gnyis phye bas brgyad de /
NK120(e)001:603: dbye gzhi la ltos nas skyes bu bzung bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:604: dbye chos la ltos nas gang zag ya brgyad ces bya'o //
NK120(e)001:606: theg pa'i 'jug sgo nyan thos dang 'dra la /
NK120(e)001:609: gzung don rtogs pa spong phyir dang //
NK120(e)001:610: 'dzin pa mi spong phyir du ni //
NK120(e)001:611: rten gyi bse ru lta bu'i lam //
NK120(e)001:612: yang dag bsdus par shes par bya //
NK120(e)001:614: gang zag gi bdag med rtogs pa nyan thos dang 'dra la /
NK120(e)001:615: de'i steng du chos kyi bdag gi gzung cha rdul phra rab kyang rang bzhin med par rtogs kyang /
NK120(e)001:616: da dung 'dzin sems skad cig ma don dam du
NK120(e)001:618: pas na bdag med phyed dang gnyis rtogs pa zhes
NK120(e)001:619: bya ste / ska ba dpal brtsegs kyi lta rim las /
NK120(e)001:620: de bzhin rang rgyal theg pa yang //
NK120(e)001:621: phyi rol bcu gnyis sgyu ma tsam //
NK120(e)001:622: rdul kyang phyogs chas ma grub 'phags //
NK120(e)001:623: shes pa skad cig rjes su mthun //
NK120(e)001:626: de yang phyi nang gi rtel 'brel gnyis te /
NK120(e)001:627: phyi'i rten 'brel 'bras bu las shes te /
NK120(e)001:628: 'bras bu de ci las byung brtags pas me tog las byung /
NK120(e)001:632: de sa bon las byung ste rgyu dang 'brel ba drug /
NK120(e)001:639: dus dbyar dgun ston dpyid bzhis bsgyur nas byung bar shes te phyi'i rten 'brel lo //
NK120(e)001:640: nang gi rten 'brel dur khrod du phyin nas keng
NK120(e)001:641: rus kyi phung po la brtags pas shi ba las
NK120(e)001:642: byung bar shes / de na ba las /
NK120(e)001:654: de gang las byung brtags pas ma rnyed de stong par rtogs pas stong nyid du shes /
NK120(e)001:655: rgyu snga ma la brten nas phyi ma 'byung ba
NK120(e)001:656: la ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar brtags pas
NK120(e)001:658: de ltar bden bzhi bcu drug gi steng du rten
NK120(e)001:659: 'brel lugs 'byung bcu gnyis bkag nas lugs ldog stong
NK120(e)001:660: pa bcu gnyis khrigs chags su sgrom /
NK120(e)001:664: dbang rnon bse ru lta bu gcig pur bzhugs pa
NK120(e)001:665: ni nyan thos kyi sde snod la dmigs nas bskal
NK120(e)001:667: mthar sangs rgyas mi bzhugs pa'i zhing du stan thog
NK120(e)001:668: gcig tu sbyor lam drod nas mi slob lam gyi
NK120(e)001:669: bar du mngon du byas te rang rgyal dgra bcom
NK120(e)001:671: dbyig gnyen zhabs kyi mngon pa mdzod las /
NK120(e)001:672: ston dang bse ru byang chub pa //
NK120(e)001:673: bsam gtan mtha' rten gcig la kun //
NK120(e)001:674: de yi sngon du thar cha mthun //
NK120(e)001:676: dbang rtul ne tso lta bu khyur bzhugs pa tshogs
NK120(e)001:677: spyod che chung gnyis ni rim par lam bzhi'am gsum
NK120(e)001:678: mngon du mdzad de 'bras bu mngon du rtogs pa
NK120(e)001:680: phyi nang rten 'brel sgyu ma mig yor tshul //
NK120(e)001:681: dngos po'i gzugs la thogs med rab tu 'jug /
NK120(e)001:682: dge bshes mi slob rang gi rig pas rtogs /
NK120(e)001:683: byang chub sar bgrod yid bzhin bde ba mchog /
NK120(e)001:686: theg pa'i 'jug sgo smon pa dang 'jug pa'i bdag
NK120(e)001:687: nyid can gyi byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i
NK120(e)001:688: sdom pa blang / lta ba ni /
NK120(e)001:689: sems tsam pas gzung ba rang bzhin med pa dang /
NK120(e)001:690: der 'dzin gyi shes pa'ang stong par rtogs kyang rang
NK120(e)001:691: gsal gyi shes pa ngo bos mi stong par 'dod
NK120(e)001:692: pas rang lugs la bdag med gnyis rtogs par 'dod
NK120(e)001:693: kyang / dbu ma pas gzhal na chos kyi bdag med phra ba ma rtogs la /
NK120(e)001:694: dbu ma pas ni kun rdzob tu chos thams cad chu zla ltar snang ba /
NK120(e)001:695: don dam par spros pa thams cad yongs su zhi
NK120(e)001:696: ba'i tshul du bdag gnyis kyis stong pa mtha' bral
NK120(e)001:697: dbu ma chen por rtogs pa ste /
NK120(e)001:698: sangs rgyas gsang ba'i lam rim las /
NK120(e)001:699: mnyam pa'i don nyid mi shes shing //
NK120(e)001:700: kun rdzob don dam gnyis 'byed la //
NK120(e)001:701: chos dang gang zag bdag med pa //
NK120(e)001:702: 'di ni byang chub sems dpa' yin //
NK120(e)001:705: gzhan don kho nar yongs su dmigs pa'i snying rje chen po sgom pa kun rdzob byang sems dang /
NK120(e)001:706: de dag rnam pa ma 'gag par cing yang snang la /
NK120(e)001:707: don la gang du'ang ma dmigs pas spros pa thams
NK120(e)001:708: cad dang bral ba'i ngang du bzhag pa ni don
NK120(e)001:709: dam byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:710: slob lam bzhir byang chub phyogs kyi chos sum cu rtsa bdun sgom /
NK120(e)001:712: bdag bas gzhan gces kyi sgo nas sems can gyi
NK120(e)001:713: don byed pa'i spyod pa pha rol tu phyin pa
NK120(e)001:714: drug dang bsdu ba'i dngos po bzhi la spyod /
NK120(e)001:716: bskal pa grangs med gsum du sa bcu lam lnga
NK120(e)001:717: rim gyis bgrod nas mi slob pa'i lam bcu gcig
NK120(e)001:718: kun tu 'od kyi sa la rang don chos kyi
NK120(e)001:719: skur grol te gzhan don gzugs sku gnyis la brten
NK120(e)001:720: nas sems can gyi don 'khor ba ma stongs kyi
NK120(e)001:723: bdag med gnyis rtogs pha rol phyin rdzogs pa'i //
NK120(e)001:724: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK120(e)001:725: sangs rgyas sar bgrod go 'phang thob pa'i lam //
NK120(e)001:726: bden pa gnyis kyis rab tu thob par 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:728: theg pa de gsum gyis kun 'byung las dang nyon
NK120(e)001:729: mongs pa'i lam las thar par 'dren par byed pas
NK120(e)001:730: na kun 'byung 'dren pa'i theg pa dang /
NK120(e)001:731: so so'i lam des mthar thug gi 'bras bu de mtshon par byed pas na mtshan nyid dang /
NK120(e)001:732: de la sbyor bar byed pa'i rgyu mtshan tsam yin pas na rgyu'i theg pa zhes kyang bya'o //
NK120(e)001:733: gnyis pa 'bras bu sngags kyi theg pa la phyi nang gnyis kyi /
NK120(e)001:734: thog mar phyi rgyud dka' thub rig byed kyi theg pa la gsum las /
NK120(e)001:735: dang po kri ya ste bya ba'i rgyud ni /
NK120(e)001:736: 'jug sgo chu dang cod pan gyi dbang mtha' rten dang bcas pas snod rung du sgrub /
NK120(e)001:737: lta ba bdag gi de kho na nyid ces rang
NK120(e)001:738: gi sems nyid stong gsal gyi ye shes yod med
NK120(e)001:739: snang stong spros pa'i mtha' thams cad dang bral bar
NK120(e)001:740: lta / sgom pa de kho na nyid bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:741: bya rgyud tsam po ba la bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa med kyang /
NK120(e)001:742: bya rgyud khyad par can la lha'i de kho na
NK120(e)001:743: nyid bdag nyid lha drug gi sgo nas bskyed de
NK120(e)001:745: bdag gi de kho na nyid lta ba'i ngang du 'jog pa stong pa'i lha /
NK120(e)001:746: de las kun rdzob zla dkyil gyi rnam par sgom pa yi ge'i lha /
NK120(e)001:747: zla ba'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra bcas bkod pa sgra'i lha /
NK120(e)001:748: de yongs su gyur pa las rigs gsum so so'i lha bsgom pa gzugs kyi lha /
NK120(e)001:749: de lha rang rang gi rigs gang yin pa de'i dam rgyas 'debs pa phyag rgya'i lha /
NK120(e)001:750: gnas skabs thams cad du lha'i ting nge 'dzin gyi
NK120(e)001:751: 'du shes dang mi 'bral ba mtshan ma'i lha ste
NK120(e)001:752: drug gi sgo nas bdag dam tshig par bskyed /
NK120(e)001:753: de'i mdun du ye shes pa spyan drangs te rje
NK120(e)001:754: khol gyi tshul du bltas nas mchod bstod sogs bya
NK120(e)001:755: ba ni lha'i de kho na nyid de /
NK120(e)001:756: stong pa yi ge sgra gzugs dang //
NK120(e)001:757: phyag rgya mtshan ma drug yin no //
NK120(e)001:759: gzhi la gzhol ba bdag mdun lhar bsgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:760: sems la gzhol ba lha'i thugs kar zla dkyil bsam pa /
NK120(e)001:761: sgra la gzhol ba zla dkyil gyi steng du sngags phreng rang sgra dang bcas pa gsal btab ste /
NK120(e)001:762: srog rtsol bsdams pa'i sbyor bas lha sngags la dmigs
NK120(e)001:763: pa rtse gcig tu bsgril te bzla ba ni bzlas
NK120(e)001:764: brjod kyi de kho na nyid de /
NK120(e)001:766: sgra dang sems dang gzhi la gzhol //
NK120(e)001:767: gsang sngags mi 'gyur gzhi la gnas //
NK120(e)001:768: yan lag ma nyams gsang sngags bzlas //
NK120(e)001:769: ngal na bdag la ngas gsos shig /
NK120(e)001:771: yang rang nyid lhar gsal ba'i thugs kar me dpung
NK120(e)001:772: gi dbus su zla ba sngags phreng bcas gsal btab
NK120(e)001:773: pa mer gnas te zhi sogs las thams cad sgrub
NK120(e)001:774: pa'i gzhi dang / de las sngags kyi rang sgra
NK120(e)001:775: dril bu'i sgra ltar grags par bsam pa ni sgrar
NK120(e)001:776: gnas te zhi gnas sgrub pa'i rten gzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:777: sngags kyi sgra de la dpyad cing gzhig na cir
NK120(e)001:778: yang ma grub pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK120(e)001:779: shes kyi ngang la mnyam par 'jog pa sgra mtha'
NK120(e)001:780: zhes lhag mthong 'char ba'i nyer len gyi rgyur gyur
NK120(e)001:781: pa ste bsam gtan gyi de kho na nyid de
NK120(e)001:783: gsang sngags mer gnas dngos grub ster //
NK120(e)001:784: sgrar gnas dngos grub ster bar dran //
NK120(e)001:785: sgra mthas thar pa ster bar byed //
NK120(e)001:788: khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i bya ba la gtso bor spyod /
NK120(e)001:790: mi tshe bdun na rigs gsum rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob pa'o //
NK120(e)001:791: gnyis pa u pa ya ste spyod rgyud ni /
NK120(e)001:792: 'jug sgo chu dang cod pan gyi steng du rdor dril ming dbang bcas bskur bas smin par byed /
NK120(e)001:795: u pa ya ni 'di lta ste //
NK120(e)001:796: lta ba yo gar lta ba la //
NK120(e)001:797: spyod pa kri yar spyad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:798: de phyir gnyis ka'i rgyud ces grags //
NK120(e)001:802: yi ge dang ni yi ge sbyar //
NK120(e)001:803: de bzhin gzhi las gzhir gyur nyid //
NK120(e)001:804: shin tu dam pa'i yid las ni //
NK120(e)001:807: bdag gnas rnal 'byor srung ba rnams sngon du 'gro bas /
NK120(e)001:808: yi ge dang po don dam byang chub sems stong pa nyid dang /
NK120(e)001:809: de'i snang cha kun rdzob byang sems zla dkyil bsgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:810: yi ge gnyis pa de'i steng du bzla bya'i sngags rang sgra bcas bkod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:811: gzhi dang po de dag yongs su gyur pa las
NK120(e)001:812: bdag nyid lhar bskyed pa la sngags rgya la sogs
NK120(e)001:813: pas byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:814: gzhi gnyis pa mdun du ye shes pa bskyed pa
NK120(e)001:815: spun nam grogs po'i tshul du bltas te thugs kar
NK120(e)001:816: zla dkyil la sngags phreng bkod nas srog bsdams te
NK120(e)001:817: rtse gcig pa'i sbyor bas ting nge 'dzin brtan par
NK120(e)001:818: byed pa rnams mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor /
NK120(e)001:819: 'jug pa'i sems chos thams cad rnam par dpyad pas skye med du rtogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:820: gnas pa'i sems rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes mngon du gyur pa dang /
NK120(e)001:821: ldang ba'i sems de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la snying rje chen pos lhag par 'jug pa'o //
NK120(e)001:822: de ltar 'jug gnas ldang gsum gyis khyad par du
NK120(e)001:823: byas pa'i don dam byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa
NK120(e)001:825: des na thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i las rab 'byams sgrub par byed pa'o //
NK120(e)001:827: bya rgyud ltar gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i kun spyod grogs dang ldan par spyod //
NK120(e)001:829: mi tshe lnga nas rigs bzhi rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sa thob ste /
NK120(e)001:830: rigs bzhi ni las rigs rin chen rigs la bsdus pa'o //
NK120(e)001:831: gsum pa yo ga ste rnal 'byor rgyud ni /
NK120(e)001:832: 'jug sgo rig pa'i dbang lnga'i steng du rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang drug thob par byas /
NK120(e)001:835: yo ga'i theg par gnas 'dod pas //
NK120(e)001:836: 'og min rdo rje dbyings su blta //
NK120(e)001:838: don dam bden pa spros pa'i mtshan ma kun dang
NK120(e)001:839: bral ba rang bzhin 'od gsal stong pa nyid dang
NK120(e)001:840: / kun rdzob tu cir snang thams cad chos nyid
NK120(e)001:841: rtogs pa'i byin rlabs rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor
NK120(e)001:844: dang po'i sbyor ba sngon du song nas /
NK120(e)001:845: bdag nyid mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi'i sgo nas bskyed de /
NK120(e)001:847: mi rtog zla ba gsum rdo rje //
NK120(e)001:848: spro bsdus bsgom pa'i sku ru gsal //
NK120(e)001:849: ting 'dzin byin rlabs dbang bskur mchod //
NK120(e)001:850: mngon byang lnga dang cho 'phrul bzhi //
NK120(e)001:851: bsgom zhing mchod pa byas pa yang //
NK120(e)001:852: bsod nams ldan phyir bya ba yin //
NK120(e)001:858: sku yongs rdzogs la mngon par byang chub pa lngas bskyed la /
NK120(e)001:859: de nas 'khor gyi lha bkod pa ting nge 'dzin gyi cho 'phrul /
NK120(e)001:860: phyag rgya bzhis rgyas gdab pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i cho 'phrul /
NK120(e)001:861: rigs gang yin gyis dbang bskur ba dbang bskur ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK120(e)001:862: phyag mchod bstod pa bya ba mchod pa'i cho 'phrul ste cho 'phrul bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:864: thugs dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NK120(e)001:867: phrin las las kyi phyag rgya rnams kyis rgyas btab
NK120(e)001:868: nas ye shes pa dgug bstim byas te dam ye
NK120(e)001:869: dbyer med kyi ngang nas bzlas pa tshul bzhin du
NK120(e)001:870: byas mthar ye shes pa gshegs pa la sogs pa'i
NK120(e)001:871: sgo nas bsgrub pa mtshan bcas kyi rnal 'byor dang
NK120(e)001:872: / don dam par mtshan ma med pa'i ngo bo
NK120(e)001:873: nyid dang de'i byin rlabs lhar snang ye shes kyi
NK120(e)001:874: snang cha gnyis po gnyis su med pa'i ngang la
NK120(e)001:875: 'jog pa mtshan med kyi rnal 'byor te /
NK120(e)001:878: khrus dang gtsang sbra sogs phyi'i kun spyod kyang grogs tsam du bsten nas /
NK120(e)001:879: gtso bor lha'i rnal 'byor la gnas pas rang gzhan gyi don spyod pa ste /
NK120(e)001:881: lha yi ting 'dzin la gnas te //
NK120(e)001:882: sems can thams cad yongs mi btang //
NK120(e)001:883: rtag tu sangs rgyas yid la byed //
NK120(e)001:884: rtag tu sangs rgyas mchod pas mchod //
NK120(e)001:887: mi tshe gsum na stug po bkod pa'i sa la
NK120(e)001:888: sku gsum ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid can du 'tshang
NK120(e)001:889: rgya ba ste / kun byed las /
NK120(e)001:890: yo ga stug po bkod 'dod pas //
NK120(e)001:891: mi tshe gsum na grol bar 'dod //
NK120(e)001:893: de gsum gyis phyi dka' thub la brten nas nang gi don rig par byed pa'am /
NK120(e)001:894: yang na dka' thub dang gtsang sbra sogs bram ze
NK120(e)001:895: rig byed pa ltar brten pas na dka' thub rig
NK120(e)001:897: blang dor dang spangs gnyen thams cad phyi mtshan nyid
NK120(e)001:898: rgyu'i theg pa dang tshul 'dra bas na phyi thub
NK120(e)001:899: pa rgyud kyi theg pa zhes bya'o //
NK120(e)001:900: gsum pa dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa la gsum las /
NK120(e)001:901: dang po bla med pha rgyud bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni /
NK120(e)001:902: 'jug sgo phyi phan pa'i dbang bcu /
NK120(e)001:904: gsang ba zab mo'i dbang gsum ste dbang chog bco brgyad kyis rgyud smin par byas /
NK120(e)001:906: chos thams cad sems nyid snang stong dbyer med lhag
NK120(e)001:907: pa'i chos sku chen por lta ba don dam dang
NK120(e)001:908: / de nyid kyi rtsal snang rtog tshogs thams cad
NK120(e)001:909: sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du rang snang
NK120(e)001:911: de gnyis kyang snang stong phyogs re ba ma yin te ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:912: tha snyad du dbyer med ces brjod na'ang der 'dzin
NK120(e)001:913: bsam brjod kyi yul las 'das pa'i phyir bden pa
NK120(e)001:914: dbyer med lhag pa'i chos sku chen por gtan la
NK120(e)001:916: nang gses pha ma gnyis med gsum du phye bas /
NK120(e)001:917: gsang 'dus dang gshin rje sogs pha rgyud rnams su thabs bskyed rim gyi spros pa dang /
NK120(e)001:918: rdzogs rim gsang dbang gi nyams len rlung gtso bor
NK120(e)001:919: byed pas gsal stong rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye
NK120(e)001:920: shes / yang dag dang 'khor lo sdom pa sogs ma rgyud rnams su bskyed rim cha tsam dang /
NK120(e)001:921: rdzogs rim sher dbang gi nyams len khams byang chub
NK120(e)001:922: sems kyi thig le gtso bor byed pas bde stong
NK120(e)001:923: rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes /
NK120(e)001:924: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba sogs gnyis med kyi rgyud rnams su bskyed rdzogs zung 'jug dang /
NK120(e)001:925: rdzogs rim dbang bzhi pa'i nyams len bde gsal rnam
NK120(e)001:926: par mi rtog pa'i ye shes chen po 'od gsal
NK120(e)001:927: lhan cig skyes pa de nyid nyams su len cing
NK120(e)001:928: / spyir bskyed rim rnams sgong skyes dang mngal skyes sbyong ba'i rim pa gtso che bar sgom zhing /
NK120(e)001:929: de thams cad ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyis khog dbub ste /
NK120(e)001:930: ngo bo dag rdzogs smin gsum tshang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:931: srog sdom gzer bzhis rgyas btab ste bsgom /
NK120(e)001:933: thabs la mkhas pas zin pa'i 'khor ba'i chos ci
NK120(e)001:934: la'ang ma chags par sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga sogs
NK120(e)001:935: blang dor med par spyod pa ste /
NK120(e)001:937: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ni //
NK120(e)001:938: ta na dang ni ga na dang //
NK120(e)001:939: dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga po la //
NK120(e)001:940: thabs chen lta ba'i spyod pa spyad //
NK120(e)001:943: nye rgyud gsum gyis mtshams sbyar te rig 'dzin rnam
NK120(e)001:944: pa bzhis bsdus pa'i lam lnga mthar phyin nas tshe
NK120(e)001:945: 'adi'am bar dor sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa zung
NK120(e)001:946: 'jug rdo rje 'chang gi go 'phang thob pa ste
NK120(e)001:948: 'di ni bcom ldan bdag nyid che //
NK120(e)001:949: sku gsum mi phyed las byung ba //
NK120(e)001:950: ye shes rgya mtshos rnam par brgyan //
NK120(e)001:954: yang na lus 'di spangs ma thag /
NK120(e)001:955: brtson pa mi ldan pas kyang 'grub //
NK120(e)001:957: gnyis pa ma rgyud lung a nu yo ga la /
NK120(e)001:959: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo bcu /
NK120(e)001:960: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bcu gcig /
NK120(e)001:961: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bcu gsum /
NK120(e)001:962: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo gnyis te /
NK120(e)001:963: dbang chog sum cu so drug las yan lag gi
NK120(e)001:964: dbang brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye bas smin par
NK120(e)001:966: dbyings skye med spros pa dang bral ba yum kun
NK120(e)001:967: tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'am ye
NK120(e)001:968: ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya /
NK120(e)001:969: de nyid 'gag pa med pa yul can bde ba
NK120(e)001:970: chen po rang byung rig par 'od gsal ba ni
NK120(e)001:971: ye shes kun tu bzang po'am rang bzhin lhun gyis
NK120(e)001:973: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i sras bde
NK120(e)001:974: ba chen po rtsa ba byang chub sems kyi dkyil
NK120(e)001:977: snang srid bzang mo'i mkha' klong las //
NK120(e)001:978: ma bskyed dkyil 'khor kun tu shar //
NK120(e)001:979: shar ba nyid nas shar ba med //
NK120(e)001:980: yab yum sras bcas bde chen po //
NK120(e)001:982: de ltar gzhi chos thams cad dkyil 'khor rnam pa
NK120(e)001:983: gsum ma 'dres par rtog dpyod kyi rjes su 'jug
NK120(e)001:986: don gyi rjes su 'jug pa rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi ngang la 'jog pa dang /
NK120(e)001:987: yi ge'i rjes su 'jug pa bskyed sngags brjod pa
NK120(e)001:988: tsam gyis chu las nya ldang ba ltar rtsal snang
NK120(e)001:989: snod bcud lha'i 'khor lor gsal ba grol lam dang
NK120(e)001:990: / steng sgo 'khor lo bzhi'am drug dang /
NK120(e)001:991: 'og sgo mkha' gsang gi snyoms 'jug la brten nas
NK120(e)001:992: lhan skyes kyi ye shes bskyed par byed pa thabs
NK120(e)001:993: lam ste / de ltar thabs grol gyi lam gang
NK120(e)001:994: rung la brten nas rtogs pa'i yon tan rtsal du
NK120(e)001:996: snang sems thams cad bde ba chen po'i ye shes
NK120(e)001:997: kyi rol par shes pa'i sgo nas blang dor med
NK120(e)001:1000: dbyings dang ye shes longs spyod rdzogs //
NK120(e)001:1003: gnas skabs su tshogs lam 'dun pa sems dpa'i rnal 'byor /
NK120(e)001:1004: sbyor lam rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK120(e)001:1005: mthong lam dbugs chen 'byin pa'i rnal 'byor /
NK120(e)001:1006: sgom lam lung chen thob pa'i rnal 'byor te /
NK120(e)001:1007: slob lam bzhi mthar phyin nas /
NK120(e)001:1008: 'bras bu mi slob lam rtsal chen rdzogs pa'i rnal
NK120(e)001:1009: 'byor tshe 'di nyid la mngon du byas te 'bras
NK120(e)001:1010: chos nyer lnga dbyer med lhun gyis grub pa'i bdag
NK120(e)001:1011: gnyid bde ba chen po'i sku mngon gyur pa ste
NK120(e)001:1013: a nu yo ga'i theg pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1014: bar ma chod pa tshe gcig gis //
NK120(e)001:1015: sangs rgyas sa la nges par 'gro //
NK120(e)001:1017: gsum pa gnyis su med pa'i rgyud man ngag a ti yo ga la /
NK120(e)001:1019: dbang bzhi pa rtsal du bton pa spros bcas /
NK120(e)001:1022: rab tu spros med bzhi'i dbang thob par byas /
NK120(e)001:1024: snang srid 'khor 'das kyis bsdus pa'i chos thams cad
NK120(e)001:1025: ye nas rig pa'i ngo bor sangs rgyas pa'i rang
NK120(e)001:1028: gcig pu bzhir nges pas gtan la phab /
NK120(e)001:1030: le lo can 'bad med du grol ba tshig gsum
NK120(e)001:1031: gnad la brdeg pa'i sgo nas ka dag ye babs
NK120(e)001:1032: rang gnas sor bzhag gi ngang skyong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:1033: brtson 'grus can 'bad bcas su grol ba bzhugs stangs
NK120(e)001:1034: gsum dang gzigs stangs gsum gyi gnad gcun te lhun
NK120(e)001:1035: grub thod rgal sgron ma drug gi gseng lam la
NK120(e)001:1036: brten nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsang mdzod kyi sgo
NK120(e)001:1039: cir snang thams cad chos nyid kyi rol par shar
NK120(e)001:1040: bas dgag sgrub 'dzin zhen blang dor las 'das par
NK120(e)001:1041: spyod pa ste / nam mkha' che las /
NK120(e)001:1042: bya ba med pas las rnams zin //
NK120(e)001:1045: a ti yo ga'i spyod pa ni //
NK120(e)001:1046: lta sgom srog dang ldan pa yis //
NK120(e)001:1047: shugs las byung ba'i spyod pa ni //
NK120(e)001:1048: ji ltar smyon pa'i spyod pa bzhin //
NK120(e)001:1049: gang la'ang thogs pa med par spyod //
NK120(e)001:1055: chos nyid zad pa ste snang ba bzhi po mthar phyin cing /
NK120(e)001:1057: lhun rdzogs kun tu bzang po'i sa'am ye shes bla
NK120(e)001:1058: ma'i sa la da lta nyid nas gnas pa mthar
NK120(e)001:1059: phyin te 'ja' lus 'pho chen rdo rje'i gar gyis
NK120(e)001:1060: srid khams stongs kyi bar du 'gro ba'i don 'bad
NK120(e)001:1061: med du lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK120(e)001:1062: de gsum gyis nyon mongs pa thams cad ched du
NK120(e)001:1063: gnyer pos spangs mi dgos par chos thams cad mnyam
NK120(e)001:1064: pa chen por rig pa'i ye shes kyis dbang bsgyur
NK120(e)001:1065: te lam du byed pa'i thabs dang ldan pas na
NK120(e)001:1066: dbang bsgyur thabs kyi theg pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1067: nang sems nyid sku dang ye shes kyi rol par
NK120(e)001:1068: snang bas dngos grub gzhan las mi 'tshol bar rang
NK120(e)001:1069: byung gi ye shes su mthong bas na nang rgyud
NK120(e)001:1071: de lta na rnam grol gyi lam thams cad theg pa rim pa dgu po der 'du la /
NK120(e)001:1072: de thams cad kyang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i theg pa 'dir 'dus shing rdzogs pa yin te /
NK120(e)001:1073: kun byed rgyal po'i rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:1074: yod ni gcig las med pa la //
NK120(e)001:1075: bstan ni rnam pa gnyis su bstan //
NK120(e)001:1076: byung ni theg pa dgu ru byung //
NK120(e)001:1079: de ltar theg rim dgu po'i mtshan nyid ngos 'dzin
NK120(e)001:1080: bde ba'i slad du so so'i rnam bzhag phyogs mtshon
NK120(e)001:1081: mdo tsam zhar la brjod zin nas /
NK120(e)001:1082: da ni rtsa ba'i gzhung la 'jug ste /
NK120(e)001:1083: gong gi sa bcad gsum pa so byang gnyis sngags
NK120(e)001:1084: sdom gyi yan lag tu 'gyur tshul bstan pa la
NK120(e)001:1085: gsum / rigs can gsum la sngags kyi lam zhugs yod par sgrub pa /
NK120(e)001:1086: sngags lam la 'jug sgo mang yang 'dir spro bya min par bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:1087: skabs 'dir gtan la dbab bya'i don ngos bzung ba'o //
NK120(e)001:1088: dang po rigs can gsum la sngags kyi lam zhugs yod par sgrub pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1089: nyan rang byang sems rigs can so so la //
NK120(e)001:1090: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i lam zhugs yod do zhes //
NK120(e)001:1091: 'bum lnga'i rgyud kyi lung las gsal bar grub //
NK120(e)001:1093: spyir gdul bya rnams kyi khams sam rigs kyi dbye ba du ma zhig yod na'ang /
NK120(e)001:1097: mchog byanga chub semsa dpa'i rigas can gsum yin cing /
NK120(e)001:1098: de dag so so la gsang sngags rdo rje theg
NK120(e)001:1099: pa rig pa 'dzina pa'i lam du zhugsa pa yoda
NK120(e)001:1100: do zhesa 'buma phrag lnga pa de kho na nyid
NK120(e)001:1101: ye shes grub pa'i rgyud kyi lunga lasa gasla bar
NK120(e)001:1103: rdo yi rigs kyi bye brag zhig /
NK120(e)001:1104: bzhu bas lcags dang zangs dngul 'byung //
NK120(e)001:1105: gser 'gyur rtsi yi dngos po yis //
NK120(e)001:1106: kun kyang gser du bsgyur bar byed //
NK120(e)001:1107: de bzhin sems kyi bye brag gis //
NK120(e)001:1108: rigs can gsum gyi sdom pa yang //
NK120(e)001:1112: dper bstan pa'i rdo khams dman 'bring rab gsum po
NK120(e)001:1113: de grub mthas blo ma bsgyur ba'i rigs can gsum
NK120(e)001:1115: rdo de gsum bzhu ba las byung ba'i lcags zangs
NK120(e)001:1116: dngul gsum ni rim bzhin nyan thos rang rgyal byang
NK120(e)001:1117: sems kyi rigs can gsum so so'i lam la zhugs
NK120(e)001:1119: de gsum ka'ang gser 'gyur gyi rtsis gser du bsgyur
NK120(e)001:1120: ba ni nyan rang byang sems kyi sdom ldan sngags
NK120(e)001:1121: bla med kyi dkyil 'khor du zhugs na thams cad
NK120(e)001:1122: kyang rig pa 'dzin par 'gyur ba la khyad par
NK120(e)001:1123: med pa'i dape'o // gnyis pa sngags lam la 'jug
NK120(e)001:1124: sgo mang yang 'dir spro bya min par bstan pa
NK120(e)001:1125: med pa'i dape'o // ni / bsam pa'i dbye bas sngags la 'jug pa'i tshul //
NK120(e)001:1126: chos sgo mang yang de dag spro bya min //
NK120(e)001:1128: gdul bya rnams kyi khams dbang bsam pa'i bye brag
NK120(e)001:1129: gi dbye basa gsang sngagas rdo rje theg pa'i lam
NK120(e)001:1131: gzhi nas 'jug pa rang rang gi lam la ma
NK120(e)001:1132: zhugs par dbang rnon 'ga' zhig dang po nyid nas
NK120(e)001:1133: 'jug pa dang / lam nas 'jug pa lha mi
NK120(e)001:1134: nyan rang byang sems kri yog sde gsum ste lam
NK120(e)001:1135: bzhi po la slob bzhin pas 'jug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1136: 'bras bu nas 'jug pa lam de dag gi rang 'bras mthar phyin nas 'jug pa ste /
NK120(e)001:1137: de la sogs pa 'juga pa'i tshul gyi bye brag
NK120(e)001:1138: chos kyi sgo 'phar manga po zhig snang na yanga
NK120(e)001:1139: 'dir de dag re re nas brjod pa la dgos
NK120(e)001:1140: pa chung zhing don gyi snying po la sgrib pa'i
NK120(e)001:1141: phyir spro bar bya ba mina pas mi 'chad do
NK120(e)001:1142: // gsum pa skabs 'dir gtan la dbab bya'i don ngos bzung ba la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:1143: dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi thob tshul spyir bshad /
NK120(e)001:1144: dbang 'bring gi thob tshul bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:1145: dang po dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi thob tshul spyir bshad pa la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:1148: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1149: 'dir ni dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum las /
NK120(e)001:1151: skabs 'dira ni gdul bya la dabnga po raba dang /
NK120(e)001:1153: tha ma dang gsuma du yod pa lasa zhes so //
NK120(e)001:1154: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:1155: dbang rab sdom gsum gcig car du thob tshul /
NK120(e)001:1156: dbang 'bring sdom gsum so sor nod tshul /
NK120(e)001:1157: dbang rtul sdom gsum rim 'jug gis dkri tshul lo //
NK120(e)001:1158: dang po dbang rab sdom gsum gcig car du thob tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:1159: rab mchog sbyangs pa mthar son skal ldan de //
NK120(e)001:1160: dbang bskur thob pas sdom gsum gcig car skye //
NK120(e)001:1161: rtogs grol dus mnyam in+d+ra b+hu ti bzhin //
NK120(e)001:1163: dbang po yang raba mchoga tu gyur pa sngon gyi
NK120(e)001:1164: dus su tshogs gnyis kyi sbyangas pa mathara sona pa
NK120(e)001:1165: ni las 'phro skal pa mchog dang ldana pa'i phyir
NK120(e)001:1166: / de 'dra ba la tshe 'dir lam thun mong
NK120(e)001:1167: pas rgyud sbyang ba la ma ltos par dabnga bskura
NK120(e)001:1168: thoba pa tsam gyis so byang sngags kyi sdoma pa
NK120(e)001:1169: gsuma po gciga cara du skye ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:1170: dper na dbang don gyi ye shes rtogsa pa dang
NK120(e)001:1171: rgyud grola ba dusa manyama pa o rgyan gyi rgyal
NK120(e)001:1172: po in+d+ra b+hu ti lta bu ste /
NK120(e)001:1173: sngon rgyal po des ston pa thub pa'i dbang po
NK120(e)001:1174: la 'dod yon ma spangs par sangs rgyas thob pa'i
NK120(e)001:1176: ston pas las can du gzigs nas de ma thag
NK120(e)001:1177: dkyil 'khor chen po mngon du snang bar mdzad de
NK120(e)001:1178: dbang bskur bas dus de nyid du zug 'jug gi
NK120(e)001:1180: de'ang sngags kyi sdom pa gang zhig gzhan gnod gzhir bcas spong ba so thar /
NK120(e)001:1181: gzhan phan gzhir bcas sgrub pa byang sems /
NK120(e)001:1182: de nyid dag mnyam chen po'i thabs kyis zin pa sngags kyi sdom pa'i ngo bo yin no //
NK120(e)001:1183: gnyis pa dbang 'bring sdom gsum so sor nod tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:1184: 'bring ni sdom gsum so so'i cho ga la //
NK120(e)001:1185: brten nas rim thob n+aa gardzu na ltar //
NK120(e)001:1187: gang zag dbang po 'bringa ni 'dul ba'i las chog
NK120(e)001:1188: la brten nas so thar rigs bdun gang rung gi
NK120(e)001:1190: de nas srol gnyis gang rung gi cho gas byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1191: de'i steng du gsang sngags phyi nang gi cho gas sngags kyi sdom pa ste /
NK120(e)001:1192: de ltar sdoma pa gsuma po so soo'i gzhung gi
NK120(e)001:1193: cho ga la brten nasa rim pa bzhin thoba par
NK120(e)001:1194: byas pa slo dpon chen po n+aa ga rdzu na'am
NK120(e)001:1195: mgon po klu sgrub kyi rnam par thar pa ltar
NK120(e)001:1196: ro // gsum pa dbang rtul sdom gsum rim 'jug gis dkri tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:1197: tha ma skal dman shin tu gdul dka' de //
NK120(e)001:1198: gso sbyong bslab pa'i gnas bcu grub mtha' bzhi //
NK120(e)001:1199: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud kun rim shes nas //
NK120(e)001:1200: bla med 'jug pa brtag pa gnyis par gsungs //
NK120(e)001:1202: dbang po tha ma sngon dang da ltar tshogs gnyis
NK120(e)001:1203: bsags pa'i skala ba damna pa shina tu gdula bar
NK120(e)001:1204: daka'a ba de rnams rim gyis lam la dkri dgos
NK120(e)001:1205: pas / dang po 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs dang thar pa'i phan yon bshad pas blo bcos nas /
NK120(e)001:1206: thog mar gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa'i dus khrims nod cing /
NK120(e)001:1207: de'i rjes su dge bsnyen gyi sdom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1208: dge tshul gyi bslaba pa'i gansa bcu nas dge slong gi sdom pa'i bar rim par sbyin la /
NK120(e)001:1209: gruba mtha' bzhi'i dang po bye ma do gnyis kyi
NK120(e)001:1210: bdag med gtan la dbab tshul la goms su bcug
NK120(e)001:1211: / de rjes byang sems kyi sdom pa byin nas dbu sems gnyis kyi lta ba la sems sbyong /
NK120(e)001:1212: mthar rang rang gi dbang bskur sngon du 'gro bas
NK120(e)001:1213: gtsang sbra'i spyod lam dang bzlas brjod sogs lus ngag
NK120(e)001:1214: gi bya ba gtso bor ston pa bya ba'i rgyud
NK120(e)001:1215: dang / lus ngag gi bya ba dang sems kyi
NK120(e)001:1216: ting nge 'dzin cha mnyam du ston pa spyod pa'i
NK120(e)001:1217: dang / rgyud dang / sems kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK120(e)001:1218: gtso bor ston pa rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kun gyi
NK120(e)001:1219: lta sgom spyod gsum gyis bsdus pa'i nyams len rnams
NK120(e)001:1220: rima par shesa shing nyams 'og tu chub par byas
NK120(e)001:1221: dang / rgyud dang / nasa / thabs shes gnyis
NK120(e)001:1222: su med pa'i rnal 'byor bde ba chen pos khyad
NK120(e)001:1223: par du byas pa'i thabs ston pa nang rgyud bla
NK120(e)001:1224: meda kyi dbang gis smin par byas nas bskyed rdzogs
NK120(e)001:1225: zung 'jug gsum gyi rgyud sde la rim gyis 'juga
NK120(e)001:1226: para bya ba'i tshul kye rdo rje brtaga pa gnyis
NK120(e)001:1227: pa'i phyi ma 'dul ba'i le'u las gsal bar gsungas
NK120(e)001:1228: dang / rgyud dang / nasa / te / de las /
NK120(e)001:1229: dang po gso sbyong sbyin par bya //
NK120(e)001:1230: de rjes bslab pa'i gnas bcu nyid //
NK120(e)001:1231: de la bye brag smra ba bstan //
NK120(e)001:1232: mdo sde pa'ang de bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:1233: de nas rnal 'byor spyod pa nyid //
NK120(e)001:1234: de yi rjes su dbu ma bstan //
NK120(e)001:1235: sngags kyi rim pa kun shes nas //
NK120(e)001:1236: de rjes kye yi rdo rje bstan //
NK120(e)001:1237: slo mas gus pas blangs nas ni //
NK120(e)001:1240: de dang mthun par phur pa zhe sdang khros pa'i rgyud las kyang /
NK120(e)001:1241: so sor thar pa dang por sbyin //
NK120(e)001:1242: de la nyan thos chos rnams bstan //
NK120(e)001:1243: de nas byang chub sdom chen sbyin //
NK120(e)001:1244: de la dbu ma'i chos rnams bshad //
NK120(e)001:1245: mthar ni 'bras bu theg chen gyi //
NK120(e)001:1248: de dag spyir bstan pa tsam yin gyi /
NK120(e)001:1249: gong gi sdom gsum rim thob yin na dbang 'bring dang /
NK120(e)001:1250: rim 'jug yin na dbang po tha ma kho na yin pas khyab pa min pa'ang shes par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:1251: gnyis pa 'dir bstan dbang po 'bring gi thob tshul bye brag tu bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:1252: rten mchog dman dmigs bsal dang bcas pa /
NK120(e)001:1253: sdom pa gsum so so'i rnam bzhag /
NK120(e)001:1254: sdom pa 'og ma gnyis gong ma'i yan lag tu 'gro tshul /
NK120(e)001:1255: sdom gsum so so'i don shes sla ba'i phyir sdom bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:1257: dang po rten mchog dman dmigs bsal dang bcas pa bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1258: 'dir ni dbang po 'bring gi tshul 'chad de //
NK120(e)001:1259: dge slong dge tshul dge bsnyen sdom ldan de //
NK120(e)001:1260: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rab 'bring tha yin zhes //
NK120(e)001:1261: phur ba'i rgyud dang dus 'khor las gsungs shing //
NK120(e)001:1262: 'on kyang ye shes ldan pa gtso bor gzung //
NK120(e)001:1264: skabs 'dira ni dabnga po 'bringa gi tshula nyid 'achada par bya ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:1265: de'ang spyir btang du sngags lam la 'jug pa'i rten
NK120(e)001:1266: dge slong dang dge tshul dang dge bsnyen gyi sdoma
NK120(e)001:1267: pa dang ldana pa de gsum rim pa ltar sngags
NK120(e)001:1268: kyi rdo rje 'dzina pa'i raba dang 'bringa dang tha
NK120(e)001:1269: ma yina no zhesa phura pa'i rgyud dang dusa 'khora
NK120(e)001:1270: gyi rtsa rgyud lasa mthun par 'di skad du /
NK120(e)001:1271: gsum las dge slong mchog yin 'bring //
NK120(e)001:1272: dge tshul zhes bya de dag las //
NK120(e)001:1273: khyim na gnas pa tha ma'o //
NK120(e)001:1275: 'ona kyang mtha' gcig tu ma nges te /
NK120(e)001:1276: rten khyim pa yin kyang mthong lam rnam par mi
NK120(e)001:1277: rtog pa'i ye shesa rtogs pa mchog dang ldana pa
NK120(e)001:1278: ni don dam pa'i dge slong yin pas na de
NK120(e)001:1279: nyid gtso bor bzunga dgos pa dmigs bsal te /
NK120(e)001:1281: sa thob ma gtogs khyim pa ni //
NK120(e)001:1282: rgyal po'i bla mar mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:1285: rgyan gyis brgyan par byas kyang chos spyod cing //
NK120(e)001:1286: dul zhing yang dag sdom la tshangs par spyod //
NK120(e)001:1287: 'byung po kun la chad pa spangs pa ste //
NK120(e)001:1288: dge slong dge sbyong de yin //
NK120(e)001:1290: gnyis pa sdom pa gsum so so'i rnam bzhag bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1291: snga 'gyur rgyud sde'i rtsa ba kun 'dus las //
NK120(e)001:1292: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:1293: so thar sems bskyed dbang bskur nyid yin te //
NK120(e)001:1294: so sor 'dzin na nyan thos byang sems dang //
NK120(e)001:1295: rig pa 'dzin pa zhes su mkhas la grags //
NK120(e)001:1297: spyir sdom pa gsum gyi tha snyad du grags pa la /
NK120(e)001:1298: so thar gyi skabs bslab tshigs gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:1299: byang sems kyi skabs sdom sdud don byed gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:1300: sngags kyi skabs sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig la
NK120(e)001:1301: sdom pa gsum du bzhag pa sogs mang du snang
NK120(e)001:1302: mod / 'on kyang skabs 'dir bstan bya ngos bzung
NK120(e)001:1303: ba'i tshul ni snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sde'i rtsa ba
NK120(e)001:1304: kun 'dusa rig pa'i mdo las 'di skad ces /
NK120(e)001:1305: de ltar sdom pa gsum po yang //
NK120(e)001:1306: rang dang gzhan don phan pa che //
NK120(e)001:1308: ranga don zhi bde tsam dang /
NK120(e)001:1309: gazhana dona du rdzogs byang thob 'dod dang /
NK120(e)001:1310: thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pas rang gzhan
NK120(e)001:1311: la phana pa rlabs po che grub par bashada pa
NK120(e)001:1312: ni rim pa bzhin so thara gyi sdom pa dang
NK120(e)001:1313: / semas bskyed kyi sdom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1314: dabnga bskur ba las thob pa'i sngags kyi sdom pa dang gsum po 'di nyid yina te /
NK120(e)001:1315: de dag kyang so sora 'dzina na snga ma la so thar nyan thosa dang /
NK120(e)001:1316: bar pa la sems bskyed byang seemsa dang /
NK120(e)001:1317: phyi ma la riga pa 'dzina pa zhesa su mkhas pa rnams la gragas pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:1318: gsum pa sdom pa 'og ma gnyis gong ma'i yan lag tu 'gro tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:1319: de ltar thun mong sdom pa 'og ma gnyis //
NK120(e)001:1320: 'dir ni bla med dbang gi yan lag tu //
NK120(e)001:1321: rgyud sde rgya mtshor bshad ltar 'dir 'chad do //
NK120(e)001:1323: bshad ma thag pa de ltar thun mong gi sdoma
NK120(e)001:1324: pa 'oga ma so thar dang byang sems gnyisa po
NK120(e)001:1325: skabs 'dir ni sngags bla meda rdo rje theg pa'i
NK120(e)001:1326: dabnga gi yan lag tu 'gro ba'i tshul yang 'di
NK120(e)001:1327: lta ste / so byang gi sdom ldan des sngags
NK120(e)001:1328: sdom thob pa na so thar sngags kyi nyes spyod
NK120(e)001:1329: lta ste / sdom pa dang / byang sdom rnam
NK120(e)001:1330: snang gi dam tshig tu 'gyur ba gang zhig sngags
NK120(e)001:1331: bla med kyi spyi dang khyad par lhag pa'i dam
NK120(e)001:1332: tshig las spyi'i dam tshig tu so byang dang sngags
NK120(e)001:1333: phyi rgyud kyi dam tshig thams cad tshang ba'i phyir
NK120(e)001:1334: lta ste / sdom pa dang / dang / der
NK120(e)001:1335: ma zad sdom pa 'og ma gnyis sngon du ma
NK120(e)001:1336: song ba'i rdo rje 'dzin pa'i rgyud la'ang dbang bskur
NK120(e)001:1337: ba kho nas thob pa'i so byang gi sdom pa
NK120(e)001:1340: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK120(e)001:1341: rig 'dzin nang gi sdom pa'i tshogs //
NK120(e)001:1342: ma lus bdag gis yongs su bzung //
NK120(e)001:1343: zhes pa la sogs pas dbang gi sngon 'gro'i dus su khas blangs pa'i phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:1344: mnyam pa chen po'i dam tshig dang ldan pa'i rig
NK120(e)001:1345: pa 'dzin pa'i rgyud la 'og ma'i 'dul sdom thams
NK120(e)001:1346: cad ngang gis 'du ba'ang yin te /
NK120(e)001:1347: rtsa rgyud gsang ba snying po las /
NK120(e)001:1348: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK120(e)001:1349: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK120(e)001:1350: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK120(e)001:1351: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK120(e)001:1354: dge slong byang chub sems dpa' dang //
NK120(e)001:1358: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK120(e)001:1359: rig 'dzin nyid kyi dge slong ngo //
NK120(e)001:1360: zhes pa la sogs pa'i rgyud sde rgya mtsho nas
NK120(e)001:1361: ji skad bashada pa ltar bstan bcos 'dira yang de
NK120(e)001:1363: bzhi pa sdom gsum so so'i don shes sla ba'i
NK120(e)001:1364: phyir le'u 'og ma gsum gyi sdom bstan pa ni
NK120(e)001:1365: / sdom gsum so sor khog dbub gleng gzhi dang //
NK120(e)001:1366: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob pa'i tshul //
NK120(e)001:1367: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs //
NK120(e)001:1368: tha mar nyams na gso tshul bzhi res sdom //
NK120(e)001:1370: de ltar sdoom gsum spyi'i lus rnam par gzhag pa mdor bstan nas /
NK120(e)001:1371: dngos don le'u phyi ma gsum gyis rgyas par 'chad
NK120(e)001:1372: pa la sdoma pa gsuma so sora gang las byung
NK120(e)001:1373: ba'i tshul dang 'brel bar ngo bo dang dbye ba'i
NK120(e)001:1374: sgo nas khoga dbuba pa'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:1375: dang po sdoma pa ma thoba pa cho ga la sogs pa'i sgo nas thoba pa'i tshula dang /
NK120(e)001:1376: bar du thob pa'i sdom pa so so'i bsrung bya'i
NK120(e)001:1377: rnam grangs bshad pas mi nyamas par bsrunga ba'i thabas
NK120(e)001:1378: dang / tha mara ltung ba byung ba sgo bzhi'i
NK120(e)001:1379: dbang gis nyamsa par 'gyur na slar gso ba'i tshul
NK120(e)001:1380: te rnam grangs bzhi resa sdoma du bsdus nas 'chad
NK120(e)001:1382: lnga pa le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:1383: sdom gsum spyi'i bshad gzhi'i rim par phye ba ste dang pa'o //
NK120(e)001:1385: sdoma pa gsuma gyi rnam gzhag spyi'i bashada gzhi'i rima
NK120(e)001:1386: pa legs para phye ba ste le'u dang po'i rnam
NK120(e)001:1387: par bshad pa'o //// da ni spyi'i sa bcad gnyis
NK120(e)001:1388: pa sdom gsum so so'i rang bzhin dang bslab bya
NK120(e)001:1389: zhib tu ston pa'i sgo nas rgyas par bshad pa
NK120(e)001:1390: par bshad pa'o //// la gsum ste / so thar /
NK120(e)001:1393: dang po 'dul ba so thar gyi chos tshul ston pa le'u gnyis pa'i gzhung 'di la gsum /
NK120(e)001:1394: ston pas dam pa'i chos 'dul ba ji ltar gsungs pa /
NK120(e)001:1395: de bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung ba /
NK120(e)001:1396: de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK120(e)001:1397: skabs 'dir spyi'i go don du 'o skol nang pa
NK120(e)001:1398: sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa'i 'byung khung ston pa sangs
NK120(e)001:1399: rgyas kyi mtshan nyid dang byon tshul nyid shes pa
NK120(e)001:1400: gal che bas na dmigs kyis mdo tsam brjod par
NK120(e)001:1401: bya ste / de yang rang cag gi ston pa
NK120(e)001:1402: mnyam med sh+aakya'i rgyal po 'di nyid nges don yin
NK120(e)001:1403: lugs kyi dbang du byas na /
NK120(e)001:1404: thog ma med pa'i dus nas mngon par sangs rgyas
NK120(e)001:1405: te chos nyid 'od gsal gyi zhing khams su sku
NK120(e)001:1406: dang ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang la dus
NK120(e)001:1407: gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dang dgongs pa ro
NK120(e)001:1408: gcig tu bzhugs pa las ma g.yos bzhin du sems
NK120(e)001:1409: can rnams kyi don du de bzhin gshegs pa'i rnam
NK120(e)001:1410: par rol pa bsam gyis mi khyab par snang bas
NK120(e)001:1411: gdul bya rnams so so'i skal ba dang 'tshams par
NK120(e)001:1413: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba rtsa ba'i rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:1414: thugs rje chen pos 'brel ba na //
NK120(e)001:1415: 'gro drug dus gnas ma lus snang //
NK120(e)001:1418: bskal pa bye stong bsam gyis mi khyab par //
NK120(e)001:1419: de yi tshad ni nam yang med pas na //
NK120(e)001:1420: byang chub mchog rab 'di ni ngas thob kyi //
NK120(e)001:1421: ngas ni rtag tu chos kyang rab 'chad do //
NK120(e)001:1423: yab sras rgyal ba'i mdo las kyang //
NK120(e)001:1424: dpa' bo chen po thabs mkhas de //
NK120(e)001:1425: sems can yongs su smin mdzad phyir //
NK120(e)001:1426: bye ba phrag brgyar rgyal ba nyid //
NK120(e)001:1427: sangs rgyas nyid du bstan gyur kyang //
NK120(e)001:1428: da dung du yang 'dren pa khyod //
NK120(e)001:1429: sangs rgyas mang por ston par mdzad //
NK120(e)001:1430: ces gsungs pa ltar yin la /
NK120(e)001:1431: tha snyad rnam 'jog gi dbang du byas te theg pa thun mong pa ltar na /
NK120(e)001:1432: spyir dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas dpag tu med pa mkha' khyab tu bzhugs pa las /
NK120(e)001:1433: bdag cag gi ston pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas sh+aakya thub pa 'di nyid /
NK120(e)001:1434: dang por byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed //
NK120(e)001:1435: bar du bskal pa grangs med gsum du tshogs bsags /
NK120(e)001:1436: mthar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas te chos kyi
NK120(e)001:1437: 'khor lo ma lus pa bskor bar mdzad pa yin
NK120(e)001:1438: te / yon tan yongs su bkod pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)001:1439: des bla na med pa'i byang chub tu sems dang po bskyed pa nas bzung ste /
NK120(e)001:1440: bskal pa chen po grangs med pa gsum du brtson pa chen pos tshogs bsags shing /
NK120(e)001:1441: tshe lo brgya pa'i tshe sems can long ba 'dren pa rnams la gzigs te /
NK120(e)001:1442: 'dzam bu'i gling 'di nyid du sangs rgyas te chos
NK120(e)001:1443: kyi 'khor lo bsam gyis mi khyab pa yongs su
NK120(e)001:1444: bskor te / zhes gsungs pa ltar /
NK120(e)001:1445: ston pa 'di sngon rdza mkhan gyi khye'u snang byed du gyur pa'i tshe /
NK120(e)001:1446: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub pa chen po'i drung du thugs bskyed par bshad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1447: mdo bskal pa bzang po las kyang /
NK120(e)001:1448: nga ni sngon tshe dman par gyur pa na //
NK120(e)001:1449: de bzhin gshegs pa sh+aakya thub de la //
NK120(e)001:1450: 'jam gang zhig ni rab tu phul nas kyang //
NK120(e)001:1451: dang por byang chub mchog tu thugs bskyed do //
NK120(e)001:1453: de nas tshogs bsags tshul la theg pa chung ngu'i lugs ltar na /
NK120(e)001:1454: rnam gzigs mar me rin chen gtsug /
NK120(e)001:1455: grangs med gsum gyi tha mar byung //
NK120(e)001:1456: dang po sh+aakya thub pa yin //
NK120(e)001:1457: kun la thams cad snying rje yis //
NK120(e)001:1458: sbyin par byas pas sbyin pa rdzogs //
NK120(e)001:1459: chags bcas yan lag bcad kyang ni //
NK120(e)001:1460: mi 'khrugs bzod dang tshul khrims kyi //
NK120(e)001:1461: skar rgyal bstod pas brtson 'grus kyi //
NK120(e)001:1462: de ma thag tu ting 'dzin blo //
NK120(e)001:1464: bskal pa grangs med gsum la rim par sangs rgyas bdun khri lnga stong dang /
NK120(e)001:1466: bdun khri bdun stong gi bar mnyes par mdzad ces 'byung /
NK120(e)001:1468: lam lnga dang sa bcu yongs su rdzogs par 'gro dgos pa yin pas /
NK120(e)001:1469: 'phags pa'i sa brnyes nas skad cig re rer yang
NK120(e)001:1470: phyogs bcu rab 'byams mu med pa'i sangs rgyas grangs
NK120(e)001:1471: med tshad med pa dag yongs su mnyes pa dang
NK120(e)001:1472: / bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs mtha' yas pa bsags shing rdzogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1473: sems can grangs med pa yongs su smin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1474: zhing khams tshad med pa yongs su sbyangs shing /
NK120(e)001:1475: sa bcu rim gyis bgrod pa'i mthar 'og min gyi
NK120(e)001:1476: zhing khams su rgyun matha'i ye shes kyis yang dag
NK120(e)001:1477: pa'i mtha' mngon du mdzad de sangs rgyas kyi go
NK120(e)001:1478: 'phang brnyes shing / de las ma g.yos bzhin du
NK120(e)001:1479: gtsang ma'i steng dbang phyug chen po'i 'og min dang
NK120(e)001:1480: 'phang brnyes shing / / gzugs kyi khams kyi 'og min dang /
NK120(e)001:1482: 'dzam bu gling rnams su sprul pa'i sku ston par mdzad pa yin te /
NK120(e)001:1484: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK120(e)001:1485: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK120(e)001:1486: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos par //
NK120(e)001:1487: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK120(e)001:1488: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK120(e)001:1491: bzo yi gnas la mkhas pa 4pa dang //
NK120(e)001:1494: byang chub 8snying por gshegs pa dang //
NK120(e)001:1496: byang chub chos kyi 11'khor lo dang //
NK120(e)001:1497: mya ngan 12'das par gshegs mdzad rnams //
NK120(e)001:1498: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK120(e)001:1499: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK120(e)001:1500: zhes gsungs pa ltar mdzad pa bcu gnyis kyi sgo nas don mdzad pa ste /
NK120(e)001:1501: gong du smos pa ltar thugs bskyed pa nas brtsams
NK120(e)001:1502: te tshogs lam gyi rten la tshogs gnyis yongs su
NK120(e)001:1504: skye rgu rnams tshe lo nyi khri ba'i dus sangs
NK120(e)001:1505: rgyas 'od srung 'jig rten du byon pa'i tshe bram
NK120(e)001:1507: de'i sku skye ba phyi ma la dga' ldan gyi
NK120(e)001:1508: gnas su lha'i bu dam pa tog dkar por skye
NK120(e)001:1509: ba bzung ste lha rnams chos kyi smin par mdzad
NK120(e)001:1510: / dza m+bu'i gling gi mi rnams tshe lo brgya
NK120(e)001:1511: pa'i dus su 'dul ba'i skabs su babs par mkhyen
NK120(e)001:1516: dus te gzigs pa rnam pa lngas gzigs nas lha
NK120(e)001:1517: rnams la 'chi 'pho rnam par sbyong ba'i chos kyi
NK120(e)001:1518: rnam grangs gsungs mthar glang po che thal dkar mche
NK120(e)001:1519: ba drug ldan gyi tshul du dga' ldan gyi gnas
NK120(e)001:1521: der sa mo lug gi lo'i chu stod zla ba'i
NK120(e)001:1522: nya la sh+aakya'i rgyal po zas gtsang ma'i btsun mo
NK120(e)001:1523: sgyu 'phrul ma gso sbyong la gnas pa'i glo g.yas
NK120(e)001:1524: nas zhugs te lhums gzhal yas khang du byin gyis
