NK120(e)001:1525: brlabs pa la bzhugs nas lha mi'i 'khor khri phrag
NK120(e)001:1526: bye ba mang po la skye gnas rnam par sbyong
NK120(e)001:1527: ba'i chos 2bstan / der sa bcu'i nges pa mtshon
NK120(e)001:1528: pas zla ba bcu'i phung po rdzogs pa lcags sprel
NK120(e)001:1529: sa ga zla ba'i tshes bdun la yum sgyu 'phrul
NK120(e)001:1530: ma lum+bi ni'i tshal du 'chag par gshegs te shing
NK120(e)001:1531: klag sha'i yal ga la bzung ba na gnod pa
NK120(e)001:1532: med par rtsib log g.yas pa'i go bar nas na
NK120(e)001:1533: bza' dang bcas te len pa med par thang du
NK120(e)001:1534: byon te phyogs bzhir gom pa bdun bdun bor nas
NK120(e)001:1535: ba'i chos 2bstan / / nga ni 'jig rten 'di na mchog yin no //
NK120(e)001:1537: bar snang gi lhas bstod pa sogs ngo mtshar ba'i ltas mang po dang bcas te sku 3bltams /
NK120(e)001:1538: de nyid skye rgu'i bdag mo la sogs pa ma
NK120(e)001:1539: ma sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis bskyed bsrings te yig
NK120(e)001:1540: dpon kun gyi bshes gnyen sogs slob dpon so so
NK120(e)001:1543: sgyu rtsal sogs la bslabs nas bzo'i gnas thams cad
NK120(e)001:1544: la mkhas shing stobs dang sgyu rtsal phul du phyin
NK120(e)001:1545: pa'i tshul bstan nas sh+aakya pa rnams pham par 4mdzad
NK120(e)001:1546: / de nas 'jig rten pa dang tshul mthun par
NK120(e)001:1547: 'jug pa'i phyir sh+aakya'i bu mo sa 'tsho ma dang
NK120(e)001:1549: ri dwags skyes rnams 'khor drug khri dang bcas khab
NK120(e)001:1550: tu bzhes nas dgyes par rol pa'i tshul bstan bzhin
NK120(e)001:1551: dgung lo nyer dgu'i bar du pho brang du bzhugs
NK120(e)001:1553: de nas dgung lo nyer dgu pa la gnas gtsang
NK120(e)001:1554: ma'i lhas bskul te skye rga na 'chi'i chu bo
NK120(e)001:1555: bzhi dang dge sbyong gi gzugs gzigs pa'i rkyen byas
NK120(e)001:1556: te nges par 'byung bar dam bcas pa na /
NK120(e)001:1557: zas gtsang ma'i tshogs rnams gzhon nu rab tu 'byung
NK120(e)001:1558: gis dogs te khor yug mel tshes bsrungs kyang chibs
NK120(e)001:1559: basngagasa ldan gyi steng na rgyal chen bzhis sri zhu
NK120(e)001:1560: dang bcas nam mkha'i dbyings su gshegs nas mchod rten
NK120(e)001:1561: rnam dag gi drung du babs shing nyid kyi dbu
NK120(e)001:1562: skra nyid kyis bor te rab tu 6byung /
NK120(e)001:1563: de nas rtog ge ba gdams ngag che bar grags
NK120(e)001:1564: pa ring 'phur dang lhag spyod gnyis las 'jig rten
NK120(e)001:1565: pa'i ting nge 'dzin nod pa'i tshul bstan nas lnga
NK120(e)001:1566: sde bzang po dang bcas chu klung nee rany+dza na'i
NK120(e)001:1567: 'gram na lo drug tu dka' ba spyad nas mkha'
NK120(e)001:1568: khyab kyi ting nge 'dzin la mnyam par 7bzhag /
NK120(e)001:1569: ji zhig na lha rnams kyis bskul nas ting nge
NK120(e)001:1570: 'dzin las bzhengs te bzhud pa'i lam du mtha' gnyis
NK120(e)001:1571: spangs pa dbu ma'i lam ma gtogs pa 'jig rten
NK120(e)001:1572: na grags pa'i dka' thub tsam gyis grol bar 'dzin
NK120(e)001:1573: pa dgag pa'i phyir bram ze'i bu mo legs skyes
NK120(e)001:1574: mas ba men lnga brgya'i 'o ma nying khur byas
NK120(e)001:1575: pa drangs pa gsol bas sku lus mtshan dpe shin
NK120(e)001:1576: tu gsal ba gser gyi gtan pa phyis pa ltar
NK120(e)001:1577: gyur cing / lam du r+ts+wa tshong bkra shis ldan
NK120(e)001:1578: las reg na 'jam pa'i r+ts+wa phyag gang bzhes pa
NK120(e)001:1579: bsnams nas rdo rje gdan 8du byon /
NK120(e)001:1580: de nas dgung lo so lnga pa shing rta sa
NK120(e)001:1581: ga zla ba'i nya la rdo rje gdan byang chub
NK120(e)001:1582: shing gi snying po can du r+ts+wa'i 'ding ba la
NK120(e)001:1584: stan 'dir bdag gi lus 'di skam yang rung //
NK120(e)001:1585: pags pa rus pa'i tshogs rnams zhig kyang rung //
NK120(e)001:1586: bskal mang rnyed daka'i byang chub ma thob bar //
NK120(e)001:1587: stan 'di las ni lus bskyod mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:1588: zhes dam bca' brtan po mdzad /
NK120(e)001:1589: der srod kyi cha la bdud kyi rgyal pos bslu brid kyi tshig dang /
NK120(e)001:1590: bdud kyi bu mo bdun gyis chags pa'i zol gyis
NK120(e)001:1591: bslu bar brtsams kyang g.yo ba'i skabs ma rnyed pa
NK120(e)001:1592: na / bdud dmag bye ba dung phyur drangs pa'ang byams pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 9btul /
NK120(e)001:1593: thun dang po'i skabs de nyid du mnyam par bzhag
NK120(e)001:1594: ste rab matha'i bsam gtan la brten nas rdzu 'phrul
NK120(e)001:1595: gyi mngon shes dang lha'i rna ba /
NK120(e)001:1596: gung thun la gzhan sems shes pa /
NK120(e)001:1598: lha'i mig gi mngon shes rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:1599: thun tha ma skya rengs 'char khar zag pa zad
NK120(e)001:1600: pa'i mngon shes bsgrubs pas bla na med pa'i ye
NK120(e)001:1601: shes brnyes nas mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas kyi
NK120(e)001:1602: byang chub brnyes pa de'i tshe sa chen po 'di
NK120(e)001:1603: yang rab tu g.yos shing 'od zer gyi snang ba
NK120(e)001:1604: dpag tu med pa byung ba la lha rnams kyis
NK120(e)001:1605: 10bstod / de'i tshe na 'jig rten na dgra bcom pa gcig go //
NK120(e)001:1606: de nas bdud rtsi zab mo rtog ge'i spyod yul ma yin par ston pa'i slad du /
NK120(e)001:1607: zab zhi spros bral 'od gsal 'dus ma byas //
NK120(e)001:1608: bdud rtsi lta bu'i chos zhig kho bos rnyed //
NK120(e)001:1609: su la bstan kyang go bar mi 'dug pas //
NK120(e)001:1610: mi smra nags 'dab nyid du gnas par bya //
NK120(e)001:1611: zhes gsungs te zhag bdun phrag bdun du chos ma gsung bar bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK120(e)001:1612: lha'i dbang po tshangs pa dang brgya byin gnyis kyis
NK120(e)001:1613: chos kyi 'khor lo bskor bar yang nas yang du
NK120(e)001:1614: bskul bas / tshangs pa ma ga d+ha yi sems can gang //
NK120(e)001:1615: rna bar ldan zhing dad dang shes rab ldan //
NK120(e)001:1616: mi 'chi 'du byed rtag tu chos nyan pa //
NK120(e)001:1617: de dag la ni bdud rtsi'i sgo dabye'o //
NK120(e)001:1618: zhes zhal gyis bzhes pa'i sgra 'og min gyi bar du grags /
NK120(e)001:1619: de nas rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul dbus sngon gyi drang srong rnams kyis brten par mdzad pa'i gnas /
NK120(e)001:1620: bdag cag gi ston pa 'dis kyang rgyal ba bye
NK120(e)001:1621: ba phrag khrig la bsnyen bkur mchod sbyin du ma
NK120(e)001:1622: mdzad pa'i yul w+aa r+aa na s+ai drang srong lhung
NK120(e)001:1623: ba ri dwags mi 'jigs pa'i nags tshal du gshegs
NK120(e)001:1624: nas der rdzogs sangs rgyas nas zhag bdun phrag bdun
NK120(e)001:1625: 'das pa chu stod zla ba'i tshes bzhi nas brtsams
NK120(e)001:1626: te / chos lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa
NK120(e)001:1627: gtso bor ston pa rjod byed 'dul ba sde snod
NK120(e)001:1628: bka' dang po bden pa bzhi'i chos kyi 'khor lo
NK120(e)001:1629: te / // mi'i 'khor gyi thog ma kun shes koon+dina ya /
NK120(e)001:1633: bzang ldan te lnga sde bzang po dang lha brgyad
NK120(e)001:1634: khri dang bcas pa la bden bzhi lan gsum du
NK120(e)001:1636: lha brgyad khris bden pa mthong /
NK120(e)001:1637: lnga sdes ye shes khong chud kyis bsnyen par rdzogs te dgra bcom pa 11thob /
NK120(e)001:1638: de'i tshe 'jig rten na dgra bcom pa drug go //
NK120(e)001:1639: de yang spyir lung bzhis bsdus pa'i 'dul ba'i sde
NK120(e)001:1640: snod ni ston pa sangs rgyas pa nas mya ngan
NK120(e)001:1641: las ma 'das kyi bar du byung ba dang bcas
NK120(e)001:1642: pa'i rnam par bzhag pa thams cad ston pa'i phyir
NK120(e)001:1643: chos 'khor dang po kho na'i mtshan gzhir nges pa
NK120(e)001:1644: ma yin kyang / 'khor ba'i mtshan nyid spang bya
NK120(e)001:1645: las ldog pa'i lam ston pa'i phyir gtso che ba'i
NK120(e)001:1646: dbang du byas te bzhag pa yin /
NK120(e)001:1648: 'dul ba'i 'dul ba bcas rang gi rnam gzhag che long tsam dang /
NK120(e)001:1649: 'dul ba'i mdo sde ting nge 'dzin dang tshangs par
NK120(e)001:1650: spyod pa'i rnal 'byor du bya ba'i rim pa dang
NK120(e)001:1651: / 'dul ba'i mngon pa de rnams kyi rab dbye
NK120(e)001:1652: rgya cher bshad pa sogs spang gnyen gyi rim pas
NK120(e)001:1653: nyams su len pa'i thabs rnams bka' dang po bden
NK120(e)001:1654: pa bzhi'i chos kyi rnam grangs so //
NK120(e)001:1655: 'khor lo bar pa dang tha ma gnyis kyi tshul ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur ba bzhin dang /
NK120(e)001:1656: khyad par sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams las ni /
NK120(e)001:1657: 'og min gzhan 'phrul dbang byed kyi gnas dang /
NK120(e)001:1658: ri rab kyi rtse mo dang /
NK120(e)001:1659: mi'i gnas kyi 'jig rten dpal ldan 'bras spungs dang /
NK120(e)001:1663: bsil ba'i tshal la sogs pa gnas dang dus dang
NK120(e)001:1664: 'khor mtha' gcig tu ma nges pa la dkyil 'khor
NK120(e)001:1665: sprul bshad la sogs pa'i sgo nas rgyud sde mtha'
NK120(e)001:1666: yas par gsungs pa'i rnam gzhag thun mong ma yin
NK120(e)001:1668: rgyal ba'i phrin las tshad med pa'i chos kyi sgo dang /
NK120(e)001:1671: dus snga phyi la sogs pa so so'i skye bo'i
NK120(e)001:1672: blos nam yang bsam par nus pa ma yin la
NK120(e)001:1673: / de lta bu'i cho 'phrul chen po'i phrin las
NK120(e)001:1674: kyi rol pa tshad med pas mthong thos dran reg
NK120(e)001:1675: gi skye 'gro thams cad thar pa bde ba'i lam
NK120(e)001:1677: ston pa thub pa'i dbang po nyid dgung lo brgyad
NK120(e)001:1678: cu'i grangs su phebs te sku dngos kyi gdul bya
NK120(e)001:1679: phal che ba btul zin pa'i skabs sh+aa ri'i bu
NK120(e)001:1680: dang lhan cig dgra bcom pa brgyad khri /
NK120(e)001:1681: mo'u gal gyi bu dang lhan cig dgra bcom pa bdun khri bcas sngon du mya ngan las 'das /
NK120(e)001:1682: de nas ston pa nyid gyad yul grong khyer r+ts+wa
NK120(e)001:1683: can du gshegs te shing s+aa la zung gi bar
NK120(e)001:1684: tha ma'i gzims khri la bzhugs nas kyang dri za
NK120(e)001:1685: rab dga' dang kun tu rgyu rab bzang gi bar
NK120(e)001:1686: btul nas dngos kyi gdul bya rdzogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1687: bstan pa 'khor rnam pa bzhi dang bcas pa gnas brtan chen po 'od srung la gtad de /
NK120(e)001:1688: skye bo rtag 'dzin can rnams 'dul ba dang /
NK120(e)001:1689: le lo can mang po chos la bskul ba dang /
NK120(e)001:1690: sangs rgyas 'jig rten du byon pa shin tu dkon pa'i 'du shes bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:1691: dgung grangs gya gcig tu phebs pa lcags 'brug sa
NK120(e)001:1692: ga zla ba'i nya la dgongs pa chos kyi dbyings
NK120(e)001:1693: su yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul bstan
NK120(e)001:1694: / 12 de dang lhan cig dgra bcom pa khri brgyad stong yang mya ngan las 'das /
NK120(e)001:1695: der gdung las zhugs rang 'bar te sku gdung sil bur gyur /
NK120(e)001:1696: rang rang gi skal pa'i khyad par dang 'tshams par
NK120(e)001:1697: cha brgyad du bgos pa mchod rten gyi snying por
NK120(e)001:1698: byas so // de nas bka'i bsdu ba ji ltar
NK120(e)001:1699: byas pa'i tshul sogs ni 'og nas 'byung ba ltar
NK120(e)001:1700: byas so // la / de ltar ston pa sangs
NK120(e)001:1701: rgyas 'jig rten 'dir byon tshul gyi rnam par thar
NK120(e)001:1702: pa mdo tsam spyir shes par byas nas /
NK120(e)001:1703: skabs don gong gi nang gses sa bcad dang po
NK120(e)001:1704: ston pas dam chos 'dul ba ji ltar gsungs pa'i
NK120(e)001:1705: tshul ni / gleng gzhi ston pas w+aa r+aa na s+ai ru //
NK120(e)001:1706: lhag pa'i tshul khrims gtsor ston bden pa bzhi //
NK120(e)001:1709: 'dir chos 'khor dang po 'dul ba'i sde snod gleng ba'i gzhi ni phun sum tshogs pa lnga ste /
NK120(e)001:1710: ston pa phun sum tshogs pa mnyam med thub pa'i dbang po de nyid kyis /
NK120(e)001:1711: gnas phun sum tshogs pa rgya gar 'phags pa'i yul
NK120(e)001:1712: dbus sngon rang sangs rgyas mang po lhag med du
NK120(e)001:1713: song nas ring bsrel sar lhung ba'i gnas w+aa r+aa
NK120(e)001:1714: na s+ai drang srong lhung ba ri dwags mi 'jigs
NK120(e)001:1716: dus phun sum tshogs pa ston pa mngon par rdzogs
NK120(e)001:1717: par sangs rgyas nas zhag grangs bdun phrag bdun pa
NK120(e)001:1718: chu stod zla ba'i tshes bzhi nas brtsams te /
NK120(e)001:1719: chos phun sum tshogs pa lhag pa'i tshul khrimas kyi
NK120(e)001:1720: bslab pa brjod bya'i ga tso bora ston pa rjod
NK120(e)001:1721: byed 'dul ba'i sde snod bka' dang po bdena pa
NK120(e)001:1723: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa lha brgyad khri dang bcas
NK120(e)001:1724: te mi'i 'khor gyi thog ma lnga sde bzang por
NK120(e)001:1725: gsungas pa'o // gnyis pa chos 'khor de nyid bsdus
NK120(e)001:1726: nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung ba'i tshul ni
NK120(e)001:1727: gsungas pa'o // / 'od srung sogs kyis bsdus //
NK120(e)001:1728: bye brag bshad mdzod la sogs 'phags pas brtsams //
NK120(e)001:1729: yon tan 'od dang sh+aakya 'od kyis spel //
NK120(e)001:1730: snga 'gyur sdom rgyun zhi ba 'tsho dang ni //
NK120(e)001:1731: phyis nas sh+aakya sh+r+ai las kyang dar //
NK120(e)001:1733: 'di la bsdu ba rim pa gsum du byung ba las /
NK120(e)001:1735: de'ang mchog zung gnyis dang ston pa bcom ldan 'das
NK120(e)001:1736: lhan cig par dgra bcom pa shin tu mang po
NK120(e)001:1738: lha rnams kyis dge slong dbang yod pa dag mya
NK120(e)001:1739: ngan las 'das te dam pa'i chos ni me shi
NK120(e)001:1740: ba'i du ba tsam du gyur te zhes pa la
NK120(e)001:1741: sogs pa'i 'phya ba bsal ba'i phyir du /
NK120(e)001:1742: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rjes thog lo de nyid la /
NK120(e)001:1743: gnas rgyal po'i khab kyi nya gro d+ha'i phug par /
NK120(e)001:1744: rgyal po ma skyes dgras gnas mal dang yo byad
NK120(e)001:1745: rnams sbyar nas gnas brtan chen po 'oda srunga la
NK120(e)001:1746: sogas dgra bcom pa lnga brgya 'dus te dbyar gnas
NK120(e)001:1747: pa'i dus su / 'phags pa kun dga' bos mdo sde /
NK120(e)001:1749: 'od srung chen pos mngon pa'i sde snod de dgra bcom pa de rnams kyis bsdusa so //
NK120(e)001:1751: ston pa mya ngan las 'das nas lo brgya dang
NK120(e)001:1752: bcu lon pa na yangs pa can gyi dge slong
NK120(e)001:1753: rnams kyis / hu lu hu lu yi rangs dang //
NK120(e)001:1754: kun spyod snod dang lan tsh+wa dang //
NK120(e)001:1755: lam dang sor gnyis dkrugs dang gding //
NK120(e)001:1756: gser la rung ba bya ba ste //
NK120(e)001:1758: ces pa ltar rung ba ma yin pa'i gzhi bcu byas pa de bsal ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:1759: rgyal po d+harma a sho kas yon sbyar te kusma
NK120(e)001:1760: p+au ri'i gtsug lag khang du grags pa la sogs
NK120(e)001:1761: pa'i dgra bcom pa bdun brgya 'dus pas mi rung
NK120(e)001:1763: sde snod gsum ka tshang ba tshar gcig legs par bton /
NK120(e)001:1764: mthun pa dang bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong yang mdzad do //
NK120(e)001:1766: rgyal po d+harma a sho ka'i tsha bo mya ngan
NK120(e)001:1767: bral gyi bu rgyal po dba' bo sde'i dus nas
NK120(e)001:1768: brtsams te / bdud kyi byin gyis brlabs pa'i dge slong lha chen po dang /
NK120(e)001:1771: yid brtan rnams rim par byung bas /
NK120(e)001:1772: gzhan lan gdab dang mi shes pa //
NK120(e)001:1773: yid gnyis dang ni yongs su brtag /
NK120(e)001:1774: bdag nyid gso bar byed pa ste //
NK120(e)001:1775: 'di ni ston pa'i bstan pa yin //
NK120(e)001:1776: zhes chos ma yin pa'i gzhi lnga sgrags te /
NK120(e)001:1777: rgyal po dpa' bo de'i tshe smad /
NK120(e)001:1778: dga' bo dang pad+ma chen po'i tshe ril po /
NK120(e)001:1779: ka nish+ka'i tshe stod yan te rgyal po bzhi'i ring dge 'dun rnams rtsod par gyur cing /
NK120(e)001:1780: ston pas 'dul ba yi ger 'bri ba ma gnang
NK120(e)001:1781: bas yun ring por song ba na so thar gyi
NK120(e)001:1782: mdo 'don tshul ma mthun pa'i dbang gis sde pa
NK120(e)001:1784: ji ltar na gnas brtan klus rtsod pa spel ba'i rgyus gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba las /
NK120(e)001:1787: mang pos bkur ba gsum gyes te rtsa ba'i sde pa bzhir gyis /
NK120(e)001:1788: de rjes yid brtan gyis rtsod pa rgya cher spel bas /
NK120(e)001:1789: sde pa bzhi yang rim gyis bco brgyad du gyes te /
NK120(e)001:1790: gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba bdun /
NK120(e)001:1792: gzhan gnyis las gsum gsum gyes par grags /
NK120(e)001:1793: de nas re zhig gi tshe rtsod pa cung zad
NK120(e)001:1794: zhi nas so sor gnas pa'i dus rgyal rabs bzhi
NK120(e)001:1795: tsam song ba na rgyal po ka nish+kasa sbyin bdag
NK120(e)001:1796: byas nas bka' bsdu gsum pa mdzad /
NK120(e)001:1797: 'di la bzhed pa mi 'dra ba 'ga' zhig snang yang /
NK120(e)001:1798: kha che ba rnams kha che'i yul rna rgyan gyi
NK120(e)001:1799: gtsug lag khang du 'phags pa rtsib legs sogs dgra
NK120(e)001:1801: ba su mi tra sogs btsun pa chen po bzhi brgya dang /
NK120(e)001:1802: byang chub sems dpa' lnga brgya 'dus te /
NK120(e)001:1803: rgyal po kri kri'i rmi lam lung bstan pa'i mdo
NK120(e)001:1804: las drangs nas gyes pa bco brgyad po thams cad
NK120(e)001:1805: sangs rgyas kyi bkar bsgrubs shing /
NK120(e)001:1806: 'dul ba'i sde snod thams cad yi ger bkod /
NK120(e)001:1807: mdo sde dang mngon pa sngar yi ger ma 'khod pa rnams kyang dus der yi ger bkod cing /
NK120(e)001:1808: sngar 'khod pa rnams la'ang dag ther byas so //
NK120(e)001:1809: de nas dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos 'byung tshul dang 'brel bar bstan pa ji ltar bskyangs pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1810: byang phyogs ri bo 'bigs byed gar mkhan gyi gtsug lag khang du /
NK120(e)001:1812: thams cad 'dod la sogs pa'i dgra bcom pa lnga
NK120(e)001:1813: brgyas spyi mthun du nyan thos kyi thun mong ma
NK120(e)001:1814: yin pa'i bstan bcos bye braga bashada mdzoda chen po
NK120(e)001:1816: sogas khong nas gzhan yang bstan pa skyong ba'i skyes
NK120(e)001:1817: bu sangs rgyas dang 'dra ba'i nyan thos chen po
NK120(e)001:1818: dang bla ma grags pa sogs dgra bcom pa 'aphagas
NK120(e)001:1819: pa'i tshogs dang / rgyal po legs rgyal dge ba
NK120(e)001:1820: sogs bram ze chen po'i sde la sogs pa mkhas
NK120(e)001:1821: btsun bzang po'i dpal dang ldan cing rtogs pa'i yon
NK120(e)001:1822: tan la mnga' brnyes pa rnams kyis dgongs 'grel gyi
NK120(e)001:1823: bstan bcos du ma brtsamsa shing /
NK120(e)001:1824: khyad par 'od byed kyi sa brnyes pa'i slob dpon yona tan 'oda kyis mdo rtsa ba dang /
NK120(e)001:1825: de'i rang 'grel stong phrag bcu gnyis pa /
NK120(e)001:1828: las brgya rtsa gcig gi 'grel pa karma sha tam ste gzhung lnga mdzad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1829: slob dpon sh+aakya 'oda kyis dge tshul gyi sum brgya pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1830: de'i 'grel pa 'od ldan bcas mdzad cing spel bas /
NK120(e)001:1831: lho phyogs 'phags pa'i yul nas byang phyogs sham+b+ha la
NK120(e)001:1832: dang nye ba'i bar gyi sa chen po 'di dag
NK120(e)001:1833: ngur smrig gi rgyal mtshan 'dzin pas khyab par gyur
NK120(e)001:1834: pa ni slob dpon 'di gnyis kyi bka' drin kho
NK120(e)001:1835: na'o // de las gangs can bod kyi ljongs 'dir
NK120(e)001:1836: chos rgyal chen po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi bkas
NK120(e)001:1837: bcad pa ltar gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i
NK120(e)001:1838: sde pa gcig pu las ma byung la /
NK120(e)001:1839: de'ang bstan pa snga 'gyur gyi skabs su byung ba'i 'dul ba so thar gyi sdoma pa'i rgyun ni /
NK120(e)001:1840: mnyam med ston pa thub pa'i dbang po nas /
NK120(e)001:1841: sh+aa ri'i bu la sogs pa rim par brgyud /
NK120(e)001:1842: gangs can thog ma'i 'dren pa mkhan chen zhi ba 'tsho las /
NK120(e)001:1846: smar sh+aakya mu ne rnams bsnyen par rdzogs shing /
NK120(e)001:1847: phyis rgyal po glang dar gyis bstan pa la tho
NK120(e)001:1848: 'tshams pa'i dus smar g.yo gtsang gsum gyis 'dul dpe
NK120(e)001:1849: dre'u rgyab gcig bkal te ri bo dan tig tu
NK120(e)001:1850: byon / der bla chen dgongs pa rab gsal dang /
NK120(e)001:1851: de las dbus gtsang gi mi bcu bsnyen par rdzogs shing /
NK120(e)001:1852: klu mes tshul khrims shes rab sogs kyis rgya cher
NK120(e)001:1853: spel ba la brten nas da lta'i bar sdom rgyun
NK120(e)001:1854: ma nyams par bzhugs pa la smad 'dul du grags
NK120(e)001:1855: / de dang mtshungs par phyi 'gyur gyi sdom rgyun
NK120(e)001:1856: stod 'dul du grags pa ni rgya gar shar phyogs
NK120(e)001:1857: kyi pan+di ta d+harma p+aa la mnga' ris su phebs
NK120(e)001:1858: nas 'dul ba'i sdom rgyun dang bshad rgyun spel bas
NK120(e)001:1859: / / mkhan bu'i gtso bo sa d+hu p+aa la /
NK120(e)001:1862: p+aa la rnam gsum du grags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:1863: de nas zhang zhung rgyal ba'i 'byung gnas sogs byon
NK120(e)001:1864: pa las phyi zhig gi bar du sdom rgyun yod
NK120(e)001:1865: par snang na'ang deng sang nges gsal ma thos /
NK120(e)001:1866: yang phyis su khro phu lo ts+aa ba byams pa
NK120(e)001:1867: dpal nas kha che pan chen sh+aakya sh+r+ai gdan drangs
NK120(e)001:1868: te dpal gyi mtha' can gsum zhes sa skya pan+di
NK120(e)001:1869: ta kun dga' rgyal mtshan dpal bzang po /
NK120(e)001:1871: rdo rje dpal rnams bsnyen par rdzogs pas /
NK120(e)001:1872: de gsum lasa kyang rgyun shin tu mang bar 'phel
NK120(e)001:1873: ba da lta'i bar du dara bzhin pa 'di la
NK120(e)001:1875: gsum pa de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:1876: thob bya sdom pa'i ngo bo dang dbye ba spyir bshad //
NK120(e)001:1877: thob byed cho ga'i lag len bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:1878: dang po spyir bshad pa la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:1881: dang po sdom pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK120(e)001:1882: ngo bo nges 'byung bsam pas kun slangs nas //
NK120(e)001:1883: gzhan gnod gzhir bcas ldog pa lus ngag las //
NK120(e)001:1884: skye phyir gzugs can yin ces 'dod pa dang //
NK120(e)001:1885: spong sems rgyun chags sa bon la 'dod pa //
NK120(e)001:1886: rang gi sde pa gong 'og so so'i lugs //
NK120(e)001:1888: de la so thar gyi sdom pa'i ngo bo'am mtshan nyid ni /
NK120(e)001:1889: ngesa par 'abyung ba'i bsam pasa kuna tu bslangas nasa /
NK120(e)001:1890: gazhana la gnoda pa gzhi dang bacasa pa las ldoga
NK120(e)001:1891: pa nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims gang zhig 'dod
NK120(e)001:1893: de'ang lus ngag gi las lam bdun spong ba la
NK120(e)001:1894: rang sde'i grub mtha' smra ba thams cad mthun yang
NK120(e)001:1895: / gzugs can dang shes pa sogs gang la 'jog zhal mi mtshungs te /
NK120(e)001:1896: nyan thos bye brag smra bas so thar gyi sdom
NK120(e)001:1897: pa de rang dang mkhan slob sogs kyi lusa dang
NK120(e)001:1899: rnam par rig byed dang rig byed ma yin pa gnyis ka'i ngo bor skyee la /
NK120(e)001:1900: de nas skad cig gnyis pa phyir rig byed ma
NK120(e)001:1901: yin pa'i gzugas can du gnas pa yin zhesa 'doda
NK120(e)001:1903: rnam rig min rnam gsum zhes bya //
NK120(e)001:1904: sdom dang sdom pa min dang gzhan //
NK120(e)001:1905: sdom pa so sor thar zhes bya //
NK120(e)001:1907: nyan thos mdo sde bas rgyud yongs su 'gyur ba'i khyad par la 'dod de /
NK120(e)001:1909: las sngon du 'gro zhing sems phyir zhing 'byung ba gang yin pa de ni rgyud yin la /
NK120(e)001:1910: de gzhan dang gzhan du skye ba ni yongs su 'gyur ba yin no //
NK120(e)001:1912: don du sems byung sems pa la 'dod pa yin te /
NK120(e)001:1913: sems pa yid kyi las yin no //
NK120(e)001:1915: theg chen sems tsam pas ni 'chal tshul spong ba'i
NK120(e)001:1916: semas pa rgyun chagas sa bona dang bcas pa la
NK120(e)001:1918: de'ang sems rkyang pa la byas na rgyun med cing /
NK120(e)001:1919: bag chags tsam la byas na stong rgyu byung ba'i
NK120(e)001:1920: gnas skabs su'ang rjes su 'brang bas na mi stong
NK120(e)001:1922: dbu ma pas ni spong sems mtshungs ldan dang bcas pa la 'dod pa yin te /
NK120(e)001:1924: spong ba'i sems ni thob pa la //
NK120(e)001:1925: tshul khrims pha rol phyin par bshad //
NK120(e)001:1927: de lta na nang pa sangs rgyas pa ranga gi
NK120(e)001:1928: sde pa grub mtha' gonga 'oga la so so'i blo
NK120(e)001:1929: khyad kyis 'dod lugsa la mi 'dra bar mtho dman
NK120(e)001:1931: gnyis pa sdom pa'i dbye ba ni /
NK120(e)001:1932: dbye ba bsnyen gnas dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis //
NK120(e)001:1933: khyim pa'i phyogs yin dge tshul pha ma dang //
NK120(e)001:1934: dge slob ma dang dge slong pha ma lnga //
NK120(e)001:1935: rab byung la yin so thar ris brgyad po //
NK120(e)001:1936: rdzas su bsdu na bzhir 'dod mdzod kyi lugs //
NK120(e)001:1938: de ltar ngo bo bstan pa'i sdom pa de la rten gyi sgo nas dbye ba byas na /
NK120(e)001:1939: spyir rang rang gi sdom pa sgrub byed kyi rgyu
NK120(e)001:1940: phun sum tshogs pa la brten nas thob pa'i nges
NK120(e)001:1941: 'byung gi tshul khrims yin pa tsam du 'dra na'ang
NK120(e)001:1942: / bye brag rang rang gi mi mthun pa'i phyogs
NK120(e)001:1943: su gyur pa'i spang bya'i khyad par nyin zhag phrug
NK120(e)001:1944: gcig tu spang bya brgyad spong bar khas blangs pa
NK120(e)001:1945: bsnyen gansa yin te 'di la dus khrims zhes kyang
NK120(e)001:1946: / zer / 'di dge bsnyen gyis blangs na de'i
NK120(e)001:1947: gso sbyong du 'gro ba'i phyir gso sbyong zhes kyang
NK120(e)001:1948: / zer / grags / de bzhin du spang bya
NK120(e)001:1949: gcig nas lnga'i bar du ji srid 'tsho'i bar spong
NK120(e)001:1950: bar khas blangs pa dge bsnyen pha ma gnyisa te
NK120(e)001:1951: / zer / grags / / 'di la 'dul bar yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen las ma bshad kyang /
NK120(e)001:1952: mngon pa las ni skyabs gsum 'dzin pa sogs dbye ba mang /
NK120(e)001:1953: 'di gsum khyim pa'i phyogas kyi sdom pa yina no //
NK120(e)001:1954: yang spang bya bcu ji srid 'tsho'i bar du spong
NK120(e)001:1955: bar kha blangs pa dge tshul pha ma gnyis dang
NK120(e)001:1956: / de'i steng spang bya bcu gnyis lo gnyis la
NK120(e)001:1957: sogs par spong bar khas len pa dge slob ma
NK120(e)001:1958: / dang / spong bdun 'khor dang bcas pa ji
NK120(e)001:1959: srid 'tsho'i bar du spong bar khas len pa dge
NK120(e)001:1960: slonga pha ma gnyis kyi sdom pa ste /
NK120(e)001:1961: 'di lnga po ni raba tu byung ba'i phyogs kyi sdom pa la dbye ba yina te /
NK120(e)001:1962: de dag bsdoms pas so thara risa brgyad po rdzasa
NK120(e)001:1963: su bsdu na dge slong pha ma gnyis rdzas gcig
NK120(e)001:1964: / dge tshul pha ma gnyis dang dge tshul ma'i bye brag dge slob ma bcas rdzas gcig /
NK120(e)001:1965: dge bsnyen pha ma gnyis rdzas gcig ste de rnams
NK120(e)001:1966: mtshan phan tshun du gyur pas ming 'pho ba tsam
NK120(e)001:1967: las rdzas tha dad pa med pa'i phyir sdom rdzas
NK120(e)001:1968: gsum yin la / bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa dang bzhira bsdu bar 'doda pa mdzoda kyi lugas te /
NK120(e)001:1970: so sor thar ces bya rnam brgyad //
NK120(e)001:1971: rdzas su rnam pa bzhi yin no //
NK120(e)001:1972: mtshan las ming ni 'pho ba'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:1973: tha dad de dag 'gal ba med //
NK120(e)001:1975: gnyis pa thob byed cho ga'i lag len bye brag tu bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:1976: ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i tshul /
NK120(e)001:1977: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba'i thabs /
NK120(e)001:1978: sdom pa skye ba'i lus rten /
NK120(e)001:1980: de ltar bsrung ba'i phan yon no //
NK120(e)001:1981: dang po ma thob pa thob par byed pa'i tshul la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:1984: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:1985: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul la //
NK120(e)001:1988: de lta bu'i sdom pa de ni 'ga' zhig tsam
NK120(e)001:1989: ma gtogs chos nyid kyis thob pa ma yin cing
NK120(e)001:1990: / brda las byung ba la ltos dgos pas na /
NK120(e)001:1991: dang po bslab bya'i sdoma pa de nyid ma thoba pa thoba pa'i tshul la /
NK120(e)001:1992: tshegs chung ngus rdzogs pa sngon chog dang /
NK120(e)001:1993: tshegs dang bcas pas rdzogs pa da ltar gyi cho
NK120(e)001:1994: ga ste lena pa'i tshul gnyis su nges pa yin
NK120(e)001:1995: te zhes so // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:1998: dang po sngon cho ga ni /
NK120(e)001:2000: rang byung ye shes khog chud 'phrin gyis rdzogs //
NK120(e)001:2001: ston par khas blangs tshur shog gsol bzhi dang //
NK120(e)001:2002: dris pa'i lan ldon lci chos khas blangs sogs //
NK120(e)001:2003: gdul bya blo dag mkhan po 'phags pas yin //
NK120(e)001:2005: de la dang po ston pa sangs rgyas pa'i sngon du dang /
NK120(e)001:2007: de nas yun ring po ma lon pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2008: mya ngan las 'da' kha yan chod du byung ba la sngona gyi cho ga zhes bya ste /
NK120(e)001:2009: de ni nyan thos bye brag smra bas /
NK120(e)001:2010: rnam pa bcus bsnyen par rdzogs so zhes pa ltar dbye na bcu las /
NK120(e)001:2011: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas dang rang sangs rgyas gnyis zad
NK120(e)001:2012: pa shes pa dang mi skye ba shes pas byang
NK120(e)001:2013: chub brnyes pa'i tshe ranga byung gi 1dang /
NK120(e)001:2014: lnga sde bzang po mthong lam gyi ye shesa skyes pa khonga du chud pas 2dang /
NK120(e)001:2015: de gsum ni rang rgyud la ngang gis don dam pa'i dge slong skyes pas bsnyen par rdzogs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2016: mchod sbyin ma pha ma'i dbang du song ba la
NK120(e)001:2017: dge slong ma ut+pa las pho nya byas te dge
NK120(e)001:2020: khyod ni bdag gi ston pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2021: bdag ni khyod kyi nyan thos so //
NK120(e)001:2022: zhes ston para khasa blangsa pas 4dang /
NK120(e)001:2023: sh+aa ri'i bu sogs srid pa tha ma ba 'ga' zhig la /
NK120(e)001:2024: ston pas bu tshur shoga tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod
NK120(e)001:2025: cig ces gsungs pa tsam gyis bsnyen rdzogs kyi dngos
NK120(e)001:2027: dge 'dun gyi grangs yul dbus su bcu tshogs dang /
NK120(e)001:2028: mtha' 'khob tu lnga tshogs kyis gsola bzhi'i las kyis
NK120(e)001:2029: rab byung bsnyen rdzogs gcig char du byas pa 6dang
NK120(e)001:2031: gcig tu bde ba ni gang zhes drisa pa na /
NK120(e)001:2033: lam de la mkho ba ni gang zhes dris pa la /
NK120(e)001:2034: dad pa'o zhes pa'i lana ldona pa la thugs dgyes pa tsam gyis 7dang /
NK120(e)001:2035: sru skye rgu'i bdag mo dang /
NK120(e)001:2036: sh+aakya'i bu mo lnga brgyas lci chosa brgyad spong bar khasa blangas pas 8te /
NK120(e)001:2038: pha'i dge 'dun las bsnyen par rdzogs pa1 /
NK120(e)001:2039: zla ba phyed phyed nas pha'i dge slong las gdams sdom pa nod pa /
NK120(e)001:2041: pha'i dge slong yod sar dbyar khas blangs te gnas pa3 /
NK120(e)001:2042: gnyis ka'i tshogs las dgag dbye bya ba4 /
NK120(e)001:2043: dge slong gi tshul khrims 'chal ba mi brjod pa5 /
NK120(e)001:2044: dge slong la co 'dri ba sogs mi byed pa6 /
NK120(e)001:2045: dge slong gsar bu la'ang phyag 'tshal ba sogs gus pa bya ba7 /
NK120(e)001:2046: lci chos las 'das na pha'i dge 'dun las mgu ba spyad pa 8rnams so //
NK120(e)001:2047: sogs kyi sgras bzang sde'i tshogs drug cu skyabs gsum khas blangs pas bsnyen par 9rdzogs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2048: de la sngon chog btags pa ba dgu dang /
NK120(e)001:2049: dngos gnas pa gcig gsol bzhi'i las kyis rdzogs pa ste /
NK120(e)001:2050: de dag ni sngon gyi gdula bya rnams las nyon rnam smin gyi sgrib pa gsum shas chung zhing /
NK120(e)001:2051: shes rab rgyud dang dbang po smin pas blo daga pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2052: rdzogs byed kyi makhana po yang 'aphagas pa kho na'i khyad chos yina pas 10tshegs med pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2053: gnyis pa da ltar gyi cho ga la gsum /
NK120(e)001:2054: bsgrub bya gang zag gi mtshan nyid /
NK120(e)001:2055: sgrub byed mkhan slob sogs kyi mtshan nyid /
NK120(e)001:2056: ji ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul lo //
NK120(e)001:2057: dang po bsgrub bya gang zag gi mtshan nyid ni /
NK120(e)001:2058: da lta'i cho ga nges pa lnga bral zhing //
NK120(e)001:2059: ma ning la sogs skye ba'i bar chad dang //
NK120(e)001:2060: rgyal pos ma gnang la sogs gnas pa dang //
NK120(e)001:2061: bya rog skrod mi nus sogs khyad par dang //
NK120(e)001:2062: skra ser can sogs mdzes pa'i bar chad med //
NK120(e)001:2063: nges 'byung blo can skal bzang skyes bu de //
NK120(e)001:2065: da lta'i cho ga 'gal rkyen rang rang gi bslab
NK120(e)001:2066: bya la ltos nas nges pa lnga dang bral ba
NK120(e)001:2067: dge slong la dngos dang dge tshul la'ang cha 'dra
NK120(e)001:2069: mthun rkyen tshang ba'i yul 'dir bsrung gi gzhan du
NK120(e)001:2070: bsrung mi nus snyam pa lta bu yul nges pa
NK120(e)001:2071: dang / lo dang zla ba 'di tsam du bsrung
NK120(e)001:2072: gi de phan chod bsrung mi nus snyam pa lta
NK120(e)001:2074: 'thab rtsod kyi skabs ma gtogs gzhan du bsrung snyam pa lta bu tshe nges pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2075: dgra ma gtogs gzhan gyi srog mi gcod snyam pa lta bu sems can nges pa /
NK120(e)001:2076: bslab bya rags pa rnams las phra ba rnams la
NK120(e)001:2077: bslab mi nus snyam pa lta bu yan lag ngesa
NK120(e)001:2078: pa ste de lnga dang brala zhing /
NK120(e)001:2079: der ma zad 'gal rkyen bar chad kyi chos bzhi dang mi ldan pa zhig dgos te /
NK120(e)001:2080: ma ning la sogas pa 'og tu 'chad pa ltar
NK120(e)001:2081: sdom pa'i rten min pa rnams la ni sdom pa
NK120(e)001:2082: phog kyang mi skye bas na skye ba'i bar chada
NK120(e)001:2083: can dang / rgyal po dang pha mas ma gannga
NK120(e)001:2084: ba la sogas pa la sdom pa skye yang rang
NK120(e)001:2085: dbang du ma gyur pas 'bab dgos pa sogs yun
NK120(e)001:2086: ring por mi gansa pa'i bar chad dang /
NK120(e)001:2087: bya roga skrod mi nus pa'i byiis pa'am nad dang
NK120(e)001:2088: sdug bsngal gyis gzir ba sogas la sdom pa skye
NK120(e)001:2089: gnas gnyis ka'i rten du rung yang bslab pa la
NK120(e)001:2090: sbyor mi bzod pas yon tan gong nas gong du
NK120(e)001:2091: khyad para du 'gyur mi nus pa'i bar chad dang
NK120(e)001:2092: / skra sera can sogs kha dog la skyon chags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2093: lag zlum sogs lus byad mi sdug pa dbyibs la skyon chags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2094: bshan pa sogas rigs la skyon chags pa ste de
NK120(e)001:2095: dag la sdom pa skye gnas khyad par du 'gyur
NK120(e)001:2096: ba gsum ka rung yang lus byad mi sdug pa
NK120(e)001:2097: sogs kyi rkyen gyis khyim pa rnams bstan pa la
NK120(e)001:2098: ma dad pa'i rgyu byed pa'i phyir na mdzesa pa'i
NK120(e)001:2099: bar chada de rnams meda pa dgos la /
NK120(e)001:2100: 'on kyang phyi ma gnyis po 'di bstan pa la
NK120(e)001:2101: phan pa sogs dgos pa khyad par can yod na
NK120(e)001:2102: sdom pa skye la nyes byas tsam las dgag bya
NK120(e)001:2104: de lta na dgag phyogs nas nges pa lnga dang
NK120(e)001:2105: bral zhing bar chad bzhi dang mi ldan pa dang
NK120(e)001:2106: / sgrub phyogs nas mthun rkyen phun sum tshogs pa lnga dang ldan pa ste /
NK120(e)001:2107: rgyud tshogs su ma tshang zhing sdom ro med pa /
NK120(e)001:2109: shes pa rang bzhin du gnas pa /
NK120(e)001:2110: chos gos gsum dang lhung bzed tshang ba /
NK120(e)001:2111: thob mtshams sogs kyi don go zhing brda' 'phrod pa bcas gzhir bzhag /
NK120(e)001:2112: khyad par 'jigs skyob dang legs smon tsam ma yin
NK120(e)001:2113: par ngesa par 'byunga ba'i blos myang 'das gsum gang
NK120(e)001:2114: rung don du gnyer ba'i blo cana skala pa bazanga
NK120(e)001:2115: po'i skyesa bu de lta bu ni snod dang ldan
NK120(e)001:2116: pa yin no // gnyis pa sgrub byed mkhan slob sogs kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK120(e)001:2117: legs gsungs 'dul ba rgya mtsho mtha' dag dang //
NK120(e)001:2118: brgya rtsa gcig pa'i las phran la byang ba'i //
NK120(e)001:2121: sgrub par byed pa po mkhan slob dge 'dun rnams kyang kha skong gi chos bcu gsum tshang ba /
NK120(e)001:2122: mkhas pa'i yon tan sde snod gsum spyi dang khyad
NK120(e)001:2123: par du legas par gsungas pa lung bzhis bsdus pa'i
NK120(e)001:2124: 'dula ba rgya mtsho matha'a daga gi tshig don ma
NK120(e)001:2125: lus pa khong du chud pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2126: de las kyang las brgya rtsa gciga pa'i lasa phrana
NK120(e)001:2127: re re bzhin la tshig phyed kyang ma 'khrul bar
NK120(e)001:2128: blo thog nas thon cing lag len sogs shig tu
NK120(e)001:2129: byang ba / btsun pa'i yon tan tshul khrims rnam par dag pa /
NK120(e)001:2130: bshags sdom byin rlabs tshun chad kyis nyes byas phra ba tsam gyis kyang ma gos pa /
NK120(e)001:2131: dmigs bsal bsgrub bya'i ngos nas mthong thos dogs gsum gyi skyon med pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2132: khyad par bsnyen par rdzogs nas lo bcu lon cing
NK120(e)001:2133: brtan mkhas kyi yon tan phul du byung ba'i makhana
NK120(e)001:2134: po dang las slob dag yul dbus matha'i khyad par
NK120(e)001:2135: gyis dge 'dun bcu tshogs sam lnga tshogs dang bacasa
NK120(e)001:2136: pasa so // gsum pa ji ltar bsgrub pa'i tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:2138: snga ma ma byas rdzogs pa'ang mdo sder snang //
NK120(e)001:2139: thob mtshams brjod pa gsum gyi tha mar 'dod //
NK120(e)001:2141: de lta bu'i dge 'dun gyi dbus su dge bsnyen /
NK120(e)001:2143: dge slong ste bslab tshigs gsum po rima par 'bogs
NK120(e)001:2144: pa'i cho ga bzhina du bsnyen para rdzogas par bya
NK120(e)001:2145: ba yin la / gal te bslab tshigs snga ma
NK120(e)001:2146: gnyis ma byasa par bsnyen par rdzogas pa'ang drin lan
NK120(e)001:2147: bsab pa'i mdo sdera snang ste /
NK120(e)001:2150: gal te khyim pa khrims lnga ma nos par thal byung du khrims bcu nos na /
NK120(e)001:2153: dus gcig tu dge bsnyen gyi khrims dang dge sbyong gi khrims rnam pa gnyis thob bo //
NK120(e)001:2154: gal te khrims lnga yang ma nos /
NK120(e)001:2155: khrims bcu yang ma nos par thal byung du khrims
NK120(e)001:2156: rdzogs par nos na'ang dus gcig tu khrims gsum char
NK120(e)001:2160: khyim pa rab tu ma byung ba zhig bsnyen par rdzogs par bgyi na bsnyen par rdzogs zhes bagyi'am /
NK120(e)001:2162: nye bar 'khor bsnyen par rdzogs zhes bya'o //
NK120(e)001:2164: 'di ni tshig phyi ma blangs pas snga ma zhar la thob pa'i don du snang mod /
NK120(e)001:2165: 'on kyang 'dul ba rang las sdom pa skye la nyes byas su 'gyur zhes bshad do //
NK120(e)001:2166: de ltar nod pa'i sdom pa de bsgrub bya'i rgyud
NK120(e)001:2167: la thoba pa'i mtshamsa ni dge 'dun gyis gsol ba
NK120(e)001:2168: sngon du 'gro bas las brjod pa lan gsuma gyi
NK120(e)001:2169: tha ma'i bya ba brjod pa rdzogs ma thag pa
NK120(e)001:2170: der sdom pa skye bar 'doda pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:2171: gnyis pa thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba'i thabs la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2174: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2175: bar du thob pa mi nyams bsrung ba la //
NK120(e)001:2177: de ltar sdom pa de nyid thob pa tsam gyis mi chog gi /
NK120(e)001:2178: bar du thob zin pa de nyid mi nyamsa par tshul bzhin bsrung dgos te /
NK120(e)001:2179: ma bsrung na nyes dmigs chen po dang /
NK120(e)001:2180: bsrung na phan yon chen po dang ldan pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:2181: dge slong la rab tu gces pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)001:2182: la la'i tshul khrims bde ba ste //
NK120(e)001:2183: la la'i tshul khrims sdug bsngal yin //
NK120(e)001:2184: tshul khrims ldan pa bde ba ste //
NK120(e)001:2185: tshul khrims 'chal pa sdug bsngal yin //
NK120(e)001:2187: des na bsrunga ba'i thabs su dgag sgrub kyi bslab
NK120(e)001:2188: bya gnyis su shes nas spang blang tshul bzhin du
NK120(e)001:2190: dang po dgag phyogs kyi bslab bya la slob pa'i rnam grangs 'di ltar ro zhes so //
NK120(e)001:2191: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2192: dngos bstan blang dor gyi bslab bya rgyas par bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:2193: shugs bstan de'i rung mthun bsdus te bstan pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2194: dang po dngos bstan blang dor gyi bslab bya rgyas par bshad pa la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2195: khyim pa'i phyogs kyi bslab bya dang /
NK120(e)001:2196: rab byung gi phyogs kyi bslab bya'o //
NK120(e)001:2197: dang po khyim pa'i phyogs kyi bslab bya la'ang gsum /
NK120(e)001:2202: mchog gsum so so'i thun mong ma yin pa'i bslab bya dang /
NK120(e)001:2203: gsum ka'i thun mong gi bslab bya'o //
NK120(e)001:2204: dang po mchog gsum so so'i thun mong ma yin pa'i bslab bya ni /
NK120(e)001:2205: bslab bya skyabs 'gro thun mong min gsum ni //
NK120(e)001:2206: skyabs gzhan mi 'tshol sems can 'tshe ba spongs //
NK120(e)001:2207: mu stegs mi 'grogs so sor gus bskyed do //
NK120(e)001:2209: thog ma nyid du bslab par bya ba'i gnas dkon
NK120(e)001:2210: mchog gsum la skyabsa su 'gro ba'i gang zag gis
NK120(e)001:2211: thuna monga mina pa'i bslab bya gsuma ni rim pa
NK120(e)001:2212: bzhin / sangs rgyas la skyabs su song nas 'jig
NK120(e)001:2213: rten pa'i lha sogs skyabsa gnas gazhana mi 'tshola ba
NK120(e)001:2214: bzhin / dang / chos la skyabs su song nas
NK120(e)001:2215: semas can la gnod pa'i sems kyi 'tshe ba'i rigs
NK120(e)001:2216: bzhin / dang / sponga ba dang / dge 'dun
NK120(e)001:2217: la skyabs su song nas grogs mu stegas can nam
NK120(e)001:2218: de'i phyogs mthun lta log can rnams dang mi 'grogas
NK120(e)001:2219: pa bcas dgag bya gsum ste /
NK120(e)001:2221: gang zhig sangs rgyas skyabs 'gro ba //
NK120(e)001:2222: de ni yang dag dge bsnyen te //
NK120(e)001:2223: nam du'ang lha ni gzhan dag la //
NK120(e)001:2224: skyabs su 'gro ba ma yin no //
NK120(e)001:2225: dam pa'i chos la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK120(e)001:2226: 'tshe zhing gnod pa'i sems dang bral //
NK120(e)001:2228: mu stegs can dang 'grogs mi bya //
NK120(e)001:2230: sangs rgyas kyi sku'i rten dang s+aats+tsha'i chag dum tsam tshun dang /
NK120(e)001:2231: chos kyi rten gsung rab yig 'bru gcig tshun dang /
NK120(e)001:2232: dge 'dun gyi gzugs lhan pa ser po btab pa
NK120(e)001:2233: yan chad la so sora dkon mchog de dang de'i
NK120(e)001:2234: 'du shes bzhag nas gusa pa bskyed do //
NK120(e)001:2235: de rnams ni sgrub pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK120(e)001:2236: gnyis pa gsum ka'i thun mong gi bslab bya ni /
NK120(e)001:2237: srog dang bya dgar dkon mchog gsum mi spang //
NK120(e)001:2238: dgos gal che yang thabs gzhan mi 'tshol zhing //
NK120(e)001:2239: dus mchod mi bcag rang gzhan skyabs 'gror 'god //
NK120(e)001:2240: gar 'gro'i phyogs kyi sangs rgyas la phyag 'tshal //
NK120(e)001:2241: lnga rnams thun mong bslab byar jo bos bzhed //
NK120(e)001:2243: rang gi sroga gi phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:2244: rgyal srid la sogs pa'i bya dag'a chen po'i phyir yang dkona mchoga gsuma mi sponga pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2245: dgosa gala ji ltar che yang dkon mchog gsum la
NK120(e)001:2246: blo gtod pa las 'jig rten pa'i thabas gazhana mi
NK120(e)001:2247: 'tshola zhing / rtag tu dkon mchog gsum gyi yon
NK120(e)001:2248: tan dran pas dus kyi mchoda pa mi bacaga pa
NK120(e)001:2249: 'tshola zhing / dang / phan yon shes pas ranga
NK120(e)001:2250: skyabs su 'gro zhing gazhana rnams kyang skyabsa su 'gro
NK120(e)001:2252: rang nyid gara 'gro na'ang de'i phyogsa kyi sangsa rgyas
NK120(e)001:2253: yid la bya zhing sku gzugs sogs la phyag 'atshala
NK120(e)001:2254: ba ste / de lnga po rnams ni dkon mchog
NK120(e)001:2255: gsum po thuna monga gi bslab bya yin par jo
NK120(e)001:2256: bo rjes bzheda par gsungs so //
NK120(e)001:2257: gnyis pa bsnyen gnas kyi bslab bya la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2258: dus khrims kyi bslab bya dngos bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:2259: de gtan khrims su byin na go mi'i dge bsnyen du 'gyur tshul lo //
NK120(e)001:2260: dang po dus khrims kyi bslab bya dngos bshad pa ni //
NK120(e)001:2261: rtsa bzhi spong ba tshul khrims yan lag yin //
NK120(e)001:2262: chang spong bag yod yan lag mal che mtho //
NK120(e)001:2263: gar phreng la sogs phyi dro'i kha zas gsum //
NK120(e)001:2264: brtul zhugs yan lag bsnyen gnas sdom pa yin //
NK120(e)001:2265: yan lag 'di brgyad gtan du ma yin pas //
NK120(e)001:2266: yon tan brten min de phyir so thar ni //
NK120(e)001:2267: mtshan nyid ldan pa ris bdun kho na yin //
NK120(e)001:2272: rdzun smra ba ste rtsa ba bzhi phyogs mthun dang
NK120(e)001:2273: bcas pa sponga ba tshul khrims brtan par byed pa'i
NK120(e)001:2275: chang btung ba spong ba baga yoda gong 'phel du byed pa'i yan lag dang /
NK120(e)001:2276: mala chena po dang mthona po gnyis dang /
NK120(e)001:2278: rgyan phreng 'dogs pa la sogas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2279: dus min pa phyi dro'i kha zasa bcas de gsuma
NK120(e)001:2280: spong ba brtul zhugsa dag par byed pa'i yan lag
NK120(e)001:2281: ste / 'di brgyad po bsrung pa ni bsnyen gansa kyi sdoma pa yina te /
NK120(e)001:2283: tshul khrims yan lag bag yod pa'i //
NK120(e)001:2284: yan lag brtul zhugs yan lag ste //
NK120(e)001:2285: bzhi gcig de bzhin gsum rim bzhin //
NK120(e)001:2286: zhes yan lag gi nges pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2287: gzhan la bsnyen gnas yod mod kyi //
NK120(e)001:2288: skyabs su ma song ba la med //
NK120(e)001:2289: ces rten gyi nges pa bstan pa bzhin dang /
NK120(e)001:2292: bdag la 'di yis mi gnod ces //
NK120(e)001:2293: blo ldan chang la yid mi rton //
NK120(e)001:2294: myong tshe bsil yang rnam smin tsha //
NK120(e)001:2295: chang gis dmyal bar 'gro bar byed //
NK120(e)001:2297: de ltar yan lag 'di brgyad po nyin zhag phrug
NK120(e)001:2298: gcig gi dus khrims las gatana du bcas pa'i khrims
NK120(e)001:2300: sdom pa gong ma rnams kyi yona tana skye ba'i
NK120(e)001:2301: rten mina pas de'i phyir na gong ma'i yon tan
NK120(e)001:2302: gyi rten du gyur pa so thara ni matshana nyid
NK120(e)001:2303: dang ldana pa risa bduna kho na yina par nges
NK120(e)001:2305: so sor thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK120(e)001:2306: rtag tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK120(e)001:2307: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yi //
NK120(e)001:2308: skal pa yod kyi gzhan du min //
NK120(e)001:2310: gnyis pa de nyid gtan khrims su byin na go m+ai'i dge bsnyen du 'gyur tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:2311: 'di brgyad ji srid 'tsho yi bar bsrung na //
NK120(e)001:2312: go m+ai'i dge bsnyen yin kyang yod smra'i min //
NK120(e)001:2313: gnas brtan sde pa'i lugs su dbyig gnyen bzhed //
NK120(e)001:2315: gal te yan lag 'di brgyad po ji srid 'tsho yi bar du khas blangs nas bsrunga na /
NK120(e)001:2316: slob dpon tsan+d+ra pas 'di ltar blangs pas tsan+d+ra go
NK120(e)001:2317: m+ai zhes grags pa ltar go m+ai'i dge bsnyen yin
NK120(e)001:2318: kyang / gzhi thams cad yod par smra ba'i lugs kyi 'dul ba las bshad pa mina mod kyang /
NK120(e)001:2319: 'phags pa gnas brtan sde pa'i lugas su yin par slob dpon dbyig gnyen gyis bzheda de /
NK120(e)001:2321: go m+ai'i dge bsnyen zhes bya ba 'di ni 'phags
NK120(e)001:2322: pa gnas brtan sde pa'i man ngag brgyud pa las
NK120(e)001:2323: thos kyi bde bar gshegs pas gsungs pa ni ma
NK120(e)001:2325: 'on kyang theg chen gyi sde snod las 'byung ste /
NK120(e)001:2326: rgyal bu snying rje cher sems kyis 'di ltar khas
NK120(e)001:2327: blangs par dkon mchog brtsegs pa las gsungs pa'i phyir
NK120(e)001:2328: ro // gsum pa dge bsnyen gyi bslab bya la gsum /
NK120(e)001:2329: dge bsnyen gyi spang bya lnga ngos bzung ba /
NK120(e)001:2330: de bsrung tshul gyi grangs las dge bsnyen gyi dbye ba bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:2331: phyogs mthun gyi bslab bya bstan pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2332: dang po dge bsnyen gyi spang bya ngos bzung ba ni /
NK120(e)001:2333: gsod rku rdzun smra 'dod pas log par g.yem //
NK120(e)001:2334: myos 'gyur spong rnams dge bsnyen sdom pa ste //
NK120(e)001:2336: de la bsrung bya ni gsoda pa ste srog gcod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2337: rku ba ste ma byin pa len pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2338: mi'i chos bla ma'i rdzun smra ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2339: 'dod pasa log par g.yema pa ste rtsa ba bzhi yin cing /
NK120(e)001:2340: 'di dag la yul gyi yan lag tu mi yin pa dgos te /
NK120(e)001:2341: de ma tshang na rtsa bar gtogs pa'i nyes pa
NK120(e)001:2342: tsam du zad kyi rtsa ba dngos ma yin pas
NK120(e)001:2343: sdom pa nyams par mi 'gyur la /
NK120(e)001:2344: 'dir mi tshangs spyod mi 'jog par 'dod log 'jog
NK120(e)001:2345: pa ni khyim pas bsrung sla ba la sogs pa'i
NK120(e)001:2347: log g.yem shin tu dmad phyir dang //
NK120(e)001:2348: sla phyir mi byed thob phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:2350: de dag gi yan lag tu myos 'gyur spong ba
NK120(e)001:2351: ste de ma spang na bslab pa gzhan bsrung mi
NK120(e)001:2352: nus pa'i phyir bslab gzhi lnga po de rnams ni
NK120(e)001:2353: dge bsnyen gyi sdoma pa ste /
NK120(e)001:2354: dang po bzhi rtsa ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2355: phyi ma gcig yan lag go //
NK120(e)001:2356: gnyis pa de bsrung tshul gyi grangs las dge bsnyen gyi dbye ba bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2357: nyan thos bye brag smra ba'i lugs dang /
NK120(e)001:2359: dang po nyan thos bye brag smra ba'i lugs ni /
NK120(e)001:2360: gang 'dod khas len grangs ltar sna gcig spyod //
NK120(e)001:2361: sna 'ga' phal cher spyod dang yongs rdzogs spyod //
NK120(e)001:2362: gcig gnyis gsum dang lnga spong /
NK120(e)001:2364: rang gi ganga bsrung 'doda pa ltar khasa lena pa'i
NK120(e)001:2365: grangs ji lta bar srog gcod pa tsam spong ba
NK120(e)001:2366: lta bu sna gciga spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2367: de'i steng du ma byin len tsam spong ba lta bu sna 'ag'a spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2368: de gnyis kyi steng du rdzun spong ba lta bu phala chera spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2369: de gsum gyi steng du 'dod log chang dang bcas pa spong ba yongas rdzogas spyod pa ste /
NK120(e)001:2370: de dag rim bzhin spang bya gciga dang /
NK120(e)001:2374: de'ang dang po yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi bslab pa
NK120(e)001:2375: nod nas phyis sna gcig sogs gang 'dod ltar bsrung
NK120(e)001:2376: ba la de dag spyod ces 'dod do //
NK120(e)001:2377: gnyis pa mdo sde pa'i lugs ni /
NK120(e)001:2379: mi tshangs spyod spong tshangs spyod dge bsnyen no //
NK120(e)001:2380: 'di dang go m+ai gnyis ni khyim pa dang //
NK120(e)001:2381: rab byung gnyis ka min zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK120(e)001:2383: gong gi bslab gzhi lnga po de yi stenga du
NK120(e)001:2384: mi tshangas par spyod pa sponga ba ni tshangas spyod
NK120(e)001:2385: dge bsnyen te / ji skad du /
NK120(e)001:2386: rgyan gyis brgyan par byas kyang chos spyod la //
NK120(e)001:2387: zhes sogs kyis bstan par mdo sde pas 'dod pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:2388: 'di dang go mi'i dge bsnyen gnyis ni khyim thabs
NK120(e)001:2389: spangs pas 'dod pa 'khrig bcas kyi khyima pa dang
NK120(e)001:2390: / ngur smrig sogs kyi rtags ma blangs pas raba
NK120(e)001:2391: byung gnyis ka mina no zhesa makhasa pa rnamas bzheda
NK120(e)001:2393: 'di gnyis kyi tshul cho 'phrul bstan pa'i mdo las gsal bar gsungs te /
NK120(e)001:2395: rab byung yon tan du ma ldan pa zhes //
NK120(e)001:2396: de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyis basngagasa mod kyi //
NK120(e)001:2397: sems can kun la snying rjer gyur pas na //
NK120(e)001:2398: 'gro la phan phyir bdag gis rgyal srid sgrub //
NK120(e)001:2399: ji srid 'tsho'i bar tshangs par spyod byed cing //
NK120(e)001:2400: gso sbyong yan lag brgyad pa'ang blang bar bgyi //
NK120(e)001:2402: gsum pa phyogs mthun gyi bslab bya bstan pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2404: sngags pa khyim pas kyang bslab dgos par ga dmas pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2406: mi dge lhag drug phyogs mthun spang bya dang //
NK120(e)001:2408: mi dge ba bcu las lus kyi las gsum brjod ma thag pa ltar dang /
NK120(e)001:2409: ngag gi las rdzun dor bas lhag ma phra ma /
NK120(e)001:2414: log lta gsum ste druga dang /
NK120(e)001:2415: rtsa ba bzhi'i phyogsa su mthuna pa dud 'gro gsod
NK120(e)001:2416: pa la sogs pa'i spang bya rnams ni sdom pa
NK120(e)001:2417: mi gtong yang 'gyod sdom dang bcas pa'i phyir bcos
NK120(e)001:2418: par bya dgos pa'i bslab bya yin no //
NK120(e)001:2419: gnyis pa sngags pa khyim pas kyang bslab dgos par gdams pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2420: dge bsnyen sdom ldan rig pa 'dzin pas kyang //
NK120(e)001:2421: rab byung rtags dang cho ga ma gtogs pa //
NK120(e)001:2422: lhag rnams nyams su len par dpung bzang bshad //
NK120(e)001:2424: dge bsnyen gyi sdoma pa dang ldana pa'i khyim pa
NK120(e)001:2425: sngags lam la zhugs pa'i riga pa 'dzina pa des
NK120(e)001:2426: kyanga / ngur smrig bgo ba dang lhung bzed 'chang
NK120(e)001:2427: ba dang skra 'dreg pa sogs raba byung ba'i rtagsa
NK120(e)001:2428: kyanga / rnams dang / las kyi cho ga dang
NK120(e)001:2429: bcas rkyang 'ga' zhig ma gtogas pa'i lhag ma rnams
NK120(e)001:2430: 'dul ba las ji ltar 'byung ba bzhin du nyamas
NK120(e)001:2431: su lena dgos para dpunga bazanga las /
NK120(e)001:2432: rgyal ba ngas gsungs so sor thar pa yi //
NK120(e)001:2433: tshul khrims rnam dag 'dul ba ma lus las //
NK120(e)001:2434: sngags pa khyim pas rtags dang cho ga spangs //
NK120(e)001:2435: lhag ma rnams ni nyams su blang bar bya //
NK120(e)001:2436: zhes bshad pa'i phyir sngags pa rab byung gis ni lta smos kyang ci 'tshal lo //
NK120(e)001:2437: gnyis pa rab byung phyogs kyi bslab bya bstan pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:2438: dge tshul pha ma'i bslab bya bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:2439: dge slob ma'i bslab bya bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:2440: dge slong pha ma'i bslab bya bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2441: dang po dge tshul gyi bslab bya bshad pa la'ang gsum /
NK120(e)001:2443: phyogs mthun bsdam bya'i nyes byas /
NK120(e)001:2444: bar ma rab byung gi dus su blang ba las 'das pa'i phyogs mthun no //
NK120(e)001:2445: dang po dge tshul gyi blang 'das dngos la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2447: yan lag gi chos drug go //
NK120(e)001:2448: dang po rtsa ba'i chos bzhi ni /
NK120(e)001:2449: srog gcod rku dang mi tshangs spyod dang rdzun //
NK120(e)001:2451: mi'am mir chags pa'i sroga gcoda pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2452: rin thang tshang ba'i dngos po rku ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2453: lam gsum gang rung la brten nas mi tshangas par spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2454: mi'i chos bla ma'i rdzuna smra ba ste bzhi po 'di bsrung na tshul khrims su 'gyur zhing /
NK120(e)001:2455: ma bsrung na khrims 'chal du 'gyur bas na rtsa ba zhes bya ste /
NK120(e)001:2456: de'ang 'chab med gsor rung dang 'chab bcas gsor mi rung ba dge slong dang 'dra ste /
NK120(e)001:2458: mi gsod la sogs bzhi rnams kyis //
NK120(e)001:2459: dge tshul las ni nyams gyur na //
NK120(e)001:2460: dge slong bzhin du dge tshul la'ang //
NK120(e)001:2461: phyi nas sdom skye'i skal ba med //
NK120(e)001:2463: gnyis pa yan lag gi chos drug ni /
NK120(e)001:2464: chang 'thung gar sogs phreng sogs mal che mtho //
NK120(e)001:2465: phyi dro'i kha zas gser dngul spong ba ste //
NK120(e)001:2466: zhum pa spangs phyir rags pa bcur dril gsungs //
NK120(e)001:2468: myos par 'gyur ba'i changa 'thunga ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2469: rgod bag gis rang gar ngag nas glu len cing
NK120(e)001:2470: lus kyis gara bsgyur ba rol mo'i rigs 'bud cing
NK120(e)001:2471: dkrol ba sogas rtsed mo'i rigs byed gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:2472: 'phyor sgeg gi rna cha gdu bu la sogs rgyan 'dogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2473: me tog dang rin po che sogs kyi phrenga bas spras pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2474: sman spos sogs lus la dri bzang pos bgos te
NK120(e)001:2475: kha dog 'chang ba sogas rgyan gyi rigs byed gsum
NK120(e)001:2476: dang / gser dngul za 'og sogs rgyu rin thang can gyi mala chen po dang /
NK120(e)001:2477: rin thang chung yang shing khri khru gang las lhag
NK120(e)001:2478: pa'i mtho ba la skabs ma yin par 'dug pa
NK120(e)001:2479: dang / rang gling gi nyi ma phyed yol zin
NK120(e)001:2480: nas phyi dro'i dus su kha zasa za ba dang
NK120(e)001:2481: dang / / reg pa tsam rung yang chags sred
NK120(e)001:2482: kyis gsera dngula phug nor du 'chang ba sponga ba
NK120(e)001:2483: dang / / ste / drug po la yan lag ces rtsa ba bsrung ba'i thabs yin cing /
NK120(e)001:2484: de'ang chang ni bag yod kyi yan lag dang /
NK120(e)001:2485: gzhan lnga brtul zhugs kyi yan lag go //
NK120(e)001:2486: de'ang bri dza'i bu bzhin du bslab gzhi mang po
NK120(e)001:2487: thos pas sems zhuma ste bslab pa len pa las
NK120(e)001:2488: ldog pa spanga ba'i phyir du ragas pa bcu po
NK120(e)001:2489: 'dir dril nas gsungas pa yin la /
NK120(e)001:2490: de rnams char gtog dasanga bcas pa'i sgo nas dbye na blang 'das so gsum du 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:2492: rtsa bzhi gsod gsum gzhi med nas //
NK120(e)001:2493: sun 'byin bar lnga shes bzhin bshes //
NK120(e)001:2494: 'phya dang zas cung lhag mas skur //
NK120(e)001:2496: gar gsum phreng gsum mal che mtho //
NK120(e)001:2497: dus min rin chen bar ma gsum //
NK120(e)001:2498: de ltar sum cu rtsa gsum mo //
NK120(e)001:2499: zhes pas rtsa ba bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:2500: srog gcod kyi pham 'dra'i char gtogs dud 'gro gsod pa /
NK120(e)001:2501: srog chags dang bcas pa'i r+ts+wa chur 'debs pa /
NK120(e)001:2502: srog chags dang bcas pa'i chur spyod pa ste gsod pa gsum /
NK120(e)001:2503: rdzun gyi char gtogs gzhi med pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2504: bag tsam ste pham pa'i kur 'debs gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2508: shes bzhin du rdzun smra ba /
NK120(e)001:2511: zas cung zad kyi phyir chos ston zhes skur pa 'debs pa /
NK120(e)001:2514: lhag por len phyir 'bras chen 'geb pa ste bcu gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2515: de ltar na rtsa ba bzhi dang de'i char gtogs pa bco lnga bcas bsdoms pas bcu dgu /
NK120(e)001:2521: dri'i kha dog 'chang ba ste gsum rnams bsdoms pas drug /
NK120(e)001:2525: gser dngul len pa rnams bsnan pas sum cu /
NK120(e)001:2526: 'og nas 'byung ba'i nyams pa gsum dang bcas pas
NK120(e)001:2527: dge tshul gyi blang 'das sum cu rtsa gsum yin
NK120(e)001:2528: no // gnyis pa phyogs mthun bsdam bya'i nyes byas ni /
NK120(e)001:2529: chos gos lhung bzed 'chang ba 'bral ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2530: sa brko rin chen reg dang me la reg /
NK120(e)001:2531: btang nas za dang shing 'dzeg shing gcod dang /
NK120(e)001:2532: byin len r+ts+wa sngon khrod du mi gtsang 'dor //
NK120(e)001:2533: gsog 'jog za dang sa bon 'joms pa rnams //
NK120(e)001:2534: gnang ba'i nyes med bcu gsum ma gtogs pa //
NK120(e)001:2535: dge slong ji zhin spang blang mtha' dag gcig /'chang
NK120(e)001:2536: ba'i zlar bsdu gos rgyu zla bar 'jog /'bral ba'i
NK120(e)001:2537: zlar bsdu dgon pa'i 'bral spang byed //
NK120(e)001:2538: gsog 'jog zlar bsdu gsog 'jog byed pa'ang gnang //
NK120(e)001:2540: chos gosa lhag por 'chang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2544: rina chena gyi rigs la rega pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2546: blos btang nas yang za ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2547: shinga la mi gang las mthor 'dzegas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2548: shinga sogs skye ba gcod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2549: byin lena ma byas par za ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2550: r+ts+wa sngona gyi khrod du mi ga tsanga ba 'dora ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2551: gsoga 'joga tu song ba za ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2552: rung ba ma byas bar sa bona 'jomas pa rnamas
NK120(e)001:2553: ni dge tshul rnams la ston pas rjes su gannga
NK120(e)001:2554: ba'i nyesa meda bcu gsuma pa ste /
NK120(e)001:2555: 'di rnams bstan bcos byed brag bshad pa las gsungs la /
NK120(e)001:2556: de rnams ma gtogsa pa dge slong ji lta ba
NK120(e)001:2557: bzhina du spanga bya dang blang bya mtha' daga thun
NK120(e)001:2558: mong pa yin pas gciga tu 'gyur mod /
NK120(e)001:2559: 'on te dge tshul gyi skabs 'dir bshags yul la
NK120(e)001:2560: mi ltos par yid kyis bsdoms pa tsam gyis 'dag
NK120(e)001:2561: go // de'i steng du gos lhag por 'achanga ba'i
NK120(e)001:2562: zlar bsdu ba gosa rgyu zla ba las lhag par
NK120(e)001:2563: go // 'joga pa dang / gos dang 'brala ba'i
NK120(e)001:2564: zlar bsdu ba 'jigs pa dang bral yang dgona pa'i
NK120(e)001:2565: gnas su 'brala spanga byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2566: gsoga 'joga za ba'i zlar bsdu ba 'tsho ba tsam
NK120(e)001:2567: gyi phyir gsoga 'joga byed pa'ang gannga ba yin la
NK120(e)001:2568: / de gsum gyi steng du bod kyi 'dul 'dzin rnams kyis rung mthun bsdu ba la /
NK120(e)001:2570: ma smras 'dun bsgyur ma rdzogs nyal //
NK120(e)001:2571: zhes pa ltar gsum bsnan pas nyes med bcu dgur 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:2572: gsum pa bar ma rab byung gi dus su blangs pa las 'das pa'i phyogs mthun ni /
NK120(e)001:2573: khyim rtags spong nyams rab byung rtags len nyams //
NK120(e)001:2574: brnyas pas mkhan por nyams te nyams pa gsum //
NK120(e)001:2575: spang ba dge tshul sdom pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK120(e)001:2577: dge tshul gyis gos dkar po sbu gu can lta
NK120(e)001:2578: bu bsam ma thag pas nyin gcig tsam gyon na
NK120(e)001:2579: khyim pa'i rtag sponga ba las nyamsa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2580: chos gos sogs raba byung gi rtags lena pa las nyamsa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2581: bslab pa la ma gus shing brnyas pasa makhana por gsol ba btab pa las nyamsa pa ste /
NK120(e)001:2582: nyamsa pa gsum po 'di bar ma rab byung gi
NK120(e)001:2583: sdom pa gtong byed dngos dang dge tshul gyi blangs
NK120(e)001:2584: 'das so // de ltar nyams pa gsum po dang
NK120(e)001:2585: bcas pa spang bar bya ba ni dge tshul pha
NK120(e)001:2586: ma gnyis kyi sdoma pa'i bslab par bya pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2587: gnyis pa dge slob ma'i bslab bya la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2590: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2591: dge slob ma ni dge tshul thob pa'i steng //
NK120(e)001:2593: dge sloba ma ni dge tshul ma'i bslab gzhi bcu
NK120(e)001:2594: thoba pa'i stengdu dge slob ma'i sdom pa blangs nas
NK120(e)001:2595: lo gnyis la de'i bslab bya la slob pa ste
NK120(e)001:2596: / de yang dge tshul ma'i pham 'dra'i nyes byas
NK120(e)001:2597: ma byung na gsham gsal rtsa ba'i chos drug lta
NK120(e)001:2598: bu byung yang de la bslab pa 'khrugs pa zhes
NK120(e)001:2599: slar yang sdom pa nod de lo gnyis la bslab
NK120(e)001:2601: de dge slob ma'i sdom pa gtong byed dngos ma yin no //
NK120(e)001:2602: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2604: rjes mthun gyi chos drug go //
NK120(e)001:2605: dang po rtsa ba'i chos drug ni /
NK120(e)001:2606: gcig 'gro chur rkyal skyes reg lhan gcig 'dug /
NK120(e)001:2607: smyan bya nyes 'chab rtsa ba'i chos drug go //
NK120(e)001:2609: lam du rang gciga pur 'gro ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2611: skyes pa'i lus la rega pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2612: de dang lhan gciga tu 'duga pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2613: pho mo phan tshun smyan bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2614: zla mo'i nyes pa 'achaba pa bcas spong ba ni rtsa ba'i chosa drug go //
NK120(e)001:2615: gnyis pa rjes mthun gyi chos drug ni /
NK120(e)001:2616: gser bzung 'dom spu 'dreg dang sa brko spang //
NK120(e)001:2617: byin len med dang gsog 'jog byas mi za //
NK120(e)001:2618: r+ts+wa sngon mi gcod 'di dag rjes mthun drug /
NK120(e)001:2620: gsera la sogs pa'i rin po che bzunga ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2622: sa brko ba rnams spanga ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2623: zas byin lena meda par za ba spang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2624: gsoga 'joga byas te mi za ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2625: r+ts+wa sngona po mi gcod pa ste 'di daga rnams ni rjesa su mthuna pa'i chos druga go //
NK120(e)001:2626: gsum pa dge slong pha ma'i bslab bya bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2629: dang po dgag pa'i bslab bya la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2630: dge slong pha'i dgag pa'i bslab ba 4dang /
NK120(e)001:2631: dge slong ma'i dgag pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK120(e)001:2632: dang po dge slong pha'i dgag pa'i bslab bya la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2635: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2636: dge slong khrims la nyis brgya lnga bcu gsum //
NK120(e)001:2638: dge slonga gi bslab khrimas la pham pa'i sde dang /
NK120(e)001:2643: nyes byas kyi sde ste de drug po la nang
NK120(e)001:2644: gses kyi dbye bas khrims nyis brgya lnga bcu rtsa
NK120(e)001:2645: gsuma yod do // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la drug /
NK120(e)001:2651: nyes byas kyi sde bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2652: dang po pham pa'i sde la gsum /
NK120(e)001:2656: dang po gzhi mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2657: sdom pa'i rtsa ba pham pa bzhi zhes pa //
NK120(e)001:2659: bcas ldan dge slong gis 'di dag bsrungs na sdoma
NK120(e)001:2660: pa phyi ma ma lus pa'i rtsa ba yin la
NK120(e)001:2661: / gal te nyams na gnyen po'i phyogs ma lus
NK120(e)001:2662: pa mthu med par bcom pa'i phyir phama pa bzhi
NK120(e)001:2663: / zhesa grags pa'o // gnyis pa rtsa ba rgyas par bshad pa la bzhi /
NK120(e)001:2664: mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa /
NK120(e)001:2665: ma byin len gyi pham pa /
NK120(e)001:2667: mi chos bla ma'i rdzun sma ba'i pham pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2668: dang po mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2669: gzhi yi yan lag cha kun bzung 'os pa //
NK120(e)001:2670: skye gnas lam du pho dbang las rung ni //
NK120(e)001:2671: bsam pa ngo tsha 'jigs med chags sems kyis //
NK120(e)001:2672: sbyor ba drud pa mthar thug sim pa thob //
NK120(e)001:2673: des ni tshangs par spyod las rnam par nyams //
NK120(e)001:2675: de'ang dge slong gis 'di bzhi gang rung la spyad
NK120(e)001:2676: na skad cig ma der sdom pa rnam par dag
NK120(e)001:2677: pa'i lhag ma tsam yang med par byed pas na
NK120(e)001:2678: rtsa ba'i ltung ba dang mi mthun phyogs kyi gnyen
NK120(e)001:2679: po mthu med par bcom pa'i phyir pham pa zhes
NK120(e)001:2680: grags te / de yang mi tshangs spyod la gzhan
NK120(e)001:2681: gyi gzhi yi yan lag 'khrig pa'i tshor ba skyed
NK120(e)001:2682: nus pa'i lus phyed du longs pa yan chad yan
NK120(e)001:2683: lag gi cha shas kuna bzunga bar 'osa pa kha'am
NK120(e)001:2685: skye gansa chu lam gsum po gang rung du /
NK120(e)001:2686: rang gi gzhi yi yan lag brten byed pho yi
NK120(e)001:2687: dabnga po nad la sogs pas sma ma phab par
NK120(e)001:2688: lasa su runga ba de ni /
NK120(e)001:2689: bsam pa rang ngor ltos pa'i ngo tsha ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2690: gzhan ngor ltos pa'i 'jigas pa ste khrel 'dzem meda
NK120(e)001:2691: par reg bde nyams su myong bar 'dod pa'i chagas
NK120(e)001:2692: semas kyis / sbyor ba brten bya der rtsal zhing
NK120(e)001:2693: drud pa las mthar thuga pags rim gyi mtshams las
NK120(e)001:2694: 'das nas lus tshor bde ba'i sima pa thoba pa
NK120(e)001:2695: semas kyis / ste / yan lag bzhi po tshang
NK120(e)001:2696: ba desa ni tshangas para spyod pa'i sdom pa lasa
NK120(e)001:2697: rnam par nyamsa pas na pham par 'gyur pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2698: gnyis pa ma byin len gyi pham pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2699: brku ba'i gzhi ni mi gzhan nor yin pa //
NK120(e)001:2700: bsam pa rang nyid 'tsho phyir rku sems kyis //
NK120(e)001:2701: yul dus rin thang tshang ba sbyor bas brkus //
NK120(e)001:2702: mthar thug brkus sam brkur bcug brtsad nas thob //
NK120(e)001:2704: brku bar bya ba'i gzhi ni rang dang nor mi
NK120(e)001:2705: gcig pa'i gazhana gyis bdag tu bzung ba'i nora rdzas
NK120(e)001:2706: yina pa / bsam pa ranga nyid kyi bza' ba
NK120(e)001:2707: dang bgo ba la sogs pa 'tsho bar bya ba'i
NK120(e)001:2708: phyir du rku ba'i semas kyis /
NK120(e)001:2709: yul gang du'ang dusa de dang bstun pa'i rina thanga tshanga ba /
NK120(e)001:2710: lus kyi rnam pa rig byed kyi sbyor basa dus
NK120(e)001:2711: gcig la brkus pa mathara thug rang gis brkus sama
NK120(e)001:2713: brtsad pa gang yang rung ba'i sgo nas rdzas de
NK120(e)001:2714: bdag po dang bral te rang lag tu 'byor nas
NK120(e)001:2716: 'di la brku rdzas rin thang gi tshad ni ka ri ka lnga bcu pa las /
NK120(e)001:2717: kar+sha pa na bzhi cha brkus //
NK120(e)001:2718: de bskus tshul khrims zhig par 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:2719: zhes gsungs pa sngon gyi gsungs tshul de la gzhig
NK120(e)001:2720: ste deng sang bod yul du phyogs tsam gzhig na
NK120(e)001:2722: yul dus kyi dbang gis mtha' gcig tu ma nges so //
NK120(e)001:2723: gsum pa srog gcod pa'i pham pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2724: srog gcod gzhi ni mi gzhan ma 'khrul bar //
NK120(e)001:2725: bsam pa gsod sems gsod bya der shes pa //
NK120(e)001:2726: sbyor ba gsod par brtsams nas ma bzlog par //
NK120(e)001:2727: mthar thug srog gi dbang po dgag pa dang //
NK120(e)001:2728: gsod bcug yi rang basngagasa sogs rkyen byas kyang //
NK120(e)001:2730: sroga gcoda kyi gzhi ni mi'am mir chags pa rang
NK120(e)001:2731: las rgyud tha dad pa mi gazhana dang ma 'khrula
NK120(e)001:2732: bar / bsam pa bdag gis 'di nyid nges par bsad par bya'o snyam pa'i gsoda semas kyis /
NK120(e)001:2733: gsoda par bya ba de la dera 'du shesa pa /
NK120(e)001:2734: sbyor ba dug dang mtshon cha la sogs pas gsoda
NK120(e)001:2735: para brtsamsa nasa bya ba las ma bzlog para mathara
NK120(e)001:2736: thug rang nyid ma shi ba'i sngon du de nyid
NK120(e)001:2737: sroga gi dabnga po 'agga pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2738: de ltar rang nyid kyis bsad pa tsam du ma zad gzhan la gsoda du bcuga pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2739: bsad pa la shin tu legs shes yi ranga bas
NK120(e)001:2740: basngagasa pa brjod pa la sogas pas rkyen byas nas
NK120(e)001:2742: der ma zad dge slong mang pos gros byas nas
NK120(e)001:2743: gcig gis bsad kyang thams cad la pham pa 'byung
NK120(e)001:2745: dmag la sogs pa don gcig phyir //
NK120(e)001:2746: thams cad byed pa po bzhin ldan //
NK120(e)001:2748: bzhi pa mi chos bla ma'i rdzun gyi pham pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2749: rdzun gyi gzhi ni smra shes don go'i mir //
NK120(e)001:2750: bsam pa 'du shes bsgyur nas brjod blo skyes //
NK120(e)001:2751: sbyor ba mngon shes la sogs yon tan tshogs //
NK120(e)001:2752: med kyang yod ces bla ma'i rdzun smras pas //
NK120(e)001:2753: mthar thug gzhan gyis rdzun de go na nyams //
NK120(e)001:2755: rdzun gyi gzhi ni gang la smra ba'i yul rang las rgyud gzhan pa'i mi smra shesa pa /
NK120(e)001:2757: shes pa rang bzhin du gnas pa /
NK120(e)001:2759: mtshan gnyis ma yin pa ste tha snyad lnga dang ldan pa'i mira /
NK120(e)001:2760: bsam pa de'i 'du shesa gzhan du bsgyur nasa bslu 'dod kyi gtam brjod 'dod kyi blo skyes te /
NK120(e)001:2761: sbyor ba mngona par shes pa lnga la sogas pa
NK120(e)001:2762: 'dod khams las gong du 'phags pa'i bsam gtan dang
NK120(e)001:2763: po nas sangs rgyas kyi sa'i bar gyi yon tan
NK120(e)001:2764: du ma'i tshogas rang la meda kyang yod cesa 'phags
NK120(e)001:2765: pa'i chos bla ma'i rdzun ngag mtshan nyid bzhi ldan
NK120(e)001:2766: gyis smras pasa / mathara thug gazhana gyis rang gis
NK120(e)001:2767: smras pa'i rdzun desa 'du shes bsgyur ma nus kyang
NK120(e)001:2768: don go bar gyur na dge slong rang gi sdom
NK120(e)001:2774: yul de'i rna bar mngon sum du smras pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2775: de ltar pham pa bzhi po 'di la gzhi /
NK120(e)001:2778: mthar thug ste yan lag bzhi tshang ba'o //
NK120(e)001:2779: gsum pa skabs kyi don bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:2780: 'di bzhi gang spyad dge slong de pham phyir //
NK120(e)001:2781: phas pham bzhi zhes thams cad mkhyen des gsungs //
NK120(e)001:2783: des na 'di bzhi po rang rang gi yan lag
NK120(e)001:2784: thams cad tshang bas ganga spyad kyang dge slong de
NK120(e)001:2785: mi mthun phyogs kyi gnyen po mthu med par bcom
NK120(e)001:2786: nas phama pa'i phyir na phasa phama pa bzhi zhesa
NK120(e)001:2787: rgyal ba thams cad mkhyen pa desa gsungas te /
NK120(e)001:2789: dge slong dag gis de dag las ltung ba gang
NK120(e)001:2790: yang rung ba zhig byas na thog ma ji lta
NK120(e)001:2791: bar phyis kyang de bzhin du pham par 'gyur ba
NK120(e)001:2792: yin te / dge slong rnams dang lhan cig gnas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2793: longs spyod du mi dbang gis /
NK120(e)001:2796: de ltar na bslab bya 'di rnams phyi'i rkyen gnas
NK120(e)001:2797: kyi bla ma mtshan nyid dang ldan pa las 'dul
NK120(e)001:2798: ba nas gsungs pa'i blang dor gyi gnas ma lus
NK120(e)001:2799: pa la shin tu mkhas par sbyangs 1shing /
NK120(e)001:2800: nang gi rkyen bsam pa phun sum tshogs pa blang dor la spro ba'i brtson 2 'grus /
NK120(e)001:2801: 'jug ldog gi gnas la bzod pa'i bag 3yod /
NK120(e)001:2802: rang rgyud la nyes pa byung ma byung rtog pa'i
NK120(e)001:2803: shes 4bzhin rnams la brten nas bslab bya'i gnas thams
NK120(e)001:2804: cad la dran shes brtan po rgyun mi chad pa'i
NK120(e)001:2805: sgo nas bsrung dgos pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:2806: gnyis pa lhag ma'i sde la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2809: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2810: dge 'dun lhag ma bcu gsum zhes grags pa //
NK120(e)001:2812: gso ba dge 'duna la rags las shing sdom pa
NK120(e)001:2813: rnam dag gi lhag ma cung zad tsam lus pa
NK120(e)001:2814: la grangs bcu gsuma yod pa yin zhesa gragas pa
NK120(e)001:2815: la dbye na / nang sems can la chags pa lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:2816: phyi yo byad la chags pa gnyis te 'dod pa las gyur pa bdun /
NK120(e)001:2817: gnod pa las gyur pa gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2818: bgo ba las gyur pa bzhi rnams su yod do //
NK120(e)001:2819: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2820: bsgrod min gnas su khu ba 'byin pa dang //
NK120(e)001:2821: chags pas bud med lus kyi cha shas 'dzin //
NK120(e)001:2822: 'khrig tshig rjen smra bud med chags phyir bkur //
NK120(e)001:2823: pho mo phan tshun smyan byas 'dus te 'phrad //
NK120(e)001:2824: rang don tshad lhag khang pa khang chen brtsigs //
NK120(e)001:2825: brjod gzhi med dang snyad ka bag tsam la //
NK120(e)001:2826: brten nas dge slong skur btab dge 'dun dbyen //
NK120(e)001:2827: dbyen de'i rjes phyogs bslab pa dang 'gal ba //
NK120(e)001:2828: khyim sun byin tshe skrod byed la bsnyon pa //
NK120(e)001:2829: ltung byung bskul tshe bka' blo mi bde ba'o //
NK120(e)001:2831: bsgroda bya'i lam gsum mina par rang ngam gzhan gyi
NK120(e)001:2832: yan lag gi gansa su khu ba dbyung 'dod kyi
NK120(e)001:2833: bsam pas rang gi pho dbang las su rung bas
NK120(e)001:2834: reg cing brtsal ba las khu ba 'byin pa'i bde
NK120(e)001:2836: chagas pa'i sems kyis brten rung bud meda la reg
NK120(e)001:2837: 'dod kho nas de'i lus kyi cha shasa skra sogs
NK120(e)001:2838: la rjen par 'dzina te bar du ma chod par
NK120(e)001:2839: reg pa'i bde ba myong ba dang 2 /
NK120(e)001:2840: brda 'phrod pa'i bud med brten rung la 'khriga pa
NK120(e)001:2841: spyod pa'i dngos ming tshiga tu rjen par smra zhing
NK120(e)001:2842: des kyang don go ba dang 3 /
NK120(e)001:2843: yul bud med la chagsa pa don du gnyer ba'i
NK120(e)001:2844: phyir bdag lta bu'i dge slong la 'khrig pas bsnyen
NK120(e)001:2845: bkur na bsnyen bkura thams cad las mchog go zhes
NK120(e)001:2846: basngagasa pa'am yul gyis smras pa dang du blangs kyang
NK120(e)001:2847: rung ste des brda 'phrod pa dang 4 /
NK120(e)001:2848: rang las gzhan pa'i pho mo gnyis phana tshun sbyor
NK120(e)001:2849: 'dod kyis rang ngam bskos pa'i 'phrin gsum gyi sgo
NK120(e)001:2850: nas smyan byas pas de gnyis 'dusa te dbang po
NK120(e)001:2851: 5'phrada pa ste de lnga ni nang sems can la
NK120(e)001:2853: gzhi rgyal pos ma gnang ba sogs rtsod pa can dang /
NK120(e)001:2855: chu sogs kyis 'jig rkyen yod pa bcas ma dag gsum dang ldan pa'i sa gnas su /
NK120(e)001:2856: dge 'dun las gnang ba ma thob par ranga gi
NK120(e)001:2857: dona du gzhan la 'bad pas btsal ba'i yo byad
NK120(e)001:2858: kyis srid du mi'i khru bco brgyad dang /
NK120(e)001:2859: zheng du khru phyed dang bcu gcig gi tshad las
NK120(e)001:2860: lhag pa'i khanga pa rang ngam gzhan la bskos pas
NK120(e)001:2861: brtsigs kyang rung ste thog phub zin pa dang 6
NK120(e)001:2862: / gang zag bzhir longs pa yan chad kyi don
NK120(e)001:2863: nam dkon mchog gi ched du'ang dge 'dun las gnang
NK120(e)001:2864: ba ma thob par ma dag gsum gyi sa na
NK120(e)001:2865: khanga chena brtsigsa nas thog phub pa 7ste de gnyis
NK120(e)001:2866: ni phyi'i yo byad la chags pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2867: yul dge slong gzhan la brjod pa'i gzhi mthong thos
NK120(e)001:2868: dogs gsum meda bzhin du pham pa bzhi gang rung
NK120(e)001:2869: byung zhes skur 'debs kyi tshig gsal por smras pa
NK120(e)001:2871: gleng ba'i snyad ka baga tsam yod pa la brten
NK120(e)001:2872: nasa yul dge slonga gzhan la tshig zur gyis pham
NK120(e)001:2873: bzhi gang rung gi sgo nas skur pa btab pa
NK120(e)001:2874: yul gyis go ba 9 ste de gnyis ni gnod
NK120(e)001:2876: mtshams nang gcig tu bcas ldan dge slonga gis rang
NK120(e)001:2877: mi the ba'i dbye bya dge 'duna du longs pa
NK120(e)001:2878: phyogs gnyis su chos min dbyen gyis 'byed pa la
NK120(e)001:2879: zlog byed lngas bzlog kyang de'i tha ma brjod pa
NK120(e)001:2880: gsum pa'i mtha' la mi gtong 10ba dang /
NK120(e)001:2881: dge slong gang dge 'dun dbyen byed pa'i dge slong
NK120(e)001:2882: de'i rjesa su phyogsa nas bslaba pa dang 'agla bar
NK120(e)001:2883: byed pa la zlog byed lngas bzlog kyang mi gtong
NK120(e)001:2884: ba 11dang / dge slong gang zhig chang 'thung zhing
NK120(e)001:2885: bud med dang lhan du bza' btung la spyod pa
NK120(e)001:2886: sogs bslab pa dang 'gal ba'i ngan spyod kyi bya
NK120(e)001:2887: bas khyim pa rnams kyi sems sun 'byin te mi
NK120(e)001:2888: dad par byed pa'i tshe de dge 'dun gyi gnas
NK120(e)001:2889: nas bskrad pa na skrod byed dge 'dun la 'gro
NK120(e)001:2890: min bzhi'i bsnyon tshig gis skur pa 'debs pa zlog
NK120(e)001:2891: byed lnga'i mthar mi gtong ba 12dang /
NK120(e)001:2892: dge slong gzhan la ltung ba byung ba na dge 'dun gyi phyir bcos bya bar bskula ba'i tshe /
NK120(e)001:2895: kho bo la ci yang ma smra zhig ces dang
NK120(e)001:2896: du ma blangs pa bka'a blo mi bde ba'i gzhir
NK120(e)001:2897: zhugs pa zlog byed lnga'i mtha' la mi gtong 13ba'o
NK120(e)001:2898: // 'di bzhi ni bgo ba las gyur pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2902: gsum pa spang ltung gi sde la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:2904: dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:2905: dang po rnam grangs mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:2906: spong ba'i ltung byed sum cu'i sde bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:2908: gang la ltung ba byung ba'i dngos po de spong ba'i sgo nas phyir bcos dgos shing /
NK120(e)001:2909: ma bcos na rnam smin ngan song du ltung bar byed pas na /
NK120(e)001:2910: de'i grangs suma cu yod pa'i sde rnams rim par bashada pa la zhes so //
NK120(e)001:2911: gnyis pa dbye ba rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:2914: lhung bzed sogs kyi sde gsum po re re la'ang nang gses bcu re yod pa las /
NK120(e)001:2915: bcu tshan dang po gos sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:2916: rang gi gos lhag zhag bcu 'das par 'chang //
NK120(e)001:2917: chos gos dang bral zhag gcig lon pa dang //
NK120(e)001:2918: gos rgyu zla gcig 'jog dang dge slong mar //
NK120(e)001:2919: chos gos 'khru 'jug de la gos rgyu len //
NK120(e)001:2920: nye min khyim par gos rgyu slong ba dang //
NK120(e)001:2921: ster na stod g.yogs smad g.yogs lhag por len //
NK120(e)001:2922: rang la ster bsam chos gos gnas dpags pa //
NK120(e)001:2923: rin dang khru tshad kyis slong brtags dran slong //
NK120(e)001:2924: gos rin rin chen bskur ba len rnams so //
NK120(e)001:2926: de la sra brkyang ma bting ba'i gang zag gis
NK120(e)001:2927: ranga gi dbang byar yod cing bdag tu bzung ba'i
NK120(e)001:2928: gosa lhag po 'khor gsum khebs pa'i matha'i tshad du
NK120(e)001:2929: longs pa'am / gal te byin gyis brlab rung gi
NK120(e)001:2930: chos gos rnam gsum yod pa'am med kyang chos gos
NK120(e)001:2931: kyi kha skong ba'i re ba med na khru gang
NK120(e)001:2932: gi tshad du longs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:2933: kha skong gi re ba dang bcas pa na 'khor
NK120(e)001:2934: gsum khebs pa yan gyi gos lhag byin gyis ma
NK120(e)001:2935: brlabs par rang stobs sam shan stobs kyis zhaga bcu
NK120(e)001:2938: rigs log ma log gnyis te mu bzhi yod cing /
NK120(e)001:2939: shan 'jug pa ni zhag bcu pa'i gos snga ma
NK120(e)001:2940: byin gyis ma brlabs par zhag dgu lon pa dang
NK120(e)001:2941: / 'di nyid rigs mthun gyi gos gcig rnyed na /
NK120(e)001:2942: snga mas zhag dgu lon pa'i shan de /
NK120(e)001:2943: phyi ma la zhugs pas zhag bcu 'das te bcu
NK120(e)001:2944: gcig pa'i skya rengs shar ba na gos snga mas
NK120(e)001:2945: rang stobs dang / phyi mas shan stobs kyis spang ltung gnyis dus gcig la bskyed /
NK120(e)001:2947: sngo dro zhag bcu pa'i gos gcig rnyed /
NK120(e)001:2948: phyi dro yang gcig rnyed pa lta bu'o //
NK120(e)001:2950: 'ong tu 'chad pa'i zla 'jog gi gos des zla gcig ma 'das par spang ltung mi bskyed kyang /
NK120(e)001:2951: zla 'jog des zhag gcig nas nyer dgu gang rung lon pa na /
NK120(e)001:2952: phyis chos gos gsum tshang bar rnyed na /
NK120(e)001:2953: zla 'jog de zhag bcu pa'i gos su rig log ste /
NK120(e)001:2954: zhag bcu 'das pa na zla 'jog gis rang stobs dang phyi mas shan stobs kyis spang ltung bskyed /
NK120(e)001:2956: snga phyi gnyis ka zla bar zhag rung ba yin na rigs ma log mod /
NK120(e)001:2957: gos snga ma rnyed nas gcig nas nyer dgu bar gang rung lon pa na /
NK120(e)001:2958: phyi ma zhig rnyed na snga ma'i shan zhugs nas
NK120(e)001:2959: so gcig pa'i skya rengs shar ba na snga mas
NK120(e)001:2960: rang stobs dang phyi mas shan stobs kyis spang ltung
NK120(e)001:2961: bskyed pa sogs lhung bzed sman ltung ba bcas thams
NK120(e)001:2962: cad la 'gre / lhung bzed kyi shan 'jug tshul ni snga ma'i rig pas shes so //
NK120(e)001:2963: byin gyis brlab tshul kyang snga phyi gnyis shan ma 'dres gong snga ma byin gyis brlab dgos /
NK120(e)001:2964: snga ma byin gyis ma brlabs na phyi ma byin gyis brlabs kyang go mi chod /
NK120(e)001:2965: byin gyis brlabs pa'i chosa gosa gsum gang rung dang
NK120(e)001:2966: brala nas gnas tha dad par zhaga gciga lona pa
NK120(e)001:2968: chos gos gang rung med par kha skong gi re
NK120(e)001:2969: ba dang bcas pas gosa rgyu tshad khru gang nas
NK120(e)001:2970: 'khor gsum khebs pa'i bar byin gyis ma brlabs par
NK120(e)001:2971: rang stobs sam shan stobs kyis zla ba gciga 'das
NK120(e)001:2972: nas so gcig pa'i skya rengs shar ba na zla
NK120(e)001:2974: bdun brgyud tshun gyi nye du ma yin pa'i dge
NK120(e)001:2975: slonga mara rang gi chosa gosa rnying pa 'khrura 'juga
NK120(e)001:2977: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma de la
NK120(e)001:2978: gosa kyi rgyu 'khor gsum khebs pa'i tshad longs pa
NK120(e)001:2979: yan chad lena pa la zhugs nas thob pa 5dang
NK120(e)001:2980: / rang la chos gos rnam gsum tshang bzhin du
NK120(e)001:2981: nye du mina pa'i khyim para gosa kyi rgyu 'khor
NK120(e)001:2982: gsum khebs pa'i tshad longs pa yan chad slong ba
NK120(e)001:2983: la zhugs nas thob pa dang 6 /
NK120(e)001:2984: chos gos rnam gsum tshang bar med na nye min
NK120(e)001:2985: khyim par slong bar rigs kyang gos mang po ster
NK120(e)001:2986: na stod g.yogas dang smad g.yogas gcig las lhag pora
NK120(e)001:2987: lena pa 7dang / nye min khyim pas ranga la
NK120(e)001:2988: ster bsam ste chos gosa 'di sbyin gansa dge slong
NK120(e)001:2989: 'di la 'bul dgos zhes blos dapagas pa las /
NK120(e)001:2990: 'bul lam mi 'bul brtags pa'i ched du rina dang
NK120(e)001:2991: khru tshad kyis dran pa brjod de slong ba la
NK120(e)001:2993: nye min khyim bdag pho mo so sos rang la
NK120(e)001:2994: gos re re'am mang po 'bul bar thos dpags kyis
NK120(e)001:2995: de brtagas pa'i bsam pas drana bskul slong ba la
