NK120(e)001:2997: sbyin bdag pho nya zhal ta ba ste khyim pa
NK120(e)001:2998: gsum las sbyin bdag gis chos gosa kyi rina rung
NK120(e)001:2999: ba ma yin pa rina chen gser dngul lta bu
NK120(e)001:3000: pho nya ba la bskura ba pho nyas dge slong
NK120(e)001:3002: de len du mi rung bas na /
NK120(e)001:3003: pho nya des dge slong rang gi zhal ta ba la gtad nas gos 'grub tu bcug pa las /
NK120(e)001:3004: gos dus su ma byung na dge slong gis zhal
NK120(e)001:3005: ta ba la dngos su bskul ba lan gsum bya
NK120(e)001:3006: / de la ma byung na kho'i gan du lan
NK120(e)001:3007: gsum mthong sar cang mi smra bas bsdad nas bslangs
NK120(e)001:3008: pa la nyes pa med cing /
NK120(e)001:3009: bskul bsdad drug po de las lhag par lena pa la zhugs nas thob 10pa rnams so //
NK120(e)001:3010: bcu tshan gnyis pa stan sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3011: srin bal nang tshangs byas pa'i stan byed dang //
NK120(e)001:3012: dkon sar bal nag 'ba' zhig stan du 'dings //
NK120(e)001:3013: bal nag cha gnyis stan byed lo drug ni //
NK120(e)001:3014: ma song stan gsar byed dang tshad ldan gyi //
NK120(e)001:3015: gding ba yod kyang slar bzo bal nag ni //
NK120(e)001:3016: rnyed nas lam gyi dpag tshad gsum mthar byed //
NK120(e)001:3017: dge slong ma la bal 'khru rmel bcug dang //
NK120(e)001:3018: gser dngul len dang tshong 'bun mngon mtshan can //
NK120(e)001:3021: rin thang che ba srina bala gyi nanga tshangas byas pa'i stan byed pa 1dang /
NK120(e)001:3022: shin tu dkona sara bala naga 'ab'a zhiga gis nang tshangs byas pa stan du 'dinga 2ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3023: bal dkar po bsres kyang bala naga stan gyi cha
NK120(e)001:3024: gnyisa las lhag pa'i stan byed pa'am byed du 'jug
NK120(e)001:3025: pa dang 3 / stan snga ma yod bzhin lo
NK120(e)001:3026: druga ni ma songa zhing dge 'dun la gnang ba
NK120(e)001:3027: ma thob par stan gasra pa nang tshangs can byed
NK120(e)001:3028: pa dang 3 / pa dang 4 / tshad ldan
NK120(e)001:3029: gyi gdinga ba rnying pa yoda kyang gsar pa slara
NK120(e)001:3030: bzo ba na rnying pa nas bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK120(e)001:3031: mtho gang ste mi'i khru phyed do gsar pa la
NK120(e)001:3032: ma bslan par longs spyad pa 5dang /
NK120(e)001:3033: rang dbang ba'i dngos po bala naga la sogs pa
NK120(e)001:3034: ni rnyed nasa chags sems kyis nyin gcig gi nang
NK120(e)001:3035: du dge tshul lta bu 'khur khyer gro gas med
NK120(e)001:3036: na lam gyi dapaga tshad gsuma tshun gnang la de
NK120(e)001:3037: phan chad mathara byed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:3038: de nas rgyangs grags su khyer bas sam khyer grogs
NK120(e)001:3039: yod na dang po nas brtsams te rgyangs grags gcig
NK120(e)001:3041: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slong ma la dge
NK120(e)001:3042: slong gis bala 'khru zhing rmela du bcuga pa 7dang
NK120(e)001:3043: / dge slong gis rung ba ma byas pa'i gsera
NK120(e)001:3044: dngul sogs rin po che la chud 'dza' ba sogs
NK120(e)001:3045: kyi rkyen med bzhin du chags pas reg gam reg
NK120(e)001:3046: tu bcug nas bdag gir byas te lena pa 8dang
NK120(e)001:3047: / / nye min khyim par dge slong gis khe
NK120(e)001:3048: spog 'dod pas tshonga zog rin po che sogs 'buna
NK120(e)001:3049: bskyed du btang nas mngona matshana can gyi zog rtsa
NK120(e)001:3050: de las bskyed gos khru gang yan longs pa thob
NK120(e)001:3051: / / pa 9dang / dge slong gi khe spog
NK120(e)001:3052: 'dod pa'i ched du nye min khyim pa la rin
NK120(e)001:3053: po che las gzhan pa'i dngos po 'bru dang gos
NK120(e)001:3054: sogs mod na nyo zhing dkon na tshonga par byed
NK120(e)001:3056: bcu tshan gsum pa lhung bzed sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3058: zhag bcu 'das 'chang lhung bzed zung 'chang ba //
NK120(e)001:3059: gla rngan med par 'thag 'jug 'thag rgya bskyed //
NK120(e)001:3060: dge slong gos byin slar 'phrog brtad byung gos //
NK120(e)001:3061: sbyin dus bshad las snga bar bdag gir byas //
NK120(e)001:3062: dgon par 'jigs bcas gos bral zhag bdun 'das //
NK120(e)001:3063: ras chen dgag dbye zin kyang zla phyed 'das //
NK120(e)001:3064: dge 'dun bsngosa pa'i rnyed pa bdag tu bzung //
NK120(e)001:3065: na sman zhag bdun 'das na gsog 'jog go //
NK120(e)001:3067: dge slong rang gi lhung bzeda tshad ldan byina gyis
NK120(e)001:3068: ma barlabas pa'am brlabs kyang shan stobs kyis zhaga bcu
NK120(e)001:3069: 'adsa par 'achanga nas bcu gcig pa'i skya rengs shar
NK120(e)001:3070: ba 1dang / rgyu dbyibs kha dog gi rung zhing
NK120(e)001:3071: mthe bo'i lto gang gis lhag mar phul dgu shong
NK120(e)001:3072: ba yan chad kyi lhung bzed yod bzhin du nye
NK120(e)001:3073: min khyim pa la lhung bzeda gzhan bslangs pas thob
NK120(e)001:3074: na de dang zunga 'achanga ba yin cing /
NK120(e)001:3075: 'di yang byin ma brlabs par zhag bcu 'das na ltung ba snga mar 2'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:3076: lhung bzed kyi tshad phul dgu shong ba chung tshad dang /
NK120(e)001:3077: phul bco brgyad shong ba che tshad /
NK120(e)001:3079: phul re re la khyor ba phyed ba zhi re yod do //
NK120(e)001:3080: nye du min pa'i thag mkhan la gla rngana meda
NK120(e)001:3081: para rang ngam bskos pas gos 'athaga tu 'juga ste
NK120(e)001:3083: nye min khyim pas rang la 'bul rgyu'i gos 'thag tu bcug pa na /
NK120(e)001:3084: bdag pos ma gnang par bsngo tshod las lhag par
NK120(e)001:3085: 'athaga rgya bskyed du bcug nas thob pa dang 4dang
NK120(e)001:3086: / rang dge slong gis dge slong gzhan la gosa
NK120(e)001:3087: sogs byin pa slar 'phroga ste de dang bral ba
NK120(e)001:3088: / dang 5 / dbyar gnas pa'i dge 'dun la
NK120(e)001:3089: phul ba brtad pa ni glo bur ba'i ming ste
NK120(e)001:3090: des na dbyar nang du byung ba'i gosa so sor
NK120(e)001:3091: byin pa'i dusa su bashada pa dgag dbye byas pa'i
NK120(e)001:3092: phyi de nyid lasa snga bar dbyar nang du badga
NK120(e)001:3095: dgag dbye'i phyi de nyid du ma bgos pa ste /
NK120(e)001:3096: de ltar sngas phyis kyi ltung ba gsum mo //
NK120(e)001:3098: brtad pa las byung ba'i gos lnga po /
NK120(e)001:3099: nad pa dang nad pa'i phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:3101: 'gro bar chas pa la sbyin pa /
NK120(e)001:3103: rkyen ldan de dag la dbyar matha'i zhag bcu'i nang du so sor sbyin na nyes pa med cing /
NK120(e)001:3104: yang dbyar nang du chos smra ba'i rnyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3105: nad pa'i rim gro la sogs pa'i ched du sbyin pa'i rnyed pa ni 'dir ma gtogs 6so //
NK120(e)001:3106: dge slong dgona para gnas pas 'jigas pa dang bacasa
NK120(e)001:3107: pa'i sar chos gosa rnam gsum dang zhag drug brala
NK120(e)001:3108: bar gnang yang zhaga bduna 'adsa te skya rengs shar
NK120(e)001:3109: ba 7dang / dbyar gyis gos rasa chena dbyar khas
NK120(e)001:3110: len pa de'i zla gcig gi sngon du btsal zhing
NK120(e)001:3111: rnyed na tshol sngas pa'i spang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3112: dagga dbye zina nas kyang zla ba phyed las 'adsa par 'chang na zhag phyis pa'i spang ba 8dang /
NK120(e)001:3113: sbyin bdag gis dge 'duna la bsngosa pa'i gos sogs
NK120(e)001:3114: kyi rnyed para rang la bsgyur te badga tu bzunga
NK120(e)001:3115: ba 9dang / na ba la phan pa'i smana byin
NK120(e)001:3116: rlabs kyi rang dus zhaga bduna 'adsa nasa gsoga 'joga
NK120(e)001:3117: tu song ba bcangs pa la spang rung tha mar
NK120(e)001:3118: ba 9dang / 10bzhag go // 'dir thun tshod du rung ba'i sman thun tshod las 'das nas so //
NK120(e)001:3119: de rnams phyir bcos kyi skabs byin 'phrogs dang /
NK120(e)001:3120: lhung bzed tshol ba gnyis kyi rdzas rtsa ba nas spang dgos shing /
NK120(e)001:3121: gzhan rnams zhag gcig gi ring spang ba sngon du btang dgos so //
NK120(e)001:3122: bzhi pa ltung byed 'ba' zhig pa'i sde la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:3125: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3126: ltung byed 'ba' zhig dgu bcu tham pa ni //
NK120(e)001:3128: de yang spyad na ngan song du ltung bar byed
NK120(e)001:3129: cing bshags dus spang bral sngon du btang ma dgos
NK120(e)001:3130: pas na 'ab'a zhiga pa zhes bya la /
NK120(e)001:3131: de'i grangs dgu bcu thama pa bshad pa ni zhes pa'o //
NK120(e)001:3132: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK120(e)001:3134: shes bzhin dang ni sa bon dang //
NK120(e)001:3135: ma bskos pa dang yang yang dang //
NK120(e)001:3136: chu dang khyim dang bsam bzhin dang //
NK120(e)001:3137: mgron mang rkun ma chos ston no //
NK120(e)001:3138: zhes pa'i sdom ltar bcu tshan dgu las /
NK120(e)001:3139: bcu tshan dang po shes bzhin sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3140: shes bzhin rdzun smra dge slong skyon brjod pa //
NK120(e)001:3141: phra mas 'byed dang skyo sngogs bzlum kyang dbye //
NK120(e)001:3142: bud med chos ston bsnyen par ma rdzogs dang //
NK120(e)001:3143: lhan cig chos 'don gnas ngan len ltung brjod //
NK120(e)001:3144: mi chos bla ma bden smra bshes ngor 'phya //
NK120(e)001:3148: de yang pham pa'i rdzun dang /
NK120(e)001:3149: gzhi med bag tsam gyi lhag ma'i rdzun dang /
NK120(e)001:3150: shes bzhin du chos dang chos min 'gal 'dur smra ba sbom por gyur pa'i rdzun dang /
NK120(e)001:3151: yang dag dri ba'i dus ltung ba yod bzhin mi smra ba nyes byas kyi rdzun te bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:3152: ltung byed rang gi nang tshan du bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:3158: khyad gsod bcas 6ma yin pa shesa bzhina du rdzuna smra ba nyan pa pos go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3160: yul dge slonga la yul dus der skyon du grags
NK120(e)001:3161: pa'i tshig phan sems ma yin pas brjod pa pha
NK120(e)001:3164: yul dge slong mthun pa dag phra mas 'byed par byed pa go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3166: dge slong gnyis rtsod pa dge 'dun gyis skyo sngogas
NK120(e)001:3167: kyis bzlum par byas zin kyang de nyid slar yang
NK120(e)001:3168: dbye 'dod pas bshig par brtsam pa'i tshig smras pa
NK120(e)001:3169: go ba dang / lnga pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3170: khrims grogs med par yul nyan 'dod kyi buda meda
NK120(e)001:3171: la des mi shes pa'i chosa tshig lnga'am drug las
NK120(e)001:3174: rgod bag gi bsam pas bsnyen para ma rdzogas pa
NK120(e)001:3175: dang lhan ciga tu chosa kyi tshig gdangs sna tshogs
NK120(e)001:3178: yul khyim pa la dgos pa med par dge slong
NK120(e)001:3179: gzhan la gansa ngana leena pham lhag gi ltung ba
NK120(e)001:3180: byung ba gleng bar ma bskos bzhin du ltung ba
NK120(e)001:3183: mi chos bla ma'i yon tan thob pa'i dge slong
NK120(e)001:3184: gis yul bsnyen par ma rdzogs pa la dgos pa
NK120(e)001:3185: khyad par can med bzhin du de thob po zhes
NK120(e)001:3186: bdena par smras pa yul gyis go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3188: dge 'dun gyi bya ba byas pa'i dge slong la
NK120(e)001:3189: rung ba tshad ldan gyi yo byad cung zad byin
NK120(e)001:3190: pa la mi bzod pas dge 'dun gyi rdzas gang
NK120(e)001:3191: zag la bshesa ngora byas nas byin no zhes 'phyas
NK120(e)001:3192: pa pha rol pos go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3194: gso sbyong gi dus lta bu so thar gyi mdo
NK120(e)001:3195: 'don pa'i tshe bslaba gzhi phra zhing phra ba 'di
NK120(e)001:3196: lta bu 'don pas ci byas zhes khyad du gsoda
NK120(e)001:3197: ba'i tshig smras pa gzhan gyis go ba rnams so
NK120(e)001:3198: // bcu tshan gnyis pa sa bon sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3200: bdag gi ngor 'phya bsgo ba rnar gzon ni //
NK120(e)001:3201: ltung byung gleng la ma thos lan gzhan 'debs //
NK120(e)001:3202: khri dang 'ding ba ma bsdus bting song dang //
NK120(e)001:3203: dge slong skrod dang tho mtshams phyis gnon byas //
NK120(e)001:3204: mal khris bug dbyung srog chags ldan pa'i chu //
NK120(e)001:3205: r+ts+war 'debs gtsug lag pha gu rim gnyis brtsigs //
NK120(e)001:3209: rung ba min pa ni ma nyams pa'i sa bona
NK120(e)001:3210: 'joms par byed cing r+ts+wa shing sogs skye ba gcoda
NK120(e)001:3211: pa'am nyams par byed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:3212: nyams pa'i tshe r+ts+wa dang nas sogs re re'i grangs bzhin ltung bar 'gyur zhing /
NK120(e)001:3213: star ka la sogs pa'i 'bras bu smin pa sdong
NK120(e)001:3214: bu las phral bar byas pa sogs nyes byas so
NK120(e)001:3217: bkas pa'i rung ba gsum las /
NK120(e)001:3218: 'bras lta bu snod du blugs nas bsnyen par ma
NK120(e)001:3219: rdzogs pas phyogs bzhi nas mes reg tsam byed pa
NK120(e)001:3220: dang / la phug lta bu mtshon gyis rma btod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3221: star ka lta bu kha bkas pa bcas so //
NK120(e)001:3223: zhal ta bas chos dang mthun pa byas kyang 'dis
NK120(e)001:3224: badga gi ngora gnas mal sogs gang yang rung ba
NK120(e)001:3225: ngan par byas so zhes 'phya ba la dge 'dun
NK120(e)001:3226: gyis gsol ba'i las kyis ngan pa'i grangs su bcug
NK120(e)001:3228: rang la ltung ba byung ba bsgo ba rnara gzona
NK120(e)001:3229: pa'i sgo nas ni dge slong gzhan gyis phyir bcos
NK120(e)001:3230: su gzhug pa'i phyir ched du ltung ba byung ba
NK120(e)001:3231: de glenga pa lta bu chos mthun gyi bsgo ba
NK120(e)001:3232: dang dri ba dris pa la de ma thosa pa
NK120(e)001:3233: ltar ram khyad gsod lta bus lana gazhana log par
NK120(e)001:3234: 'debas pa'i tshig smras pa yul gyis go ba dang
NK120(e)001:3236: dge 'dun gyi khri dang khri'u sogs gnas mal la longs spyad nas rang gis ma bsdus shing /
NK120(e)001:3237: gzhan la'ang ma bcol bar bla gab med sar bor bas chud zos pa'am /
NK120(e)001:3238: ma zos kyang de'i nye 'khor nas 'dom zhe dgu 'das te phyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3240: dge 'dun gyi gtsug lag khang srog chags skye ba'i
NK120(e)001:3241: nyes dmigs yod sar r+ts+wa la sogs pa'i 'dinga ba
NK120(e)001:3242: la longs spyad zin nas rang ngam bsgos pas ma
NK120(e)001:3243: bsdus par bting bzhin bor bas chud zos pa'am ma
NK120(e)001:3244: zos kyang nye 'khor las 'dom zhe dgu 'das te
NK120(e)001:3245: songa ba dang / drug pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3246: gtsug lag khang nas dge slong gzhan zhe sdang gis
NK120(e)001:3247: skrod dam skrod du bcug pas de phyi rol du
NK120(e)001:3248: thon pa dang / bdun pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3249: gtsug lag khang du sngar zhugs pa'i dge slong gzhan
NK120(e)001:3250: la tho 'tshamsa pa'i bsam pas phyis gnona byas te
NK120(e)001:3251: lus ngag gis zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3253: gtsug lag khang gi steng thog snyi ba la mala
NK120(e)001:3254: khri rkang pa rnon pos btsug nas lus ljid phab
NK120(e)001:3255: ste 'dug pas bug pa dbyung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3257: sroga chagas dang ldana pa'i chu dang r+ts+wa shing sogs
NK120(e)001:3258: la der shes bzhin du chu ni r+ts+wa sogs skam
NK120(e)001:3260: r+ts+wa sogs chur 'debas pas dud 'gro ji snyed shi ba de snyed kyi ltung byed dang /
NK120(e)001:3262: gzhi mi brtan pa dang chu khung ma btod pa
NK120(e)001:3263: sogs 'jig rkyen yod sar spyod lam bzhi shong yan
NK120(e)001:3264: chad kyi gtsuga lag khang rang ngam bskos pas nyin
NK120(e)001:3265: gcig la pha gu'i rima pa 'jim pa dang bcas
NK120(e)001:3266: pa gnyisa sam gsum las lhag pa brtsigsa pa shes
NK120(e)001:3267: bzhina du bgyis na ltung bar 'gyur ba rnams so
NK120(e)001:3268: // bcu tshan gsu ma pa ma bskos pa sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3270: ma bskos chos ston bskos kyang nyi nub dang //
NK120(e)001:3271: kha zas phyir ston gos btsems chos gos sbyin //
NK120(e)001:3272: don mthun lam 'grogs gru de gyen mthur 'gro //
NK120(e)001:3273: dben par gcig 'dug pa dang 'greng ba dang //
NK120(e)001:3274: sbyor bcug zas za rnams ni spang bar bya //
NK120(e)001:3276: 'di mana bcu tshan 'di dge slonga mara brten nas 'byung ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:3278: de yang dge slong ma'i ston par ma bskosa pa'am
NK120(e)001:3279: bskos kyang mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i dge slong
NK120(e)001:3280: gis dge slong ma la chosa ston nas go ba
NK120(e)001:3282: dge slong ma'i sto na par bskos kyang 'jigs pa
NK120(e)001:3283: dang bcas pa'i gnas su nyi ma nub zin rjes
NK120(e)001:3284: su'ang chos ston pa des go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3286: dge slong ma'i ston par 'os shing bskos pas rnyed pa'i phyir chos mi ston kyang /
NK120(e)001:3287: phrag dog gis kha zasa cung zad tsam gyi phyir
NK120(e)001:3288: chos ston no zhes skur pa btab pa yul gyis
NK120(e)001:3289: go ba dang / bzhi pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3290: nye min dge slong ma'i gos btsemsa te grub pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3292: nye min dge slong ma la bshes ngo tsam gyi
NK120(e)001:3293: phyir rang gi chosa gosa rung ba tshad ldan sbyin
NK120(e)001:3294: pa de lag tu thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3296: nye min dge slong ma dang lhan cig dona mthuna
NK120(e)001:3297: pas mgron thabs su lam la 'grogas te 'gro na
NK120(e)001:3298: rgyangs grags re re 'das pa la ltung ba re
NK120(e)001:3299: re dang phyed la nyes byas dang /
NK120(e)001:3301: de bzhin dge slong ma dang lhan cig grur zhugs
NK120(e)001:3302: nas gru de nyid thad kar mi 'gro bar gyen
NK120(e)001:3303: dang mthura du 'gro na sngar bzhin rgyangs grags re
NK120(e)001:3306: nye min bud med dang dbena pa skyabs yod sar
NK120(e)001:3307: khrims grogs med par gnas gciga tu 'dom gang tsam
NK120(e)001:3308: gyis bar chod kyang gnyis ka sa la 'duga pa
NK120(e)001:3310: dben par bud med dam khyad par dge slong ma dang lhan cig 'grenga ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3312: dge slong gis nyes min dge slong ma la sbyin
NK120(e)001:3313: bdag khyim pa la rang dang mi 'brel ba'i yon
NK120(e)001:3314: tan brjod cing sbyor du bcuga pa'i dus rung gis
NK120(e)001:3315: zasa za ba na ltung bar 'gyur ba rnamas ni
NK120(e)001:3316: spanga bar bya ba rnams so //
NK120(e)001:3317: bcu tshan bzhi pa yang yang sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3318: yang yang zas za mu stegs 'dug pa'i sar //
NK120(e)001:3319: zhag gcig lhag bsdad za dang lhung bzed do //
NK120(e)001:3320: za dang zos rjes bza' bca' za ba dang //
NK120(e)001:3321: spang zas ltung 'byung ched du rdzun gyis stob //
NK120(e)001:3322: gnang min mtshams nang logs su 'dus nas za //
NK120(e)001:3323: dus min phyed yol za dang gsog 'jog za //
NK120(e)001:3324: byin len ma byas sman bzhi khar mid pa //
NK120(e)001:3325: bsod pa zhim pa'i zas slong //
NK120(e)001:3328: bsod snyoms lan gcig gis gso mi nus pa'i nad kyi btab pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3329: dge 'dun dang mchod rten gyi las dang /
NK120(e)001:3331: dpag tshad phyed du phyin pa bcas ma yin zhing
NK120(e)001:3332: sra brkyang ma bting ba'i dge slong gis khyim pa
NK120(e)001:3333: nye du ma yin pa la /
NK120(e)001:3334: dus rung gi zas nyi ma gcig la khyim snga
NK120(e)001:3335: mar zos zin kyang yang khyim gnyis pa dang gsum
NK120(e)001:3336: pa la sogs pa las yanga yanga bslangs te kha
NK120(e)001:3339: nye min khyim pa'i gnas su mu stegsa pa 'duga
NK120(e)001:3340: pa'i sara sbyin bdag gis ma bstab par zhaga gciga
NK120(e)001:3341: las lhag par bsdada de nyi ma gnyis pa'i zas
NK120(e)001:3342: za ba dang / gsum pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3343: nye min khyim pas ci bder stob pa ma yin
NK120(e)001:3344: par dus rung gi zas che tshad lhung bzeda gang
NK120(e)001:3346: chung tshad gsum ste bre phyed dang lnga las lhag
NK120(e)001:3347: pa bslangs nas gnas gzhan du khyer te za ba
NK120(e)001:3349: na dus dang mu ge'i dus min par dus rung
NK120(e)001:3350: gi zas zosa te blos bcad cing ngag tu brjod
NK120(e)001:3351: nas de'i rjesa su bza' baca'a gang rung lhag po
NK120(e)001:3352: ma byas par sngar gyi bza' bca' gang rung za
NK120(e)001:3353: ba dang / lhag po bya tshul ni yul dge
NK120(e)001:3354: slong gnas ma btang ba'i mdun du tsog pus spangs
NK120(e)001:3355: zas bzung nas gsol ba btab pas yul des blangs
NK120(e)001:3356: nas kham gnyis sam gsum mam phud za zhing zas
NK120(e)001:3357: spangs pa yin na za mi dgos /
NK120(e)001:3358: gang ltar yang de bza' ba po la gtad nas bzar rung ba'o //
NK120(e)001:3360: dge slong gzhan gyis spangsa pa'i zasa lhag por ma
NK120(e)001:3361: byas bzhin du de la ngan sems kyi ltung ba
NK120(e)001:3362: 'byung ba'i cheda du lhag por byas so zhes rdzun
NK120(e)001:3363: gyis stob pa'i tshig smras pa des go nas zos
NK120(e)001:3364: na stob pa po la ltung ba byung ba dang
NK120(e)001:3366: na ba sogs gannga ba'i dus mina par matshama nanga
NK120(e)001:3367: du bsam pa mi mthun pas dge 'dun spyi'i las
NK120(e)001:3368: sgo nas logas su dge slong gsum yan chad lhan
NK120(e)001:3369: cig tu 'dusa nasa dus rung gi zas za ba
NK120(e)001:3371: na ba sogs kyi rkyen med par dus rung gi
NK120(e)001:3372: zas za ba'i dus mina pa rang gang du gnas
NK120(e)001:3373: pa'i rang gling gi nyi ma phyed yola nas skya
NK120(e)001:3374: rengs dang po ma shar gyi bar du za bas
NK120(e)001:3375: mgul du ji tsam mid pa de tsam gyi ltung
NK120(e)001:3377: nad pas kyang za ba'i tshe dus dran bya dgos so //
NK120(e)001:3379: na ba sogs kyi rkyen med par sman bzhi gang
NK120(e)001:3380: rung byin len byas pa rang dus las 'das pas
NK120(e)001:3381: gsoga 'joga tu song zhing ma zhig pa za ba
NK120(e)001:3382: dang / 'dir gsog 'jog tu 'phros pa bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:3383: chud za ba sogs kyi rkyen med par zas gang
NK120(e)001:3384: la byin len ma byas pa'i gong du dge slong
NK120(e)001:3386: dge slong rang dbang ba'i mtshams dngos sam de'i nye
NK120(e)001:3387: 'khor gyi nang du zas rjen pa zhig btsos pa
NK120(e)001:3388: dang 2 / mtshams nang der de 'dra'i dngos po zhag lon pa dang 3 /
NK120(e)001:3389: de 'dra'i dngos po rjen par mtshams kyi phyi nang gang rung du dge slong gis btsos 4pa'o //
NK120(e)001:3390: de bzhin nad la phan pa'am mu ge'i dus min par zos na nyes byas so //
NK120(e)001:3392: bdag nyid zan chad pa dang nad la phan pa
NK120(e)001:3393: sogs kyi rkyen med par byin lena ma byas pa
NK120(e)001:3395: chu dang so shing ma gtogs sman bzhi gang rung kham gcig yan chad khar mida pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3397: nod pa po'i glo dang rgyab ma yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3398: mtshams gzhan gyis ma chod par mdun du stob pa pos lag gnyis bkan te bstab cing /
NK120(e)001:3399: nod pa pos kyang lag gnyis gan rkyal du bkan nas blang ngo //
NK120(e)001:3400: de ltar byin len byas pa 'jig pa'i rgyu ni lung rnam 'byed las /
NK120(e)001:3401: phrogs dang 'dril dang reg pa dang //
NK120(e)001:3402: bsngosa dang dge slong min gyur dang //
NK120(e)001:3404: dor ba yis ni byin len 'jig /
NK120(e)001:3406: nad la phan pa sogs kyi rkyen med par 'o
NK120(e)001:3407: ma sogs yul dus der bsoda para grags shing zhima
NK120(e)001:3408: pa'i zasa bzang po nye min khyim pas ci bder
NK120(e)001:3409: ma bstabs kyang chog mi shes pas slong ste zos
NK120(e)001:3410: na ltung byed du 'gyur ba rnams so //
NK120(e)001:3411: bcu tshan lnga pa chu dang sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3413: chur spyod nyal po byed pa'i shul du nyal //
NK120(e)001:3414: dben pa'i skyabs su 'greng dang gcer bur rgyu //
NK120(e)001:3415: dmag blta dmags sar zhag gnyis lhag par bsdad //
NK120(e)001:3416: dmag gi ru bkod byed dang dge slong brdeg /
NK120(e)001:3417: brdeg tsam gnas ngan len gyi ltung ba 'chab //
NK120(e)001:3420: rang don du sroga chagas dang bacasa pa'i chur ma brtags par longs spyod pa ste /
NK120(e)001:3421: lus dang gos sogs 'khrud pa dang 'gog cing bsgyur ba sogs byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3423: srog chags yod pa'i r+ts+wa shing gcod cing mer 'jug
NK120(e)001:3424: pa sogs srog chags 'chi ba mthong yang ltos med
NK120(e)001:3425: du spyod na shi ba ji tsam de snyed kyi
NK120(e)001:3426: ltung ba'o // de'i don du chu tshags kyi dbye ba dpyangs tshags dang /
NK120(e)001:3428: ril pa zhabs tshags can sogs gang rung bcang bar bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:3429: mar me 'od khang bya ba bcas dgos so //
NK120(e)001:3431: khyim pa pho mo rang khyim du nyala bo byed
NK120(e)001:3432: pa la zhugs pa'am der phyogs pa la de dang
NK120(e)001:3433: nye ba'i shula du nyal lam /
NK120(e)001:3434: 'dug pa de dag dge slong der yod pa rnams kyi tshor ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3436: der dben pa'i skyabsa su 'grenga ste gnas pa tshor ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3438: nad pa dang nye du dang dge ba la sbyor
NK120(e)001:3439: ba'i don sogs dgos pa khyad par can med par
NK120(e)001:3440: mu stegs pa'i rab byung gcera bur rgyu ba pho
NK120(e)001:3441: mo gang rung la dus rung gi zas rang gi
NK120(e)001:3442: lag gis byin cing des thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3444: rgyal pos bos pa sogs rkyen dang dgos pa med
NK120(e)001:3445: par dge slong gis rang gi gnas kyi nye 'khor
NK120(e)001:3446: las 'das te damga gi dpung la blta bar phyin
NK120(e)001:3449: rkyen dang dgos pa med par damga gi dpung yod
NK120(e)001:3450: pa'i sara zhaga gcig gam gnyisa las lhag para bsdada
NK120(e)001:3452: gal te rkyen dgos kyis dmag gi nang du sdod
NK120(e)001:3453: dgos byung yang rang dgar go mtshon la reg pa
NK120(e)001:3454: dang / damga dpung gi ru bshams bkoda sogs byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3456: rang khros pas dge slonga gzhan la brdeg gam brdega
NK120(e)001:3457: tu bcug pas phog pa na brdeg thang de snyed
NK120(e)001:3458: kyi grangs dang / dgu pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3459: khros pas dge slong gzhan la brdeg par brtsam pa ste brdeg tshul byas pa des go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3461: mthol yul mtshan nyid ldan pa'i dbus su /
NK120(e)001:3462: dge slong gzhan la gnas ngana lena gyi ltung ba
NK120(e)001:3463: pham lhag gang rung byung ba ngo shes sam the
NK120(e)001:3464: tshom za ba la dgos pa khyad par can med
NK120(e)001:3465: bzhin du 'achaba ste mtshan mtha' 'das na ltung byed
NK120(e)001:3467: pham lhag las gzhan pa'i ltung ba gzhan 'chab na nyes byas so //
NK120(e)001:3468: bcu tshan drug pa khyim dang sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3469: dge slong zas gcod me la reg tu bcug /
NK120(e)001:3470: dge 'dun las la 'dun phul phyir ldog smra //
NK120(e)001:3471: bsnyen ma rdzogs dang nub gnyis lhag par nyal //
NK120(e)001:3472: sdig lta'i chos lugs mi gtong phebs par smra //
NK120(e)001:3473: dge tshul sdig lta mi gtong lhan cig nyal //
NK120(e)001:3474: rung ba'i tshon min kha dog can gos gyon //
NK120(e)001:3475: rin chen dmag chas rol mo'i chas la reg /
NK120(e)001:3476: tsha dus rang gar khrus byed /
NK120(e)001:3479: dge slonga gzhan la khyim pas dus rung gi zasa
NK120(e)001:3480: 'dren pa na ngan sems kyis de 'gog pa'i tshig
NK120(e)001:3481: smras nas gcod du bcug pa khyim pas go ba
NK120(e)001:3483: rgod bag gi bsam pas me la rega gam reg tu bcug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3484: 'dir chos ldan gyi bya ba'i ched du gnang ba yin snyam pas dus dran bsten dgos so //
NK120(e)001:3486: dge 'duna gyis dge slong gi ched du lasa byas
NK120(e)001:3487: shing chags pa la dang po 'duna pa phul nas
NK120(e)001:3488: phyis 'dun pa phyir byin cig ces ldog pa'i tshig
NK120(e)001:3491: bsnyen par ma rdzogas pa dang lhan cig gnas gcig
NK120(e)001:3492: tu rkyen dgos med par nub gnyis las lhag para
NK120(e)001:3493: nyal bas nub gsum 'das te bzhi pa'i skya rengs
NK120(e)001:3494: shar ba dang / gal te gnas khang gcig tu
NK120(e)001:3495: nyal yang khru phyed dang dgus chod na ltung ba
NK120(e)001:3496: shar ba dang / med do // lnga pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3497: chang 'thung ba dang phyi dro za ba sogs la
NK120(e)001:3498: nyes pa med do zhes sdig pa can gyi lta
NK120(e)001:3499: ba'i chosa lugas smra ba nyid bzlog byed lnga'i mtha'
NK120(e)001:3502: dge 'dun gyi gnas nas phyung ba'i dge slong dang
NK120(e)001:3503: lhan cig gtam phebas para smra ba sogs spyod lam
NK120(e)001:3504: mthun pas mtshan matha'i skad cig 'das pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3506: dge tshul sdig lta mi gtong ba dge 'dun gyis
NK120(e)001:3507: bsnyil ba dang lhan cig nyal ba sogs spyod lam
NK120(e)001:3508: mthun pas mtshan mtha' 'das pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3510: chu tshag ma gtogs runga ba'i tshona gsum gyis kha
NK120(e)001:3511: bsgyur ba mina pa kha doga dkar po can gyi
NK120(e)001:3512: gosa khru gang yan chad gzhan gyi ma g.yogs par
NK120(e)001:3515: tshon chen brgyad kyis bsgyur ba gyon na nyes byas so //
NK120(e)001:3518: sbyin bdag bsod nams 'dod pas bstabs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3519: chos 'chad pa sogs don khyad par can sgrub pa'i
NK120(e)001:3520: skabs ma yin par rang la mi dbang ba'i nor
NK120(e)001:3521: bu mu tig sogs rina chena dang /
NK120(e)001:3523: rnga bo che sogs rola mo'i chasa la rgod bag gis rang ngam bskos pas rega pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3525: dbyar zla gsum dang na ba sogs gnang ba'i dus min par /
NK120(e)001:3526: tsha ba cung tsam yod pa'i dus su sngar khrus
NK120(e)001:3527: byas nas ring por ma lon bzhin ranga gar khrus
NK120(e)001:3528: byed cing lus phyed chur nub pa na ltung bar
NK120(e)001:3530: bcu tshan bdun pa bsam pa sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3532: dge slong byas la 'gyod bskyed gag tshil bsgog /
NK120(e)001:3533: chur rtse bud med gnas gcig nyal ba dang //
NK120(e)001:3534: dge slong dngangs byed de yi yo byad sbed //
NK120(e)001:3535: sngar byin gdengs med slar blangs spyod pa dang //
NK120(e)001:3536: gzhi med skur btab bud med lhan cig tu //
NK120(e)001:3540: gsod sems kyis dud 'gro'i rigs gsod dam gsoda du
NK120(e)001:3541: bcug nas ji snyed shi ba de snyed kyi dang
NK120(e)001:3543: dge slong byas pa gzhan la khyod sdom pa ma
NK120(e)001:3544: skyes zhes sam yang na nyams so zhes sogs 'gyod
NK120(e)001:3545: pa bskyed pa'i tshig smras pa des go ba dang
NK120(e)001:3547: dge slong gzhan gyi lus skyi g.ya' bar bya ba'i
NK120(e)001:3548: phyir mchan khung sogs la reg ste gaga tshila bsgoga
NK120(e)001:3550: rgod bag gi bsam pas lus phyed nub pa'i chur rtse ba'am rtser bcug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3552: khrims grogs med par dge slong bud meda dang lhan
NK120(e)001:3553: cig gansa gciga tu nyal ba na mtshan mtha' 'das
NK120(e)001:3555: dge slonga gzhan dangngas par byed 'dod pas 'jigs snang
NK120(e)001:3556: sna tshogs ston nam ston du bcug pas de dngangs
NK120(e)001:3559: dge slong sogs rab byung sde lnga gang yang rung
NK120(e)001:3560: ba de yi chos gos dang lhung bzed sogs 'tsho
NK120(e)001:3561: ba'i yo byad gang rung rku 'dod dang /
NK120(e)001:3562: phan sems min par sbed dam sbed du bcug nas sbas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3564: dge slong gzhan la sngar rang gis gos byin pa
NK120(e)001:3565: rku sems dang yid bcug min par des gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:3566: gdengas meda bzhin slar blangas nas ci dgar longs spyod
NK120(e)001:3568: mthong thos dogs gsum gyi gzhi meda pa'i dge slong
NK120(e)001:3569: gzhan la lhag ma bcu gsum gang rung gis skur
NK120(e)001:3570: pa btab pa des go ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3572: nye min bud meda dang lhan ciga tu skyes pa'i
NK120(e)001:3573: khrims grogs meda para lam du 'gro na rgyangs grags
NK120(e)001:3574: re la ltung ba re dang /
NK120(e)001:3575: de'i phyed la nyes byas su 'gyur ba rnams so //
NK120(e)001:3576: bcu tshan brgyad pa mgron mang rkun ma la sogs pa'i sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3578: nyi shu ma lon pa la bsnyen rdzogs phog /
NK120(e)001:3579: sa brko mgron bos zla bzhi lhag par zos //
NK120(e)001:3580: mi shes brjod dang 'thab pa'i nyan rna byed //
NK120(e)001:3581: nyes med mi smra 'gro dang mi gus 'gal //
NK120(e)001:3582: chang 'thung sdus min phyi dro grong du rgyu //
NK120(e)001:3585: sho gam ma byin pa'am rkuna ma dang lhan cig
NK120(e)001:3586: 'gro na'nga snga ma dang mtshungsa te rgyangs grags 'das
NK120(e)001:3588: bsgrub bya skyes pa mngal bshol brtsis kyang lo nyi
NK120(e)001:3589: shu ma lona pa la der shes sam yid gnyis
NK120(e)001:3590: kyis bsnyen rdzogas phoga na las brjod pa gsum pa'i
NK120(e)001:3591: bya ba brjod pa rdzogs nas byed pa brjod pa
NK120(e)001:3592: 'go rtsom pa'i tshe mkhan po la ltung byed dang
NK120(e)001:3593: / slob dpon dang dge 'dun la nyes byas su gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3595: dgos pa khyad par can med par sor bzhi yan chad kyi sa brko ba'am brkor bcug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3597: sbyin bdag gis dus ji tsam mgrona du bosa pa las lhag par 'dug gam /
NK120(e)001:3598: tshigs bzhag pa med na zla ba bzhi las lhag par bsdad nas zosa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3600: dge slong gzhan gyis rang la bslab bskul byed pa
NK120(e)001:3601: na bskul ba po la khyed kyi mi shes pas
NK120(e)001:3602: gzhan la ma dris par mi slob bo zhes pa
NK120(e)001:3603: lta bu khyad gsod kyi tshig brjod pa go ba
NK120(e)001:3605: rang dang rtsod zlar gyur pa'i dge slong gzhan gnyis
NK120(e)001:3606: yan chod gros byed pa la 'thab mo pa de
NK120(e)001:3607: slar spar ba'i ched du nyan rna byed pas rang
NK120(e)001:3610: rang kha skong du 'os pa'i gos sbyong sogs chos
NK120(e)001:3611: ldan gyi las gral du 'dus nas gsol ba tsam
NK120(e)001:3612: yang ma byas pa'i gong du dge 'dun mthun pa
NK120(e)001:3613: sgrub byed kyi 'dun pa ma phul ba'am ltag 'og
NK120(e)001:3614: gi dge slong la nyes pa med par cang mi
NK120(e)001:3615: smra bar 'gro ba ste thos pa'i nyes 'khor las
NK120(e)001:3616: 'das pa dang / gsol ba thos nas phyin na nyes byas dang /
NK120(e)001:3617: rang kha skong du mi 'os pa sogs ltung ba med do //
NK120(e)001:3619: ston pa sangs rgyas sam dge 'dun nam dge 'dun
NK120(e)001:3620: zhal ta bas rang la chos ldan gyi bka' bsgo
NK120(e)001:3621: ba'i don la bdag gis bsgrub mi nus pa'i tshul
NK120(e)001:3622: gyis shad sbyang med par mi gusa pa'i rnam pas
NK120(e)001:3626: rgun chang sogs bcos pa'i chang dang /
NK120(e)001:3627: de dag gi sbang ma sogs myos pa'i nus pa
NK120(e)001:3628: can 'thunga ngam za 'dod kyis mgul du mid pa
NK120(e)001:3629: dang / gal te bskol bas chang gi ro nus nyams par byas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3630: nad la phan pa 'i phyir khar bsrel ba tsam dang /
NK120(e)001:3631: lus la bskus pa tsam byas na nyes pa med do //
NK120(e)001:3633: dus mina par rang gling gi nyi ma byed yol
NK120(e)001:3634: nas phyi dro phan chad sang skya rengs ma shar
NK120(e)001:3635: gyi bar rkyen dgos med par der 'khod kyi grogs
NK120(e)001:3636: la ma smras par khyim pa'i grong du rgyu bar
NK120(e)001:3637: byed pas rang gi sgo gtan dang nye 'khor las
NK120(e)001:3638: 'das na ltung bar 'gyur ba rnams so //
NK120(e)001:3639: bcu tshan dgu pa chos ston sogs kyi sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3640: zas bcas phyi dro rgyu dang khyim gsum 'das //
NK120(e)001:3641: rgyal po btsun mor rtse ba'i khab tu nyal //
NK120(e)001:3642: mdo sogs 'don la da gdod shes zer dang //
NK120(e)001:3643: rin chen khab ral khri rkang tshad lhag bzos //
NK120(e)001:3644: ngan sems shing bal khri steng brdal te bgos //
NK120(e)001:3645: gding g.yan ras chen chos gos tshad lhag go //
NK120(e)001:3648: dge slong gis snga dro rang tshig gis dge 'dun
NK120(e)001:3649: rnams khyim pa'i gnas su zasa la spyan drangs nas
NK120(e)001:3650: / sbyin bdag la dang ba dang bacasa dus la
NK120(e)001:3651: brim zhes ma bsgos par rang nyid khyim nas khyim
NK120(e)001:3652: gsum bar du rgyu bas dge 'dun gyi gdugs tshod
NK120(e)001:3654: phyi dro yang khyim nas khyim du rgyu ba dang
NK120(e)001:3655: bcas pas khyim gsum phan chad 'adsa pas dge 'dun
NK120(e)001:3656: gyi chos kyi longs spyod la gnas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3658: chos ldan gyi don du bos pa sogs dgos pa
NK120(e)001:3659: khyad par can med bzhin rgyal po btsuna mora rtse
NK120(e)001:3660: ba ste btsun mo dang bcas pa'i khaba tu nyi
NK120(e)001:3661: ma dmar thag chod nas skya rengs tha ma ma
NK120(e)001:3662: shar gyi bar 'gro na de'i nye 'khor las 'das
NK120(e)001:3663: par slebs pa'am nyin mo phyin nas mtshan mo nyal
NK120(e)001:3665: so thar gyi mdo sogs 'dona pa la lan gnyis
NK120(e)001:3666: yan chad thos shing mdo de la don de yod
NK120(e)001:3667: par sngar nas shes kyang don 'di yod pa da
NK120(e)001:3668: gdoda shes so zhes 'dul bar gtogs pa'i bslab pa
NK120(e)001:3669: khyad gsod kyi tshig zera pha rol pos go ba
NK120(e)001:3671: ba so sogs rina thang chen po'i rigs kyis khab
NK120(e)001:3672: rala byed dam byed du bcug ste zin pa dang
NK120(e)001:3674: dge slong gis khri'am khri'u'i rkanga pa khru gang gi
NK120(e)001:3675: tshad las lhag par bzos pa'am bzor bcug ste bzosa
NK120(e)001:3676: zin pa dang / drug pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3677: dge slong gis ngana semas kyis shinga bala dge 'dun
NK120(e)001:3678: gyi khri'am khri'u'i steng du brdala te bgosa par byas
NK120(e)001:3680: gdinga ba srid du khru gsum dang zheng du khru do dang sor drug /
NK120(e)001:3682: gayana dgab srid du khru drug dang /
NK120(e)001:3685: rasa cheena srid du khru dgu dang /
NK120(e)001:3686: zheng du khru gsum dang sor bco brgyad tshad yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3688: rang re la ston pa'i sku lus kyi tshad tsam
NK120(e)001:3689: med par de'i chosa gosa kyi tshad dam de las
NK120(e)001:3690: lhag par byed du bcug ste zin pa na ltung
NK120(e)001:3692: de la ston pa'i chos gos kyi tshad ni srid
NK120(e)001:3693: du ston pa nyid kyi khru lnga yin pas mi
NK120(e)001:3694: phal pa'i khru bco lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:3695: zheng du ston pa'i khru gsum la phal pa'i khru dgu yod do //
NK120(e)001:3699: chos gos rnams tshad las lhag par brgal 'dug na bshags dgos pas /
NK120(e)001:3700: de'i tshe khab ral bcag cing shing bal bsdu /
NK120(e)001:3701: khri rkang dang gos tshad lhag song ba rnams bcad nas /
NK120(e)001:3705: zhes dri nas ma bshags na nyes byas so //
NK120(e)001:3706: lnga pa sor bshags kyi sde la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:3709: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3710: so sor bshags bya'i sde ni bzhi yin te /
NK120(e)001:3712: smre sngags kyi rnam pas so sora bashagas par bya
NK120(e)001:3713: ba'i sde tshan bshad pa ni rab byung dang khyim
NK120(e)001:3714: pa'i gzhi las gyur pa gnyis su phye bas bzhira
NK120(e)001:3717: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3718: dge slong ma las grong du zas bslangs zos //
NK120(e)001:3719: khyim du dge slong mas bsgos ma bzlog zos //
NK120(e)001:3720: bslab sdom sbyin las rung min bslangs te zos //
NK120(e)001:3721: nags ma nyul bar dgon par bslangs zos bzhi'o //
NK120(e)001:3724: nye du ma yin pa'i dge slonga mas rang nyid
NK120(e)001:3725: kyis bza' ba'i ched du bsgrubs pa'i dus rung gi
NK120(e)001:3726: zas de lasa gronga ngam de'i nye 'khor dang lam
NK120(e)001:3727: po che gang rung du zas de nyid bslangsa te
NK120(e)001:3728: zosa pa dang / gnyis pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3729: sbyin bdag gis mgron du bos pa'i khyim du dge
NK120(e)001:3730: slonga mas gral rim par 'brim du mi 'jug par
NK120(e)001:3731: nga'i mgron 'di la 'di drong zhes bsgosa nas 'brim
NK120(e)001:3732: bcug pa dge slong gcig gi ma bzlog par dge
NK120(e)001:3733: slong ji snyed pas zosa pa las sor bshags su
NK120(e)001:3735: dge 'dun blo mthun pas gsol ba'i las kyis khyim
NK120(e)001:3736: pa ci rigs las dgag bya dang dgos pa'i dbang
NK120(e)001:3737: gis zas mi slong ba'i bslab sdom sbyin pa na
NK120(e)001:3738: / khrims der gtogs pa'i dge slong gi de lasa
NK120(e)001:3739: len du rung ba lo ma la sogs pa mod
NK120(e)001:3740: pa mina pa'i dus rung gi zas bslangs te zosa
NK120(e)001:3742: grong las rgyangs grags dpags pa'i 'jigs bcas kyi gnas
NK120(e)001:3743: su dge 'dun gyis nags nyul bar bskos pa'i dge
NK120(e)001:3744: slong gis dge 'dun dang sbyin bdag gi gnod pa
NK120(e)001:3745: bsrung ba'i bya ba 'dis ci bya snyam pas nagas
NK120(e)001:3746: ma nyul bar dgona para khyim pa las dus rung
NK120(e)001:3747: gi zas blangsa te zosa pa dang bzhi'o //
NK120(e)001:3748: drug pa nyes byas kyi sde la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:3751: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3752: nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis zhes grags pa //
NK120(e)001:3754: nyes pa phra mo'i rang bzhin yin pas nyes byas
NK120(e)001:3755: zhes bya ste de la grangs ni sdoms kyis bsdus
NK120(e)001:3756: pa brgya dang bcu gnyis zhesa gragas pa rnams 'di
NK120(e)001:3758: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK120(e)001:3760: dang po gos bgo ba'i sde ni /
NK120(e)001:3761: sham thabs zlum min brtsengs 'jol glang sna 'dra //
NK120(e)001:3762: lteb dang phur ma gdengs ka lta bu bdun //
NK120(e)001:3763: zlum min ring thung stod gsum gos kyi bcu //
NK120(e)001:3765: shama thabas yas mas mtho dman mi mnyam pas zlum por bgo ba mina pa dang 1 /
NK120(e)001:3766: ha cang brtsengsa che bas pus mor slebs pa dang 2 /
NK120(e)001:3767: 'jola che bas long bu la reg pa dang 3 /
NK120(e)001:3768: glang po'i sna dang 'dra bas mas zur gyi grwa mdun rgyab tu 'chang ba dang 4 /
NK120(e)001:3769: ska rags kyi gong du t+aa li'i lo ma ltar blteb pa 5dang /
NK120(e)001:3770: ska rags kyi bar nas 'bru'i phur ma ltar 'bur ba dang 6 /
NK120(e)001:3771: ska rags kyi steng du sbrul gyi gdengas ka lta
NK120(e)001:3772: bu mtho dman 'dug pa 7ste mi byed pa bduna
NK120(e)001:3773: dang / snam sbyar dang bla gos zlum por bgos pa mina pa dang 8 /
NK120(e)001:3775: ha cang thunga ba ma yin pa ste stod kyi
NK120(e)001:3776: gyon lugs gsum bcas gos kyi bgo tshul la nyes
NK120(e)001:3778: gnyis pa spyod yul du 'gro ba'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3779: ma bsdams bgo ba ca co mig g.yeng dang /
NK120(e)001:3780: ring lta mgo bstums gos bardzesa phrag la gzar //
NK120(e)001:3781: lag pa gnya' gong bsnol dang ltag par bsnol //
NK120(e)001:3782: mchongs brkyang rkang pa'i brang dang rting btsugs 'gro //
NK120(e)001:3783: lag pa dkur brten lus bsgyur lag pa g.yugs //
NK120(e)001:3784: mgo bsgyur phrag pa sprad dang lag sbrel rnams //
NK120(e)001:3785: mi byed khyim 'gro'i spyod pa nyi shu'o //
NK120(e)001:3787: khyim du 'gro ba'i tshe dran shes kyis lus ngag ma bsdamas pa dang 1 /
NK120(e)001:3788: bla gos mthang gos sogs med pa'am legs par bgo ba ma yin pa 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3789: rang dgar ca co'i sgra byed pa 3dang /
NK120(e)001:3790: miga g.yas g.yon du g.yenga bas blta ba dang 4 /
NK120(e)001:3791: mig gnya' shing gang las ringa bar blta ba dang 5 /
NK120(e)001:3792: mgo gos kyis bstumsa pa dang 6 /
NK120(e)001:3793: sham thabs sogs gosa 'doms snang bar bardzesa pa dang 7 /
NK120(e)001:3794: bla gos phraga pa'i phyogs gnyis la gazara ba dang 8 /
NK120(e)001:3795: lag pa gnyis gnya' gonga du bsnol dang 9 /
NK120(e)001:3796: lag gnyis ltag para bsnol ba dang 10 /
NK120(e)001:3798: gom pa che bas sgyid pa brkyang ba dang 12 /
NK120(e)001:3799: rting pa btegs nas rkang pa'i brang gis 'gro ba dang 13 /
NK120(e)001:3800: rting pa btsugas te tsog pus 'gro ba dang 14 /
NK120(e)001:3801: lag pa dkur brten nas gru mo brgyangs te 'gro ba dang 15 /
NK120(e)001:3802: lus dkyogs por bsgyur te 'gro ba 16dang /
NK120(e)001:3803: lag pa gnyis g.yugs bzhin 'gro ba dang 17 /
NK120(e)001:3804: mgo g.yas g.yon du bsgyur nas 'gro ba dang 18 /
NK120(e)001:3805: gzhan dang phraga pa sprad de 'gro ba 19dang /
NK120(e)001:3806: gzhan dang lag pa sbrel te 'gro ba rnams mi
NK120(e)001:3807: byed par zhi dul gyis khyim du 'gro ba'i spyod
NK120(e)001:3808: pa nyi shu 20rnams la bslab par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:3809: gsum pa stan la 'dug pa'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3810: stan la ma bsgos ma brtags 'phongs brdeg dang //
NK120(e)001:3811: rkang brkyang bsnol dang barla bsnol long bu brtsegs //
NK120(e)001:3812: khri 'og rkang dgug rkang pa gdangs te 'dug /'doms mthong rnam spangs 'dug tshul dgu yin no //
NK120(e)001:3814: gzhan gyi khyim du stan la khyim bdag gis ma bsgosa par 'dug pa dang 1 /
NK120(e)001:3815: srog chags yod med ma brtagas par 'dug pa 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3816: lus ljid phab nas 'phongsa brdega gis 'dug pa 3dang /
NK120(e)001:3817: rkanga pa brkyang ste bsnol nas 'dug pa dang 4 /
NK120(e)001:3819: long bu'i steng du longa bu brtsegas nas 'dug pa 6dang /
NK120(e)001:3820: hor 'dug gi rnam pas khri 'oga tu rkanga pa dgug nas 'dug pa 7dang /
NK120(e)001:3821: rkanga pa phan tshun gadngas te 'duga pa dang 8 /
NK120(e)001:3822: 'domas mthonga bar byas nas 'dug pa rnams spangas te
NK120(e)001:3823: skyil krung sogs 'duga tshul legs pas 'dug pa bcas
NK120(e)001:3824: dgu po la bslab par bya ba yina no //
NK120(e)001:3825: bzhi pa zas bslang ba'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3826: legs par mi len mu kha mnyam par len //
NK120(e)001:3827: mthar chags mi len lhung bzed zur mig blta //
NK120(e)001:3828: bzed sngas sngar byung sbas nas bzed pa dang //
NK120(e)001:3829: snod gzhan steng bzed spang ba zas blang brgyad //
NK120(e)001:3831: 'dul ba dang mi 'gal bar zas legas par mi lena pa 1dang /
NK120(e)001:3832: lhung bzed kyi mu dang kha da chad du len pa 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3833: 'bras chan dang tshod ma'am zan dang bya na mnyam par lena pa dang 3 /
NK120(e)001:3834: gral rim ltar mathara chagas su mi lena pa4dang /
NK120(e)001:3835: lhung bzeda la yid gtad de mi len par zura miga gis blta 5ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3836: zas 'dren pa po ma slebs par snod bzeda sngas pa 6dang /
NK120(e)001:3837: lhag po 'dod pas zas sngar byung sbas nasa yang bzed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3838: snod gazhana gyi steng du lhung bzeda bzung nas bzed
NK120(e)001:3839: pa rnams spang bar byas te zasa blang ba la
NK120(e)001:3841: lnga pa zas za ba'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3842: 'gal za kham che chung dang ran par min //
NK120(e)001:3843: kha gdangs za bzhin smra dang tsug tsug dang //
NK120(e)001:3844: cag cag hu hu phu phu lce phyung za //
NK120(e)001:3845: 'bru nas gud phye zas la skyon 'phya dang //
NK120(e)001:3846: kham gcig mkhur spo rkan tog kham 'phro bcad //
NK120(e)001:3847: lag pa ldag 'gyog lag sprug skyom skyom byed //
NK120(e)001:3848: mchod rten 'drar byed nyer gcig za tshe spangs //
NK120(e)001:3850: 'dul ba dang 'agla bas legs par mi za ba 1dang /
NK120(e)001:3851: zas kyi khama ha cang che ba 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3853: rang ngam 'jig rten dang mthun pa'i kham rana para mina pa 4dang /
NK120(e)001:3854: kham kha sgor ma slebs gong nas kha gdangsa pa 5dang /
NK120(e)001:3855: za bzhina du gtam smra ba 6dang /
NK120(e)001:3856: za ba'i tshe skyur ba la tsug tsug 7dang /
NK120(e)001:3859: tsha ba la phu phu'i sgra dang bcas pa 10dang /
NK120(e)001:3860: lce phyir phyung nas za ba 11dang /
NK120(e)001:3861: yos sogs 'bru re re nasa gud du phye ste za ba 12dang /
NK120(e)001:3862: zasa la skyon brjod nas 'phya smod byas pa 13dang /
NK120(e)001:3863: khama gciga mkhura ba g.yas g.yon du spo zhing za ba 14dang /
NK120(e)001:3864: rkan tog cing za ba 15 dang /
NK120(e)001:3865: dud 'gro ltar khama 'phro bcad de za ba 16dang /
NK120(e)001:3866: lag pa la zas chags pa lces ldag pa 17dang /
NK120(e)001:3867: lhung bzed dang phor pa sogs lces ldag cing mdzub mo dang thur mas brad nas 'gyoga pa 18dang /
NK120(e)001:3868: lag pa la zas chags pa sprug pa 19dang /
NK120(e)001:3869: zas dang bcas pa'i lhung bzed sogs skyom skyom byed pa 20dang /
NK120(e)001:3870: zas la mchod rten gyis gzugs 'dra bar byed nas
NK120(e)001:3871: gzhom zhing za ba 21rnams te de ltar nyer gciga
NK120(e)001:3872: po zas za ba'i tshe spangsa la tshul bzhin du
NK120(e)001:3873: za ba la bslab par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:3874: drug pa lhung bzed la spyod pa'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3875: lhung bzed la 'phya phyir blta lag pa ni //
NK120(e)001:3876: zas 'bags chu snod mi reg chu mi gtor //
NK120(e)001:3877: ma dris 'bags chu 'pho dang zas lhag bzhag /
NK120(e)001:3878: sa rjen gad kha ri gzar bang rim bzhir //
NK120(e)001:3879: mi bzhag gad g.yang rkan gzar du mi 'khru //
NK120(e)001:3880: langs dang chu drag mi bcu bcu bzhi'o //
NK120(e)001:3882: gzhan gyi lhung bzeda la 'phya ba'i phyir blta bar mi bya ba 1dang /
NK120(e)001:3883: lag pa la ni zasa kyis 'abgas pas chu snod la mi reg pa 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3884: zas dang bcas pa'i 'bags chu drung na yod pa'i dge slong la mi gtora ba 3dang /
NK120(e)001:3885: khyim bdag la ma drisa par zas dang 'bagsa pa'i
NK120(e)001:3886: khrus chu de'i khyim du 'pho bar mi byed pa
NK120(e)001:3887: 4 dang / zasa lhag lhung bzed du bazhaga nas mi 'dor ba 5dang /
NK120(e)001:3888: lhung bzed 'og gzhi med pa'i sa rjena 6dang /
NK120(e)001:3890: ri do chad kyi g.yang gazara po 8dang /
NK120(e)001:3891: ri gzar po ral bar gzhol ba banga rim can te de bzhira mi bazhaga pa 9dang /
NK120(e)001:3894: rkan gazara du lhung bzed mi 'khru ba 12dang /
NK120(e)001:3895: langas te lam gyi gzhi mdo rnams su mi bkru ba 13 dang /
NK120(e)001:3896: 'bab chu drag po'i rgyun las ldog ste lhung bzed
NK120(e)001:3897: kyi chu mi bcu ba ste bcu bzhi 14po la
NK120(e)001:3898: bslab par bya'o // bdun pa chos 'chad pa'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3899: chos ston sde ni langs nyal rang dmar 'dug /
NK120(e)001:3900: mdun nas 'gro la phyi bshad lam po'i 'gram //
NK120(e)001:3901: mgo g.yogs bardzesa gzar lag pa gnya' ltag bsnol //
NK120(e)001:3902: do ker bcings dang zhwa gyon cod pan btags //
NK120(e)001:3903: phreng ba dang ni mgo dkris glang rta zhon //
NK120(e)001:3904: khyogs dang bzhon pa mchil lhwam gyon pa dang //
NK120(e)001:3905: mkhar ba gdugs mtshon ral gri dgra cha mda' //
NK120(e)001:3906: go cha gyon la mi bshad nyer drug go //
NK120(e)001:3908: chosa ston pa'i sde tshan 'di ni nyan pa po
NK120(e)001:3909: min bzhin du 'dug pa la 'chad pa po langas
NK120(e)001:3911: de bzhin du nyan pa po mal sar nyal nas yod pa can 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3912: nyan pa po stan mtho sar 'dug pa la ranga nyid dam'a bar 'duga nas 3dang /
NK120(e)001:3913: mduna nasa 'gro ba la phyi bzhin 'ong nas bshad pa 4dang /
NK120(e)001:3914: lam po'i dbus nas 'gro ba la 'grama nas 'gro bzhin pas 5dang /
NK120(e)001:3915: mi na bar mgo gos sogs kyis g.yogas pa 6dang /
NK120(e)001:3918: lag pa gnyis gnya' gong du bsnol ba 9dang /
NK120(e)001:3920: skra spyi bor bsdus nas do ker te thor cog bcingsa pa 11dang /
NK120(e)001:3922: mgo la cod pana btagsa pa 13dang /
NK120(e)001:3923: mgo la rgyan gyi phreng ba bcings pa 14dang ni /
NK120(e)001:3924: mgora lwa thod kyis dkris pa 15dang /
NK120(e)001:3925: glanga po che la zhon pa 16dang /
NK120(e)001:3928: bzhona pa gzhan shing rta sogs la zhon pa 19dang /
NK120(e)001:3930: lag na mkhar ba thogs pa 21dang /
NK120(e)001:3932: mdung sogs mtshona cha thogs pa 23dang /
NK120(e)001:3934: dgra cha ste mad'a gzhu thogs pa 25dang /
NK120(e)001:3935: go cha gyon pa rnams la chos mi bashada pa
NK120(e)001:3936: ste 26nyer druga por bslab par byas nas tshul bzhin
NK120(e)001:3938: de yang nyan pa po na ba'i rkyen dbang du gyur pa sogs la ni nyes pa med do //
NK120(e)001:3939: brgyad pa sgrub pa'i sde tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:3940: sgrub tshul gsum ni 'grengs te bshang gci 'dor //
NK120(e)001:3941: chu dang r+ts+wa la bshang gci snabs mi 'dor //
NK120(e)001:3943: sgrub pa'i tshul la bslab bya gsum po ni mi
NK120(e)001:3944: na bar 'grengas te bashanga gci mi 'dora ba 1dang
NK120(e)001:3945: / gzhan du 'dor sa ma rnyed pa'i rkyen med par chu yi nang du 2dang /
NK120(e)001:3946: r+ts+wa sngon po yod pa'i phyogs la gashanga gci dang
NK120(e)001:3947: mchil snabsa stugs pa sogs mi 'dora ba la bslab
NK120(e)001:3948: par 3bya'o // dgu pa rgyu ba'i bslab bya gcig ni /
NK120(e)001:3949: shing la mi gang mthor 'dzeg rgyu gcig go //
NK120(e)001:3951: stag la sogs pa'i gnod pa med par shinga la
NK120(e)001:3952: mi ganga tsam las mtho bar 'dzegas par mi bya
NK120(e)001:3953: ba ste rgyu ba'i bslab bya gciga go ////
NK120(e)001:3954: gnyis pa dge slong ma'i dgag pa'i bslab bya bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:3955: dge slong ma la pham brgyad lhag nyi shu //
NK120(e)001:3956: spang ltung so gsum ltung byed brgya brgyad cu //
NK120(e)001:3957: sor bshags bcu gcig nyes byas brgya bcu gnyis //
NK120(e)001:3958: sum brgya drug cu rtsa bzhi mdo tsam mo //
NK120(e)001:3960: dge slonga ma'i dgag pa'i bslab bya la mi tshangs par spyod pa sogs thun mong ba bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:3961: reg pa lus bkan 'chab dang bzlog pa'o //
NK120(e)001:3962: zhes thun min bzhi ste phama pa brgyad dang /
NK120(e)001:3963: smyan byas pa gzhi med nas bka' blo mi bde ba'i bar thun mong ba bdun dang /
NK120(e)001:3964: lci yang len pa sogs thun min bcu gsum ste lhag ma nyi shu dang /
NK120(e)001:3965: 'chang bral 'jog gsum thun mong ba bcu dgu dang /
NK120(e)001:3966: lhung bzed lhag po zhag gcig 'das bar 'chang ba
NK120(e)001:3967: sogs thun min bcu bzhi ste spang ba'i ltung ba
NK120(e)001:3968: so gsuma dang / shes bzhin rdzun smra sogs thun mong ba bdun cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK120(e)001:3969: bsnyen par rdzogs nas lo bcu gnyis ma lon par
NK120(e)001:3970: gzhan gyi mkhan mo byed pa sogs thun min brgya
NK120(e)001:3971: dang brgyad de ltung byed brgya dang brgyad cu dang
NK120(e)001:3972: / bslab pa bral te khyim du 'jug pa thun mong ba gcig dang /
NK120(e)001:3973: 'o zho mar zhun slong ba sogs thun min bcu ste sora bashagas bcu gciga po dang /
NK120(e)001:3974: ma bsgos par stan la 'dug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3975: r+ts+wa sngon khrod du mi gtsang ba 'dor ba ma gtogs pa'i thun mong ba brgya dang bcu /
NK120(e)001:3976: sham thabs rnyed pa snang bar dkri ba dang /
NK120(e)001:3977: chags pas khyim gzhan du 'gro ba ste thun min
NK120(e)001:3978: gnyis dang bcas nyes byas brgya dang bcu gnyis te
NK120(e)001:3979: / thams cad bsdoms pas sum brgya dang drug cu rtsa bzhi bsrung bar bya ba yin na'ang /
NK120(e)001:3980: bod 'dir dge slong ma'i sdom rgyun ma dar bas mdora bsdus pa de tsam mo //
NK120(e)001:3981: gnyis pa mthun phyogs bsgrub pa'i bslab bya la gsum /
NK120(e)001:3982: bslab pa yongs su sbyong ba'i gzhi gsum /
NK120(e)001:3983: bde bar gnas pa'i rkyen gyi gzhi lnga /
NK120(e)001:3984: 'dir ma smos kyang thams cad la khyab pa las kyi gazhi'o //
NK120(e)001:3986: bsgrub pa'i bslab bya yongs su sbyong ba'i tshul //
NK120(e)001:3987: gso sbyong dbyar gnas dgag dbye //
NK120(e)001:3989: mthun phyogs bsgrub pa'i bslaba bya ni skyon yongas su
NK120(e)001:3990: sbyong ba'i tshul gyis bslab pa nyid gong nas gong
NK120(e)001:3991: du 'phel ba'i thabs bslab pa nyams pa gso zhing
NK120(e)001:3992: spang bya sdig pa sbyong ba'i gzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:3993: dgos ched rnam pa bcu'i phyir dbyar snga phyi gang rung la zla ba gsum du gansa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:3994: de'i ring la ltung ba gleng ba dang rdzas bgo ba dagga par skabs dbye ba'o //
NK120(e)001:3995: 'di dag cung zad zhib tu 'chad na /
NK120(e)001:3996: spyir 'dul ba gzhis bstan don gzhi bcu bdun yod pa las /
NK120(e)001:3997: dang po rab byung gi gzhi ni sdom pa ma thob pa thob pa'i tshul te sngon du song /
NK120(e)001:3998: de ltar thob pa'i bslab pa yongs sbyong gi gzhi la /
NK120(e)001:4001: dgag dbye gsum gtso bor ston pa las /
NK120(e)001:4002: dang po gso sbyong gi tshul la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4003: sngar bsags kyi sgrib pa sbyong zhing lhag pa sems
NK120(e)001:4004: dang shes rab dag par bya ba'i phyir gzhi gnas
NK120(e)001:4006: phyis 'byung gi rgyun tshe 'di'i zag pa sdom zhing
NK120(e)001:4007: lhag pa tshul khrims dag par bya ba'i phyir mthun
NK120(e)001:4010: gzhi tshul khrims la gnas pa'i gang zag 'dod chung chog shes dang ldan pa des /
NK120(e)001:4011: lam gyi rgyu sde snod kyi gzhung thos shing /
NK120(e)001:4013: bsam don bsgom par byed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:4014: de la spong ba'i gnas der 'gal spong mthun sgrub kyi rkyen tshogs pa na /
NK120(e)001:4015: bsgom bya lam gyi ngo bo la /
NK120(e)001:4019: 'dod chags shas che ba'i gnyen por mi sdug pa bsgom pa ste /
NK120(e)001:4020: mdog dbyibs reg bya bsnyen bkur la //
NK120(e)001:4021: chags pa'i gnyen po 'du shes dgu //
NK120(e)001:4025: bem po'i 8rang bzhin g.yo ba med9 //
NK120(e)001:4027: zhe sdang gi gnyen por byams pa bsgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4028: gti mug gi gnyen por rten cing 'brel bar 'byung bar bsgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4029: rnam rtog shas che ba'i gnyen por /
NK120(e)001:4031: sems dmigs pa gtad nas 'jog par byed /
NK120(e)001:4032: de'i rgyun g.yeng bar mi 'gyur bas kun tu 'jog par byed /
NK120(e)001:4033: rnam par g.yeng na slar yang nges par 'jog par byed /
NK120(e)001:4034: yang sems nang du bsdu bas nye bar 'jog par byed /
NK120(e)001:4035: ting nge 'dzin la sems mi dga' ba dul bar byed /
NK120(e)001:4036: nyon mongs ba dang rnam rtog zhi bar byed /
NK120(e)001:4037: sgrib pa lnga nye bar zhi bar byed /
NK120(e)001:4038: 'du byed pa dang bcas pas rgyud gcig tu byed /
NK120(e)001:4039: 'du byed pa med par mnyam par 'jog par byed /
NK120(e)001:4041: sems gnas pa'i thabs dgus 'dod pa'i sems rags pa
NK120(e)001:4042: zhi bar byas nas zhi gnas 'grub par byed pa'o
NK120(e)001:4045: zhi gnas grub par gyur pa yis //
NK120(e)001:4046: dran pa nyer bzhag bsgom par bya //
NK120(e)001:4047: zhes pas lus tshor sems chos bzhi la gtsang bde rtag bdag tu lta ba'i gnyen por /
NK120(e)001:4048: rang mtshan mi gtsang ba sogs dang /
NK120(e)001:4049: spyi mtshan mi rtag pa sogs bzhir bsgom pa'i rnal 'byor la spyod cing /
NK120(e)001:4050: de ltar tshogs lam la sogs pa'i lam lnga byang phyogs so bdun gyi rim pas bgrod de /
NK120(e)001:4051: rgyun zhugs la sogs pa'i 'bras bu bzhi thob par byed pa 'o //
NK120(e)001:4052: gnyis pa phyis 'byung gi rgyun tshe 'di'i zag pa
NK120(e)001:4053: sdom zhing lhag pa tshul khrims dag par bya ba'i
NK120(e)001:4054: phyir mthun pa'i gso sbyong ni /
NK120(e)001:4056: mthun pa'i gso sbyong ni rnam pa lnga ste /
NK120(e)001:4059: bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong dang /
NK120(e)001:4060: gnod pa dbyung ba'i gso sbyong dang /
NK120(e)001:4061: bsdum pa'i gso sbyong dang lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:4063: spyir gso sbyong gi tshul ji ltar bya ba la /
NK120(e)001:4064: ltung ba bshags sdom byin brlab bya ba sogs nas bag yod par gdams pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4065: ma lhags pa yod na 'dun pa blangs nas brjod
NK120(e)001:4066: pa'i bar sbyor ba'i chos rnams sngon du song nas
NK120(e)001:4067: / dge 'dun thugs bstun te mdo 'don pa dngos gzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:4068: de la dang po bcu bzhi pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4070: rgyal dang dbo dang sa ga dang //
NK120(e)001:4071: chu stod khrums smad smin drug bcas //
NK120(e)001:4072: 'di rnams kyis ni nag po'i phyogs //
NK120(e)001:4073: zla phyed gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4074: zhes pa ltar lo re la gso sbyong bcu bzhi pa drug dang /
NK120(e)001:4075: gnyis pa bco lnga pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4076: zla ba de rnams kyi yar ngo'i drug dang /
NK120(e)001:4077: zla ba gzhan drug po'i yar ngo mar ngo'i drug
NK120(e)001:4078: drug ste bco brgyad la gso sbyong bco lnga pa
NK120(e)001:4079: byed pa ni zhag mi thub pa dor ba'i dbang
NK120(e)001:4080: gis so // de dag ni dus nges pa'i gso sbyong ngo //
NK120(e)001:4081: gsum pa bkra shis pa'i gso sbyong ni /
NK120(e)001:4082: rten gsum rab tu gnas pa sogs dmigs bsal bkra shis pa'i dus su bya ba'o //
NK120(e)001:4083: bzhi pa gnod pa dbyung ba'i gso sbyong ni /
NK120(e)001:4084: nad yams sogs gnod pa byung zin bzlog pa'am /
NK120(e)001:4085: slar mi 'byung ba'i phyir byed pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4086: lnga pa bsdum pa'i gso spyong ni /
NK120(e)001:4087: dge 'dun rnams dbyen bsdum pa'am 'khon pa bsdum pa'i phyir bya ba'o //
NK120(e)001:4088: 'di rnams ni dus ma nges pa'i gso sbyong zhes bya ste /
NK120(e)001:4089: gsol ba'i las kyi tshe rang rang gi dus brjod
NK120(e)001:4090: dgos pa'i khyad par tsam ma gtogs gzhan cho ga
NK120(e)001:4091: thams cad dus nges pa'i gso sbyong dang 'dra'o //
NK120(e)001:4092: de ltar gso sbyong gi tshul la /
NK120(e)001:4093: gnas der dge slong gsum man chad las med na dus kyi bar du bsgug pa'am /
NK120(e)001:4094: yang na gso sbyong yod pa'i gnas su 'gro ba'am /
NK120(e)001:4095: de ltar ma grub na dmigs bsal gyi cho ga ni /
NK120(e)001:4096: phan tshun gcig gi mdun du gcig 'dug nas byin gyis brlab cing /
NK120(e)001:4097: rang gcig pu las med na yid kyis bsam zhing brjod /
NK120(e)001:4098: de tsam yang ma grub na thub pa'i sngon gyi
NK120(e)001:4099: gso sbyong tshigs su bcad pa phyed dang bzhi tsam
NK120(e)001:4100: 'don par bya'o // gnyis pa dbyar gnas ni /
NK120(e)001:4106: zhes pa ltar phan yon brgyad dang ldan pas na /
NK120(e)001:4107: de ji ltar bya ba la gnyis te /
NK120(e)001:4109: gro zhun zla ba'i tshes gcig nas //
NK120(e)001:4110: snga ma'i dbyar de gtso bo yin //
NK120(e)001:4111: de nyid khrum gyi zla ba yi //
NK120(e)001:4112: tshe gcig nas ni phyi mar grags //
NK120(e)001:4113: zhes pa ltar dbyar snga phyi gang yin yang dbyar
NK120(e)001:4114: gnas pa'i yul la 'thab krol can sogs med cing
NK120(e)001:4115: sde snod 'dzin pa sogs yod pas bde bar gnas
NK120(e)001:4117: steng g.yogs sgo glegs dang bcas pa'i gtsug lag khang
NK120(e)001:4118: ral grum bcos pa dang byi dor bya ba sogs
NK120(e)001:4119: zhag bcu'am zla phyed tsam gyi snga rol nas sta
NK120(e)001:4120: gon bya ba sogs ring ba'i sbyor ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4121: dbyar snga phyi gang khas len pa'i zla ba de'i
NK120(e)001:4122: snga ma'i zla ba rdzogs pa'i nya la gso sbyong
NK120(e)001:4123: byas te gnas dang gnas mal dag stob rgyu yod
NK120(e)001:4124: na / de stob pa po dge slong gcig gam du ma bsko zhing /
NK120(e)001:4125: med na tshul shing brim pa po nyid bsko bar bya ste /
NK120(e)001:4126: las byed pa pos bsko byar spro ba dri /
NK120(e)001:4127: spro na gsol ba dang gnyis kyi las kyis bskos la /
NK120(e)001:4128: des khrims su bya ba brtan par brjod nas /
NK120(e)001:4129: tshul shing blang pa'i phyir las byed pas gsol ba 'ba' zhig pa'i las kyis thugs bstun la /
NK120(e)001:4130: bskos pas tshul shing 'brim zhing blangs pa'i grangs go bar bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4131: gnas dang gnas mal stob cing /
NK120(e)001:4132: gnas mal la log par mi spyad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4133: sang nangs par gnas par khas blangs pa dag go bar bya ba rnams nye ba'i sbyor ba'o //
NK120(e)001:4134: de nas dngos gzhi dbyar snga ma yin na dbyar 'bring hor zla drug pa'i nya dang /
NK120(e)001:4135: phyi ma yin na dbyar tha hor zla bdun pa'i nya la gso sbyong byas te /
NK120(e)001:4136: de'i phyi nyin tshes bcu drug gi nang par gnas
NK120(e)001:4137: steng g.yogs dang bcas par dge slong gi mdun du
NK120(e)001:4138: sngags lan gsum brjod pas khas blangs ngo //
NK120(e)001:4139: dmigs bsal yul med na 'dir gnas par bya'o snyam
NK120(e)001:4140: du dam bcas pas kyang gnas pa'i go chod do
NK120(e)001:4141: // de ltar dbyar gnas pa'i tshe na /
NK120(e)001:4142: dam tshig bsrung ba rnam drug ste //
NK120(e)001:4143: dam bca' gnas su 'brel ba dang //
NK120(e)001:4144: 'khrug long mi bya thos sogs brtson //
NK120(e)001:4145: ral grum bcos dang yun ring gso sbyong sogs kyi yun du /
NK120(e)001:4149: zhes pa'i sdom ltar nang khrims bcas la mi 'gal bar bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4151: dus nges pa ni zhag bdun la sogs pa'i snga
NK120(e)001:4152: rol nas spyod yul du go bar bya ba sogs
NK120(e)001:4153: ring sbyor dang / dbyar snga ma yin na dbyug zla dang /
NK120(e)001:4154: phyi ma yin na smin drug zla ba'i tshes bco
NK120(e)001:4155: lnga'i snga dro dge 'dun rnams 'dus nas bzod gsol
NK120(e)001:4156: dang rgyun chags gsum pa nas dge tshul gyi bshad
NK120(e)001:4157: pa'i bar gso sbyong ltar byas la /
NK120(e)001:4158: 'du bar ma nus pa yod na 'dun pa dang dgag dbye blangs nas brjod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4160: dgag dbye la thugs bstun pa rnams nye sbyor ro //
NK120(e)001:4161: de nas dngos gzhi r+ts+wa dar+b+ha brim zhing dgag dbye'i sngags lan gsum brjod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4168: byed pa po ste drug gis dbye ba'i dmigs bsal rnams kyang shes par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4170: zla ba phyed dang gnyis 'das pa'i nya shi gang
NK120(e)001:4171: rung la rkyen dbang gis dgag dbye byar rung zhing
NK120(e)001:4172: / dmag 'khrugs sogs byung nas dge 'dun thams cad
NK120(e)001:4173: gyes dgos na tshogs kyi dgag dbye bya ba dang
NK120(e)001:4174: / / dge slong gang rung rkyen dbang gis 'gro dgos na'ang 'di byar rung ngo //
NK120(e)001:4175: gnyis pa bde bar gnas pa'i rkyen gyi gzhi lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:4177: ko lpags gnas mal sman sogs gzhan du shes //
NK120(e)001:4179: dang po gosa kyi gzhi ni /
NK120(e)001:4180: rgyu log 'tsho med cing 'dul ba dang mthun pa'i sgo nas bsgrub cing /
NK120(e)001:4182: sngon po btsag dang ngur smrig rtsi //
NK120(e)001:4183: 'di dag rung ba'i tshon gsum ste //
NK120(e)001:4184: zhes pa ltar gyi kha dog bsgyur ba'i gos te /
NK120(e)001:4189: dge slong gi lus 'tsho ba'i ched du gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:4190: gos rung ba tshad ldan re re nges par rang
NK120(e)001:4191: ming gis byin gyis brlab rung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:4205: ras chen te yo byad bcu gsum mo //
NK120(e)001:4206: de la snam sbyar ni snam phran dgu nas nyer lnga'i bar te /
NK120(e)001:4209: bcu gsum pa gsum ni glegs bu phyed dang gsum pa /
NK120(e)001:4212: bcu dgu pa gsum ni glegs bu phyed dang bzhi pa /
NK120(e)001:4215: nyer lnga pa gsum ni glegs bu phyed dang lnga pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4216: tshad ni che skor gsum dpangs su khru gsum dang srid du khru lnga /
NK120(e)001:4217: chung gsum de las khru phyed phyed phri ba /
NK120(e)001:4218: 'bring gsum de gnyis kyi bar ro //
NK120(e)001:4219: bla gos ni snam phran bdun dang glegs bu phyed dang gsum pa /
NK120(e)001:4220: tshad snam sbyar ltar gsum mo //
NK120(e)001:4221: mthang gos ni snam phran lnga dang glegs bu phyed dang gnyis pa /
NK120(e)001:4222: tshad dpangs su khru do dang /
NK120(e)001:4224: tha na 'khor gsum khebs pas kyang rung /
NK120(e)001:4226: de'i gzan gyi tshad mthang gos dang 'dra zhing /
NK120(e)001:4228: de'i gzan gyi tshad bla gos dang 'dra ste /
NK120(e)001:4229: de dang de nyin mo dang mtshan mo bla gos
NK120(e)001:4230: dang mthang gos kyi nang du gyon rgyu yin pa'i
NK120(e)001:4231: phyir / gdong phyis srid dang zheng du khru gang ba /
NK120(e)001:4232: rnag gzan bla gos dang mnyam pa /
NK120(e)001:4233: skra bzed srid du khru gsum dang zheng du khru phyed dang gnyis pa /
NK120(e)001:4236: ras chen gsum gyi tshad ni sngar ltung byed kyi skabs su bshad zin pa ltar la /
NK120(e)001:4237: mkho ba'i yo byad ni ska rags sogs so //
NK120(e)001:4238: rgyun du dgos pa'i yo byad drug ni /
NK120(e)001:4243: gnas skabs 'bral spangs khegs pa'i sngags rten la chos gos gsum gang rung gi rgyu dang /
NK120(e)001:4244: khyim pa'i gos lta bu gang rung khru gang yan chad do //
NK120(e)001:4245: gnyis pa mkho ba'i yo byad kyi gos ni /
NK120(e)001:4246: 'tsho ba'i yo byad gang rung gi dbyibs su ma
NK120(e)001:4247: grub pa'i gos khru gang yan chad rang gzhan gnyis
NK120(e)001:4248: ka'i ming gis byin gyis brlab nas bcang rung ba
NK120(e)001:4249: ste / dar gos sogs nor gyi 'du shes dang /
NK120(e)001:4250: zhwa la sogs pa gos kyi 'du shes skye ba gnyis so //
NK120(e)001:4251: gsum pa lhag po'i gos ni /
NK120(e)001:4252: gzhan ming nyid kyis brlabs pa'am yid gtad de bcangs
NK120(e)001:4253: rung gi gos 'tsho ba'i dang mkho ba'i yo byad
NK120(e)001:4255: de rnams la zhen chags spangs pa'i sgo nas lus
NK120(e)001:4256: la rma dang gos la rma dkris kyi 'du shes
NK120(e)001:4257: sogs dge ba'i bsam pas longs spyad nas /
NK120(e)001:4258: mthar rnying nas bcos su mi rung ba'i dus sbyin
NK120(e)001:4259: bdag gi bsod nams spel ba sogs kyi ched du
NK120(e)001:4260: mchod rten dang gtsug lag khang gi ser kha la
NK120(e)001:4261: bslan par bya'o // de ltar chos gos rnam pa gsum sogs bcang tshul la /
NK120(e)001:4263: spyir rab byung tshul ldan gyis bcang zhing /
NK120(e)001:4264: khyad par snam sbyar ni dge slong gis bcang ngo //
NK120(e)001:4266: spyir khyim pa'am mu stegs can dang /
NK120(e)001:4267: khyad par snam sbyar ni dge tshul man chad kyi rtags las 'phags par bya ba'i phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:4268: rang nyid ston pa'i rnam thar gyi rjes su 'jug
NK120(e)001:4269: cing dge sbyong gi dran pa gso ba'i ched du
NK120(e)001:4270: bcangs pa'o // gnyis pa ko lpagas kyi gzhi ni /
NK120(e)001:4271: spyir yul dbus su gnas mal skyob pa'i phyir ko lpags kyi lhwam tsam dang /
NK120(e)001:4272: gtsug lag khang las gzhan pa'i khyim du stan gzhan
NK120(e)001:4273: med na ko lpags la 'dug pa tsam gnang gi
NK120(e)001:4275: mtha' 'khob tu ni grang ba skyob pa'i phyir lhwam dang mal stan gnyis ka brten par gnang zhing /
NK120(e)001:4276: mig nad can dang grang nad can la dom lpags kyi stan yang gnang /
NK120(e)001:4277: shin tu grang ba che ba chu la chab rom
NK120(e)001:4278: chags pa'i yul du zhwa dang lhwa ma yu ba
NK120(e)001:4279: can sogs ci dgar bsten pa gnang ba'i bslab byar
NK120(e)001:4280: gsungs so // gsum pa gansa mala gyi gzhi ni /
NK120(e)001:4283: ngos gcig gi dbus su dri'i gtsang khang bya ba nyid do //
NK120(e)001:4284: de'i mdun du sgo khang ngo //
NK120(e)001:4285: gru bzhi bzang ba nyid do //
NK120(e)001:4286: zhes sogs kyis gtsug lag khang brtsigs pa'i cho ga dang /
NK120(e)001:4287: brtsigs nas sgor gnod sbyin lag na rdo rje dang /
NK120(e)001:4288: sgo khang du 'khor ba'i 'khor lo cha lnga pa sogs bri bar bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4289: zhes ri mo 'bri ba'i tshul dang /
NK120(e)001:4290: der phyag bya ba'i tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:4291: so sor thar pa'i sdom pas mchog la rab tu byung bas phyag bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4293: khyim pas rab tu byung ba la'o //
NK120(e)001:4294: thams cad kyis sangs rgyas la'o //
NK120(e)001:4295: zhes sogs rgyas par gsungs pa ltar dang /
NK120(e)001:4296: gtsug lag khang yal bar mi dor ro //
NK120(e)001:4297: zhes sogs kyis ji ltar bskyang ba'i sgo nas gnas par bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4298: spyod lam ci 'dod pas lung dpog go //
NK120(e)001:4299: zhes sogs kyis der chos dang zang zing gi longs
NK120(e)001:4300: spyod la ji ltar spyod pa'i tshul rgyas par gsungs
NK120(e)001:4301: pa bzhin shes par bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:4302: gtsug lag khang dang der yod pa'i gnas mal sogs
NK120(e)001:4303: yo byad thams cad la longs spyod pa'i tshul yang
NK120(e)001:4305: mi slob pa ni bdag por spyod //
NK120(e)001:4306: slob pa sbyin pa spyod pa ste //
NK120(e)001:4307: bsam gtan klog dang ldan pa ni //
NK120(e)001:4308: rjes gnang spyod pas nyes pa med //
NK120(e)001:4309: lhag ma le los bcom pa yi //
NK120(e)001:4310: bdag nyid rnams ni bu lon spyod //
NK120(e)001:4311: khrims 'chal rnams la nam du yang //
NK120(e)001:4312: gtsug lag khang sogs nyer spyod bkag /
NK120(e)001:4314: khyad par khrims 'chal bkag pa'i tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:4316: tshul khrims 'chal bas sa ni gom pa gang //
NK120(e)001:4317: zas ni kham gcig btung ba chu phor gang //
NK120(e)001:4318: tsam zhig dge 'dun rdzas la longs spyod na //
NK120(e)001:4319: log 'tsho yin te dmyal bar skye bar gsungs //
NK120(e)001:4320: zhes pa la sogs pa'i tshul la spang blang byed pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4321: bzhi pa sman gyi gzhi la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4325: de yang log 'tsho dang bral zhing mtha' gnyis spangs
NK120(e)001:4326: pa'i sgo nas bsgrubs pa'i sman gang zhig dri ro
NK120(e)001:4327: reg bya gsum gyi bdag nyid du gyur pa'i kham
NK120(e)001:4330: skye mched gsum gyi bdag nyid do //
NK120(e)001:4332: gnyis pa dbye ba la bzhi /
NK120(e)001:4336: 'tsho ba'i bar bcangs pa rnams so //
NK120(e)001:4338: bkres pa'i nad sel pa la gtso bor gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:4339: sman tshul ldan rab tu byung bas spyir btang la
NK120(e)001:4340: phyi dro longs spyod du mi rung ba'i bza' ba
NK120(e)001:4341: lnga dang bca' ba lnga ste /
NK120(e)001:4343: sna tshogs 'bras chan 1'bras bu sna tshogs btsos pa /
NK120(e)001:4346: 3las kyis shi ba dang tshong 'dus gsum brgyud pa /
NK120(e)001:4347: phye dang 4khur 5ba snum nang btsos pa /
NK120(e)001:4350: rtsa ba sdong bu me tog 'bras //
NK120(e)001:4351: lo ma yang ni bca' ba lnga //
NK120(e)001:4353: gnyis pa thun tshod du rung ba ni /
NK120(e)001:4354: skom pa'i nad sel ba la gtso bor gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:4355: sman bcas ldan dge slong gis thun tshod kyi matha'i
NK120(e)001:4356: bar byin gyis brlab nas longs spyod du rung ba
NK120(e)001:4357: btung pa'i rgyu brgyad lta bu ste /
NK120(e)001:4359: chu shing 'bras dang ku shu go la dang /
NK120(e)001:4360: a shwar+tha dang u dum+b+aa ra dang /
NK120(e)001:4361: ba ri sha ka dang ni rgu 'bru dang //
NK120(e)001:4362: brgyad pa 'bra go dag ni yin par bshad //
NK120(e)001:4364: gzhan yang btsos pa'i tsh+wa ste rgun chang sogs kyi sing po /
NK120(e)001:4365: 'bru'i tsh+wa ste nas chang gro chang sogs kyi shul nas byung ba'i sing po /
NK120(e)001:4366: zho kha chu ste zho'i khu ba /
NK120(e)001:4367: dar ba'i dwangs ma ste chur khu /
NK120(e)001:4368: rtsa ba mo ste 'bras dang khre sogs btsos nas
NK120(e)001:4369: phab ma btab par mnan pa'i tsang shu zhes bod
NK120(e)001:4370: du rtsabs su grags pa rnams te /
NK120(e)001:4371: de dag kyang btung ba mtshan nyid lnga ldan zhes /
NK120(e)001:4376: 'dam bu nyag ma'i mdog lta bu dwangs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4377: gsum pa zhag bdun pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4378: rlung nad sel ba gtso bor gnang ba'i sman dge
NK120(e)001:4379: slong gis zhag bdun pa'i matha'i bar byin gyis brlabs
NK120(e)001:4380: nas longs spyod du rung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:4390: bu ram gyi dbu ba sogs so //
NK120(e)001:4391: bzhi pa 'tsho ba'i bar bcangs pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4392: 'du ba'i nad sel ba la gtso bor gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:4393: sman dge slong gis ji srid 'tsho'i bar byin gyis
NK120(e)001:4394: brlabs nas longs spyod du rung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:4396: rtsa ba sdong bu 'dab ma dang //
NK120(e)001:4397: me tog 'bras bu sman la sogs //
NK120(e)001:4399: rtsa ba'i sman gla sgang dang yung ba lta bu /
NK120(e)001:4400: sdong bu'i sman tsan+dana dang sle tre lta bu /
NK120(e)001:4401: 'dab ma'i sman nim pa'i lo ma lta bu /
NK120(e)001:4402: me tog gi sman pa sha ka'i me tog lta bu /
NK120(e)001:4403: 'bras bu'i sman a bar skyur gsum lta bu ste /
NK120(e)001:4404: de dag kyang gtso bor zas kyi don du khyab par byed pa ma yin pa rnams so //
NK120(e)001:4405: sman de dag bsten tshul la /
NK120(e)001:4406: dus rung gi sman snga dro'i dus kho nar bsten du rung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:4407: nad la phan na dus min du bsten pa'ang gnang /
NK120(e)001:4408: sman gzhan gsum byin gyis ma brlab pa ni gang
NK120(e)001:4409: zag nad pa yin min thams cad la gnang zhing
NK120(e)001:4410: / dus thams cad du bsten du rung mod /
NK120(e)001:4411: 'on kyang byin gyis brlab dgos so //
NK120(e)001:4412: sman nam zas ji ltar bsten pa'i cho ga ni /
NK120(e)001:4413: bdag nyid la nad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4414: zas la sman gyi 'du shes bzhag ste dran shes
NK120(e)001:4415: dang ldan pas dkon mchog gsum rjes su dran pa'i
NK120(e)001:4416: sgo nas / zas la cha bzhir bgo bya ste //
NK120(e)001:4417: dang por lha la bshos gtsang 'bul //
NK120(e)001:4418: de rjes chos skyong srung ma la //
NK120(e)001:4419: gtor ma shin tu rgya cher bya //
NK120(e)001:4420: rang gis zos shing 'thungs pa yi //
NK120(e)001:4421: lhag ma 'byung po rnams la byin //
NK120(e)001:4422: zhes pa'i cho gas zas la ran par longs spyad de yon sbyong mdo bsngo rnams bya /
NK120(e)001:4423: zhar byung de dag bzhag pa'i gnas mtshams nang yin
NK120(e)001:4424: yang rjen btsos dang zhag lon sogs rung ba'i khang
NK120(e)001:4427: byas zin pa'i rnying pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4428: mtshams nang gcig tu gtsug lag khang du ma'i rung
NK120(e)001:4429: khang gcig tu byas pa ba lang gi lhas lta
NK120(e)001:4430: bu gsum ste / de dag gi mtshan nyid dang byin gyis brlab tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:4433: 'tshod la 6ba gab dang bcas drug /'degs 1bsdu 2las 3phral 4byung ba bzhi //
NK120(e)001:4435: gzhan yang sogas zhes pa'i khongs nas thams cad la khyab pa las kyi gzhi sogs ston te /
NK120(e)001:4436: de la las chags pa'i ga zhi dang /
NK120(e)001:4440: chags pa'i dus sogs rgyas par gazhana du gsal ba las shesa par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4442: gnyis pa shugs bstan de'i rung mthun bsdus te bstan pa'i sgo nas don bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:4443: mdor na ye nas gnang dang bkag pa med //
NK120(e)001:4444: byar rung dang nye mi rung bzlog byed na //
NK120(e)001:4445: de dag spyod cig mi rung dang nye zhing //
NK120(e)001:4446: rung ba bzlog na kun tu spong zhes gsungs //
NK120(e)001:4448: de ltar bshad pa'i spang blang gi gnad rnams nges
NK120(e)001:4449: par byas nas dngos su ma gsungs pa'i gnang bkag
NK120(e)001:4450: gi bslab bya rnams la ji ltar slob pa'i tshul
NK120(e)001:4451: mdora bsdu na / gzhi gang la ston pa sangs
NK120(e)001:4452: rgyas kyis ye thog ma nyid nasa gannga ba dang
NK120(e)001:4453: bakaga pa gnyis ka meda na /
NK120(e)001:4454: gang zhig byar runga bar gsungs pa dang nye zhing /
NK120(e)001:4455: mi rung bar gsungs pa las bzlog par byed na
NK120(e)001:4456: de daga the tshom med par spyod ciga dang nyes
NK120(e)001:4457: par mi 'gyur ba ma zad yon tan kyang thob
NK120(e)001:4458: par 'gyur ro // de bzhin gang spyad du mi
NK120(e)001:4459: rung bar gsungs pa dang nye zhing runga ba las
NK120(e)001:4460: bzlog na de dag kun tu spongas shig ces gsungs
NK120(e)001:4461: par 'gyur ro // te / lung phran tshegs las /
NK120(e)001:4462: bcom ldan 'das kyis yongs su mya ngan las 'da'
NK120(e)001:4463: ba'i dus de'i tshe nyid na dge slong rnams la
NK120(e)001:4464: bka' stsal pa / dge slong dag ngas khyod la 'dul ba rgya cher ni bstan na /
NK120(e)001:4465: mdor bsdus te ma yin no //
NK120(e)001:4466: 'on kyang mdor bsdus pa yang nyon cig /
NK120(e)001:4467: dge slong dag ngas khyod la gang zhig thog ma nyid nas gnang ba yang med /
NK120(e)001:4469: gal te rung ba dang nye ba yin zhing mi
NK120(e)001:4470: rung ba bzlog par byed pa yin na ni rung
NK120(e)001:4471: ba yin par bzung bar bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4472: gal te mi rung ba dang nye ba yin zhing
NK120(e)001:4473: rung ba bzlog par byed pa yin na mi rung
NK120(e)001:4474: ba yin pas kun tu spyad par mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:4476: gsum pa sdom pa skye ba'i lus rten bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4477: skye ba'i rten ni mu stegs mtshams med byas //
NK120(e)001:4478: sgra mi snyan dang za ma mtshan gnyis dang //
NK120(e)001:4479: ma ning rigs lnga mtshan gsum gyur pa dang //
NK120(e)001:4480: sprul pa ma gtogs gling gsum skyes pa yi //
NK120(e)001:4481: skyes pa bud med sdom pa'i rten du 'dod //
NK120(e)001:4483: de lta bu'i so thar gyi sdom pa de skye
NK120(e)001:4484: ba'i lus rten ni las kyi sgrib pa shas che
NK120(e)001:4485: ba mu stegas can nam der zhugs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4486: matshamas med pa lnga byasa pa la sogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4487: rnam smin gyi sgrib pa shas che ba sgra mi snyan pa lta bu gnas rigs nyams pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4488: gang zhig grong pa'i chos med pa //
NK120(e)001:4489: de ni za ma zhes su brjod //
NK120(e)001:4490: ces pa ltar za ma dang /
NK120(e)001:4491: matshana gnyis gcig car du byung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4495: nyams pa ste ma ninga rigas lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:4496: matshana lan gsuma du gyur pa sogs mtshan nyams pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4497: mi ma yin pa mi'i rnam par sprul pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4498: mi ma yin pa'i 'gro ba po sogs ni 'gro
NK120(e)001:4499: ba nyams pa zhes de rnams sdom pa skye ba'i
NK120(e)001:4500: bar chad can yin pas na ma gtogsa la /
NK120(e)001:4501: de las gzhan shar nub lho'i gling gsuma du skyes
NK120(e)001:4502: pa yi skyes pa dang buda meda rnams so thar
NK120(e)001:4503: gyi sdoma pa skye ba dang gnas pa gnyis ka'i
NK120(e)001:4506: gling gsum skyes pa bud med las /
NK120(e)001:4507: 'gro ba gzhan la sdom pa bkag /
NK120(e)001:4509: bzhi pa nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4512: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4513: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:4515: de ltar rung ba'i rten de la thob pa'i sdom pa nyid tshul bzhin du bsrung zhing /
NK120(e)001:4516: gal te nyon mongs mang pa sogs kyis nyams par
NK120(e)001:4517: gyur na tha mara nyamsa pa de phyir bcos na
NK120(e)001:4520: gnyis ni rnam par byang bar 'gyur zhing /
NK120(e)001:4521: nyon mongs par mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4522: gnyis kyis zag pa 'phel bar mi 'gyur ba ste /
NK120(e)001:4524: ltung ba mi byin pa gang yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4525: ltung ba byung nas chos bzhin du phyir bcos pa gang yin pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4526: zhes gsungs pa ltar de'i tshul bashada pa la /
NK120(e)001:4528: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4529: sdom pa gtong ba'i rgyu dang /
NK120(e)001:4531: dang po sdom pa gtong ba'i rgyu bshad pa la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4534: dang po thun mong ba ni /
NK120(e)001:4535: gtong ba bslab pa phul dang shi 'phos dang //
NK120(e)001:4536: mtshan gnyis gcig car byung dang lan gsum gyur //
NK120(e)001:4537: rgyu 'bras med ltas rtsa ba chad rnams lci //
NK120(e)001:4539: so thar gyi sdom pa rtsad nas gtong ba'i rgyu ni bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:4540: brda 'phrod pa'i drung du bsam pa snying thag pa nas bslab pa phul na gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4541: yang dag par blangs pa dang 'gal ba'i rnam rig bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4543: sdom ba rang gi ngo bo /
NK120(e)001:4548: slob pa'i grogs rnams 'bul tshul gsungs pa ltar /
NK120(e)001:4549: gzhan yang tshangs par spyad daka'o zhes pa la sogs
NK120(e)001:4550: pa ni dngos su phul ba min yang de'i rgyu
NK120(e)001:4551: bstan pas nyams par byas pa yin pas na sdom
NK120(e)001:4552: pa gtong ba la khyad par med de /
NK120(e)001:4554: bslab pa ma phul bslab pa nyams par ma byas par //
NK120(e)001:4556: de bzhin du shi 'phosa pas gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4558: matshana gnyis gciga car byung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4559: mtshan lana gsuma 'gyur bas gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4561: rgyu 'brasa meda lta'i log lta skyes pas gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4562: dge ba'i rtsa ba chad pas sdom pa'i rten gzhi med pa'i 4phyir /
NK120(e)001:4564: phyi ma 'di ni theg pa che chung thams cad
NK120(e)001:4565: kyi sdom pa'i gtong rgyur gsungs pas shin tu lci
NK120(e)001:4566: ba'o // de ltar spyi'i gtong rgyu bzhi'i steng bsnyen gnas kyi gtong rgyu bsnan pas lngar bshad de /
NK120(e)001:4568: bslab pa phul dang shi 'phos dang //
NK120(e)001:4569: mtshan gnyis dag ni byung ba dang //
NK120(e)001:4570: rtsa ba chad dang mtshan 'das las //
NK120(e)001:4571: so sor thar pa'i 'dul ba gtong //
NK120(e)001:4574: de dag ni don mdor bsdu na gtong ba'i rgyu lnga yin no //
NK120(e)001:4576: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:4577: bye brag so so'i gtong rgyu /
NK120(e)001:4578: spyi la 'dod pa mi 'dra ba'i khyad par /
NK120(e)001:4579: rtsa ltung gtong rgyu yin min las 'phros te sde lnga'i dngos gzhi mi bskyed pa'i rgyu bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4580: dang po bye brag so so'i gtong rgyu ni /
