NK120(e)001:4581: nyi shu ma lon bsnyen rdzogs rjes su shes //
NK120(e)001:4582: dge slong sdom gtong bsten phyir khas blangs 'das //
NK120(e)001:4583: dge slob ma'o mtshan 'das bsnyen gnas kyi //
NK120(e)001:4584: sdom pa gtong rnams so so'i thun mong min //
NK120(e)001:4586: lo nyi shu ma lona pa la lon par 'du
NK120(e)001:4587: shes nas bsnyena rdzogas blangs pa de'i rjesa su nyi
NK120(e)001:4588: shu ma lon gong du de ltar ngo shesa na
NK120(e)001:4589: de'i tshe mngal bshol gyi zla bas kha bskang bar
NK120(e)001:4590: bya zhing / de ltar bskang yang ma tshang na dge slong gi sdom pa gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4592: shes na ni de zhig go //
NK120(e)001:4593: gal te de skyes pa na ma lon pa'i 'o //
NK120(e)001:4594: mngal na gnas pa dang bshol gyi zla ba dag dang yang bcas te'o //
NK120(e)001:4596: mi tshangs spyod bsten par byed pa'i phyir khasa blangsa
NK120(e)001:4597: nas bslab pa las 'adsa pas dge slob ma'i sdom
NK120(e)001:4598: pa gtong ba'o // de yang mdor /
NK120(e)001:4599: bsten pa'i phyir gzhan la khas blangs pa na /
NK120(e)001:4602: mtshan mo matha'i skad cig ma 'adsa pas bsnyen gnas kyi sdom pa gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4603: de srid du 'phangs pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:4604: de ltar gsum po sngar gyi spyi'i gtong bzhis gtong bar ma zad /
NK120(e)001:4605: rang rang rnams so so'i gtong rgyu sdom pa de
NK120(e)001:4606: dang de gtong bas na thun moonga mina pa'i gtong
NK120(e)001:4607: tshul lo // gnyis pa spyi la 'dod pa mi 'dra ba'i khyad par ni /
NK120(e)001:4608: rtsa ltung byung dang dam chos nub na'ang gtong //
NK120(e)001:4609: kha che'i yul gyi bye brag smra ba rnams //
NK120(e)001:4610: sdom ldan rtsa ltung byung ba gnyis ldan na //
NK120(e)001:4611: nor ldan bu lon can bzhin 'dod pa dang //
NK120(e)001:4612: kha cig rtsa bzhi gcig spyad kun nyams zer //
NK120(e)001:4615: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung bas gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4616: rgyud ngo tsha khrel med chen pos nyams pa'i phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:4617: gos dmar ba'i sde pa na re /
NK120(e)001:4618: lung gi dama chosa nub pa na'ang gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4619: bslab pa'i mtshams rnam par bzhag pa med pa'i phyir ro zhes 'dod cing /
NK120(e)001:4620: de la thogs med sku mched lung chos nub pa tsam gyis sdom pa sngar yod mi gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4621: rtogs pa'i dam chos ma nub pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4622: 'on kyang de tshe sngar med gsar skye med de /
NK120(e)001:4623: 'bogs byed kyi cho ga'i rnam bzhag med pa'i phyir gsungs /
NK120(e)001:4624: kha che'i yula gyi nyan thos bye brag tu smra ba rnams ni /
NK120(e)001:4625: rtsa ltung 'chab bcas byung yang sdom pa mi gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:4626: phyogs gcig nyams pas sdom pa zad par gtong ba mi rigs pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4627: de 'a dra de sdom pa dang ldana pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4628: rtsa ltung byung ba gnyis ldana yin pa'i phyir na /
NK120(e)001:4629: mi 'ga' zhig nor yang ldan la bu lona yang
NK120(e)001:4630: chags pa can bzhina no zhes 'doda pa ltar dang
NK120(e)001:4632: kha cig ltung bar gyur las smra //
NK120(e)001:4633: gzhan dag dam chos nub pa las //
NK120(e)001:4634: kha che rnams ni byung ba la //
NK120(e)001:4635: bu lon nor bzhin gnyis su 'dod //
NK120(e)001:4637: 'dul 'dzin kha ciga pham pa sdom pa'i gtong rgyu ma yin te /
NK120(e)001:4638: pham pa byung ba'i dge slong la dge slong gi sdom pa'i rdzas tshang bar yod pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4639: nyams tshul la ltos na kun nyams pa yin te /
NK120(e)001:4640: rtsa ba bzhi las srog gcod kyi pham pa 'chab bcas lta bu gciga spyad pa'i tshe /
NK120(e)001:4641: sdom pa mtha' dag gi dgos pa ma lus pa
NK120(e)001:4642: kun sgrub par nus pa de las nyamsa pa'i phyir
NK120(e)001:4643: zhes zera te / rgya cher 'grel las /
NK120(e)001:4644: dge slong pham par gyur pa la ni sdom pa yod du zin kyang /
NK120(e)001:4645: de lta mod kyi dgos pa med pa nyid du 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:4646: tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa rnams dang lhan cig
NK120(e)001:4647: gnas pa dang longs spyad pa med pa'i phyir dang
NK120(e)001:4648: / sdom pa yang dag par blangs pa ni rnam par grol ba thob pa'i ched yin la /
NK120(e)001:4649: des rnam par grol ba thag ring du byas pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4650: des na de'i sdom pa ni med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK120(e)001:4652: des na nyams pa dang mi chags pa gnyis ltung ba la sbyor na nyes byas tsam mo //
NK120(e)001:4653: gsum pa rtsa ltung gtong rgyu yin min las 'phros
NK120(e)001:4654: te sde lnga'i dngos gzhi mi bskyed pa'i rgyu bshad
NK120(e)001:4655: pa ni / dang po'i las can sems 'khrugs tshor bas gzir //
NK120(e)001:4656: sgrub par ma nus pa la nyes pa med //
NK120(e)001:4658: sde lnga'i dngos gzhi'i nyes pa bskyed mi bskyed kyi
NK120(e)001:4659: mtshams 'di ltar dang po'i lasa can gyis spyad na
NK120(e)001:4661: ston pa'i bcas pa dang ma 'brel ba'i sngon du yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4662: dge slong bzang sbyin la mi tshangs spyod kyi pham pa ma byung ba bzhin /
NK120(e)001:4663: semsa 'khrugas shing sdug bsngal gyi tshora basa shin tu gzira bas spyad kyang nyes pa mi bskyed de /
NK120(e)001:4664: sems rnal du gnas pa ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4665: smyon pas mi bsad pa bzhin /
NK120(e)001:4666: bslab pa la gus pas 'bad na'ang sgrub para ma
NK120(e)001:4667: nus pa'i gnas skabs su spyad pa la nyes pa
NK120(e)001:4668: med de / rmi lam du mi tshangs spyod spyad kyang pham pa mi 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4669: des na de 'dra'i rten gyi gang zag gis ltung
NK120(e)001:4670: ba la spyad kyang dngos gzhi'i nyes pa ji lta
NK120(e)001:4671: ba bzhin bskyed pa med do //
NK120(e)001:4672: gnyis pa phyir bcos dngos bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:4673: phyir bcos kyi dbye ba bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:4674: nyes pa sbyong ba'i thabs stobs bzhir bsdu tshul bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:4675: nyes dmigs shes pa'i sgo nas nan tan du bsrung bar gdams pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4676: dang po phyir bcos kyi dbye ba bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4679: dang po 'chab mnyes ngos bzung ba ni /
NK120(e)001:4680: 'chab pa zhes grags gsang ste mi brjod pa //
NK120(e)001:4682: 'achaba pa zhes su gragas pa ltung ba'i nyes pa
NK120(e)001:4683: byung ba gzhan la gasnga 'dod kyi bsam pas kun
NK120(e)001:4684: nas bslangs te ngag gis gzhan la mi brjod pa
NK120(e)001:4685: dang / gsang ba'i lus kyi rnam 'gyur ni 'chab pa'i ltung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:4686: gang la byung ba'i rten ni ltung ba dang ltung
NK120(e)001:4687: min gyi rnam dbye shes shing dran nus pa'i dge
NK120(e)001:4688: slong nyid las gzhan la mi 'byung zhing /
NK120(e)001:4689: de yang pham pa ni 'chab sems skad cig ma tsam skyes kyang 'chab bcas su 'gyur la /
NK120(e)001:4690: lhag ma'i spo spyod la zhag tu longs par bcab dgos so //
NK120(e)001:4691: gnyis pa dbye ba dngos bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4693: lhag ma sogs phyir bcos pa'o //
NK120(e)001:4694: dang po pham pa'i phyir bcos la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:4695: pham pa 'chab bcas bcos med dang /
NK120(e)001:4697: dang po pham pa 'chab bcas bcos med ni /
NK120(e)001:4698: pham pa 'chab bcas tshe 'dir gsor mi rung //
NK120(e)001:4700: bslab pa ma phul bar phama pa bzhi gang rung
NK120(e)001:4701: byung nas skad cig ma tsam bcabs kyang pham pa
NK120(e)001:4702: 'achaba bacasa su gyur pas na tshe 'dira ltung ba'i
NK120(e)001:4703: dngos gzhi phyir gsora mi rung ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:4705: nyes rtsom byed dang khyim sun 'byin pa dang //
NK120(e)001:4706: 'dir ni gsum pa tshul khrims 'chal ba dag /'thab mo spangs te gan+di brdungs byas nas /
NK120(e)001:4707: chu shing rul pa bzhin du de bskrad bya //
NK120(e)001:4708: zhes gsungs pa ltar dge 'dun gyi gnas nas bskrad par bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:4709: 'on kyang rang gi 'gyod sdom gyis bshags pa byas
NK120(e)001:4710: na rnam smin gyi nyes pa dag nas ngan song
NK120(e)001:4711: du ltung bar mi 'gyur ba zhig 'ong bas na
NK120(e)001:4712: 'bad par bya'o // de ltar ma bshags na tshe
NK120(e)001:4713: 'di phyi'i nyes dmigs rang la 'byung bar ma zad
NK120(e)001:4714: nyes dmigs ni tshul 'chal de dang lhan cig zhag
NK120(e)001:4715: lon du nyal na lo bye ba phrag bcu bzhi
NK120(e)001:4716: dang stong phrag bcu bzhir dmyal bar skye bar bshad
NK120(e)001:4717: 'bad par bya'o // do // gal te bskrad pa
NK120(e)001:4718: de sde snod 'dzin pa yin na dge 'dun dang
NK120(e)001:4719: lhan cig longs spyod du mi dbang yang gnas longs
NK120(e)001:4720: sbyin pa sogs kyis rjes su bzung bar bya zhing
NK120(e)001:4721: 'bad par bya'o // do // / de 'dra des bzod par gsol ba'i dus su ma blangs na /
NK120(e)001:4722: de nas bzung ste gnas chos kyi rnyed pa'i rin
NK120(e)001:4723: thang rtsis nas tshangs na dge 'dun la pham pa
NK120(e)001:4725: gnyis pa 'chab med bcos yod ni /
NK120(e)001:4726: 'chab pa med na dngos po brjod pa yis //
NK120(e)001:4727: dge 'dun la bshags mthong sdom bar gyis 'dag /
NK120(e)001:4730: de las gzhan gso bar rung ba rnams phyir bcos
NK120(e)001:4731: pa'i tshul pham bzhi gang rung byung nas 'achaba pa'i
NK120(e)001:4732: sems skad cig ma tsam yang med na ltung ba'i
NK120(e)001:4733: dngosa po de mi gsang mi sbed par ngag tu
NK120(e)001:4734: brjod pa yis yul dge 'duna mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK120(e)001:4736: yul gyis nyes pa la nyes par mthong ngam zhes dris pa na /
NK120(e)001:4737: shis bzhin rdzun du ma song bar snying nas ltung
NK120(e)001:4738: ba'i nyes pa la yid ches pa'i sgo nas mthonga
NK120(e)001:4740: phyin chad legs par sdom mam zhes dris pa'i tshe /
NK120(e)001:4741: srog la bab kyang de 'dra'i nyes pa mi byed
NK120(e)001:4742: snyam pa'i bsam pas sdom lags zhes brjod de bshags
NK120(e)001:4744: de ji ltar bya ba'i tshul sbyor ba gsol gdab sngon du 'gro bas /
NK120(e)001:4745: dngos gzhi gsol bzhi'i las kyis chad pa las kyi
NK120(e)001:4746: bslab pa byin nas ji srid 'tsho'i bar dman spyod
NK120(e)001:4747: lnga dang du len zhing khyad spyod lnga spang ba'i
NK120(e)001:4748: kun spyod kyis gnas par khas blangs pas 'adga par
NK120(e)001:4749: gsungs pa ni mdo'i dngos bstan ltar yin la /
NK120(e)001:4750: de ltar bshags rjes dge slong gi sdoma pa slara
NK120(e)001:4751: noda nas chad pa las kyi bslab pa byin pa
NK120(e)001:4752: ni sems tsam pa yan chad kyi bzhed pa yin
NK120(e)001:4753: par snang ngo // gnyis pa lhag ma bcu gsum sogs phyir bcos pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4755: lci yang la ltos bshags te rim par ldang //
NK120(e)001:4757: dge 'dun lhag ma bcu gsuma po ni zhag dang
NK120(e)001:4758: ma 'brel pa'i 'chab nyes rnams bgo gyur yin na
NK120(e)001:4759: mtshams nang gi dge slong thams cad dang gzhan rnams
NK120(e)001:4760: gcig gi drung du mthol la /
NK120(e)001:4761: zhag tu longs pa'i bcab nyes ni gang zag khyad
NK120(e)001:4762: par can min pas ci tsam bcas pa'i zhag grangs
NK120(e)001:4763: dang mnyam par spo ba dang /
NK120(e)001:4764: dngos gzhi mgu ba spyad tshul rnams ni sngar spyi don gyi skabs su bshad grub la /
NK120(e)001:4765: gang zag khyad par can gyi lhag ma'i phyir bcos ni /
NK120(e)001:4767: ngo tsha dang ldan pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4771: shes pas ni gcig gi mdun du bshags pas dge 'dun lhag ma las ldang ngo //
NK120(e)001:4773: de la sogas pa ltung ba gzhan rnams lci yanga
NK120(e)001:4774: la ltos nas bashagas te rima para nyes pa las
NK120(e)001:4776: pham sbom lci ba la yul dge slong drug /
NK120(e)001:4778: lhag sbom lci ba la bzhi /
NK120(e)001:4779: yang ba la gcig gi drung du bshags pas 'dags la /
NK120(e)001:4780: spang ltung sogs sde tshan phyi ma rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:4781: dge tshul gyi nyes ltung bshags tshul rnams sngar rang
NK120(e)001:4782: rang gi bsrung bya bshad pa'i skabs phyogs tsam bstan
NK120(e)001:4783: pa bzhin no // lar dus thams cad du ltung
NK120(e)001:4784: ba rnams byung ba'i tshe mthol bshags bya ba la
NK120(e)001:4785: 'bad par bya zhing 'chi ba'i tshe ltung ba med
NK120(e)001:4787: gal te 'chi ba de'i tshe na nyes pa ma
NK120(e)001:4788: bshags pa dran rgyu yod na lus ngag gis mthol
NK120(e)001:4789: bshags tshad ldan ma nus kyang yid kyis bshags sdom
NK120(e)001:4792: mthar de la rtsal rkyen ma 'byor ba nyid na las byas pa dang 'dra'o //
NK120(e)001:4794: de rnams ni nus pa phyir bcos tshul yin la /
NK120(e)001:4795: mi nus pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i tshul ni chad
NK120(e)001:4796: las dgos pa'i rigs sngon du ma song ba dang
NK120(e)001:4798: ltung phyir rtsod pa sogs kyi rkyen dbang gis bshags
NK120(e)001:4799: pa ma grub pa rnams las gral du ma 'dus
NK120(e)001:4800: gong du byin gyis brlabs shing /
NK120(e)001:4801: ltung ba thun mong ba rnams 'dus nas gsol ba'i las kyis byin gyis brlabs pa yin /
NK120(e)001:4802: de yang bshags pas 'dag pa'i rgyu'i gtso bo ni 'gyod sdom drag po'i sems kyis yin te /
NK120(e)001:4803: de gnyis med par tshig tsam gyis bshags pas ni
NK120(e)001:4804: sdig ltung 'dag pa lta ci rdzun smra ba chen
NK120(e)001:4806: gnyis pa nyes pa sbyong ba'i thabs stobs bzhir bsdu tshul bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4807: mdor na stobs bzhir ma 'dus bshags pa med //
NK120(e)001:4808: sngar byas 'gyod bshags khong du dug song ltar //
NK120(e)001:4809: 'gyod pa snying nas rnam par sun 'byin stobs //
NK120(e)001:4810: dug la sman bzhin 'jug pa drag po yis //
NK120(e)001:4811: nyes phyir dge ba'i gnyen po kun spyod stobs //
NK120(e)001:4812: dug mi 'thung ltar phyis nas nyes sdom la //
NK120(e)001:4813: nges shes drag po rnam par sor chud stobs //
NK120(e)001:4814: sman pa bsten ltar skyabs sems ltung bshags sogs //
NK120(e)001:4815: dad pa drag pos rten gyi stobs bzhi spyad //
NK120(e)001:4817: sdig ltung gang yin kyang sbyong ba'i gnyen po mdora
NK120(e)001:4818: bsdus na stobsa bzhira ma 'dusa pa'i bashagas pa meda
NK120(e)001:4819: de / de ltar yang chos bzhi bstan pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)001:4821: byang chub sems dpa' chos bzhi dang ldan na sdig
NK120(e)001:4822: pa byas shing bshags pa thams cad zil gyi gnon
NK120(e)001:4823: par 'gyur ro // bzhi gang zhe na /
NK120(e)001:4825: rnam par sun 'byin pa kun tu spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4826: gnyen po kun tu spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4830: de'ang sngar byas pa'i nyes ltung la 'gyod bashagas bya tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:4831: dper na 'ga' zhig gis ma shes te dug 'thungs
NK120(e)001:4832: pas khong du duga songa ba ltar dug nad kyis
NK120(e)001:4833: gzir ba na de la 'gyod pa drag pos zhe
NK120(e)001:4834: gting nas slar dug skyug par 'dod pa ltar kha
NK120(e)001:4835: tsam ma yin par 'gyod pa snying nasa bskyed pa
NK120(e)001:4836: ni rnam para sun 'byin pa'i stobsa dang /
NK120(e)001:4837: dug nad sbyong ba'i gnyen po la sman bsten pa
NK120(e)001:4838: bzhina sgo gsum gyi 'juga pa drag po yisa nyes
NK120(e)001:4839: pa 'dags pa' phyir dge ba'i phyogs kyi gnyen po
NK120(e)001:4840: la 'bad pa kuna tu spyod pa'i stobsa dang /
NK120(e)001:4841: slad nas shes bzhin dug mi 'thunga ba ltar ltung
NK120(e)001:4842: ba snga ma bshags te phyis su de 'dra ba'i
NK120(e)001:4843: nyes pa mi byed snyam du bsam nasa nyes spyod
NK120(e)001:4844: sdom pa la / bshags na dag pa'i phan yon dang /
NK120(e)001:4845: ma bshags na 'di phyi'i nyes dmigs yod pa'i tshul
NK120(e)001:4846: la ngesa shesa draga po bskyed pa rnama para sora
NK120(e)001:4848: dug sbyong ba la rang rgyud kyi rten rgyud gso rung du yod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4849: yul gyi rten dug sman nyer ba'i smana pa bstena dgos pa ltar /
NK120(e)001:4850: rang rgyud kyi rten bla ma mchog gsum la skyabsa
NK120(e)001:4851: su 'gro zhing byang chub mchog tu semas bskyed pa
NK120(e)001:4852: dang / ltung ba bashagas pa'i mdo sogas la 'bad pas 'don cing /
NK120(e)001:4853: yul gyi rten bshags yul bla ma dkon mchog la
NK120(e)001:4854: yid ches pa'i dada pa draga po'i sgo nas bshags
NK120(e)001:4855: na 'dags nges pa'i phyir rten gyi stobsa yin la
NK120(e)001:4856: / de ltar stobs bzhi tshang ba'i sgo nas spyad do //
NK120(e)001:4857: 'on kyang chos 'di pa'i lugs kyi bshags tshul rnams
NK120(e)001:4858: sngar bshad pa ltar ma byas na rgyud ltung ba
NK120(e)001:4859: dngos gzhi las ldang mi nus kyang 'bras bu rnam
NK120(e)001:4860: smin shin tu yang ba myong bar 'gyur ba la
NK120(e)001:4861: stobs bzhi'i bshags pa 'di nyid shin tu gal che
NK120(e)001:4862: bas gnyis ka chun gcig dril du byed pa gnad
NK120(e)001:4863: do // gsum pa nyes dmigs shes pa'i sgo nas nan tan du bsrung bar gdams pa ni /
NK120(e)001:4864: 'on kyang sdig ltung stobs ldan re spyod na //
NK120(e)001:4865: sa thob yun du 'gor bas mig ltar bsrung //
NK120(e)001:4867: de ltar tshul bzhin bshags pas nyes pa 'dags pa de lta mod kyi /
NK120(e)001:4868: dper na rtsa ltung 'chab med la bslab pa sbyin nas phyir bcos su yod mod /
NK120(e)001:4869: 'ona kyang ji srid dgra bcom pa ma thob kyi
NK120(e)001:4870: bar de srid du pham pa'i dngos gzhi 'dag mi
NK120(e)001:4871: nus shing / de 'dra des dgra bcom pa thob pa yang gzhan las ches dka' ste /
NK120(e)001:4872: sbyang bya sdiga ltung stobsa dang ldana pa re re tsam la spyod na /
NK120(e)001:4873: de'i gnyen por sbyong byed la che thang gis 'bad
NK120(e)001:4874: du zin kyang rgyud nyes pa'i sgrib pa de rnam
NK120(e)001:4875: grol gyi sa gong ma'i yon tan thob pa la
NK120(e)001:4876: yuna ring du 'gyang ste 'gor basa na ltung ba
NK120(e)001:4877: phra zhing phra ba'ang miga gi 'bras bu ltar gces
NK120(e)001:4879: nyes pa chung ngus kyang rnam smin chen po bskyed nus pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:4881: gang zhig ston pa thugs rje'i bstan pa la //
NK120(e)001:4882: yang bar sems shing cung zad 'da' byed pa //
NK120(e)001:4883: de ni de las sdug bsngal gzhan dbang thob //
NK120(e)001:4884: smyig tshal bregs pas a mra'i tshal nyams bzhin //
NK120(e)001:4885: 'di na la la rgyal po'i tshig chen po //
NK120(e)001:4886: lan 'ga' 'das na'ang chad pa thob mi 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:4887: thub pa'i bka' lung tshul min 'da' byas na //
NK120(e)001:4888: dud 'gror skye 'gyur e la'i 'dab klu bzhin //
NK120(e)001:4890: gzhan yang nyams pa'i nyes pa snga ma las /
NK120(e)001:4891: dam chos thos par mi 'gyur la //
NK120(e)001:4892: thos pa myur du brjed par 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:4893: sa lam rtogs pa'ang yongs mi skye //
NK120(e)001:4895: gal te tshul khrims 'chal bar gyur na'ang gzhan la
NK120(e)001:4896: ma brjod na gzhan gyi khrel ba la sogs pa
NK120(e)001:4899: ma mthong bzhin du sdig pa byed na yang //
NK120(e)001:4900: dug zos bzhin du bde bar mi 'gyur te //
NK120(e)001:4901: lha dang rnal 'byor can gyi mi dag gi //
NK120(e)001:4902: rnam dag mig gis mi mthong mi srid de //
NK120(e)001:4904: nyes pa lkog tu byas kyang sa bla'i lha rnams kyis bsgrags pas /
NK120(e)001:4905: gtam ngan phyogs thams cad du khyab //
NK120(e)001:4906: 'jig rten lha dang bcas pas khrel zhing brnyas /
NK120(e)001:4907: mkhan po dang slob dpon gyi mdun du 'gro ba la ngo gnong /
NK120(e)001:4908: dge 'dun tshogs pa'i dbus su bag tsha /
NK120(e)001:4909: sbyin bdag gi yon len pa la dpa' zhum /
NK120(e)001:4910: dkar phyogs lha dang chos skyong rnams kyis mi bsrung /
NK120(e)001:4911: nag phyogs bdud rigs rnams kyis glags rnyed /
NK120(e)001:4912: tshe 'dir yang mi 'dod pa thams cad thog tu 'bab /
NK120(e)001:4913: yon tan gong ma mi skye /
NK120(e)001:4915: 'chi ba'i tshe 'gyod pa dang bcas pas dus byas
NK120(e)001:4916: te ngan song du sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar
NK120(e)001:4918: mdor na pham lhag sbom po ltung byed sor bshags
NK120(e)001:4919: nyes byas rnams las 'das na rim par tsha ba'i
NK120(e)001:4920: dmyal ba nas yang sos kyi bar du skye bar
NK120(e)001:4922: rang nyid bde bar 'dod pa dag gis shin tu
NK120(e)001:4923: bag yod pa'i sgo nas nan tan du gso ba
NK120(e)001:4925: lnga pa bsrung ba'i phan yon la gsum /
NK120(e)001:4926: tshul khrims tsam gyi phan yon //
NK120(e)001:4927: so thar gyi sdom pa'i phan yon /
NK120(e)001:4928: de yon tan thams cad kyi gzhi rten du 'gyur ba'i phan yon no //
NK120(e)001:4929: dang po tshul khrims tsam gyi phan yon ni /
NK120(e)001:4930: phan yon nad dang rgyal po'i chad phyir blangs //
NK120(e)001:4931: rkyen 'ga' sel kyang 'jigs skyob tshul khrims yin //
NK120(e)001:4932: phyi ma'i ched blangs legs smon tshul khrims zhes //
NK120(e)001:4933: lha mi'i bde 'bras thob kyang thar pa min //
NK120(e)001:4935: de ltar tshul bzhin du ma nyams par bsrungs na
NK120(e)001:4936: de'i phana yona ni tshe 'dir nada dang rgyal po'i
NK120(e)001:4937: chada pa sogs las thar ba'i phyir blangas na de
NK120(e)001:4938: dang de'i rang rang gi 'dod 'bras tshe 'di'i 'phral
NK120(e)001:4939: rkyen 'ag'a zhig sela nus kyang 'jigas skyob kyi tshul
NK120(e)001:4941: phyi ma ngan song gi sdug sngal la 'jigs nas
NK120(e)001:4942: mngon mthong lha mi'i bde ba tsam thob pa'i cheda
NK120(e)001:4943: du blangas na legas smon gyi tshul khrimas zhesa rang
NK120(e)001:4944: gi ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin lha dang mi'i bde
NK120(e)001:4945: ba'i 'brasa bu thoba pa yin kyang nges 'byung gi
NK120(e)001:4946: bsam pas ma zin pas na 'khor ba las thar
NK120(e)001:4947: pa thob pa'i thabs ni mina no //
NK120(e)001:4948: gnyis pa so thar gyi sdom pa'i phan yon ni /
NK120(e)001:4949: nges par 'byung ba'i tshul khrims sdom ldan na //
NK120(e)001:4950: dgra bcom thob pa dga' bo'i rnam thar bzhin //
NK120(e)001:4952: des na 'khor ba las ngesa para 'byung ba myang
NK120(e)001:4953: 'das gsum gang rung thob par 'dod pa'i bsam pas
NK120(e)001:4954: zin pa'i rigs brgyad gang rung gi tshul khrimas blangs
NK120(e)001:4955: nas sdom pa ma nyams par bsrung ba dang ldan
NK120(e)001:4956: na dgra bcoma pa sogs myang 'das gsum gang don
NK120(e)001:4957: du gnyer ba de thoba pa la tshegs med de
NK120(e)001:4958: / dper na gcung dag'a bosa dang po'i dus su ston pa'i bkas dbang med du sdom pa blangs /
NK120(e)001:4959: de rjes ston pas rdzu 'phrul gyis khrid de lha'i
NK120(e)001:4960: bu mo rnams bstan pas phyi ma de dang lhan
NK120(e)001:4961: cig skye bar 'dod nas bslab pa la brtson pas
NK120(e)001:4962: sngar gyi sdom pa de legs smon gyi tshul khrims
NK120(e)001:4963: su gyur / de'i 'og tu dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal
NK120(e)001:4964: bstan pas nges 'byung gi bsam pa skyes nas de
NK120(e)001:4965: phyin chad so thar gyi sdom pa mtshan nyid par
NK120(e)001:4966: gyur nas legs par bslab pas dgra bcom pa'i 'bras
NK120(e)001:4967: bu mngon du byas pa'i rnam par thara pa bzhina
NK120(e)001:4968: su gyur / no // der ma zad gnas skabs kyi phan yon kyang /
NK120(e)001:4969: tshangs pa mtshungs par spyod pa mkhas pa rnams kyis basngagasa par 'os pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4970: 'phags nor bdun gyis phyug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:4971: 'gyod pa med par 'chi ba'i dus byas nas /
NK120(e)001:4972: skye ba phyi mar pham pa bsrungs pas gzhan 'phrul dbang byed /
NK120(e)001:4976: sor bshags dang nyes byas rnams bsrungs pas ri rab
NK120(e)001:4977: la gnas pa'i lha'i gnas su skye bar 'gyur zhing
NK120(e)001:4978: / mthar thug 'gyod pa med pa'i tshul khrims rnam
NK120(e)001:4979: par dag pa la brten nas dmigs pa la rtse
NK120(e)001:4981: de la brten nas rnam par mi rtog pa'i shes
NK120(e)001:4982: rab kyis 'khor ba'i rtsa ba bdag tu 'dzin pa
NK120(e)001:4983: bcad nas nges par 'byung ba lhag med kyi myang
NK120(e)001:4986: rab basngagasa nor ni phun tshogs shing //
NK120(e)001:4987: lha yi khang bzang dam par skye //
NK120(e)001:4991: dge slong la rab tu gces pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)001:4992: shin tu legs par tshul khrims gang //
NK120(e)001:4993: bsdams pa'i mi de mdzes pa'i gzugs //
NK120(e)001:4994: 'dul ba la ni nye bar gnas //
NK120(e)001:4995: tshul khrims bslab la rang yid ches //
NK120(e)001:4996: mi de nyi ma gcig la yang //
NK120(e)001:4997: bsod nams phung po dpag tu med //
NK120(e)001:5000: gsum pa yon tan thams cad kyi gzhi rten du 'gyur ba'i phan yon ni /
NK120(e)001:5001: skyabs gsum 'dzin sogs yon tan phyi ma mchog /
NK120(e)001:5002: snga ma phyi ma'i thun mong lam yin phyir //
NK120(e)001:5003: sems bskyed sngags kyi gdul bya'ang de dang mtshungs //
NK120(e)001:5004: de phyir yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten yin //
NK120(e)001:5007: gang su gsum la skyabs 'gro ba //
NK120(e)001:5008: de dag myur du sangs rgyas 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:5009: zhes gsungs pa ltar gyi skyabsa gsuma 'dzina pa'i dge
NK120(e)001:5010: bsnyen gyi phan yon des yongs rdzogs dge bsnyen gyi
NK120(e)001:5011: sdom pa'i phan yon brgya'i char yang mi 'gyur zhing
NK120(e)001:5012: / de bzhin du sogas khongs nas dge tshul dang
NK120(e)001:5013: dge slong gi sdom pa'i yona tan snga ma snga
NK120(e)001:5014: ma bas phyi ma phyi ma rnams brgya 'gyur stong
NK120(e)001:5015: 'gyur gyi mchoga tu gyur pa yin cing /
NK120(e)001:5016: snga ma snga ma rnams phyi ma phyi ma'i thuna monga du gyur pa'i lam stegs yina pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:5017: de bzhin du so thar gyi sdom pa de dag
NK120(e)001:5018: kyang semsa bskyed kyi sdom pa'i rten du 'gro zhing
NK120(e)001:5019: / de gnyis ka gsang sngagas kyi sdom pa'i rten
NK120(e)001:5020: du 'gro ba'i phyir na sdom pa gong ma gnyis
NK120(e)001:5021: kyi gdula bya la'nga 'og ma gnyis 'gro dgos pa'i
NK120(e)001:5022: tshul gong du bshad pa de dag dang mtshungsa shing
NK120(e)001:5023: / / rgyu mtshan de yi phyir na nges 'byung
NK120(e)001:5024: gi tshul khrims ni theg pa kun gyi lung dang
NK120(e)001:5025: rtogs pa'i yona tan ma lus pa kuna gyi gzhi
NK120(e)001:5028: khrims ni rgyu dang mi rgyu'i sa bzhin du //
NK120(e)001:5029: yon tan kun gyi gzhi rten lags par gsungs //
NK120(e)001:5031: mdor na sngon bstan pa dar ba'i dus su lo
NK120(e)001:5032: grangs mang por bslab gzhi yongs rdzogs kyi tshul khrims
NK120(e)001:5034: da lta bstan pa nub la nye ba'i dus 'dir
NK120(e)001:5035: nyin zhag gcig gi yun la bslab gzhi gcig tsam
NK120(e)001:5036: bsrung ba phan yon che bar gsungs te /
NK120(e)001:5038: bskal pa bye ba gang+g+aa'i bye snyed du //
NK120(e)001:5039: dang ba'i sems kyis zas dang skom rnams dang //
NK120(e)001:5040: gdugs dang ba dan mar me'i phreng ba yis //
NK120(e)001:5041: sangs rgyas bye ba phrag khrig rim gror byas //
NK120(e)001:5042: gang zhig dam chos rab tu 'jigs pa dang //
NK120(e)001:5043: bde gshegs bstan pa 'gags par 'gyur ba'i tshe //
NK120(e)001:5044: nyin mtshan du ni bslab pa gcig spyad pa //
NK120(e)001:5045: bsod nams 'di ni de bas khyad par 'phags //
NK120(e)001:5047: de ltar brjod bya'i don mthar phyin nas le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:5048: 'dul ba so thar gyi rim par phye ba ste gnyis pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5050: bstan bcos 'di la le'u lnga las /
NK120(e)001:5051: brjod bya 'dula ba spong 'jug gi tshul khrims nyid /
NK120(e)001:5052: rjod byed kyi 'dul ba la pha ma'i 'byed /
NK120(e)001:5057: nyan thos dang thun mong ba'i bstan pa'i nyams len
NK120(e)001:5058: so thar gyi rima par phye ba ste le'u gnyisa
NK120(e)001:5060: gnyis pa byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK120(e)001:5061: ston pas pha rol tu phyin pa'i sde snod ji ltar gsungs tshul /
NK120(e)001:5062: de bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung tshul /
NK120(e)001:5063: de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5064: dang po ston pas pha rol tu phyin pa'i sde snod ji ltar gsungs tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:5065: bskal bzang 'gro ba'i 'dren pa thub chen des //
NK120(e)001:5066: bya rgod phung sogs theg chen rigs can la //
NK120(e)001:5067: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde snod dpag yas gsungs //
NK120(e)001:5069: ston pa thugs rje can de nyid bskal pa grangs
NK120(e)001:5070: med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i snga rol du dbang
NK120(e)001:5071: po'i tog ces bya bar sangs rgyas su zin kyang
NK120(e)001:5072: / bskala pa bazanga po'i dus 'dir zhing 'di'i 'gro
NK120(e)001:5073: ba rnams srid pa 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las zhi
NK120(e)001:5074: ba mya ngan las 'das pa'i grong du 'drena par
NK120(e)001:5076: slar yang mdzad pa bcu gnyis la sogs pa'i sgo
NK120(e)001:5077: nas bla na med pa'i byang chub chen po brnyes
NK120(e)001:5080: thugs rje chen pos 'jig rten mkhyen //
NK120(e)001:5081: 'jig rten kun la gzigs nas ni //
NK120(e)001:5082: chos kyi sku las ma g.yos bar //
NK120(e)001:5083: sprul pa'i rang bzhin sna tshogs kyis //
NK120(e)001:5084: skye ba mngon par skye ba dang //
NK120(e)001:5085: dga' ldan gnas nas 'pho ba dang //
NK120(e)001:5087: yongs su ma dag zhing rnams su //
NK120(e)001:5088: srid pa ji srid gnas par ston //
NK120(e)001:5089: zhes pa'i bar gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:5090: de ltar sangs rgyas nas gdul bya'i blo la ltos
NK120(e)001:5091: te chos kyi 'khor lo rim pa gsum du bskor
NK120(e)001:5093: dang po'i tshul rnams gong du brjod zin ma thag pa ltar la /
NK120(e)001:5094: 'dir bar matha'i dgongs pa khyad par shin tu rgyas
NK120(e)001:5095: pa chen po byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod ji
NK120(e)001:5096: ltar gsungs pa'i tshul ni phun sum tshogs pa lnga
NK120(e)001:5097: ldan te / ston pa phun sum tshogs pa rnam 'dren bzhi pa thuba pa chena po desa /
NK120(e)001:5098: gnas phun sum tshogs pa bya rgoda phung po'i ri bo la sogas par /
NK120(e)001:5099: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa thega pa chena po'i rigas
NK120(e)001:5100: can lha klu mi dang lha ma yin dri za
NK120(e)001:5102: thun mong ma yin pa'i 'khor sa chen po la
NK120(e)001:5103: bzhugs pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dpag tu med pa
NK120(e)001:5104: la / chos phun sum tshogs pa shin tu rgyas
NK120(e)001:5105: pa'i sde snod lhag pa sems kyi bslab pa gtso
NK120(e)001:5106: bor ston pa las brtsams te mdo sde'i 'dul ba
NK120(e)001:5107: byang sems kyi sdom pa'i mtshams rnam par gzhag pa
NK120(e)001:5108: la / dang / mdo sde'i mdo sde ting nge 'dzin zab cing rgya che ba dang /
NK120(e)001:5109: mdo sde'i mngon pa sa lam dang gzungs ting gi
NK120(e)001:5110: rab dbye ji snyed pa rnams ston pa bka' bar
NK120(e)001:5111: pa mtshan nyid med pa'i chos kyi rnam grangs dang
NK120(e)001:5112: / yang gnas gcig tu ma nges par theg pa thams cad kyi rigs can la /
NK120(e)001:5113: chos lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa gtso bor
NK120(e)001:5114: ston pa tshegs chung zhing thabs sla bas nyon mongs
NK120(e)001:5115: pa 'dul ba'i thabs ston pa mngon pa'i 'dul ba
NK120(e)001:5116: dang / de kho na nyid zab mo'i don la
NK120(e)001:5117: 'jug pa'i tshul ston pa mngon pa'i mdo sde dang
NK120(e)001:5118: dang / / rgya che ba phung khams skye mched
NK120(e)001:5119: kyi rab dbye sogs dang khyad par de bzhin gshegs
NK120(e)001:5120: pa'i snying po'i khams gtan la 'bebs pa mngon pa'i
NK120(e)001:5121: dang / / mngon pa ste / bka' tha ma
NK120(e)001:5122: nges pa don gyi rnam grangs ston pa legs pa
NK120(e)001:5123: rnam par phye ba'i chos 'khor te /
NK120(e)001:5124: tshig don shina tu zab cing rgyasa pa'i sde snoda dapaga tu med cing bsam yasa pa rnams /
NK120(e)001:5125: dus phun sum tshogs pa gdul bya'i mos pa bzhin
NK120(e)001:5126: rim gyis sam cig char du gsungas pa ltar snang
NK120(e)001:5127: bar mdzad de / mdo sde yon tan bkod pa'i rgyal po las /
NK120(e)001:5128: nga yis ci yang ma gsungs par //
NK120(e)001:5129: sems can rnams la khyab brdal snang //
NK120(e)001:5130: gang tshe rim gyis mngon 'dod pa //
NK120(e)001:5131: de dag kun la de bzhin te //
NK120(e)001:5132: dus gcig nyid du 'jug can la //
NK120(e)001:5133: chos kyi rnam grangs rdzogs par snang //
NK120(e)001:5134: yid bzhin re ba rnams skong ba'i //
NK120(e)001:5135: gsung gi che ba de nyid do //
NK120(e)001:5137: de yang 'khor lo gsum po grangs nges su 'dod tshul la /
NK120(e)001:5138: bka' dang por kun rdzob kyi bden pa gtso bor
NK120(e)001:5139: bstan pas drang don yin par thams cad mthun la
NK120(e)001:5140: / bar pa dang tha ma gnyis drang nges gang yin la bzhed pa mi mthun pa mang yang /
NK120(e)001:5141: rang lugs ni bar pa drang nges phyed ma'am gnas skabs pa'i nges don dang /
NK120(e)001:5142: tha ma nyid nges don du 'dod de /
NK120(e)001:5144: dang po gnyis kyi skabs su 'khor lo bskor ba de yang bla na mchis pa /
NK120(e)001:5147: rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su gyur pa //
NK120(e)001:5150: ngo mtshar rmad du byung ba'i chos kyi 'khor lo bskor te /
NK120(e)001:5151: 'khor lo bskor ba 'di ni bla na ma mchis pa /
NK120(e)001:5154: rtsod pa'i gzhi'i gnas su gyur pa ma lags so //
NK120(e)001:5156: gnyis pa de bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:5157: 'jam dbyangs dka' bsdus klu sgrub sogs kyis bkral //
NK120(e)001:5158: zhi ba lhas spel zab mo lta ba'i lugs //
NK120(e)001:5159: byams pas bka' bsdus thogs med sku mched bkral //
NK120(e)001:5160: jo bo rjes spel rgya chen spyod pa'i srol //
NK120(e)001:5161: pad+ma'i ring lugs n+aa gardzu nar mthun //
NK120(e)001:5163: spyir bka' bsdu la thun mong ba ni rim pa gsum sngar bshad pa ltar yin la /
NK120(e)001:5164: theg chen thun mong ma yin pa ltar na /
NK120(e)001:5165: rgyal po'i khab kyi lho phyogs bi ma sam+b+ha ba'i ri la rgyal sras 'bum phrag bcu 'dus te /
NK120(e)001:5166: byams pa 'jam dbyangs gsang bdag gsum gyis sde snod gsum bsdus par bshad cing /
NK120(e)001:5167: 'dir khyad par ba shing rta chen po'i srol gnyis kyi dbang du byas na /
NK120(e)001:5168: srol dang po theg pa chen po'i sde snod rnams las /
NK120(e)001:5169: zab mo stong pa nyid ji lta ba'i phyogs rnams rje btsun 'ajama dpal dbyangs kyis bka'a bsdus shing /
NK120(e)001:5170: de'i rjes su bzung ba rgyal bas lung bstan slob
NK120(e)001:5171: dpon klu sgrub kyis 'khor lo bar pa'i dgongs 'grel
NK120(e)001:5172: du chos thams cad rang stong du gtan la 'bebs
NK120(e)001:5173: byed dbu ma rigs tshogs dang /
NK120(e)001:5174: 'khor lo tha ma'i dgongs 'grel gzhan stong du gtan
NK120(e)001:5175: la 'bebs byed bstod tshogs sogs mdzad nas zab mo
NK120(e)001:5176: lta ba'i shing rta'i srol phyes shing /
NK120(e)001:5177: sogas khong nas de'i srol 'dzin zla ba grags pa /
NK120(e)001:5179: legs ldan 'byed sogs kyisa kyang dgongs 'grel gyi bstan bcos mang du mdzad nas bkrala la /
NK120(e)001:5180: sems bskyed kyi phyag bzhes zhi ba lha dang dze
NK120(e)001:5181: ta ri la sogs pas rgya cher spela ba ni
NK120(e)001:5182: zaba mo lta ba'i lugsa yin cing /
NK120(e)001:5183: yang srol gnyis pa ji snyed pa rgya chen spyod
NK120(e)001:5184: pa'i phyogs kyi mdo sde rnams rgyal tshabs byamsa pa
NK120(e)001:5185: mgon pos bka'i bsdu ba gnang nas gzhan stong du
NK120(e)001:5186: gtan la 'bebs pa'i bstan bcos byams chos sde lnga
NK120(e)001:5187: mdzad de / rgyal bas lung stan 'phags pa thogas med la bstan cing /
NK120(e)001:5188: des sa sde lnga la sogs pa'i bstan bcos mdzad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5189: mkhas mchog dbyig gnyen gyis pra ka ra na sde brgyad sogs mdzad de /
NK120(e)001:5190: de ltar sku mcheda gnyis kyis legs par bkrala pa'i srol nyid phyogs kyi glang po /
NK120(e)001:5192: tsan+d+ra go mi la sogs pas bzung zhing /
NK120(e)001:5193: sems bskyed kyi phyag bzhes nyid bod yul 'dir jo
NK120(e)001:5194: bo rje dpal ldan a ti shasa spel bar mdzad
NK120(e)001:5195: cing rim par brgyud ba ni rgya chena spyoda pa'i
NK120(e)001:5196: srola yin la / rang cag slob dpon chen po
NK120(e)001:5197: pad+ma'i rjes su 'jug pa gsang sngags snga 'gyur gyi
NK120(e)001:5198: ringa lugas pa rnams ni sngags kyi rgyud sde rnams
NK120(e)001:5199: las gsungs pa'i byang sdom gyi thob tshul dang de'i
NK120(e)001:5200: bslab bya'i rkang grangs phal cher 'phags pa n+aa gardzu
NK120(e)001:5202: lta ba ni srol gnyis ka dang mthun pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:5203: gsum pa de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya gtan la dbab pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5204: thob bya sdom pa'i ngo bo dang dbye ba spyir bshad /
NK120(e)001:5205: thob byed sdom pa'i lag len bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5206: dang po spyir bshad pa la'ang gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5209: dang po sdom pa'i ngo bo ni /
NK120(e)001:5210: ngo bo byams dang snying rjes rgyud brlan cing //
NK120(e)001:5211: gzhan gyi don du byang chub thob 'dod pas //
NK120(e)001:5212: sgo gsum nyes pa spong ba'i sems pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5214: brjod bya'i snying po byang chub sems kyi ngo bo
NK120(e)001:5215: ni sems can thams cad la mas bu gcig pa
NK120(e)001:5216: ltar yid du 'ong bar mthong nas bde ba dang
NK120(e)001:5217: ldan par 'dod pa'i byamsa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5218: de dag gi sdug bsngal rgyu dang bcas pa bral bar 'dod pa'i snying rjesa rgyud brlan cing /
NK120(e)001:5219: gzhan gyi dona kho na'i phyir ched du bya ba
NK120(e)001:5220: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub thob par 'doda
NK120(e)001:5222: thabs shes zung du 'jug pa'i sems smon 'jug gis
NK120(e)001:5223: bsdus pa phar phyin drug gi ngo bor gyur pa'i
NK120(e)001:5224: sgrub pa khyad par bde'i mi mthun phyogs gzhan la
NK120(e)001:5225: phan pa'i gegs dang rang gi rdzogs byang gi bar
NK120(e)001:5226: chad sgo gsuma gyi nyesa pasa sponga ba'i semsa pa
NK120(e)001:5227: rgyun chags pa'o // de ltar yang mngon rtogs rgyan las /
NK120(e)001:5228: sems bskyed pa ni gzhan don phyir //
NK120(e)001:5229: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'dod //
NK120(e)001:5231: de yang 'phags seng gnyis kyis gtso sems te yid shes nyid la bzhed cing /
NK120(e)001:5232: thogs med sku mched ni sems byung la bzhed de /
NK120(e)001:5234: byang chub sems dpa'i smon lam gyi mchog ni sems bskyed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:5235: zhes 'dun pa la bzhed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5237: don gnyis la dmigs pa'i sems pa ni sems bskyed pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5239: 'dir sems rang gis bskyed par bya bas na sems
NK120(e)001:5240: bskyed ces pa bya ba la bshad na gtso sems
NK120(e)001:5241: dang / sems bskyed par byed pas na sems bskyed
NK120(e)001:5242: ces byed pa la bshad na sems byung yin pas
NK120(e)001:5243: dang / / gnyis ka la sems bskyed kyi sgra bshad du yod ces gsungs /
NK120(e)001:5245: sems ni don gyi ngo bo rig pa yin la /
NK120(e)001:5246: sems byung de'i khyad par la dpyod pas nas /
NK120(e)001:5247: 'dir ngo bo bskyed pas khyad par zhar la bskyed par 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:5248: 'dun pa sems bskyed la sogs pa zhar la thob pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:5250: gnyis pa sdom pa'i dbye ba la gsum /
NK120(e)001:5254: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5255: dbye ba klu sgrub thogs med srol gnyis grags //
NK120(e)001:5256: re re'ang gcig nas drug bar gnyis gnyis te //
NK120(e)001:5258: dbye ba la spyir klu sgrub dang thogas meda kyi srola zhes gnyisa su gragas pa la /
NK120(e)001:5259: bye brag srol gnyis po re re la'nga gciga nasa druga gi bar du dbye zhing /
NK120(e)001:5260: de yang dbye gzhi la ltos nas smon 'jug gi dbye bas gnyisa gnyisa te zhes pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5261: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5262: gcig nas drug tshan gyi bar du dbye ba dang /
NK120(e)001:5264: dang po gcig nas drug tshan gyi bar du dbye ba ni /
NK120(e)001:5265: dang po stong nyid snying rje'i snying po can //
NK120(e)001:5266: tshogs gnyis bslab pa kun rdzob don dam gnyis //
NK120(e)001:5267: tshul khrims ting 'dzin shes rab bslab gsum dang //
NK120(e)001:5268: tshogs sbyor mos pas spyod pa'i sems bskyed dang //
NK120(e)001:5269: ma dag sa bdun lhag bsam dag pa dang //
NK120(e)001:5270: dag pa sa gsum rnam par smin pa dang //
NK120(e)001:5271: thugs rje chen po sgrib kun spangs pa ni //
NK120(e)001:5272: sangs rgyas sa yi sems bskyed dag dang bzhi //
NK120(e)001:5273: lnga ni lam lnga drug ni phar phyin drug /
NK120(e)001:5275: de yang tshan pa drug las /
NK120(e)001:5277: stong nyid rtogs pa'i shes rab kyis de ma rtogs
NK120(e)001:5278: pa la snying rjes drangs pa'i byang chub kyi sems
NK120(e)001:5279: skyes pa la ltos nas stong nyid snying rje'i snying
NK120(e)001:5280: po can gyi sems bskyed ces bya'o //
NK120(e)001:5282: bsod nams kyi tshogs dang ye shes kyi tshogas gnyisa kyi bslaba pa la ltos nas gnyis sam /
NK120(e)001:5283: rags pa brda las byung ba kun rdzob sems bskyed dang /
NK120(e)001:5284: phra ba chos nyid kyis thob pa dona dama gyi sems bskyed pa gnyisa so //
NK120(e)001:5286: dag par byed pa tshul khrimas /
NK120(e)001:5288: grol bar byed pa shesa raba kyi bslab pa gsuma la ltos nas sems bskyed gsum mam /
NK120(e)001:5289: yang na nyes spyod sdom pa /
NK120(e)001:5291: sems can don byed dang gsum po la ltos nas kyang gsum du dbye ba'o //
NK120(e)001:5293: tshogas sbyor du stong nyid mtha' bral la mosa pasa
NK120(e)001:5294: spyod pa'i sgo nas gzhan don la dmigs pa'i semas
NK120(e)001:5295: bskyed dang / ma dag sa bduna na bdag gzhan
NK120(e)001:5296: mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas lhag bsam dag pa'i
NK120(e)001:5297: bskyed dang / sems bskyed dang / dag pa sa
NK120(e)001:5298: gsuma na rnam par mi rtog pa'i ye shes rtsol
NK120(e)001:5299: med du 'byung zhing gzhan don ngang gis 'grub pas
NK120(e)001:5300: rnam para smin pa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK120(e)001:5301: dmigs pa med pa'i thugsa rje chena po sgrib gnyis
NK120(e)001:5302: bag chags dang bcas pa kun nas spangsa pa ni
NK120(e)001:5303: sangsa rgyasa kyi sa yi semsa bskyed dag dang bzhira
NK120(e)001:5304: dbye ba dang / lnga tshan ni /
NK120(e)001:5305: tshogs lam na sems dang po bskyed cing lam la
NK120(e)001:5306: gsar du 'jug pa las dang po pa'i sems bskyed
NK120(e)001:5307: dang / sbyor lam na de yongs su sbyong ba byas pa'i dang /
NK120(e)001:5308: mthong lam na chos nyid kyi don mngon sum du mthong ba'i dang /
NK120(e)001:5309: sgom lam na de lhan skyes kyi sgrib pa las rnam par grol bzhin pa'i dang /
NK120(e)001:5310: mi slob pa'i lam na 'dus ma byas pa'i ye
NK120(e)001:5311: shes ji bzhin pa mngon du gyur pa mthar thug
NK120(e)001:5312: pa'i ngang las 'gro don lhun grub tu 'byung ba
NK120(e)001:5313: sar gnas rnams kyis kyang ji bzhin spyod yul du
NK120(e)001:5314: ma gyur pas na bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i sems
NK120(e)001:5315: bskyed pa ste / de ltar lngar dbye ba ni lam lnga dang sbyor ba'o //
NK120(e)001:5317: phara phyin drug gi ldog pa la ltos nas sems bskyed drug tu 'gyur ba'o //
NK120(e)001:5318: gnyis pa sa mtshams kyi dbye ba ni /
NK120(e)001:5319: sa gser zla ba me sogs nyer gnyis ni //
NK120(e)001:5320: sa mtshams kyis phye sa bcu'i bar du'o //
NK120(e)001:5323: de yang sa gser zla ba me //
NK120(e)001:5324: gter dang rin chen 'byung gnas mtsho //
NK120(e)001:5325: rdo rje ri sman bshes gnyen dang //
NK120(e)001:5326: yid bzhin nor bu nyi ma glu //
NK120(e)001:5327: rgyal po mdzod dang lam po che //
NK120(e)001:5328: bzhon pa bkod ma'i chu dang ni //
NK120(e)001:5329: sgra snyan chu bo sprin rnams kyis //
NK120(e)001:5330: rnam pa nyi shu rtsa gnyis so //
NK120(e)001:5332: dpe grogs mtshungs chos gsum dang sbyar ba'i sgo nas dbye na /
NK120(e)001:5333: sa gsera zla ba me la sogas pa'i dpe nyer gnyis ni /
NK120(e)001:5334: grogs byang chub don gnyer gyi 'dun pa dang mtshungs par ldan pa'i sems bskyed chos can /
NK120(e)001:5336: dkar chos thams cad bskyed pa'i gzhi'i dngos po byed pa chos mthun pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:5338: rgyun gnas pa'i bsam pa byang chub kyi bar du 'gyur ba med pas gser 2lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5339: bsam pa de lhag par gyur pas dge chos gong du 'phel bas zla ba 3lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5340: phyin drug la dngos su sbyor bas sgrib pa'i bud shing bsregs pas me 4lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5341: sems can rnams tshim par byed cing mi zad pas sbyin pa gter 5lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5342: yon tan rin po che thams cad bskyed pas tshul khrims rin po che'i 'byung gnas lta bu 6dang /
NK120(e)001:5343: mi 'dod pas yid mi 'khrugs pas bzod pa mtsho lta bu 7dang /
NK120(e)001:5344: bdud kyis mi phyed pas brtson 'grus rdo rje lta 8bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5345: mtshan mas mi g.yo bas bsam gtan ri 9lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5346: sgrib gnyis kyi nad zhi bas shes rab sman 10lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5347: dge rtsa chud mi za zhing gzhan don sgrub pa la mkhas pas thabs bshes gnyen 11lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5348: rang gzhan gyi re ba skong bas smon lam yid bzhin gyi nor bu 12lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5349: gdul bya'i rgyud kyi dge ba'i lo tog smin par byed pas stobs nyi ma 13lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5350: gdul bya 'dun par byed pa'i chos ston pas ye shes glu 14dbyangs lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5351: gzhan don thogs med du sgrub pas mngon shes rgyal 15po lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5352: bsod nams dang ye shes zad mi shes pas tshogs gnyis bang mdzod lta bu 16dang /
NK120(e)001:5353: dus gsum gyi 'phags pa rnams kyi gshegs shul yin pas byang phyogs lam po che lta bu 17dang /
NK120(e)001:5354: mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i lam du 'gro bas zhi lhag bzhon pa bzang po 18lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5355: tshig don mi brjed cing gzhan la ston pas gzungs spobs bkod ma'i chu lta bu dang 19 /
NK120(e)001:5356: thar 'dod kyi gdul bya rnams la chos snyan par
NK120(e)001:5357: sgrogs pas chos kyi dga' ston sgra snyan 20lta bu
NK120(e)001:5358: dang / gzhan don 'bad med du 'byung zhing rnam
NK120(e)001:5359: pa thams cad mkhyen pa'i rgya mtshor ngang gis 'babs
NK120(e)001:5360: pas bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam chu bo 21lta bu
NK120(e)001:5361: dang / dang / chos kyi dbyings las ma g.yos
NK120(e)001:5362: bzhin gdul bya'i lo tog smin par mdzad pas chos
NK120(e)001:5363: kyi sku sprin lta bu ste nyi shu rtsa gnyis
NK120(e)001:5364: dang / dang / 22so // de dag sa matshamas kyis phye na /
NK120(e)001:5367: lhag pa'i bsam pa dang gsum ni tshogs lam gsum na'o //
NK120(e)001:5368: sbyor ba ni sbyor lam na'o //
NK120(e)001:5369: sbyin pa'i phar phyin ni mthong lam na'o //
NK120(e)001:5378: ye shes dang dgu ni sgom lam gyis bsdus pa'i sa dgu na'o //
NK120(e)001:5380: bsod nams ye shes gnyis dang /
NK120(e)001:5382: snying rje lhag mthong gnyis dang /
NK120(e)001:5384: spobs pa dang lnga ni khyad par gyi lam dag pa sa gsum ka la khyab par yod do //
NK120(e)001:5386: bgrod pa gcig pa'i lam dang /
NK120(e)001:5387: chos kyi sku dang ldan pa gsum ni sangs rgyas
NK120(e)001:5388: kyi sa zhes theg chen dgra bcom bzhugs pa sa
NK120(e)001:5389: bcu pa'i sbyor dngos rjes gsum na yod pa ste
NK120(e)001:5390: / de ltar na tshogs lam dang po nas rgyun matha'i bar du bzhag pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5391: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:5392: kun kyang bsdu na smon 'jug rnam pa gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5393: de yang bsam pas smon dang sbyor bas khyab //
NK120(e)001:5394: 'gro bar 'dod dang 'gro ba ji bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:5396: de ltar dbye sgo bdun gyi sgo nas bshad pa'i
NK120(e)001:5397: sems bskyed de dag kun kyang mdor bsdu na smon
NK120(e)001:5399: de yanga bsam pasa gzhan don du byang chub thob par 'dod pa ni smon pa sems bskyed dang /
NK120(e)001:5400: de'i ched du sbyor basa lag len du phar phyin
NK120(e)001:5401: drug la khyab par bslab pa ni 'jug pa sems
NK120(e)001:5402: bskyed de / de'i tshul yang dper na snga ma
NK120(e)001:5403: ni skyes bu don gnyer gyi sa der gang zhig
NK120(e)001:5405: phyi ma ni lam la dngos su zhugs nas 'gro ba ji bzhina pa ste /
NK120(e)001:5407: byang chub sems de mdor bsdu na //
NK120(e)001:5408: rnam pa gnyis su shes bya ste //
NK120(e)001:5409: byang chub smon pa'i sems dang ni //
NK120(e)001:5410: byang chub 'jug pa nyid yin no //
NK120(e)001:5412: bye brag ji ltar shes pa ltar //
NK120(e)001:5413: de bzhin mkhas pas 'di gnyis kyi //
NK120(e)001:5414: bye brag rim bzhin shes par bya //
NK120(e)001:5416: gnyis pa thob byed sdom pa'i lag len bye brag tu bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:5417: ma thob pa thob par byed pa /
NK120(e)001:5418: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung pa /
NK120(e)001:5419: sdom pa skye ba'i lus rten /
NK120(e)001:5422: dang po ma thob pa thob par byed pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5423: kun rdzob sems bskyed skye ba'i cho ga bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:5424: don dam sems bskyed skye ba cho ga la mi ltos par bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5425: dang po kun rdzob sems bskyed skye ba'i cho ga bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5428: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5429: dang po sdom pa ma thob thob tshul ni //
NK120(e)001:5432: de ltar sems bskyed kyi rang bzhin gtan la phab nas /
NK120(e)001:5433: dang po sems bskyed kyi sdom pa de ma thoba
NK120(e)001:5434: pa thoba par byed pa'i tshul ni 'di ltar lena
NK120(e)001:5436: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK120(e)001:5437: spyir bskyed bya kun rdzob sems bskyed kyi mtshan nyid ni /
NK120(e)001:5438: gzhan don du rdzogs byang la dmigs pa'i theg chen slob pa'i sems bskyed gang zhig /
NK120(e)001:5439: byang 'phags kyi mnyam bzhag gi ngo bor gyur pa'i sems bskyed rnam par bcad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5441: theg chen tshogs sbyor ba'i rgyud kyi dang /
NK120(e)001:5442: byang 'phags kyi rjes thob kyi ngo bor gyur pa'i sems bskyed lta bu'o //
NK120(e)001:5444: grogs dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyi stobs dang /
NK120(e)001:5446: dge rtsa byas pa'i stobs dang /
NK120(e)001:5447: theg chen gyi sde snod thos pa'i stobs dang /
NK120(e)001:5448: thos pa mang du goms pas bskyed pa dang lnga las /
NK120(e)001:5449: dang po grogs la rag las pas mi brtan pa'i sems bskyed dang /
NK120(e)001:5450: phyi ma bzhi mi mthun phyogs kyi nyams dka' bas brtan pa'i sems bskyed de /
NK120(e)001:5452: grogs stobs rgyu stobs rtsa ba'i stobs //
NK120(e)001:5453: thos stobs dge ba goms pa las //
NK120(e)001:5454: mi brtan pa dang brtan 'byung ba //
NK120(e)001:5455: gzhan gyis bstan pa'i sems bskyed bshad //
NK120(e)001:5457: gtso bor gzhan gyi mthu las byung ba kun rdzob sems bskyed len tshul la bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:5458: gang las blang ba'i slob dpon ji ltar len pa'i tshul //
NK120(e)001:5459: rten las kyang len rung ba'i dmigs bsal /
NK120(e)001:5460: sdom pa'i thob mtshams ngos bzung ba'o //
NK120(e)001:5461: dang po gang la blang ba'i slob dpon ni /
NK120(e)001:5462: sdom gnas dge ba'i bshes gnyen la //
NK120(e)001:5464: srol gnyis ka mthun par gang las blang ba'i yul byang sems kyi sdom pa la gansa shing /
NK120(e)001:5465: de 'bogs pa'i cho ga dang bslab bya la bkri mkhas pa /
NK120(e)001:5466: zang zing lhur mi byed par brtse bas rjes su
NK120(e)001:5467: 'dzin nus pa'i dge ba'i bshesa gnyena mtshan nyid dang
NK120(e)001:5468: ldan pa las len dgos la /
NK120(e)001:5470: rtag par dge ba'i bshes gnyen ni //
NK120(e)001:5471: theg chen don la mkhas pa dang //
NK120(e)001:5472: byang chub sems dpa'i brtul zhugs mchog /
NK120(e)001:5473: srog gi phyir yang mi btang ngo //
NK120(e)001:5475: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK120(e)001:5476: bla ma sdom la gnas shing mkhas //
NK120(e)001:5477: nus dang ldan las blang bar bya //
NK120(e)001:5479: gnyis pa ji ltar len pa'i tshul la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5482: dang po klu sgrub kyi lugs la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5483: gang gis blang ba'i gang zag dang /
NK120(e)001:5484: ji ltar len pa'i cho ga'o //
NK120(e)001:5485: dang po gang gis blang ba'i gang zag ni /
NK120(e)001:5486: theg chen snod gyur dad ldan slob ma yis //
NK120(e)001:5488: klu sgrub kyi lugs la brda shes shing sdom pa
NK120(e)001:5489: len 'dod yod na dal 'byor gyi lus rten kho
NK120(e)001:5490: na dgos par ma nges te /
NK120(e)001:5492: lha'i bu gang gis bla na med pa yang dag
NK120(e)001:5493: par rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems ma skyes pa
NK120(e)001:5494: de dag gis bla na med pa yang dag par
NK120(e)001:5495: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu sems bskyed par bya /
NK120(e)001:5499: klu khri nyis stong gis sems bskyed pa la sogs gsungs ba'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:5500: des na rdzogs byang don gnyer gyi bsam pa dngos
NK120(e)001:5501: su skye rung du yod pa'i sems can kun thega
NK120(e)001:5502: chena sems bskyed kyi snod du gyur pa yin cing
NK120(e)001:5503: / byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rgya mtsho lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:5504: 'bras bu bla na med pa'i byang chub chen po
NK120(e)001:5505: la dada pa dang ldan pa'i slob ma de yisa
NK120(e)001:5506: so // gnyis pa ji ltar len pa'i cho ga ni /
NK120(e)001:5507: yan lag bdun mthar smon 'jug stabs gcig tu //
NK120(e)001:5508: len cing rang gzhan dga' ba bsgom pa rnams //
NK120(e)001:5515: gdams ngag khyad par can 'khor ba'i mtha' la skyo ba bskyed cing /
NK120(e)001:5516: zhi ba'i mtha' la zhen pa bkag nas /
NK120(e)001:5517: mtha' gnyis spangs pa'i byang chub kyi sems la spro ba bskyed de /
NK120(e)001:5518: de ltar thabs gsum gyi blo bcos pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK120(e)001:5519: yul khyad par can slob dpon la man+dala phul nas gsol ba btab rjes /
NK120(e)001:5520: rten khyad par can dkon mchog gsum la skyabs 'gro bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:5521: thabs khyad par can yan lag bdun pas tshogs bsags pa'i mathara /
NK120(e)001:5522: gnyis pa dngos gzhi sems bskyed kyi sdom pa blang ba ni /
NK120(e)001:5523: sems can thams cad rang gi pha ma drin can yin la /
NK120(e)001:5524: de thams cad sdug bsngal gyis gzir ba la snying rje'i shugs drag pos /
NK120(e)001:5525: de dag gi gnas skabs dang mthar thug gi phan
NK120(e)001:5526: bde'i rgyur rang gi bde dge thams cad gtong zhing
NK120(e)001:5527: / sdug bsngal thams cad dang du blang bar bya'o
NK120(e)001:5528: snyam du zhe thag pa nas blo sbyong bar byas
NK120(e)001:5529: / te / dgongs gsol sngon du 'gro bas /
NK120(e)001:5530: ji ltar sngon gyi bde gshegs kyis //
NK120(e)001:5531: zhes sogs spyod 'jug ltar tshigs su bcad pa gnyis po lan gsum bzlas pas blang ngo //
NK120(e)001:5532: de la tshigs bcad dang pos ni sngon gyi sangs
NK120(e)001:5533: rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis thugs bskyed
NK120(e)001:5534: tshul bstan nas / tshigs bcad gnyis pas de dag
NK120(e)001:5535: gis ji ltar bslab pa de bzhin du bdag gis
NK120(e)001:5536: kyang bslab bo zhes dam bca' bas smon 'juga gnyis
NK120(e)001:5537: kyi sems bskyed dang sdom pa stabsa gciga tu lena
NK120(e)001:5540: ranga dga' ba bsgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5541: gazhana dag'a ba bsgoma du gzhug pa gnyis las /
NK120(e)001:5542: dang po rang dga' ba bsgom pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5543: deng dus bdag tshe 'bras bu yod //
NK120(e)001:5545: gnyis pa gzhan dga' ba bsgom pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5546: bdag gis de ring skyob pa thams cad kyi //
NK120(e)001:5548: gtang rag dbul zhing bslab bya mdo tsam bshad pa
NK120(e)001:5549: rnamas ni 'phags mchog klu sgruba kyi lugas yina no
NK120(e)001:5550: // gnyis pa thogs med kyi lugs la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5551: gang gis blang ba'i gang zag dang /
NK120(e)001:5552: ji ltar len pa'i cho ga'o //
NK120(e)001:5555: smon sems len la so thar mi dgos kyang //
NK120(e)001:5556: ya dag blangs pa rigs bdun sngon song nas //
NK120(e)001:5558: slob dpon thogas meda kyi bzheda pa ni rten gyi
NK120(e)001:5559: gang zag smona semas tsam lena pa la so thar
NK120(e)001:5560: gyi sdom pa sngon du 'gro mi dgosa kyang 'jug
NK120(e)001:5561: sdom ma thob pa yanga dag par blang ba la
NK120(e)001:5562: so thar rigas bduna gang rung gi sdom pa sngon
NK120(e)001:5563: du songa nasa len dgos te /
NK120(e)001:5565: so sor thar pa rigs bdun gyi //
NK120(e)001:5566: rtag tu sdom gzhan ldan pa la //
NK120(e)001:5567: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa yi //
NK120(e)001:5568: skal pa yod kyi gzhan du min //
NK120(e)001:5570: gnyis pa ji ltar len pa'i cho ga ni bar chad dri dang bslab pa khas len sogs //
NK120(e)001:5571: smon 'jug cho ga so so'i sgo nas len //
NK120(e)001:5573: ji ltar len pa'i cho ga la rten nges par
NK120(e)001:5574: bya ba sngar ltar mtha' gnyis kyi zhen pa bkag
NK120(e)001:5575: nas byang sems la spro ba bskyed pa ste gdams
NK120(e)001:5576: ngag gsum gyis blo bcos nas cho ga dngos la
NK120(e)001:5583: yul khyad par can la man+dala phul nas gsol ba 'debs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5584: rten khyad par can la skyabs su 'gro ba byas nas /
NK120(e)001:5585: thabs khyad par can yan lag bdun ldan gyis tshogs bsag go //
NK120(e)001:5587: rang stobs rigs sad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5588: gzhan stobs rdzogs byang gi phan yon mthong ba la sogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5589: sbyor ba'i stobs 'du shes gsum bskyed de /
NK120(e)001:5590: phyogs bcu na zhes sogs kyi dgongs gsol sngon du 'gro bas /
NK120(e)001:5591: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi bas skye ba 'di dang /
NK120(e)001:5594: zhes pa'i bar lan gsum bzlas pas blang ngo //
NK120(e)001:5598: gtang rag gtong ba rnams so //
NK120(e)001:5600: so thar rigs bdun gang rung blangs nas byang sems
NK120(e)001:5601: kyi sde snod la sbyangs pas dad cing bsgrub par
NK120(e)001:5602: nus pa na / 'jug sdom dngos blang ba'i cho ga la /
NK120(e)001:5607: myur du sbyin par gsol ba 'debs pa /
NK120(e)001:5609: bslaba pa'i gnas go bar byas nas spro ba dri ba rnams so //
NK120(e)001:5612: rigs kyi bu ming 'di zhes bya ba khyod //
NK120(e)001:5614: sems can gyi don byed pa'i tshul khrims nod nas /
NK120(e)001:5615: zhes lan gsum dris pa na /
NK120(e)001:5616: slob mas kyang nod lags zhes lan gsum khasa lena pas sdom pa thob par 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:5617: sogas khong nas rjes kyi cho ga ston te /
NK120(e)001:5623: de nas rang bzhin gtan la dbab pa zhes mdor
NK120(e)001:5624: bsdus te phan yon brjod pa tsam bya ba ste
NK120(e)001:5625: de ltar smona 'juga gi cho ga so so'i sgo
NK120(e)001:5626: nasa rim pa bzhin du lena pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:5627: gsum pa rten las kyang len rung ba'i dmigs bsal bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5628: rgyal ba'i rten la'ang rung bar srol gnyis mthun //
NK120(e)001:5630: spyir bla ma dge ba'i bshes gnyen las blangs na
NK120(e)001:5631: ngo tsha khrel yod kyi rten du 'gyur ba sogs
NK120(e)001:5632: dgos pa khyad par can yod mod /
NK120(e)001:5633: gal te bshes gnyen mtshan nyid dang ldan pa ma rnyed na /
NK120(e)001:5634: rgyal ba'i sku gzugs kyi rten drung la'ang bdag nyid
NK120(e)001:5635: kyis blangs kyang runga bar srol gnyis ka dgongs pa
NK120(e)001:5637: der ma zad rgyal ba sras bcas mdun gyi nam
NK120(e)001:5638: mkhar mngon sum du bzhugs par bsgom pa'i drung nas
NK120(e)001:5641: gal te bla ma ma rnyed na //
NK120(e)001:5642: de la gzhan sdom nod pa yi //
NK120(e)001:5643: cho ga yang dag bshad par bya //
NK120(e)001:5644: de la sngon tshe 'jam pa'i dpal //
NK120(e)001:5645: am+ba r+aa dzar gyur pa yis //
NK120(e)001:5646: ji ltar byang chub thugs bskyed pa //
NK120(e)001:5647: 'jam dpal gyi ni sangs rgyas zhing //
NK120(e)001:5648: rgyan gyi mdo las bshad pa ltar //
NK120(e)001:5649: de bzhin 'dir ni rab gsal bris //
NK120(e)001:5650: mgon po rnams kyi spyan snga ru //
NK120(e)001:5651: rdzogs pa'i byang chub sems bskyed cing //
NK120(e)001:5652: 'gro ba thams cad mgron du gnyer //
NK120(e)001:5653: de dag 'khor ba las bsgral to //
NK120(e)001:5654: gnod sems khro ba'i sems nyid dang //
NK120(e)001:5655: ser sna dang ni phrag dog nyid //
NK120(e)001:5656: deng nas bzung ste byang chub mchog /
NK120(e)001:5657: thob kyi bar du mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:5658: tshangs par spyod pa spyad bya zhing //
NK120(e)001:5659: sdig dang 'dod pa spang bar bya //
NK120(e)001:5660: tshul khrims sdom pa la dga' bas //
NK120(e)001:5661: sangs rgyas rjes su bslab par bya //
NK120(e)001:5662: bdag nyid myur ba'i tshul gyis ni //
NK120(e)001:5663: byang chub thob par mi spro zhing //
NK120(e)001:5664: sems can gcig gi phyir yang ni //
NK120(e)001:5665: phyi ma'i mu mthar gnas par bgyi //
NK120(e)001:5666: tshad med bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i //
NK120(e)001:5667: zhing dag rnam par sbyang bar bya //
NK120(e)001:5668: ming nas bzung ba bya ba dang //
NK120(e)001:5669: phyogs bcu dag tu rnam par gnas //
NK120(e)001:5670: bdag gi lus dang ngag gi las //
NK120(e)001:5671: thams cad du ni dag par bya //
NK120(e)001:5672: yid kyi las kyang dag bya ste //
NK120(e)001:5673: mi dge'i las rnams mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:5674: zhes gsungs pa lta bu'i tshul gyis sems bskyed blang bar bya'o //
NK120(e)001:5675: bzhi pa sdom pa'i thob mtshams dngos bzung ba ni /
NK120(e)001:5676: thob matshamasabarjoda pa gsum gyi mtha' la'o //
NK120(e)001:5678: srol gnyis gang yin kyang rung ste /
NK120(e)001:5679: sdom pa'i thob matshamas brda las byung ba yin pas na /
NK120(e)001:5680: dngos gzhi 'bogs chog bzlas pa'i brjod pa lan gsuma gyi mtha' ma la thob par bzhed pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5681: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed skye ba cho ga la mi ltos par bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5682: don dam sems bskyed cho gas blangs thob pa //
NK120(e)001:5683: gsang sngags lugs yin mdo las bshad srid na //
NK120(e)001:5684: dam bca' nyid yin sgoms pa'i stobs las skye //
NK120(e)001:5686: de la dona dama pa'i semsa bskyed ni rnam par
NK120(e)001:5687: mi rtog pa'i chos nyid mngon sum du rtogs pa'i
NK120(e)001:5689: byang 'phags kyi mnyam bzhag gi ngo bor gyur pa'i dang /
NK120(e)001:5690: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i mnyam rjes dbyer med kyi ngo bor gyur pa'i sems bskyed do //
NK120(e)001:5691: de la tha snyad 'dod tshul gyis dbye na phar
NK120(e)001:5692: phyin theg pa'i skabs don dam ni chos dbyings dang
NK120(e)001:5693: / sems bskyed ni de mngon du rtogs pa'i ye shes la bshad cing /
NK120(e)001:5694: de thob pa'i tshul yang yongs 'dzin /
NK120(e)001:5696: rtogs pa ste dam pa gsum dang ldan pa'i tshul mdo sde rgyan las /
NK120(e)001:5697: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rab mnyes byas //
NK120(e)001:5698: bsod nams ye shes tshogs rab bsams //
NK120(e)001:5699: chos la mi rtog ye shes ni //
NK120(e)001:5700: skye phyir de ni dam par 'dod //
NK120(e)001:5702: sngags kyi theg par ni gzung 'dzin gnyis dang bral
NK120(e)001:5703: ba'i 'od gsal ba'i ye shes gzhi la gnas pa
NK120(e)001:5704: la bzhed de / sgyu d+r+wa las e ma mtshar lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:5706: dngos po thams cad dang bral ba //
NK120(e)001:5707: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
NK120(e)001:5708: gzugs dang 'dzin pa rnam spangs pa //
NK120(e)001:5709: chos bdag med par mnyam nyid pas //
NK120(e)001:5710: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes pa //
NK120(e)001:5711: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:5712: zhes so de 'dra de cho ga blangas nas thoba pa'i tshul sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang /
NK120(e)001:5714: rim pa lnga pa sogs las bshad pa ni gsang sngags kyi lugsa yina pas /
NK120(e)001:5715: 'bras bu ye shes kyi rnam pa lam byed du
NK120(e)001:5716: byas nas de'i rten 'brel sgrig byed tsam du rjes
NK120(e)001:5717: mthun kun rdzob kyi rnam pas bskyed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:5719: byang chub sems dpa' gsang sngags kyi sgor spyod pa
NK120(e)001:5720: rnams kyis de ltar kun rdzob kyi rnam pas byang
NK120(e)001:5721: chub kyi sems smon pa'i rang bzhin can bskyed nas
NK120(e)001:5722: / don dam pa'i byang chub kyi sems bsgom pa'i stobs kyis bskyed par bya ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:5724: sngags lugs kyi cho ga de'ang sgom byung la ma
NK120(e)001:5725: ltos par cho ga rkyang pas bskyed nus pa ma
NK120(e)001:5726: yin pa'i phyir mtshan nyid ma yin la /
NK120(e)001:5727: gal te spang skong phyag rgya par /
NK120(e)001:5728: don dam pa'i byang chub kyi mchog tu sems bskyed par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:5729: zhes gsungs pa ltar mdo lasa bshad pa srid na'ang /
NK120(e)001:5730: de ni dam bca' tsam nyid du 'dod pa yina gyi /
NK120(e)001:5731: don dam sems bskyed mtshan nyid pa ni sgom pa'i stobsa lasa ngang gis skye ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:5733: don dam pa byang chub kyi sems de ni 'jig rten las 'das pa /
NK120(e)001:5734: spros pa mtha' dag dang bral ba /
NK120(e)001:5739: rlung med pa'i mar me'i rgyun bzhin du mi g.yo ba'o //
NK120(e)001:5740: de 'grub pa ni rtag tu gus pas zhi gnas dang /
NK120(e)001:5741: lhag mthong gi rnal 'byor goms pa las 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:5742: zhes ka ma la sh+ai las sgom rim du drangs pa ltar ro //
NK120(e)001:5743: gnyis pa thob pa de nyid mi nyams par bsrung ba'i tshul bshad pa la /
NK120(e)001:5744: thog mar ji ltar bsrung tshul gyi don bshad pas khog dbub bar bya ste /
NK120(e)001:5746: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa ni //
NK120(e)001:5747: rgyas par theg pa che las 'byung //
NK120(e)001:5749: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mi btang zhing //
NK120(e)001:5750: mdo sde dag la rtag blta bas //
NK120(e)001:5752: byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'i gzhi rnams shes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:5753: bdag rkyen theg pa chen po'i dge ba'i bshes gnyen mi gtong bar gus pas bsten cing /
NK120(e)001:5754: dmigs rkyen byang sems kyi bslab pa'i gnas rgya cher
NK120(e)001:5755: ston pa'i mdo dang bstan bcos dri ma med pa
NK120(e)001:5756: rnams la thos bsam gyi sgo nas sgro 'dogs bcad
NK120(e)001:5758: mkhas par byas pa de yang shes pa tsam du
NK120(e)001:5759: ma bzhag par rang nus ci yod kyis 'bad de
NK120(e)001:5761: gzhan blang dor gyi gnas ma rmongs par shes pa don med du 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:5763: lus kyis 'di dag spyad par bya //
NK120(e)001:5764: tshig tsam brjod pas ci zhig 'grub //
NK120(e)001:5765: sman dpyad bklag pa tsam gyis ni //
NK120(e)001:5766: nad pa dag la phan 'gyur ram //
NK120(e)001:5768: des na ji ltar bsrung ba'i khyad par la /
NK120(e)001:5769: 'gal rkyen nyams pa'i rgyu spong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:5770: mthun rkyen mi nyams pa'i rgyu dang 'phel ba'i rkyen la bslab pa gnyis su 'du ste /
NK120(e)001:5774: sgom pa la lhod pa gsum ni rang don shes rab kyi gegs gsum yin la /
NK120(e)001:5775: sbyor ba le lo che ba /
NK120(e)001:5776: spyod pa gzhan mi dad pa la sbyor ba /
NK120(e)001:5777: kun slong snying rje med pa /
NK120(e)001:5778: byed las phyin ci log sgrub pa bzhi ni gzhan don spyod pa'i skyon bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:5779: de ltar rang gzhan gyi spyod pa nyams pa'i rgyu bdun spong ba la 'bad do //
NK120(e)001:5780: gnyis pa mthun rkyen mi nyams pa'i rgyu dang 'phel ba'i rkyen la bslab tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:5781: dang po sems bskyed skyes pa'i phan yon dran /
NK120(e)001:5783: rnyed par dka' ba yang yang dran par byed pa
NK120(e)001:5784: ni tshe 'dir mi nyams pa'i rgyu dran pa gsum
NK120(e)001:5785: dang / gnyis pa dus gsum du yan lag bdun pa byed pa /
NK120(e)001:5786: rgyal ba sras bcas la gsol ba 'debs pa /
NK120(e)001:5787: chos dang 'gal ba'i bdud las spong ba dang gsum
NK120(e)001:5788: ni phyi mar mi nyams pa'i rgyu phyin ci ma
NK120(e)001:5789: log pa'i thabs gsum yin la /
NK120(e)001:5790: gsum pa bsgrub bya sems can la rang bas gces pa //
NK120(e)001:5791: sgrub byed chos la nor bas gces pa /
NK120(e)001:5792: gtso bo byang sems la snying bas gces pa /
NK120(e)001:5793: bdag rkyen bshes gnyen la pha ma bas gces pa /
NK120(e)001:5794: thob bya sangs rgyas la longs spyod bas gces pa
NK120(e)001:5795: dang lnga ni 'di phyi gnyis kar mi nyams pa'i
NK120(e)001:5797: de rnams yongs bsdoms rnam grangs bcu gnyis ni mthun rkyen mi nyams pa'i rgyu yin no //
NK120(e)001:5798: gnyis pa 'phel ba'i rkyen la bslab tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:5803: byang sems kyi phan yon te /
NK120(e)001:5804: de rnams yid kyis mi brjed par dran pa ste de lnga la bslab pa nyid gzhir bzung nas /
NK120(e)001:5805: shes bzhin gyi mig gis blta ba /
NK120(e)001:5806: brtson 'grus kyi rta mchog zhon pa /
NK120(e)001:5807: nges 'byung gi lcag gis bskul ba /
NK120(e)001:5808: thar pa'i grong khyer yid la bya ba rnams ni bya ba bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:5809: mdor na kun mkhyen chen pos /
NK120(e)001:5810: rtag tu dran dang shes bzhin bag yod kyis //
NK120(e)001:5811: mi dge spang zhing dge chos rgya mtsho sgrub //
NK120(e)001:5812: ces gsungs pa ltar dran pa dang bag yod dang shes bzhin gsum mi nyams par bskyed de /
NK120(e)001:5813: 'chad 'gyur gyi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi ltung bas mi gos par bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:5814: las dang po pa'i skabs su sgrub mi nus pa ma gtogs pa /
NK120(e)001:5815: byang sems kyi bslab bya nus pa'i yul du gyur pa mtha' dag la bslab dgos te /
NK120(e)001:5817: mdor na rang gi nus pa'i yul ma yin pa'i bya ba rnams la ltung ba med de /
NK120(e)001:5818: don med pa nyid kyi de la bslab pa bcas pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:5819: gzhan la ni rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho
NK120(e)001:5820: ba dang bcas pa nyid du bzung ba kho na'o
NK120(e)001:5821: // rang gi nus pa'i yul ma yin pa gang
NK120(e)001:5822: zhig la brtson par byed na ltung bar 'gyur te
NK120(e)001:5823: // / de ni bsam mi dgos par spyir sdig
NK120(e)001:5824: pa bshags pa'i khongs su 'dus pas de las grol
NK120(e)001:5825: // / bar 'gyur ro // de dag ni mdor
NK120(e)001:5826: na byang chub sems dpa'i bslab pa'i khog pa yin
NK120(e)001:5828: ni bskal pa dpag tu med pa mtha' yas par
NK120(e)001:5831: de dag rnams kyis ji ltar bsrung tshul gyi go don bshad pas khog dbub pa song nas /
NK120(e)001:5832: da ni gang bsrung bya'i tshul khrims dngos nyid bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:5836: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5837: bar du mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:5838: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims gsum yin te //
NK120(e)001:5839: nyes spyod sdom dang dge ba chos sdud dang //
NK120(e)001:5842: de ltar dang po rang rgyud la sngar med gsar
NK120(e)001:5843: du thob pa'i sdom pa de nyid bar du mi
NK120(e)001:5844: nyamsa par bsrunga ba'i thabs la 'bad dgos te /
NK120(e)001:5845: nyams na sems can thams cad bslu bar 'gyur ba sogs nyes dmigs shin tu che zhing /
NK120(e)001:5846: ma nyams na byang chub chen po thob pa sogs phan yon shin tu che ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:5847: des na ji ltar bsrung ba'i thabsa bashada pasa la /
NK120(e)001:5848: spyir byang chub semsa dpa'i tshul khrimsa kyi rnam par
NK120(e)001:5849: bzhag pa la rtsa ba'i chings chen po gsuma gyis
NK120(e)001:5851: sems bskyed kyi bslab bya dang 'gal ba'i sgo gsum gyi nyes spyod thams cad sdom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5852: phar phyin drug gis bsdus pa'i dge ba'i chosa thams cad rang rgyud la sdud pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5853: de dag la dbang 'byor bas bsdu ba bzhi'i sgo nas semsa can gyi dona byed pa ste /
NK120(e)001:5856: de la byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK120(e)001:5858: dge ba'i chos thams cad sdud pa'i tshul khrims /
NK120(e)001:5859: sems can gyi don sgrub pa'i tshul khrims so //
NK120(e)001:5861: de gsum yang ngo bo gcig la ldog par phye ba tsam ste /
NK120(e)001:5862: dper na nor bu gcig nyid /
NK120(e)001:5865: rims nad la phan pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:5866: de ltar tshul khrims gsum la legs par bslab pas nam zhig 'tshang rgya ba'i tshe /
NK120(e)001:5867: tshul khrims snga ma gnyis kyis spangs rtog phun tshogs dang /
NK120(e)001:5868: phyi mas phrin las phun tshogs thob pa'i rgyur 'gro ba yin no //
NK120(e)001:5869: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5872: byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims la /
NK120(e)001:5875: sems can don byed gsuma du yod pa lasa /
NK120(e)001:5876: dang po nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:5878: nam snying gi mdo dang gsang chen thabs la mkhas
NK120(e)001:5879: pa'i mdo'i rjes su 'brangs pa klu sgrub kyi lugs
NK120(e)001:5880: zhi ba lhas bslab btus su phye ba dang /
NK120(e)001:5881: byang sa'i rjes su 'brangs pa thogs med kyi lugs
NK120(e)001:5882: tsan+d+ra go mis sdom pa nyi shu par phye ba'o
NK120(e)001:5883: // dang po klu sgrub kyi lugs la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:5884: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bshad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5885: yan lag gi nyes pa gzhan du zhal 'phangs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5886: dang po rtsa ba'i ltung ba bshad pa la'ang gsum /
NK120(e)001:5888: rten dang ltung ba'i dbye bsdu /
NK120(e)001:5889: thun mong smon 'jug spangs pa rtsa ltung du bstan pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5890: dang po rtsa ltung dngos bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:5891: rgyal po la 'byung nye ba lnga /
NK120(e)001:5892: blon po la 'byung nye ba lnga /
NK120(e)001:5893: phal pa la 'byung nye ba brgyad bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:5894: dang po rgyal po la 'byung nye ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:5895: dkon mchog dkor 'phrog dang ni chos spong las //
NK120(e)001:5896: tshul ldan tshul 'chal khrims gcod bslab 'bebs sogs //
NK120(e)001:5897: mtshams med las byed log lta lnga rgyal po //
NK120(e)001:5899: sangs rgyas kyi sku gzugs sam mchod rten gyi yo byad dang /
NK120(e)001:5900: dam pa'i chos kyi glegs bam dang chos smra ba'i cha rkyen /
NK120(e)001:5901: dge 'dun 'du ba'i rdzas zhing la sogs pa mdor
NK120(e)001:5902: na dkona mchoga la bsngosa pa'i dkora rdzas rin thang
NK120(e)001:5903: tshang ma tshang gang yin kyang 'dra ste /
NK120(e)001:5904: kun slong drag pos 'phroga pa'am gzhan byed du bcug
NK120(e)001:5905: nas brku bar byed pa sogs rtsa ltung dang por
NK120(e)001:5907: theg pa gsum gang yang rung ba'i lung gi chos
NK120(e)001:5908: sde snod gsum dang rtogs pa'i chos bslab pa gsum
NK120(e)001:5909: las gang rung du gtogs pa'i dge ba rnams ston
NK120(e)001:5910: pa'i bka' dang thar pa thob pa'i thabs ma yin
NK120(e)001:5911: no zhes rang gis spong ba'am gzhan spong du 'jug
NK120(e)001:5912: pa ni rtsa ltung gnyis pa chosa sponga gi lasa
NK120(e)001:5913: dang / bslab pa bzung ma bzung gi rab byung ngam /
NK120(e)001:5914: tshul khrims ldana pa'am tshul khrims 'achala ba'i dge slong
NK120(e)001:5915: gang yin kyang rung ste rab byung gi cha lugs
NK120(e)001:5916: 'dzin pa la / kun slong zhe sdang gis /
NK120(e)001:5917: de'i ngur smrig gi gos 'phrog gam /
NK120(e)001:5919: btson du 'jug pas khrimsa gcod pa /
NK120(e)001:5920: bslaba pa las khyim par 'bebas pa sogas gang rung
NK120(e)001:5921: re re'ang mang du byas sam byed du bcug na
NK120(e)001:5922: rtsa ltung gsum pa dge sbyong chad pas gcod pa
NK120(e)001:5923: dang / pha ma dgra bcom gsum gsod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5924: dge 'dun gyi dbyen byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:5925: sangs rgyas la ngan sems kyi khrag 'byin pa ste /
NK120(e)001:5926: de ltar matshamas meda lnga po'i lasa gang yang rung
NK120(e)001:5927: ba byed pa ni rtsa ltung bzhi pa mtshams med
NK120(e)001:5929: rgyu dge sdig gi las la 'bras bu bde sdug
NK120(e)001:5930: med ces loga par lta bas mi dge ba bcu
NK120(e)001:5931: las gang rung zhig byed dam byed du bcug na
NK120(e)001:5932: rtsa ltung lnga pa log lta can te /
NK120(e)001:5933: 'dis kun nas blangs te mi dge ba'i las phra
NK120(e)001:5934: mo tsam la'ang dngos su spyad na nyes pa shin
NK120(e)001:5936: de lnga ni rgyala po rnams shin tu dbang che
NK120(e)001:5937: bas 'byung nye ba'i phyir de'i ltung bar bzhag go
NK120(e)001:5938: // gnyis pa blon po la 'byung nye ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:5939: grong ljongs grong khyer grong brdal yul 'khor rnams /
NK120(e)001:5940: 'joms par byed la'ang blon por nges pa lnga /
NK120(e)001:5942: khyim gcig pa la sogs pa gronga dang /
NK120(e)001:5943: mi rigs bzhi gnas pa ljongsa dang /
NK120(e)001:5944: bzo sna bco brgyad yod pa'i gnas grong khyer dang /
NK120(e)001:5945: tshong pa mang po 'du ba'i gnas grong brdala dang /
NK120(e)001:5946: yul gru chen po tsam pa ka lta bu yula 'khor te /
NK120(e)001:5947: de rnams gang yang rung ba kun slong zhe sdang
NK120(e)001:5948: gis me la sogs pas 'jomsa para byed pa ste
NK120(e)001:5949: / 'ang sgra sdud byed kyi tshig log lta dor
NK120(e)001:5950: ba'i snga ma bzhi po'i steng na 'di dag gcig
NK120(e)001:5951: tu brtsis pa ni blona po rnams rgyal po'i bya
NK120(e)001:5952: ba byed pa'i phyir phyogs rnams su khrims kyi las
NK120(e)001:5953: la dngos su 'jug dgos pas na der 'byung ngesa
NK120(e)001:5955: gsum pa pha la pa la 'byung nye ba brgyad ni /
NK120(e)001:5956: ma sbyangs stong nyid brjod sngas nyan thos smon //
NK120(e)001:5957: rdzogs byang phyir ldog theg dman sems bskyed dang //
NK120(e)001:5958: so thar spangs nas theg chen slob pa dang //
NK120(e)001:5959: nyan thos theg par chags sogs mi bzlog pas //
NK120(e)001:5960: de bzlog de yi 'bras bu med par byas //
NK120(e)001:5961: phrag dog dbang gis bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK120(e)001:5962: rnyed dang bkur bsti'i ched du bdag 'tshong dang //
NK120(e)001:5963: dge slong chad pas gcod 'jug sug 'bul dang //
NK120(e)001:5964: spong ba'i longs spyod kha ton pa la byin //
NK120(e)001:5965: zhi gnas 'dor bcug phal la 'byung nges brgyad //
NK120(e)001:5967: blo ma sbyangsa pa'i sems can las dang po pa'am
NK120(e)001:5968: theg dman gyi rigs can sogs snod ma brtag par
NK120(e)001:5969: stong nyid mtha' bral brjod sngasa pa'i dbang gis yul
NK120(e)001:5970: des byang chub kyi sems btang nas nyan thosa kyi
NK120(e)001:5971: lam du smona na ston pa po la ltung bar
NK120(e)001:5972: 'gyur zhing / gal te yul kyang 'jug sdom dang ldan na de la'ang ltung ba 1'byung /
NK120(e)001:5973: theg chen gyi lam du zhugs pa la der shes
NK120(e)001:5974: bzhin du khyod kyis rgyu phyin drug la spyod pa
NK120(e)001:5975: 'dis 'bras bu rdzogsa byang thob par mi nus zhes
NK120(e)001:5977: de bas nyan rang gi 'bras bu bsgrub par gyis
NK120(e)001:5978: shig dang des khyod 'khor ba las nges par 'byung
NK120(e)001:5979: bar 'gyur ro // zhes thega damna du semsa bskyed du 'jug pa 2dang /
NK120(e)001:5980: nyan thos kyi rigs can so sor thar pa la slob bzhin pa'am /
NK120(e)001:5981: rab tu byung ma zin kyang slob par 'dod pa
NK120(e)001:5982: dag la dgos pa khyad par can med bzhin khyod
NK120(e)001:5983: so thara la bslab pas ci zhig bya zhes spanga
NK120(e)001:5984: du bcug nas rdzogs byang du sems bskyed la thega
NK120(e)001:5985: pa chen po klog cig dang byang chub sems kyi
NK120(e)001:5986: mthus nyes par byas pa'i las rnams 'joms so zhes
NK120(e)001:5987: de la slob tu 'jug pa dang 3 /
NK120(e)001:5988: nyan thosa kyi theg pasa chagas sogas nyon mongs pa
NK120(e)001:5989: mi bzlog pasa theg chen la slob cig ces nyan
NK120(e)001:5990: thos kyi theg pa de bzlog nas de yi lam
NK120(e)001:5991: la bslab na 'brasa bu thar pa myang 'das meda
NK120(e)001:5993: dgos pa khyad par can med par gzhan yang 'dzin du bcug par byas pa dang 4 /
NK120(e)001:5994: rnyed bkur gyi phyir phraga doga gi dabnga gisa badga
NK120(e)001:5995: nyid la yon tan med kyang yod ces bstod cing
NK120(e)001:5996: / rnyed bkur can gyi byang sems gazhana la bden
NK120(e)001:5997: pa'am brdzun pa gang yin kyang smoda par byed pa
NK120(e)001:5998: / 5dang / rnyed pa dang bkura sti thob pa'i
NK120(e)001:5999: ched du ma rtogs bzhin bdag gis chos zab mo
NK120(e)001:6000: stong pa nyid mngon sum du rtogs so zhes mi
NK120(e)001:6001: chos bla ma'i rdzun gyis badga 'tshonga pa dang 6
NK120(e)001:6002: / 5dang / / rang nyid kyis rgyal rigs lta bu'i mi dbang po che dang /
NK120(e)001:6003: chos 'di ba'i dge slong sogs dge sbyong rnams phra
NK120(e)001:6004: mas phye nas dbang po che'i phyogs la brten te
NK120(e)001:6005: dge slong la nor gyi chada pasa gcod du 'juga
NK120(e)001:6006: pa dang / de'i rkyen gyis dge sbyong gis dkon
NK120(e)001:6007: mchog gi dkor brkus nas phra ma byed pa la
NK120(e)001:6008: phag sug tu 'bula ba rang gis len nam dbang
NK120(e)001:6009: po che la byin pas nor bdag gir byas na
NK120(e)001:6010: gnyis ka la ltung bar 'a gyur ba 7dang /
NK120(e)001:6011: spong ba bsam gtan pa la sdang ba'i bsam pa
NK120(e)001:6012: de dag gi longas spyod sogs 'phrog nas klog pa
NK120(e)001:6013: kha tona pa la byin nam sbyin du 'jug pa
NK120(e)001:6014: sogs kyi sgo nas zhi gansa kyi ting nge 'dzin
NK120(e)001:6015: 'dora du bcuga pa 8rnams phala pa la 'byung ngesa
NK120(e)001:6017: gnyis pa rten dang ltung ba'i dbye bsdu bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6018: de der 'byung nyes bzhag gis kun la kun //
NK120(e)001:6019: ming du bco brgyad rdzas su bcu bzhi ste //
NK120(e)001:6021: de ltar rgyal blon phal pa so so'i rtsa ltung
NK120(e)001:6022: du bshad pa ni gtso bor gang zag de dang
NK120(e)001:6023: dera 'byung nye ba tsam gyis bazhaga gisa /
NK120(e)001:6024: don la gang zag gsum po kun la bco brgyad
NK120(e)001:6025: po kun ma lus pa rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba
NK120(e)001:6026: yin te / mdo las minga du bco brgyad du
NK120(e)001:6027: phye yang don du rdzasa su bsdu na rgyal blon
NK120(e)001:6028: gyi rtsa ltung dang po bzhi la tha dad med
NK120(e)001:6029: pas bcu bzhi po kho na ste zhes so //
NK120(e)001:6030: gsum pa thun mong smon 'jug spangs pa rtsa ltung du bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6031: smon 'jug sems btang de rnams rtsa ltung yin //
NK120(e)001:6033: theg pa dman par sems bskyed pa'am sems can blos spangs na smon sems btang ba ste /
NK120(e)001:6034: gsang chen thabs la mkhas pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)001:6035: rigs kyi bu byang chub sems dpa' nyan thos dang
NK120(e)001:6036: rang sangs rgyas yid la byed pas gnas pa 'di
NK120(e)001:6037: ni byang chub sems dpa'i rtsa ba'i ltung ba lci
NK120(e)001:6039: sngar gyi rtsa ltung bco brgyad kyi steng du smon pa btang bas bcu dgu dang /
NK120(e)001:6040: de'i steng du dkon brtsegs las gsungs pa ltar 'juga
NK120(e)001:6041: semas batanga ste dge la mi sbyor ba bsnan pas
NK120(e)001:6043: de rnams ni byang chub sems dpa'i tshul khrims kyi rtsa ltung kho na yina no //
NK120(e)001:6044: de yang byang chub sems dpa'i dbang po'i rim pas phye na /
NK120(e)001:6045: gong du bshad pa'i bco brgyad po dbang rnon gyi thun mong ma yin pa'i rtsa ltung yin la /
NK120(e)001:6046: dbang 'bring yan chad kyi bslab bya la bzhir bstan te /
NK120(e)001:6047: thabs la mkhas pa'i mdo'i don bslab btus las /
NK120(e)001:6048: byang chub sems ni yongs 'dor dang //
NK120(e)001:6049: chags dang ser sna mi zad pas //
NK120(e)001:6050: slong la sbyin par mi byed dang //
NK120(e)001:6051: sgrims te dga' bar byed pa na //
NK120(e)001:6052: sems can la ni mi bzod pas //
NK120(e)001:6053: khros pas sems can rdeg pa dang //
NK120(e)001:6054: nyon mongs pa dang gzhan mthun pas //
NK120(e)001:6055: chos ltar bcos pa ston pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6057: dbang rtul la smon sems mi 'dor ba gcig pur bzhag cing /
NK120(e)001:6058: de'i tshul yang rgyal po la gdams pa'i mdo las gsungs pa ltar sdom du byas na /
NK120(e)001:6059: bya dang byed pa mang ba dag /
NK120(e)001:6060: thams cad sgrub par mi nus kyang //
NK120(e)001:6061: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub la //
NK120(e)001:6062: 'dun dang dad dang smon pa gsum //
NK120(e)001:6064: rtag tu dran pas sgom bya zhing //
NK120(e)001:6065: rjes su yi rang byas nas kyang //
NK120(e)001:6066: rgyal dang thugs gsung sras rnams la //
NK120(e)001:6067: phul zhing sems can dang thun mong //
NK120(e)001:6068: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu bsngosa na //
NK120(e)001:6069: rang srid mi nyams tshogs rdzogs 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:6071: gal te de lta bu'i smon sdom de nyams na
