NK120(e)001:6072: 'jug sdom kyang gtong bar 'gyur bas nyes pa shin
NK120(e)001:6073: tu lci ste / sdud pa las /
NK120(e)001:6074: gal te bskal pa bye bar dge ba'i las lam bcu //
NK120(e)001:6075: spyod kyang rang rgyal dgra bcom nyid la 'dod bskyed na //
NK120(e)001:6076: de tshe tshul khrims skyon byung tshul khrims nyams pa yin //
NK120(e)001:6077: sems bskyed de ni phas pham bas kyang shin tu lci //
NK120(e)001:6079: gnyis pa yan lag gi nyes byas gzhan du zhal 'phang ba ni /
NK120(e)001:6080: yan lag nyes byas brgyad cu la sogs pa //
NK120(e)001:6081: phra phyir 'dir ni ma bshad bslab btus blta //
NK120(e)001:6083: rtsa ba bsrung thabs kyi yan lag nyes byas brgyad
NK120(e)001:6084: cu la sogas pa rnams cung zad nyes pa phra
NK120(e)001:6085: ba'i phyir bstan bcos 'dira ni ma bashada kyang bslaba
NK120(e)001:6086: btusa su de dag gsal bar bstan pa der blta
NK120(e)001:6087: bar byos shig ces zhal 'phang bar mdzad de /
NK120(e)001:6088: de'i sdom ni ji skad du /
NK120(e)001:6089: gzhan gyi sdug bsngal yid mi bde //
NK120(e)001:6090: nus bzhin zhi bar mi byed dang //
NK120(e)001:6091: bde dang yid bde mi bskyed pa //
NK120(e)001:6092: ltung ba'i gzhi ste lus sems kyi //
NK120(e)001:6093: rten gyis phye na rnam pa bzhi //
NK120(e)001:6094: da lta dang ni ma 'ongs pa'i //
NK120(e)001:6095: dus kyis phye bas rnam pa brgyad //
NK120(e)001:6096: de ched sgo gsum mi brtson dang //
NK120(e)001:6097: phan pa'i rgyu rkyen mi 'tshol dang /
NK120(e)001:6098: gnyen po'i phyogs la mi 'bad pa //
NK120(e)001:6099: de ltar rjes su bsgrub pa'i sgo //
NK120(e)001:6100: gsum gyi phye bas nyi shu bzhi //
NK120(e)001:6102: sdug bsngal yid mi bde chen po'i //
NK120(e)001:6103: gnyen po chung ngu mi bskyed pa //
NK120(e)001:6104: ltung ba'i gzhi ste 'di phyi yi //
NK120(e)001:6105: skye bas phye bas rnam pa bzhi //
NK120(e)001:6106: rang gzhan rgyud kyi phye bas brgyad //
NK120(e)001:6107: bde dang yid bde chen po'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:6108: chung ngu nyams par mi byed pa //
NK120(e)001:6109: ltung ba'i gzhi ste skye ba dang //
NK120(e)001:6110: rgyud kyis phye bas rnam pa brgyad //
NK120(e)001:6111: sgrub pa yal bar 'dor ba yi //
NK120(e)001:6112: ltung ba rnam pa bcu drug go //
NK120(e)001:6113: de ltar bzhi bcu re re la'ang //
NK120(e)001:6114: re zhig yal bar 'dor ba dang //
NK120(e)001:6115: gtan du 'dor ba rnam pa gnyis //
NK120(e)001:6116: phan yon nyes dmigs mi bzad pa'i //
NK120(e)001:6117: yan lag ltung ba brgyad cu'o //
NK120(e)001:6119: sogs khongs nas phyogs mthun gyi nyes pa mi dge ba bcu dang /
NK120(e)001:6121: log pa'i rtog pa brgyad dang /
NK120(e)001:6123: spyod yul min pa lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:6124: sdig grogs dang sdig lta 'dzin pa sogs bdud kyi las rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:6126: dge ba 'dzad pa'i rgyu bzhi la sogs pa rnams spang bar bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:6127: yan lag gi ltung ba gzhan yang /
NK120(e)001:6128: lus ngag yid kyi dgag pa dang sgrub pa'i bslab bya rnams las nyams pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6129: don med pa'i rgyug mchongs la sogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6130: bre mo'i gtam smra ba sogs dang /
NK120(e)001:6131: chags sdang mi spong ba sogs dgag pa'i bslab bya las nyams pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6132: mig phab ste blta bar bya ba sogs dang /
NK120(e)001:6133: legs par 'ongs so zhes bya ba la sogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6134: byams snying rje sgom zhing dran pa dang shes bzhin
NK120(e)001:6135: dang bag yod bsten pa sogs sgrub pa'i bslab bya
NK120(e)001:6137: de rnams kyi nang du dbang po 'bring rtul gyi nyes pa thams cad kyang 'du bar gsungs so //
NK120(e)001:6138: gnyis pa thogs med kyi lugs bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6141: dang po smon pa'i bslab bya la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6143: dkar nag chos brgyad bye brag tu bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6145: thogs med lugs kyi smon pa'i bslab bya la /
NK120(e)001:6146: sems can blos mi btang dang phan yon dran //
NK120(e)001:6147: tshogs bsags byang sems sbyong la brtson pa dang //
NK120(e)001:6148: dkar nag chos brgyad blang dor smon pa'i yin //
NK120(e)001:6150: de nas rgyal sras thogsa meda kyi lugsa kyi smon pa'i bslab bya bshad pa la /
NK120(e)001:6151: rtsa ba'i bslab bya smon sems mi 'chor ba'i thabs ni /
NK120(e)001:6152: sems can gang yang rung bas rang gi sems bsun
NK120(e)001:6153: phyung ba la brten nas da ni khyod la phan
NK120(e)001:6154: thogs pa'i dus byung yang phan mi gdags /
NK120(e)001:6155: gnod pa bzlog pa'i dus byung yang gnod pa mi
NK120(e)001:6156: bzlog snyam pa ni semsa can de nyid blos btang
NK120(e)001:6157: ba yin pas de 'dra spangs te phan lan du
NK120(e)001:6158: gnod pa byas na'ang yang lan snying rjes slon te
NK120(e)001:6160: byang chub kyi sems de mi nyams pa'i thabs phan yon dran pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6161: sdong po bkod pa'i mdor dpe nyis brgya dang sum
NK120(e)001:6162: cu'i sgo nas bshad pa rnams legs par blta zhing
NK120(e)001:6163: / tha na'ang byams smon nas 'byung ba'i tshigs bcad
NK120(e)001:6164: gi don bzhin dus rtag tu phana yona drana pas
NK120(e)001:6166: byang chub sems de'i stobs bskyed pa'i thabs ni /
NK120(e)001:6167: dge ba'i 'dun pa sngon du btang nas sbyin pa sogs bsod nams kyi tshogs dang /
NK120(e)001:6168: de dag 'khor gsum mi rtog par shes pa ye shes kyi tshogs te /
NK120(e)001:6169: tshogas gnyis zung 'brel du basgas pa la 'bad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6170: byang chub kyi sems de 'phel ba'i thabs ni /
NK120(e)001:6171: rgyu la sbyang pa byams snying rje sgom pa /
NK120(e)001:6172: sems dngos la sbyang ba nyin mtshan thun drug tu sems bskyed blang ba /
NK120(e)001:6173: spyod pa la sbyang ba rang gi bde dge sems
NK120(e)001:6174: can la bsngo zhing gzhan gyi sdig sdug bdag la
NK120(e)001:6175: len pa'i gtong len sbyong ba ste /
NK120(e)001:6176: de gsum gyi sgo nas byang chub kyi semsa sbyong ba la rtag tu brtson pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6177: byang chub kyi sems mi brjed pa'i thabs ni /
NK120(e)001:6178: 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin dakara chos bzhi dang naga
NK120(e)001:6179: chosa bzhi ste brgyad la blang dora ma nor bar
NK120(e)001:6180: byed pa ni smon pa'i bslab bya yina no //
NK120(e)001:6181: gnyis pa dkar nag chos brgyad bye brag tu bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6182: mchod 'os bslu dang 'gyod med 'gyod pa bskyed //
NK120(e)001:6183: dam par skur 'debs 'gro la g.yo sgyu spyod //
NK120(e)001:6184: nag po'i chos bzhi spang zhing ldog pa ni //
NK120(e)001:6185: dkar po'i chos bzhi yin pas kun tu spyad //
NK120(e)001:6187: rdzun gyis mchod 'osa su gyur pa bla ma dang mkhan slob sogs bslu ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6188: gzhan 'gyod pa'i gnas ma yin pa dge ba'i phyogs
NK120(e)001:6189: sgrub pa sogs la de 'gyod pa meda kyang ngan
NK120(e)001:6190: sems kyis 'gyod pa bskyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6191: sems bskyed pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dam para sdang
NK120(e)001:6192: sems kyis skyon nas brjod cing skur pa 'debas pa
NK120(e)001:6193: dang / 'gro ba gzhan la kun slong g.yo sgyu'i
NK120(e)001:6194: sgo nas bslu ba'i spyod pa rtsom pa rnams ni
NK120(e)001:6195: nag po'i chosa bzhi yin pas spang bar bya zhing
NK120(e)001:6196: dang / / de las ldog pa 'od srung gi zhus pa las /
NK120(e)001:6197: 'od srung chos bzhi dang ldan na byang chub kyi sems brjed par mi 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:6199: shes bazha na du rdzun mi smra ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6200: byang chub sems dpa' la ston pa'i du shes bskyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6201: sems can la g.yo sgyu med par lhag pa'i bsam pas gnas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6202: sems can thams cad theg pa chen po la yang dag par 'god pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6203: zhes gsungs pa ni dakara po'i chosa bzhi yin pasa kuna tu spyad par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:6204: gnyis pa 'jug pa'i bslab bya bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6206: yan lag nyes byas gzhan du zhal 'phangs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6207: dang po rtsa ltung bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6208: rnyed bkur lhag zhen bdag bstod gzhan smod dang //
NK120(e)001:6209: ser snas zang zing nod dang chos mi ster //
NK120(e)001:6210: khro bas gzhan 'tshe shad sbyang gis mi bzlog /
NK120(e)001:6211: g.yom las chos ltar bcos mos ston pa bzhi //
NK120(e)001:6212: rtsa ltung bzhi ste 'jug pa'i bslab bya'o //
NK120(e)001:6214: 'jug sems kyi mi mthun pa'i phyogs rtsa ba'i ltung
NK120(e)001:6215: bar gyur pa mdo sde na 'thor ba rnams thogs
NK120(e)001:6216: med kyis byang sar bsdus pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6217: rnyed pa dang bkura sti la lhag par zhena pas
NK120(e)001:6218: de thob pa'i phyir badga la bstod pa'am rnyed bkur
NK120(e)001:6219: can gazhana la smod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6220: sera sna'i dbang gis sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6222: mgon med pa'i slong ba po la kha zas sogs
NK120(e)001:6223: zanga zinga cung zad tsam mam nyan 'dod kyi gang
NK120(e)001:6224: zag snod du gyur cing byang sems rang la nus
NK120(e)001:6225: pa yod bzhin de gnyis la nora dang chosa mi
NK120(e)001:6226: ster ba dang / khro ba drag pos kun nas
NK120(e)001:6227: bslangs te tshig rtsub smras pa tsam gyis mi tshim
NK120(e)001:6228: par gazhana la brdeg btsog sogs 'tshe bar byed cing
NK120(e)001:6229: shada sbyong gisa kyang mi bzlog par 'khon du 'dzin
NK120(e)001:6230: ster ba dang / pa dang / gti mug gis
NK120(e)001:6231: kun nas bslangs te theg chen gyi sde snod la
NK120(e)001:6232: bka' min no zhes skur 'debs kyis spong ba'am rang
NK120(e)001:6233: ngam gzhan gyi g.yoma lasa sam rang bzos chos ma
NK120(e)001:6234: yin pa la chosa ltar bcosa pa la mos nas
NK120(e)001:6235: chos yin no zhes dam chos 'drar snang ston pa
NK120(e)001:6236: dang bzhi po 'di kun dkris chen pos spyad na
NK120(e)001:6237: byang sems kyi sdom pa rtsa ba nas gtong bar
NK120(e)001:6238: byed pas na rtsa ba'i ltung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:6239: de yang kun slong gi sgo nas bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:6240: sbyor ba'i sgo nas brgyad te de rnams spang ba ni 'juga pa'i bslaba bya'o //
NK120(e)001:6241: 'o na srol gnyis bzhed pa 'di dag gtso che ba yin zhe na /
NK120(e)001:6242: byang sems dbang rtul dang khyim pa'i phyogs lta bus
NK120(e)001:6243: sems can blos mi gtong ba 'di kho na la
NK120(e)001:6244: nan tan byed dgos pa yin /
NK120(e)001:6245: rtsig pa med na logs ris mi gnas pa bzhin du /
NK120(e)001:6246: de med na byang sems kyi sdom pa gzhan bsrung ba'i thabs gtan nas med /
NK120(e)001:6247: 'o na de sems can gcig blos gtong ba yin nam /
NK120(e)001:6248: sems can thams cad blos gtong ba yin snyam na /
NK120(e)001:6249: sems can thams cad blos gtong ba ni nyan rang
NK120(e)001:6250: gnyis las khra dang spyang ki sogs la'ang mi srid
NK120(e)001:6251: pas sems can gcig blos gtong ba'o //
NK120(e)001:6252: byang sems dbang 'bring dang rab byung gi phyogs lta
NK120(e)001:6253: bus snga ma'i steng du byang sa'i bzhi spong dgos
NK120(e)001:6254: pa yin / dbang rnon gyis sems can blos mi
NK120(e)001:6255: gtong ba gzhir bzhag gi steng du nam mkha'i snying
NK120(e)001:6256: po'i mdo'i don rtsa ltung bco brgyad po bsrung dgos
NK120(e)001:6257: pa'i don yin pas 'di dag phan tshun 'gal 'du
NK120(e)001:6259: gnyis pa yan lag nyes byas gzhan du zhal 'phangs pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6260: nyes byas phra ba zhe drug gzhan du shes //
NK120(e)001:6262: de las gzhan nyes byas phra ba zhe drug yod
NK120(e)001:6263: pa 'dir bshad par ma longs pas gazhana du shesa
NK120(e)001:6264: par bya'o zhes zhal 'phangs par mdzad pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6265: de yang sdom pa nyi shu par dge ba chos sdud dang 'gal ba so bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:6266: sems can don byed dang 'gal ba bcu gnyis su gsungs pa las /
NK120(e)001:6267: dang po la'ang nang gses sde tshan drug las /
NK120(e)001:6268: sbyin pa dang 'gal ba bdun ni //
NK120(e)001:6269: dkon mchog gsum la gsum mi mchod //
NK120(e)001:6271: rgan pa rnams la gus mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6272: dris pa la ni lan mi 'debs //
NK120(e)001:6273: mgron bos bdag gir mi byed cing //
NK120(e)001:6274: gser la sogs pa len mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6275: chos 'dod pa la sbyin mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6277: tshul khrims dang 'gal ba dgu ni /
NK120(e)001:6279: pha rol dad phyir slob mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6280: sems can don la bya ba chung //
NK120(e)001:6281: snying brtser bcas na mi dge med //
NK120(e)001:6282: 'tsho ba log pa dang du len //
NK120(e)001:6283: 'chal zhing rab tu rgod la sogs //
NK120(e)001:6284: 'khor ba gcig pus bgrod par sems //
NK120(e)001:6285: grags pa ma yin mi spong ba //
NK120(e)001:6286: nyon mongs bcas kyang 'chos mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6288: bzod pa dang 'gal ba bzhi ni /
NK120(e)001:6289: gshe la lan du gshe la sogs //
NK120(e)001:6290: khros pa rnams ni yal bar 'dor //
NK120(e)001:6291: pha rol shad kyis 'chags pa spong //
NK120(e)001:6292: khros pa'i sems kyis rjes su 'jug /
NK120(e)001:6296: le lo la sogs sel mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6297: chags pas bre mo'i gtam la brten //
NK120(e)001:6299: bsam gtan dang 'gal ba gsum ni /
NK120(e)001:6301: bsam gtan sgrib pa spong mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6302: bsam gtan ro la yon tan blta //
NK120(e)001:6304: shes rab dang 'gal ba brgyad ni /
NK120(e)001:6305: nyan thos theg pa spong bar byed //
NK120(e)001:6306: rang tshul yod bzhin de la brtson //
NK120(e)001:6307: brtson min phyi rol bstan bcos brtson //
NK120(e)001:6308: brtson par byas kyang de la dga' //
NK120(e)001:6309: theg pa chen po spang bar byed //
NK120(e)001:6310: bdag la bstod cing gzhan la smod //
NK120(e)001:6311: chos kyi don du 'gro mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6312: de la smod cing yi ger rton //
NK120(e)001:6314: gnyis pa sems can don byed dang 'gal ba bcu gnyis la nang gses sde tshan gsum las /
NK120(e)001:6315: dang po gzhan don las nyams pa'i nyes pa bzhi ni /
NK120(e)001:6316: dgos pa'i grogs su 'gro mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6317: nad pa'i rim gro bya ba spong //
NK120(e)001:6318: sdug bsngal sel bar mi byed dang //
NK120(e)001:6319: bag med pa la rigs mi ston //
NK120(e)001:6321: gnyis pa gzhan la phan mi 'dogs pa'i nyes pa drug ni //
NK120(e)001:6322: byas la lan du phan mi 'dogs //
NK120(e)001:6323: gzhan gyi mya ngan sel mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6324: nor 'dod pa la sbyin mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6325: 'khor rnams kyi ni don mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6326: gzhan gyi blo dang mthun mi 'jug /
NK120(e)001:6327: yon tan basngagasa pa smra mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6329: gsum pa ngan pa tshar mi gcod pa'i nyes pa gnyis ni /
NK120(e)001:6330: rkyen dang 'tshams par tshar mi gcod //
NK120(e)001:6331: rdzu 'phrul bsdigs la sogs mi byed //
NK120(e)001:6333: 'di dag 'grel ba ci rigs par gsum gsum du byas nas bshad de /
NK120(e)001:6334: gal te ma gus pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6336: le los nyes pa byung na ni nyon mongs pa can gyi nyes par 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:6337: gal te brjed pas nyes pa byung na ni nyon
NK120(e)001:6338: mongs pa can ma yin pa'i nyes par 'gyur la
NK120(e)001:6339: / sems 'khrugs pa la ni nyes pa med do //
NK120(e)001:6341: nyes spyod sdom pa dang 'gal ba ni bshad mi dgos te /
NK120(e)001:6342: rten rab byung yin na so thar gyi pham bzhi 'dir yang rtsa ltung dang /
NK120(e)001:6343: de ma yin pa'i ltung ba rnams byang sems kyi yan lag gi nyes byas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6344: rab byung min kyang rang sa'i rtsa ltung gi phyogs
NK120(e)001:6345: dang mthun pa'i nyes pa phra ba rnams nyes byas
NK120(e)001:6347: gnyis pa dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6350: dang po mdo bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6351: dge ba chos sdud phar phyin drug slob ste //
NK120(e)001:6353: rang gzhan kun la dge ba bsod nams kyi chosa
NK120(e)001:6354: tshogs zab mo yid bzhin du sdud par byed pa
NK120(e)001:6355: ni pha rola tu phyin pa drug la tshul bzhin
NK120(e)001:6356: du sloba par bya ba ste /
NK120(e)001:6358: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la drug las /
NK120(e)001:6359: dang po sbyin pa'i phar phyin la /
NK120(e)001:6360: dbul ba sel phyir chos nor mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK120(e)001:6362: de la sbyin pa'i ngo bo ni khyad chos bzhi
NK120(e)001:6363: ldan gyi gtong sems dge ba sa bon dang bcas
NK120(e)001:6365: d+aa na zhes pa'i sgra las /
NK120(e)001:6366: pha rol gyi dbula ba sela ba'i phyir sbyin pa zhes bya'o //
NK120(e)001:6367: dbye na chosa kyi sbyin pa ni snod brtag cing
NK120(e)001:6368: snying rje chen pos skal ba dang 'tshams par legs
NK120(e)001:6369: bshad kyi dga' ston 'gyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6370: zang zing nora gyi sbyin pa la zas gos khang
NK120(e)001:6371: khyim rta dang shing rta la sogs pa gtong ba
NK120(e)001:6372: dang / gtong ba chen po la bu dang chung ma rgyal srid sogs gtong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6373: bya dka' ba'i gtong ba la rang gi mgo dang rkang lag sogs gtong ba'o //
NK120(e)001:6374: 'on kyang pha dang ma sbyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6375: rab tu byung bas chos gos gsum sbyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6376: bsam pa ma dag na rang gis lus sbyin pa rnams mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:6377: de yang byang sems khyim pas zang zing dang rab byung gis chos sbyin gtso bor gtong bar gsungs /
NK120(e)001:6381: rgyal po sogs kyi 'jigs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6382: mthar thug 'khor ba dang ngan song gi 'jigs pa las skyobs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6383: gnyis pa tshul khrims kyi phar phyin la /
NK120(e)001:6384: spong ba'i sems kyis tshul khrims rnam gsum spyad //
NK120(e)001:6386: de la tshul khrims kyi ngo bo ni khyad chos
NK120(e)001:6387: bzhi ldan gyi spong ba'i semas kyis nyes pa bsrung
NK120(e)001:6388: 'dod kyi sems dge ba sa bon dang bcas pa'o
NK120(e)001:6390: sh+ai la'i sgra las yul gyi gdung bas mi bardzi
NK120(e)001:6391: bar bsil ba thob par byed pas na tshul khrimas
NK120(e)001:6393: dang po byang chub kyi sems gnas pa'i thabs nyes spyod sdom pa'i tshul khrims /
NK120(e)001:6394: gnyis pa rang rgyud kyi chos smin pa'i thabs dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims /
NK120(e)001:6395: gsum pa sems can rnams smin pa'i thabs sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims te /
NK120(e)001:6396: de ltar tshul khrims rnam pa gsuma po la blang
NK120(e)001:6397: dor ma nor zhing bsam sbyor dag pa'i sgo nas
NK120(e)001:6398: gzhan don du spyad par bya zhes pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6399: 'di dag la go don du nyes spyod sdom pa'i
NK120(e)001:6400: tshul khrims ni thun mong du rang gi sngar gang
NK120(e)001:6401: blangs pa'i so thar ris bdun gyi bslab bya rnams
NK120(e)001:6402: dang / thun mong ma yin pa rtsa ba dang
NK120(e)001:6403: yan lag gi ltung ba rnams ma nyams par bya
NK120(e)001:6404: dang / ba dang / dge ba chos sdud kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK120(e)001:6405: thos bsam sgom pa sogs tshogs gnyis dang phyin drug
NK120(e)001:6406: gis bsdus pa'i dge ba'i chos rang rgyud la ma
NK120(e)001:6408: skyes pa spel zhing de'i mi mthun phyogs mtha' dag spong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6409: sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims ni /
NK120(e)001:6410: bsam sbyor mtha' dag gzhan don du spyod pa'i thabs
NK120(e)001:6411: mkhas kyi dngos brgyud thams cad nas pha rol po'i
NK120(e)001:6414: rang nyid mi nyams pa'i ched du sgo gsum gyi
NK120(e)001:6415: 'du byed ma dag pa thams cad spangs shing dag
NK120(e)001:6417: gsum pa bzod pa'i phar phyin la /
NK120(e)001:6418: khong khro zab mo sdug bsngal bzod par bya //
NK120(e)001:6420: de la bzod pa'i ngo bo ni khyad chos bzhi
NK120(e)001:6421: ldan gyi mi 'khrug pa'i sems dge ba sa bon
NK120(e)001:6422: dang bcas pa'o // sgra don ni /
NK120(e)001:6423: k+shan+ta'i sgra las sdug bsngal sogs mi bde mi dga'
NK120(e)001:6424: ba'i yul la sems mi 'khrugs par bsran tshugs pas
NK120(e)001:6426: gnod byed la ji mi snyam pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6427: sdug bsngal dang du len pa'i bzod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6428: chos la nges rtog gi bzod pa dang gsum las /
NK120(e)001:6430: bdag dang bdag gi yid du 'ong ba'i grogs la
NK120(e)001:6431: gzhan gyis brdeg gshe khro ba mtshang 'bru ba sogs
NK120(e)001:6433: 'dod pa'i gegs byed pa la bzod pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6434: ji ltar bzod na khonga khro'i nyes dmigs la bsam
NK120(e)001:6435: ste pha rol gyis gnod pa byed pa la ji
NK120(e)001:6436: mi snyam du sems mi 'khrugs par gnod lan mi
NK120(e)001:6437: byed pa dang / 'khon zhe la mi 'dzin par
NK120(e)001:6438: ma zad slar yang snying rje bskyed pa bya ba
NK120(e)001:6439: byed pa dang / dang / gnyis pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6440: byang chub bsgrub pa'i dka' spyad kyi sdug bsngal mtha' dag dang du len pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6441: nad kyi zug rngu 'byin pa la dpyad brten pa bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:6443: stong nyid la sogs pa zaba mo'i don la mi skrag cing gzhan don la mi skyo ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6444: phug gi bde ba bla na med pa'i don du
NK120(e)001:6445: 'phral gyi sdug bsngal dam chos sgrub pa'i dka' spyad
NK120(e)001:6446: sogs kyis mi skyo bar dang du blang nas bzod
NK120(e)001:6447: par bya ba'o // bzhi pa brtson 'grus kyi phar phyin la /
NK120(e)001:6448: go cha dge sdud gzhan phan brtson 'grus brtsam //
NK120(e)001:6450: de la brtson 'grus kyi ngo bo ni khyad chos
NK120(e)001:6451: bzhi ldan gyi spro ba'i sems pa dge ba sa
NK120(e)001:6454: b+air+ya'i sgra las snying stobs ma zhum pas mchog gi gnas la sbyor bas na brtson 'grus so //
NK120(e)001:6456: dang po go cha'i brtson 'grus dang /
NK120(e)001:6457: gnyis pa dge ba chos sdud kyi brtson 'grus dang /
NK120(e)001:6458: gsum pa gzhan la phan pa'i brtson 'grus dang gsum las /
NK120(e)001:6460: bsam pa bdud kyis mi barji ba'i rgyu sems can
NK120(e)001:6461: thams cad rdzogs byang la ma 'khod kyi bar du
NK120(e)001:6462: bdag gis brtson pa 'dor bar mi bya'o snyam du
NK120(e)001:6463: bsam pa'i go cha bgo ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6465: lus dang srog la'ang mi blta bar byang chub chen
NK120(e)001:6466: po thob pa'i rgyu dge ba'i tshogs thams cad sdud
NK120(e)001:6467: par 'jug cing de yang sgrub pa la mi zhum
NK120(e)001:6468: zhing cung zad tsam gyis mi ngoms pa rkyen gyi
NK120(e)001:6469: mi ldog pa'i sgo nas gus rtag gis brtson par
NK120(e)001:6470: bya ba dang / gsum pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6471: don gnyis 'grub pa'i rgyu gazhana la phana pa'i dngos
NK120(e)001:6472: po sgrub pa la spro ba'i sgo nas 'jug pa'i
NK120(e)001:6474: lnga pa bsam gtan gyi phar phyin la /
NK120(e)001:6475: 'jig rten 'jig rten 'das pa'i bsam gtan bsgom //
NK120(e)001:6477: de la bsam gtan gyi ngo bo ni khyad chos
NK120(e)001:6478: bzhi ldan gyi dmigs pa la rtse gcig pa'i sems
NK120(e)001:6479: pa dge ba sa bon dang bcas pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6481: r+t+y+aen zhes pa'i sgra las sems pa'i rgyun gzhan du mi yengs par 'dzin pas na bsam gtan no //
NK120(e)001:6483: phyi rol pa dang thun mong du gyur pa'i bsam gzugs brgyad sgom pa 'jiga rten pa'i dang /
NK120(e)001:6484: 'das lam gyis thob pa'i theg gsum so so'i ting
NK120(e)001:6485: nge 'dzin 'jiga rten las 'adsa pa'i bsam gatana sgoma
NK120(e)001:6486: pa gnyis so // de yang lang gshegs las gsungs
NK120(e)001:6487: pa ltar gsum du dbye na lam la ma zhugs
NK120(e)001:6488: pa'i rgyud kyi bsam gzugs byis pa nyer spyod kyi
NK120(e)001:6489: pa gnyis so // dang / lam zhugs tshogs sbyor gyi ting nge 'dzin don rab 'byed pa'i dang /
NK120(e)001:6490: mthong lam yan chad kyi 'phags pa'i ting nge 'dzin
NK120(e)001:6491: rnams la de bzhin gshegs dge'i bsam gtan zhes bya
NK120(e)001:6493: drug pa shes rab kyi phar phyin la /
NK120(e)001:6494: thos bsam sgom pa'i shes rab zab mo spyad //
NK120(e)001:6496: de la shes rab kyi ngo bo ni khyad chos
NK120(e)001:6497: bzhi ldan gyi chos rab rnam par 'byed pa'i sems
NK120(e)001:6498: pa dge ba sa bon dang bcas pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6500: pradz+ny+aa zhes pa'i sgra las rab tu rtogs pa'am rab tu khong du chud pas na shes rab bo //
NK120(e)001:6502: thosa bsam sgom pa'i shes rab ces pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6503: 'di dag gi go don lhongs pa gnad che bas na cung zad zhib tu spros na /
NK120(e)001:6504: dang po thos pa las byung ba'i shes rab ni /
NK120(e)001:6505: gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa nang rig pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6506: des gdul bya rjes su 'dzin pa'i yan lag tu
NK120(e)001:6507: thun mong gi rig gnas bzo gso sgra tshad bzhi
NK120(e)001:6508: dang bcas pa la mkhas par bya ba ste /
NK120(e)001:6510: rig pa'i gnas lnga dag la mkhas par ma byas na //
NK120(e)001:6511: 'phags mchog gis kyang thams cad mkhyen nyid mi 'gyur te //
NK120(e)001:6512: de lta bas na gzhan dag tshar gcod rjes bzung dang //
NK120(e)001:6513: bdag nyid kun shes bya phyir de la de brtson bya //
NK120(e)001:6515: khyad par du gsung rab kyi don rnams dpyis phyin pa khong du chud par byed pa la /
NK120(e)001:6516: spyir drang nges ldem dgongs la sogs pa'i sgo nas 'jal dgos kyang /
NK120(e)001:6517: 'dir chos rnams kyi gnas lugs ji bzhin pa la
NK120(e)001:6518: nges pa thob pa'i shes rab bskyed pa'i phyir yod
NK120(e)001:6519: pa sgro 'dogs kyi mtha' sel byed ngo bo la
NK120(e)001:6521: rgyu la dpyod pa rdo rje'i ze ga ma /
NK120(e)001:6522: 'bras bu la dpyod pa yod med skye 'gog /
NK120(e)001:6523: rgyu 'bras gnyis ka la dpyod pa mu bzhi skye 'gog ste bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:6524: yod med gnyis ka'i spros pa gcod byed rten 'brel
NK120(e)001:6525: chen mo ste gtan tshig chen po lngas kun rdzob
NK120(e)001:6526: spros pa'i snang zhen thams cad spros bral du gtan
NK120(e)001:6527: la 'bebs pa bka' bar pa'i dgongs don ltar dang
NK120(e)001:6528: / blo las 'das pa'i chos nyid don dam 'od
NK120(e)001:6529: gsal ba'i ye shes stong mi stong la sogs pa'i
NK120(e)001:6530: dpyod yul las 'das pa'i bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i
NK120(e)001:6531: ngo bo bka' tha ma dang /
NK120(e)001:6532: sngags rgyud rnams su gsungs pa'i don la nges pa nang nas 'drongs pa zhig byed dgos so //
NK120(e)001:6533: de nas bsam byung gi shes rab bskyed pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6534: ji skad thos pa'i don la nye bar dpyod pas
NK120(e)001:6535: nang du sems par 'jug pa na bye brag 'byed
NK120(e)001:6536: pa'i bsam shes kyi don spyi tsam du ma lus
NK120(e)001:6537: par re re nas tshig dang don gyi rim pa
NK120(e)001:6538: rnams nor ma nor brtag cing nges par bya ste
NK120(e)001:6539: / ye shes snying po kun las btus pa las /
NK120(e)001:6540: bsreg bcad brdar ba'i gser bzhin du //
NK120(e)001:6541: legs par brtag la nga yi bka' //
NK120(e)001:6542: blang bar bya yi gus phyir min //
NK120(e)001:6543: zhes pa ltar dad pas 'jug pa tsam ma yin par yid ches bskyed pa'i lung dang /
NK120(e)001:6544: dngos stobs kyi rig pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6545: snga phyi mi 'gal ba gsum gyi brtags nas blang bar bya ste /
NK120(e)001:6547: don gang lung dang rig pa yis //
NK120(e)001:6548: legs par mngon par brjod pa dang //
NK120(e)001:6549: snga phyi 'gal ba med pa ste //
NK120(e)001:6550: dam pa rnams kyis yongs su bzung //
NK120(e)001:6552: de ltar bsam bya yongs su rdzogs pa na sgom
NK120(e)001:6553: pa las byung ba'i shesa raba zaba mo rgyud la
NK120(e)001:6555: de yang spyir ji ltar nges pa'i don rnams blang
NK120(e)001:6556: dor gyi sgo nas sgrub cing nyams su len pa
NK120(e)001:6557: dang / khyad par lhag mthong gi shes rab rnam
NK120(e)001:6558: par mi rtog pa'i ye shes nyams su blang ba
NK120(e)001:6559: dang / ni / 'khor lo bar tha dang sngags
NK120(e)001:6560: kyi rgyud de zab mo rnams su bshad pa'i dgongs
NK120(e)001:6561: don rnams 'gal med du bsam byung gis gtan la
NK120(e)001:6562: phebs pa'i ngang du blo rtog gi spros pa thams
NK120(e)001:6563: cad bcad nas 'jog par bya ba ste /
NK120(e)001:6564: sgra gcan 'dzin gyis yum la bstod pa las /
NK120(e)001:6565: smra bsam brjod med shes rab pha rol phyin //
NK120(e)001:6566: ma skyes mi 'gag nam mkha'i ngo bo nyid //
NK120(e)001:6567: so so rang rig ye shes spyod yul ba //
NK120(e)001:6568: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK120(e)001:6570: de ltar bzhag pas sprin dengs pa na nyi ma'i
NK120(e)001:6571: dkyil 'khor gsal ba ltar mnyam bzhag gi rig ngo
NK120(e)001:6572: na ngos bzung gang du'ang ma grub pa'i blo bral
NK120(e)001:6573: gyi ye shes rang gsal rjen par gnas pa ni
NK120(e)001:6574: sems kyi rang bzhin 'od gsal ba khong nas shar
NK120(e)001:6575: ba ste / de la yang yang goms pa'i stobs
NK120(e)001:6576: kyis rang gnas kyi ye shes ma rtogs pa'i sems
NK120(e)001:6577: can rnams la snying rje chen po ngang gis 'byung
NK120(e)001:6578: ba ni chos nyid yin pas /
NK120(e)001:6579: de lta bu'i stong nyid snying rje zung du 'jug
NK120(e)001:6580: pa de ni theg pa chen po'i mdo sngags kyi
NK120(e)001:6581: lam thams cad kyi dngos gzhir nges pas gnad ma
NK120(e)001:6583: de yang sbyor ba sems bskyed /
NK120(e)001:6585: rjes bsngo ba ste dam pa gsum gyis rtsis zin
NK120(e)001:6586: pa'i sgo nas spyad par bya ba ste shes rab
NK120(e)001:6588: gsum pa sems can don byed kyi tshul khrims la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6589: don byed kyi tshul khrims dngos dang /
NK120(e)001:6590: tshul khrims gsum ka dang 'brel ba'i bslab pa bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6591: dang po don byed kyi tshul khrims dngos la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6594: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6595: sems can don byed tshul khrims bsdu dngos gzhi //
NK120(e)001:6597: semsa can rnams kyi dona byed pa'i tshul khrimas ni
NK120(e)001:6598: phyin drug gis rang rgyud smin par byas nas rang
NK120(e)001:6599: don yid byed kyi blo dang ma 'dres par bsdu
NK120(e)001:6600: ba'i dngosa po bzhi yi sgo nas gdul bya rnams
NK120(e)001:6602: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6603: thog mar sbyin pas gdul bya rab bsdus nas //
NK120(e)001:6604: snyan par smra ba'i gtam gyis yid rab drangs //
NK120(e)001:6605: theg pa rim dgur dkri ba don spyod de //
NK120(e)001:6606: de dag 'dren phyir rang yang don de spyod //
NK120(e)001:6608: byang chub sems dpa' de dge ba chos sdud kyis rang rgyud smin par byas nas /
NK120(e)001:6609: gzhan rgyud smin pa'i phyir du thoga mara zang zing
NK120(e)001:6610: gi sbyin pasa gdul bya 'khor du ma 'dus pa
NK120(e)001:6612: de nas 'khor du 'dus pa de dag la snyad
NK120(e)001:6613: para smra ba'i gtam gyis yida raba tu drangsa te
NK120(e)001:6614: dam pa'i chos la yid ches kyi sgo nas don
NK120(e)001:6615: du gnyer ba'i mos 'dun bskyed du 'jug /
NK120(e)001:6616: de nas don gnyer dang ldan pa de rnams kyang
NK120(e)001:6617: chos gcig gis blo rim tha dad pa smin par
NK120(e)001:6618: mi nus pas / blo tha ma'i chung 'bring che gsum la nyan rang byang sems gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:6619: blo 'bring gsum la bya spyod rnal 'byor gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:6620: blo rab gsum la bskyed rdzogs rdzogs chen gsum ste /
NK120(e)001:6621: thega pa rima pa dgura rim gyis dkri ba ni dona spyod pa la bshad de /
NK120(e)001:6623: sbyin pa'i g.yab mos legs pos te //
NK120(e)001:6624: snyan par smra ba'i tshig gis bsu //
NK120(e)001:6625: don mthun pa yi bag phab ste //
NK120(e)001:6626: don spyod gros chen gdab par bya //
NK120(e)001:6628: de ltar dkri ba'i gdul bya de dag gi don
NK120(e)001:6629: yang nyams su len pa'i sgo nas 'drena dgos pa'i
NK120(e)001:6630: phyir ranga yanga dona de dag la mthun par spyod
NK120(e)001:6631: dgos te / rang gis ma bsgrub na mdze phos
NK120(e)001:6632: bya khyung gi gdams ngag ston pa ltar gzhan la
NK120(e)001:6633: blang dor gyi bslab bya 'doms kyang nyan du mi
NK120(e)001:6635: gnyis pa tshul khrims gsum ka dang 'brel ba'i bslab pa bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6636: mthun phyogs kun slob mi mthun mtha' dag spangs //
NK120(e)001:6637: rtag tu dran dang shes bzhin bag yod brten //
NK120(e)001:6638: 'gro 'dug za nyal spyod lam rnam pa bzhir //
NK120(e)001:6639: spyod yul yongs su dag pa'i mdo sde ltar //
NK120(e)001:6640: gang byed rigs mthun tshig gis smon lam 'debs //
NK120(e)001:6642: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas bsgrub pa'i thabs kyi mthuna phyogsa
NK120(e)001:6643: kyi dge ba rang rgyud la ma skyes pa kun
NK120(e)001:6644: bskyed pa la slob cing skyes pa rnams gong du
NK120(e)001:6645: spel ba dang / mi mthuna pa'i phyogs mi dge
NK120(e)001:6646: ba matha'a dag mi bskyed cing skyes pa rnams spangsa
NK120(e)001:6647: spel ba dang / pa dang / de yang dus
NK120(e)001:6648: rtag tu bslab pa bsrung sems mi brjed pa'i drana
NK120(e)001:6649: spel ba dang / pa dang / pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6650: rang rgyud la nyes pa byung ma byung rtog pa'i
NK120(e)001:6651: spel ba dang / pa dang / pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6652: shesa bzhina / 'jug ldog gi gnas mi 'chol bar
NK120(e)001:6653: gzob pa'i baga yoda dang gsum po rgyun chags su
NK120(e)001:6654: spel ba dang / pa dang / pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6655: shesa bzhina / brten cing / de ltar dran shes
NK120(e)001:6656: bag yod gsum dang ldan pa'i ngang nas 'gro na
NK120(e)001:6657: mig gnya' shing tsam du lta ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6658: 'duga na lus drang por bsrang ste dran pa mngon du bzhag pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6659: zas za na phud dkon mchog la mchod cing lus
NK120(e)001:6660: kyi srin bu rnams la phan 'dogs pa'i bsam pas
NK120(e)001:6661: chags zhen med par spyod nas bsngo ba bya ba
NK120(e)001:6662: dang / nyal ba na gzhogs g.yas sa la phab
NK120(e)001:6663: cing mgo bo byang du bstan te dkon mchog gsum
NK120(e)001:6664: rjes su dran pa'i ngang nas nyal ba sogs spyod
NK120(e)001:6665: lam rnam pa bzhira dge ba'i bya bas dus 'da'
NK120(e)001:6666: dang / bar bya ste / de yang ji ltar
NK120(e)001:6667: na phal po che spyod yul yongas su dag pa'i
NK120(e)001:6668: mdo sde las ji skad gsungs pa ltar /
NK120(e)001:6669: bya ba ganga dang gang byed pa thams cad de
NK120(e)001:6670: dang de'i rigas mthuna par tshiga gi sgo nas kyang
NK120(e)001:6672: gsum pa don bsdu ba la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6673: mkhas pa gzhan gyi bzhed pa zlos pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6675: dang po mkhas pa gzhan gyi bzhed pa zlos pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6676: mkhyen rab dbang phyug klong chen rab 'byams ni //
NK120(e)001:6677: smon pa'i bslab bya tshang med bzhi sgom zhing //
NK120(e)001:6678: 'jug pa'i bslab bya pha rol phyin drug spyod //
NK120(e)001:6679: bsdu na dkar nag chos brgyad 'du zhes gsungs //
NK120(e)001:6681: shes bya rnam par 'byed pa'i mkhyen raba 'phul du
NK120(e)001:6682: byung zhing gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa'i tshig
NK120(e)001:6684: lung dang rtogs pa'i yon tan gyis thugs rgyud phyug pa klong chena raba 'byamsa dpal bzang pos ni /
NK120(e)001:6685: smon pa'i bslaba bya gnad bsdus pa tshad med bzhisa
NK120(e)001:6686: blo sbyangs nas yang yang bsgoma zhing sems can gyi
NK120(e)001:6687: phan bde snying khongs su chub par 'du ste byang
NK120(e)001:6688: chub kyi sems mi 'dor ba nyid smon pa mi
NK120(e)001:6689: 'chor ba'i bslab byar bshad pa'i phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:6690: 'jug pa'i bslaba bya rgyal sras rnams kyis bsgrub bya'i
NK120(e)001:6691: dge ba mtha' dag pha rola tu phyin pa drug
NK120(e)001:6692: tu bsdu bas de dag la tshul bzhin du spyod
NK120(e)001:6693: pa ste / de yang bsdu na dakara naga chosa
NK120(e)001:6694: brgyad la blang dor byed par 'du zhes gsungsa so
NK120(e)001:6695: pa ste / // gnyis pa rang gi bzhed pa 'god pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6696: 'dir ni phan dang bde ba rnams bya zhing //
NK120(e)001:6697: 'dir yang mi phan phyi mar gnod pa spangs //
NK120(e)001:6698: srol gnyis bslab byar ma 'dus med ces smra //
NK120(e)001:6700: gzhan yang byams pas kun nas bslangs te gang ci spyod kyang rung /
NK120(e)001:6701: rang gzhan la tshe 'dira ni phana pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6702: phyi ma phan chad mthar thug tu bde ba bsgrub
NK120(e)001:6703: pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba rnamas ni thabs la mkhas pas
NK120(e)001:6705: zhe sdang gis kun nas blangs te khro rtsod kyis
NK120(e)001:6706: phan tshun gnyis ka'i rgyud ma rung bar byed pa
NK120(e)001:6707: sogs ci spyad kyang rung rang gzhan la tshe 'dira
NK120(e)001:6708: yanga mi phan zhing phyi mar yang ngan song gi
NK120(e)001:6709: rgyur 'gyur ba sogs mthar thug tu gnod pa'i rgyur
NK120(e)001:6710: 'gyur ba thams cad gzab par byas te spanga bar
NK120(e)001:6711: bya dgos par ma zad 'dir bde ba ltar snang
NK120(e)001:6712: yang phyi mar gnod pa'i rgyu thams cad brtags te
NK120(e)001:6713: nus pa ci yod kyis spong ba yang gnad bsdus
NK120(e)001:6714: pa yin no // des na rgyal sras rnams kyis
NK120(e)001:6715: spang blang gi gnas theg chen gyi mdo sde rnams
NK120(e)001:6716: las gsungs pa mtha' dag la ji ltar slob pa'i
NK120(e)001:6717: thabs shing rta'i srola gnyisa kyi bslaba bya sngar bshad
NK120(e)001:6718: pa de dag la ma 'dusa pa med cesa smra
NK120(e)001:6719: pa yin no // ba yin no // gsum pa sdom pa skye ba'i rten ni /
NK120(e)001:6720: skye ba'i rten ni lha klu 'phrog ma sogs //
NK120(e)001:6721: sdig can la yang skye bar klu sgrub bzhed //
NK120(e)001:6722: thogs med de rten so thar dgos zhes gsungs //
NK120(e)001:6723: spyir na sangs rgyas chos la dad byed cing //
NK120(e)001:6724: 'bras bu bla med byang chub la dad cing //
NK120(e)001:6725: rgyal sras spyod pa rgya mtshor dad byed na //
NK120(e)001:6726: byang sems skye bar dkon mchog t+aa lar gsungs //
NK120(e)001:6728: de lta bu'i byang chub sems kyi sdom pa gang la skye ba'i rten ni brda shes shing /
NK120(e)001:6731: lha klu 'phroga ma la sogas pa'i mi ma yin sor sdom gyi rten mi rung ba rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:6732: mtshams med byas pa la sogs pa'i sdiga can sogs
NK120(e)001:6733: rten dman pa la yanga skye bar gsungs pa ni
NK120(e)001:6734: 'phags mchog klu sgrub kyi bzheda pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6735: de yang dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK120(e)001:6736: de'i tshe chos kyi rnam grangs 'di bshad pa na lha dang /
NK120(e)001:6740: lto 'phye chen po bgrangs pa las 'das pa dag
NK120(e)001:6741: gis bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK120(e)001:6742: byang chub tu sems bskyed do //
NK120(e)001:6743: zhes gsungs pa'i rjes su 'brang ba yin la /
NK120(e)001:6744: de yang smon sems tsam zhig nges par skye ba la dgongs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:6745: 'phags pa thogas meda kyi lugs ltar na 'jug sdom
NK120(e)001:6746: ma thob pa thob par byed pa de'i rten gling
NK120(e)001:6747: gsum gyi skyes pa bud med mtshan don byed nus
NK120(e)001:6749: so thara rigs bdun gyii sdom pa gang rung 'jug
NK120(e)001:6750: sdom gyi rten du 'gro dgosa pa'i phyir zhesa gsungas
NK120(e)001:6751: pas so // des na srol gnyis po la rten
NK120(e)001:6752: rgya che chung dang 'jug sgo yangs dog sogs yod
NK120(e)001:6753: par mngon yang don la gnad gcig ste /
NK120(e)001:6754: rigs bdun sngon du song ma song gang yin kyang
NK120(e)001:6755: rung srog gcod sogs nyes pa sna gcig spong ba'i
NK120(e)001:6756: sems tsam yang med na byang sdom mi skye bas
NK120(e)001:6757: nyes spyod gang rung spong bar dam bca' nus pa
NK120(e)001:6758: zhig nges par dgos te gzhan du na sems bskyed
NK120(e)001:6759: kyi bslab bya dang 'gal ba'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:6760: de bas bzhed pa spyir bshad na gang len pa
NK120(e)001:6761: po 'gro ba'i sa pas bsdus pa ni lus rten
NK120(e)001:6762: yin la / gtso bo ni bsam pa'i rten te /
NK120(e)001:6763: ston pa sangsa rgyas bcom ldan 'das dang /
NK120(e)001:6764: de'i bstan pa dam pa'i chosa theg pa chen po'i
NK120(e)001:6765: sde snod rnams la dada par byed cinga thob bya'i
NK120(e)001:6766: 'brasa bu bla na med pa'i byanga chub la dada
NK120(e)001:6767: cing rgyala srasa byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa rgya
NK120(e)001:6768: mtsho lta bu theg chen gyi mdo sder ji skad
NK120(e)001:6769: gsungs pa thams cad la slob 'dod kyi 'dun pa
NK120(e)001:6770: dang dad par byed na byang chub kyi semsa skye
NK120(e)001:6771: bar dkona mchoga t+aa la'i mdor gsungas te /
NK120(e)001:6773: rgyal dang rgyal ba'i chos la dad gyur cing //
NK120(e)001:6774: byang chub bla na med la'ang dad gyur la //
NK120(e)001:6775: rgyal sras rnams kyi spyod la'ang dad byed na //
NK120(e)001:6776: blo dang ldan pa rnams kyi sems skye'o //
NK120(e)001:6778: gnas pa'i rten ni gang la skyes pa'i rten dang /
NK120(e)001:6779: gtong rgyu ma byung na phyi ma gang dang gang
NK120(e)001:6780: du skyes pa'i rten de dang de la'ang yod de
NK120(e)001:6781: byang chub snying po'i bar du blangs pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:6782: des na tshe phyi ma rnams su dge ba'i bshes
NK120(e)001:6783: gnyen dang 'phrad nas dran gso'i tshul du sdom pa
NK120(e)001:6784: nod pa tsam las gsar du len dgos pa ma
NK120(e)001:6785: yin no // de ltar bslab pa'i rnam grangs thams
NK120(e)001:6786: cad dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi rang rang
NK120(e)001:6787: gi nus pa dang bstun te /
NK120(e)001:6789: de bzhin du ni bslab pa la //
NK120(e)001:6790: rim pa bzhin du bslab par bgyi //
NK120(e)001:6791: zhes pa ltar dran shes kyis bzung nas bslab par byas kyang /
NK120(e)001:6792: gal te ltung ba 'byung ba'i rgyu'i dbang gis nyams par gyur na /
NK120(e)001:6793: nyes dmigs ni kun gyi smad pa'i gnas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6794: sangs rgyas rnams mi mnyes pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6795: sems can rnams mi mgu ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6797: ming don shor ba la sogs pa tshe 'dir 'byung
NK120(e)001:6798: bar ma zad phyi ma dmyal ba chen por skye
NK120(e)001:6801: dge ba'i rtsa ba ltung ba de //
NK120(e)001:6802: sems can dmyal ba chen po'i rgyu //
NK120(e)001:6804: khyad par byang sdom phul ba ni nyes pa shin tu lci ste /
NK120(e)001:6806: bla na med pa'i bde ba la //
NK120(e)001:6807: bsam pa thag pas mgron gnyer na //
NK120(e)001:6808: 'gro ba thams cad bslus byas na //
NK120(e)001:6811: bzhi pa nyams na phyir bcos pa'i tshul la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6814: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6815: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:6817: dang po byang sdom ma thob pa thob par byas /
NK120(e)001:6818: bar du thob pa de nyid ma nyams par bsrung bar bya dgos la /
NK120(e)001:6819: tha mara gal srid nyamsa par 'gyur na slar gso
NK120(e)001:6820: ba'i tshul bashada pa ni 'di lta ste zhes so
NK120(e)001:6821: // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:6822: ltung ba'i rnam gzhag mu bzhir bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:6823: gzhan don du 'gyur na lus ngag gi mi dge ba bdun gnang ba'i skabs yod par bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:6825: dang po ltung ba'i rnam gzhag mu bzhir bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6826: gang gi rigs dang mi rigs ma brtags par //
NK120(e)001:6827: rtsom mam ldog gam btang snyoms 'jog kyang rung //
NK120(e)001:6828: 'os las 'das byed thams cad ltung ba'i sde //
NK120(e)001:6829: don chen bsgrub la chung btang gzugs brnyan te //
NK120(e)001:6830: nus pa'i yul min thams cad ltung ba med //
NK120(e)001:6831: mi nus der brtson de yi gzugs brnyan yin //
NK120(e)001:6833: gang zag ganga gi dgag sgrub kyi gnas la blo
NK120(e)001:6834: nus ci yod kyis brtsam par rigas pa dang mi
NK120(e)001:6835: rigas pa gang yin thog mar brtags dgos pa las
NK120(e)001:6836: ma brtagsa bzhin du ldog para bya ba'i gnas la
NK120(e)001:6837: rtsom mama / bar tsam par bya ba las ldoga gama /
NK120(e)001:6838: 'jug ldog gi gnas la batanga snyomsa su 'joga kyang rung ste /
NK120(e)001:6839: gang ltar yang blang dor bya bar 'os pa lasa
NK120(e)001:6840: 'adsa par byed pa thams cad ltung ba'i sde yin
NK120(e)001:6841: la / de yang mu bzhi ste /
NK120(e)001:6842: de la dkon mchog brtsegs pa las /
NK120(e)001:6843: gang zhig dga' ba'i yid kyis ni //
NK120(e)001:6844: lo brgyar sbyin pa byin pa bas //
NK120(e)001:6845: gang gis nyin gcig tshul khrims dag /
NK120(e)001:6846: bsrung ba de ni khyad par 'phags //
NK120(e)001:6848: dona chena tshul khrims kyi bslab pa bsrung zhing bsgruba
NK120(e)001:6849: pa'i ched la de bas don chung ba sbyin pa
NK120(e)001:6850: gtong ba bshol te batanga ba lta bu ltung ba'i
NK120(e)001:6851: gzugas brnyan te don la ltung med dang /
NK120(e)001:6852: las dang po pas mgo sogs gtong ba lta bu
NK120(e)001:6853: rang gi nus pa'i yul mina pas na mi bsgrub
NK120(e)001:6854: pa'am 'jug ldog ma nor bar brtson pa thamsa cad
NK120(e)001:6855: la ltung ba meda ces dang /
NK120(e)001:6856: rang rang gi blo stobs kyi mi nus bzhin du
NK120(e)001:6857: yan lag gtong ba lta bu bya dka' ba'i gnas
NK120(e)001:6859: kun slong ngan pas sbyor ba dkar ba lta bu
NK120(e)001:6860: ltung med de yi gzugas brnyan tsam yina te don
NK120(e)001:6861: la ltung ba'o // gnyis pa gzhan don du 'gyur
NK120(e)001:6862: na lus ngag gi mi dge ba bdun gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:6863: skabs yod par bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:6864: gzhan phyir phan na lus ngag mi dge 'dun //
NK120(e)001:6865: gnang ba'i skabs yod don la dge ba yin //
NK120(e)001:6867: skye 'gro gazhana gyi don phyir phan nges yin na
NK120(e)001:6868: lus ngaga gis spyad pa bya ba mi dge bduna
NK120(e)001:6869: la gannga ba'i skabsa yod de /
NK120(e)001:6870: ji ltar gnang ba yin zhe na /
NK120(e)001:6871: 'gro ba mang po'i srog bskyab pa'i phyir dang bstan
NK120(e)001:6872: 'gro spyi la gnod cing 'tshe ba'i gshed ma gsod
NK120(e)001:6873: pa lta bu srog gcod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6874: nyams thag pa'i 'gro ba zas skom tsha grang gi
NK120(e)001:6875: gdung bas 'chi bar phyogs pa la 'byor ldan las
NK120(e)001:6876: zas gos brkus nas sbyin pa lta bu ma sbyin
NK120(e)001:6877: len pa dang / bud med 'dod pas gdung ste
NK120(e)001:6878: 'chi bar nye ba la gnas skabs de'i gdung ba
NK120(e)001:6879: len pa dang / sel phyir dang / mthar thug
NK120(e)001:6880: dge ba la rim gyis sbyor ba'i slad du de
NK120(e)001:6882: gsod nges kyi skye bo srog skyob pa'i phyir don
NK120(e)001:6883: phyin ci log tu sbas nas rdzun smra ba dang
NK120(e)001:6884: / chos ldan gyi gang zag sdig grogs kyis bslus
NK120(e)001:6885: nas ngan 'gror 'khrid pa las ldog pa'i phyir phra
NK120(e)001:6887: mi dge ba'i bya ba las ldog pa'i phyir gshe ba'i tshig rtsub smra ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6888: mya ngan gyis non pa'i dub pa bsang zhing chos
NK120(e)001:6889: lam du 'khrid pa'i phyir gtam rgyud sogs ngag 'khyal
NK120(e)001:6890: mang po smra ba rnams gnas skabs der mi dge
NK120(e)001:6891: ba ltar snang yang don la dge ba kho na
NK120(e)001:6892: yina te / sems kyi 'phen pa las gzhan pa'i dge sdig ma grub pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:6894: bsam pa byang chub sems dpa' yi //
NK120(e)001:6895: dge 'am yang na mi dge ba //
NK120(e)001:6896: thams cad dge ba nyid 'gyur te //
NK120(e)001:6897: gang phyir sems de gtso bo'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:6899: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK120(e)001:6900: snying rjer ldan zhing byams phyir dang //
NK120(e)001:6901: sems dge ba la nyes pa med //
NK120(e)001:6903: gsum pa phyir bcos dngos ji ltar bya ba'i tshul la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6906: dang po klu sgrub kyi lugs ni /
NK120(e)001:6907: thun 'das nyams na 'phags pa nam snying la //
NK120(e)001:6908: tho rangs gsol btab rmi lam ltung ba 'chags //
NK120(e)001:6909: lhag ma phung po gsum pa nyin mtshan du //
NK120(e)001:6910: lan gsum 'don pas gzhil ba klu sgrub lugs //
NK120(e)001:6912: spyir sdom pa gtong ba dang nyams pa'i rkyen ni //
NK120(e)001:6913: rten gzhi smon sems btang ba /
NK120(e)001:6915: spong rkyen bslab pa phul ba gsum las /
NK120(e)001:6916: dang tha gnyis ni de ma thag tu sdo ma
NK120(e)001:6917: pa rtsad nas med par 'gyur ba'i rgyu dang rkyen
NK120(e)001:6918: yin pa'i phyir bshags pa tsam gyis mi chog gis
NK120(e)001:6919: sdom pa slar blang dgos la /
NK120(e)001:6920: de las gzhan rtsa ltung rnams nyin la cha gsum
NK120(e)001:6921: mtshan la cha gsum ste drug tu phye ba'i cha
NK120(e)001:6922: gang rung gi nang ltung ba byung nas de'i thun
NK120(e)001:6923: phyi ma'i nang gnyen pos ma sleb bar 'das na
NK120(e)001:6924: thun 'adsa kyi ltung ba zhes bya ste /
NK120(e)001:6925: de ltar nyamsa pa'i ltung ba byung na de nyid
NK120(e)001:6926: phyir bcos pa'i tshul la dbang 'a bring rnams yi
NK120(e)001:6927: dam lha'i mdun du bshags pas ltung ba las ldang
NK120(e)001:6928: ba yin pas / 'dir rigs lnga spyi'i lha 'aphagas
NK120(e)001:6929: pa nam mkha'i snying po'i mdun du bshags par 'dod
NK120(e)001:6930: na nyin mtshan gyi bar ma chod par khrus dang
NK120(e)001:6931: gtsang sbra la gnas pas spos btul te mtshan nas
NK120(e)001:6933: 'phags pas bdag la zhal bstan te sdig pa dag par mdzad du gsol /
NK120(e)001:6934: zhes gsol ba drag tu btab pas dngos sam rmi
NK120(e)001:6935: lam du skal ba dang 'tshams par de nyid kyi
NK120(e)001:6936: gzugs sam ming nas bya ba'i bar ci rigs pa'i
NK120(e)001:6937: gzugs kyis ltung ba las 'byin pa'i thabs ston par
NK120(e)001:6938: 'gyur la / gal te rtags ma byung na tho
NK120(e)001:6939: rangas kyi dus su spyod lam sngar ltar byas la
NK120(e)001:6940: 'gyur la / / skya rengs skya rengs snying rje
NK120(e)001:6941: chen po legs pa khyod 'dzam bu'i gling du shar
NK120(e)001:6942: ma thag tu bdag la thugs rjes khyab par mdzod
NK120(e)001:6943: 'gyur la / / cig / nam mkha'i snying po
NK120(e)001:6944: snying rje chen po dang ldan pa la yang bdag
NK120(e)001:6945: gi tshig gis myur du bskul te thabs gang gis
NK120(e)001:6946: ltung ba myur du 'chags par 'dod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:6947: theg pa chen po 'phags pa la thabs dang shes
NK120(e)001:6948: rab thob par 'gyur ba'i thabs de bdag gi rmi
NK120(e)001:6949: lam du bstan du gsol zhes gsola ba bataba nas
NK120(e)001:6950: nyal ba'i rmi lam du gzugs skal ba bzhin ston
NK120(e)001:6952: dbang po dman pa dag gis ni stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags pa ste /
NK120(e)001:6953: rten gyi stobs theg chen dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang /
NK120(e)001:6954: bde bar gshegs pa'i rten khyad par can gyi dang /
NK120(e)001:6955: nang gi rten skyabs 'gro dang sems bskyed //
NK120(e)001:6956: kun tu spyod pa'i stobs ltung ba'i gnyen po la
NK120(e)001:6957: basngagasa pa'i theg pa chen po'i mdo gzugs khyad par
NK120(e)001:6958: can bklags shing brjod pa la sogs pa yin la
NK120(e)001:6959: / sun 'byin pa dang sor chud pa gnyis ni
NK120(e)001:6960: sngar so thar gyi skabs su bshad pa dang 'dra'o
NK120(e)001:6961: / // dbang po rab kyi ni sgyu ma dang
NK120(e)001:6962: rmi lam lta bu'i tshul gyis mkha' khyab kyi rgyal
NK120(e)001:6963: ba sras dang bcas pa'i spyan sngar tshig gis bshags
NK120(e)001:6964: rjes yang dag pa'i don la mnyam par 'jog par
NK120(e)001:6965: / // bya ste / phyogs su rgyas pa'i mdo las /
NK120(e)001:6967: drang por 'dug la yang dag ltos //
NK120(e)001:6968: yang dag nyid la yang dag blta //
NK120(e)001:6969: yang dag mthong na rnam par grol //
NK120(e)001:6974: shes bzhin gyis ma zin pas phyir bcos ma grub
NK120(e)001:6975: pa'i ltung ba'i lhag ma rnams phung po gsuma pa'i
NK120(e)001:6976: mdo nyin matshana du lana gsuma gsum 'dona pasa gzhila
NK120(e)001:6978: lar byang sdom 'di ni so thar dang mi 'dra ste /
NK120(e)001:6979: nyin re bzhin yang yang blang na sdom pa gong
NK120(e)001:6980: 'phel du 'gro ba'i thabs su 'gyur bar ma zad
NK120(e)001:6981: rtsa ltung byung ba thun tshod las ma 'das na
NK120(e)001:6982: bshags pa tsam gyis gso ru yod kyang /
NK120(e)001:6983: 'das na tshul khrims gtugs par 'gyur bas sdom pa slar len dgos par bshad cing /
NK120(e)001:6984: grangs nges pa ni med pa bcas rang gi kha
NK120(e)001:6985: na ma tho ba spyi dang bye brag byang sems
NK120(e)001:6986: kyi bslab pa thams cad la skyon byung ba'i gnyen
NK120(e)001:6987: por yang mchog tu zab pa gal che ba yin
NK120(e)001:6988: te de rnams ni klu sgrub kyi lugsa yin no
NK120(e)001:6989: // gnyis pa rgyal sras thogs med kyi lugs la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:6990: gtong rgyu ngos bzung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:6992: dang po gtong rgyu ngos bzung ba ni /
NK120(e)001:6993: smon pa'i sems ni nag po'i chos bzhi spyad //
NK120(e)001:6994: sems can snying nas blos btang de gtong 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:6995: rgyun mi 'chad spyod ngo tsha khrel med dang //
NK120(e)001:6996: de mgu dga' dang de nyid yon tan du //
NK120(e)001:6997: lta ba kun dkris chen pos sdom pa 'joms //
NK120(e)001:6998: pham pa zhes brjod chung dang 'bring la min //
NK120(e)001:7000: de la sdom pa gtong ba'i rgyu ni /
NK120(e)001:7001: smon pa'i semsa ni yan lag naga po'i chos bzhi spyad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7002: rtsa ba semas can snying thag pa nasa blos batanga na de gtonga bar 'gyur la /
NK120(e)001:7003: de btang bas 'jug sems kyang nyams par 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:7004: rnyed bkur gyi phyir bdag bstod gzhan smod sogs pham
NK120(e)001:7005: pa'i gnas lta bu'i chos bzhi gang rung rgyun mi
NK120(e)001:7007: ngo tsha dang khrela yod chung ngu tsam yang med pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7008: bya ba desa mgu zhing dag'a bar byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7009: bya ba de nyid la yona tan du lta ba
NK120(e)001:7010: de yan lag bzhi tshang na kun dkrisa chena posa
NK120(e)001:7011: bskyed pa'i ltung ba zhes bya ste sdom pa 'jomas
NK120(e)001:7012: par byed pas na phama pa zhesa brjod pa yin
NK120(e)001:7013: la / yan lag gang rung yang de la ngo
NK120(e)001:7014: tsha cher bskyed cing gzhan rkyen la ma ltos par
NK120(e)001:7015: rang nyid de las myur du ldog par byed na
NK120(e)001:7017: yan lag gang rung tshang la ngo tsha dang khrel
NK120(e)001:7018: yod cung zad skye zhing gzhan gyis bskul bas ldog
NK120(e)001:7019: na kun dkris 'bringa po zhes bya la /
NK120(e)001:7020: de gnyis kyis sdom pa gtong ba mina no //
NK120(e)001:7021: gnyis pa nyes ltung phyir bcos pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7022: phas pham byung na slar blang 'bring na gsum //
NK120(e)001:7023: tha ma gcig mdun dngos po brjod pas bshags //
NK120(e)001:7024: mthun pa'i gang zag med na yid kyis bsdams //
NK120(e)001:7025: rgya chen spyod pa'i ring lugs zla med do //
NK120(e)001:7027: de dag ji ltar bshags pa'i tshul ni smon sems btang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7028: kun dkris chen pos phasa phama pa'i gnas lta bu'i
NK120(e)001:7029: rtsa ltung gis gtong bas de dag byung na theg
NK120(e)001:7030: pa chen po'i sdom ldan bzhi yan chad kyi drung
NK120(e)001:7031: du bshags sdom dang bsags sbyangs la nan tan byas
NK120(e)001:7032: la sdom pa slar blangsa blang bar bya zhing lan
NK120(e)001:7033: gsum las lhag par bskyar du med par bshad cing
NK120(e)001:7034: / kun dkris 'bring gis bskyed pa'i pham 'dra rnams ni gsuma yan chad dang /
NK120(e)001:7035: tha ma kun dkris chung ngus spyad pa'i rtsa ltung dang /
NK120(e)001:7036: de las gzhan pa'i nyes byas zhe drug la kun
NK120(e)001:7037: slong gi dbang gis nyon mongs pa can yin min
NK120(e)001:7038: dang ltung med du 'gyur ba'ang yod pas de dag
NK120(e)001:7039: gang byung yang gang zag gciga yan chad kyi mduna
NK120(e)001:7040: du nyes pa'i dngosa po brjod pasa bashagas bsdams byas
NK120(e)001:7042: sdom pa nyi shu pa las /
NK120(e)001:7043: sdom pa slar yang blang bar bya //
NK120(e)001:7044: zag pa 'bring ni gsum la bshags //
NK120(e)001:7045: gcig gi mdun du lhag ma rnams //
NK120(e)001:7046: nyon mongs mi mang bdag sems bzhin //
NK120(e)001:7048: de thams cad la bshags yul mthuna pa'i ganga zaga
NK120(e)001:7049: theg chen sdom ldan meda na rgyal ba sras bcas
NK120(e)001:7050: yida kyis bsam pa'i spyan sngar bshags shing bsdama par
NK120(e)001:7051: bya'o // de yang lam sgron 'grel par /
NK120(e)001:7052: dum bu dang por legs par gso byed pa //
NK120(e)001:7053: skyes bu rab yin 'bring ni gnyis la'o //
NK120(e)001:7054: dum bu tha ma gso ba tha ma ste //
NK120(e)001:7055: zhes spyir dus drug dang khyad par dus re re
NK120(e)001:7056: la cha gsum gsum du phye nas de dang der
NK120(e)001:7057: gnyen pos slebs pa gang zag rab 'bring tha gsum
NK120(e)001:7058: gyi gso tshul yin par bshad do //
NK120(e)001:7059: de ltar rgya chena spyod pa'i ringa lugsa 'di ni
NK120(e)001:7060: bsrung ba'i mtshams dang gso ba'i tshul sogs las dang
NK120(e)001:7061: po pa rnams la dgongs nas shin tu gu dogs
NK120(e)001:7062: par mdzad pas na byang chub sems kyi bslab nor
NK120(e)001:7063: mi nyams bsrung gso'i man ngag mkhas tshul gzhan gyis
NK120(e)001:7064: 'gran zla bya ba'i yul du ma grub pa 'di
NK120(e)001:7065: nyid mtshungs med rgyal ba'i sras des phyi rabs gdul
NK120(e)001:7066: bya'i bsod nams kyi bgo skal du stsal ba nyid
NK120(e)001:7067: do zhes mngon par basngagasa so //
NK120(e)001:7068: lnga pa byang chub sems sdom tshul bzhin bsrung ba'i phan yon la gsum /
NK120(e)001:7069: bsod nams rgyun chags su 'byung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7070: sangs rgyas kyi sras su 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7071: bla na med pa'i byang chub thob pa'i phan yon no //
NK120(e)001:7072: dang po bsod nams rgyun chags su 'byung ba'i phan yon ni /
NK120(e)001:7073: 'di 'dra'i byang chub sems kyi rtsis zin na //
NK120(e)001:7074: gnyir sogs bag med gyur la'ang bsod nams shugs //
NK120(e)001:7077: re zhig smon pa byang chub sems bskyed kyi dbang
NK120(e)001:7078: du byas na gnas skabs su 'khor los sgyur ba
NK120(e)001:7079: dang lha'i dbang po sogs mtho ris kyi 'bras bu
NK120(e)001:7080: lan grangs du mar myong yang mi zad par 'phel
NK120(e)001:7082: dge ba gzhan kun chu shing bzhin du ni //
NK120(e)001:7083: 'bras bu bskyed nas zad par 'gyur ba nyid //
NK120(e)001:7084: byang chub sems kyi ljon shing rtag par yang //
NK120(e)001:7087: da dung 'di 'dra ba'i smon sems kyi steng du
NK120(e)001:7088: 'jug pa byang chub kyi semsa kyi rtsis zina na
NK120(e)001:7089: / dge ba byed pa'i dus ma yin par gnyid
NK120(e)001:7090: dang rtse mos g.yeng bar gyur pa la sogas pa
NK120(e)001:7091: baga med pa'i dbang du gyur pa'i gnas skabs la'ang
NK120(e)001:7092: rgyu bsoda namas kyi shugsa kyang rgyun mi chad par
NK120(e)001:7093: 'byung bar gsungs na 'bras bu mi zad par 'byung
NK120(e)001:7094: ba lta yang ci smos te /
NK120(e)001:7096: de nas bzung ste gnyid log gam //
NK120(e)001:7097: bag med gyur kyang bsod nams shugs //
NK120(e)001:7098: rgyun mi chad par du ma zhig /
NK120(e)001:7099: nam mkha' mnyam par rab tu 'byung //
NK120(e)001:7101: gnyis pa mig don gnas 'gyur ba'i phan yon ni /
NK120(e)001:7104: de ltar byang chub kyi sems rgyud la skyes ma
NK120(e)001:7105: thag tu ming 'pho sde rgyal ba'i srasa zhes 'jig
NK120(e)001:7106: rten lha dang mir bcas pa kun gyis phyag bya
NK120(e)001:7107: ba'i gnas su 'gyur ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:7109: byang chub sems skyes gyur na skad cig gis //
NK120(e)001:7110: 'khor ba'i btson rar bsdam pa'i nyam thag rnams //
NK120(e)001:7111: bde gshegs rnams kyi sras zhes brjod bya zhing //
NK120(e)001:7112: 'jig rten lha mir bcas pas phyag byar 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:7114: gal te nyes pa 'ga' zhig byung yang smon sems
NK120(e)001:7115: ma btang na rigs kyi sgo nas nyan rang dang
NK120(e)001:7116: dgra bcom zil gyis gnon cing /
NK120(e)001:7117: byang sems kyi ming yang mi 'dor ba yin te /
NK120(e)001:7120: dper na rdo rje rin po che ni chag kyang
NK120(e)001:7121: gser gyi rgyan thams cad zil gyis gnon cing rdo
NK120(e)001:7122: rje rin po che'i ming yang mi 'dor la /
NK120(e)001:7123: dbul ba yang rnam par bzlog go //
NK120(e)001:7124: de bzhin du rnam pa thams cad mkhyen par sems
NK120(e)001:7125: bskyed pa'i rdo rje rin po che nan tan dang
NK120(e)001:7126: bral yang nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas kyi yon
NK120(e)001:7127: tan thams cad zil gyis gnon cing byang chub sems
NK120(e)001:7129: 'khor ba'i dbul ba thams cad kyang rnam par bzlog go //
NK120(e)001:7131: gsum pa bla med byang chub kyi go 'phang thob pa'i phan yon ni /
NK120(e)001:7132: grangs med gsum bdun so gsum byang chub thob //
NK120(e)001:7134: de yang mthar thug gi 'bras bu thob tshul la /
NK120(e)001:7135: spyir tshogs lam du dran pa nye bar bzhag pa bzhi /
NK120(e)001:7136: yang dag par spong ba bzhi /
NK120(e)001:7137: rdzu 'phrul gyi rkang pa bzhi rnams bsgom pas /
NK120(e)001:7138: mngon shes lnga dang chos rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin sogs thob cing /
NK120(e)001:7139: de nas drod rtse gnyis dang bzod pa chos mchog
NK120(e)001:7140: gnyis te nges 'byed cha bzhi'i dang po gnyis su
NK120(e)001:7142: phyi ma gnyis su stobs lnga bsgom pas gzung rtog dang 'dzin rtog rnams nyams smad par byas te /
NK120(e)001:7143: yon tan kyang tshogs lam las ches che ba thob cing /
NK120(e)001:7144: de nas dang por chos nyid kyi bden pa mngon
NK120(e)001:7145: sum du mthong bas kun brtags kyis bsdus pa'i sgrib
NK120(e)001:7146: pa gnyis po drung 'byin gyi tshul du spangs te
NK120(e)001:7147: brgya phrag bcu gnyis la sogs pa'i yon tan thob
NK120(e)001:7148: la / de nas bsgom pa'i lam sa dgu por
NK120(e)001:7149: chos nyid mngon sum du mthong ba'i ye shes de
NK120(e)001:7150: yang yang goms pa'i stobs las dang po drug tu
NK120(e)001:7151: lhan skyes kyis bsdus pa'i sgrib pa gnyis po rim
NK120(e)001:7152: la / gyis spangs te / dag pa gsum du
NK120(e)001:7153: nyon sgrib zad nas shes sgrib phra ba'ang rim gyis
NK120(e)001:7155: sa de dag gi gnas skabs su stong phrag bcu
NK120(e)001:7156: gnyis la sogs pa'i kun rdzob kyi yon tan cher
NK120(e)001:7158: mthar rgyun matha'i rdo rje lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin
NK120(e)001:7159: gyis bag chags phra ba bcom ste mngon par rdzogs
NK120(e)001:7161: de yang byang chub sems dpa' dbang po rab 'bring tha gsum gyi lam bgrod tshul yang /
NK120(e)001:7162: dang po dbang rnon rdzi bo lta bu'am dpe med
NK120(e)001:7163: pa'i sems bskyed ces thog mar sems can thams cad
NK120(e)001:7164: sangs rgyas kyi sar bkod nas /
NK120(e)001:7165: rjes la rang nyid grol bar 'dod pa rnams ni grangas med gsuma las mi thogs te /
NK120(e)001:7167: gnyis pas ma dag sa bdun /
NK120(e)001:7168: gsum pas dag pa sa gsum mthar phyin par byas
NK120(e)001:7169: nas mthar 'bras byang chub chen po'i go 'phang thob
NK120(e)001:7170: la / gnyis pa dbang 'bring mnyan pa ltar ram
NK120(e)001:7171: ye shes dam pa'i sems bskyed ces rang dang 'gro
NK120(e)001:7172: ba mnyam du thar par 'dod pa'i byang sems rnams
NK120(e)001:7174: tshogs sbyor gnyis su gnyis re /
NK120(e)001:7176: sgom lam du gnyis kyis lam mthar phyin par byed do //
NK120(e)001:7177: gsum pa dbang rtul rgyal po lta bu'am 'dod chen
NK120(e)001:7178: po'i sems bskyed ces thog mar rang nyid grol nas
NK120(e)001:7179: de rjes gzhan sgrol bar 'dod pa'i byang sems rnams
NK120(e)001:7180: ni grangs med sum cu so gsuma thogs te /
NK120(e)001:7182: sa bcu re re la gsum gsum gyis mthar byang chub chen po'i go 'phang thoba pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:7183: de ltar brjod bya'i don mthar phyin nas le'u'i skabs bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:7184: byang chub sems dpa'i sems bskyed kyi bslab bya rim par phye ba ste gsum pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7186: byang chub semsa dpa'i semsa bskyed kyi bslab bya don
NK120(e)001:7187: dam byang chub kyi sems rang gnas kyi ye shes
NK120(e)001:7188: nyid kun rdzob thabs kyi brda la brten nas gdul
NK120(e)001:7189: bya'i ngo skal dang 'tshams par bcad pa smon pa
NK120(e)001:7190: dang 'jug pa'i sems gnyis po bskyed tshul srol gnyis
NK120(e)001:7191: kyi ring lugs ltar bshad pa'i rima pa gsal bar
NK120(e)001:7192: phyes pa ste skabs gsuma pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o
NK120(e)001:7193: //// rtsa ba'i gsum pa rig pa 'dzin pa rnams
NK120(e)001:7194: kyi bslab bya gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dam
NK120(e)001:7195: tshig sdom pa'i rim par phye ba gtan la dbab
NK120(e)001:7196: //// pa la gsum / rdo rje theg pa'i bstan
NK120(e)001:7197: pa thog mar ji ltar byung tshul smos pas khog
NK120(e)001:7198: //// pa la gsum / dbub pa / de ltar
NK120(e)001:7199: byung ba'i bstan pa bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji
NK120(e)001:7200: //// pa la gsum / dbub pa / ltar bzung
NK120(e)001:7201: tshul / de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya skabs don
NK120(e)001:7202: gzhung bsrang tshul gtan la dbab pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7203: dang po rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa thog mar ji ltar byung tshul bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7204: kun bzang rdo rje 'chang dbang ston pa des //
NK120(e)001:7205: 'og min chen por rgyud sde rgya mtsho gsungs //
NK120(e)001:7206: phyis nas 'bras spungs sogs su bzlas te bstan //
NK120(e)001:7208: thog mar ston pas rgyud sde rnams ji ltar gsungs pa'i tshul phun sum tshogs pa lnga ldan te /
NK120(e)001:7209: de yang ston pa phun sum tshogs pa ni bdag
NK120(e)001:7210: cag gi ston pa 'di nyid thog ma med pa'i
NK120(e)001:7211: dus su gzhi gdod ma'i dbyings su rig pa'i ye
NK120(e)001:7212: shes grol bas mngon par byang chub ste sku dang
NK120(e)001:7213: ye shes 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang la dus gsum
NK120(e)001:7214: gyi sangs rgyas thams cad dang dgongs pa ro gcig
NK120(e)001:7215: tu bzhugs pa las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur snang
NK120(e)001:7216: ste / ye shes gsang ba las /
NK120(e)001:7217: rang bzhin mi g.yo lhun rdzogs shing //
NK120(e)001:7218: spyod yul kun tu bzang po ste //
NK120(e)001:7219: zhes pa ltar spyod yul thams cad ye shes rang
NK120(e)001:7220: snang gi ngo bo 'ba' zhig tu dag pas kun
NK120(e)001:7221: tu bazanga po / gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pas mi phyed pas rdo rje /
NK120(e)001:7222: dbyings dang ye shes 'du 'bral med par 'achanga zhing /
NK120(e)001:7223: dkyil 'khor thams cad kyi dabnga phyug dam par gyur pa'i ston para snang ba desa /
NK120(e)001:7224: gnas phun sum tshogs pa rang snang shin tu rnam par dag pa'i zhing khams 'oga mina chena pora /
NK120(e)001:7225: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa nyid las mi gzhan pa'i
NK120(e)001:7226: rang snang gi 'khor rgyal ba zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor
NK120(e)001:7227: tshad med pas yongs su bskor pa'i dbus na /
NK120(e)001:7228: chos phun sum tshogs pa ye shes 'od gsal ba'i dgongs pa brjod du med pa nyid /
NK120(e)001:7229: dus phun sum tshogs pa gzhi rdzogs 'pho 'gyur med
NK120(e)001:7230: pa'i dbyings su rang shar ba'i tshul gyis snang bar
NK120(e)001:7231: gyur to // de'i ngang las sa bcu'i rgyun mtha'
NK120(e)001:7232: la snang ba'i gnas khyad par can 'og min du
NK120(e)001:7233: gyur to // / ston pa rigs drug pa'i rnam pas /
NK120(e)001:7234: 'khor sa matha'i byang chub sems dpa' rig pa 'dzin pa rnams la /
NK120(e)001:7235: chos gsang sngags kyi rgyud sde rgya mtsho lta bu dgongs pa brda'i gsung gis /
NK120(e)001:7236: dus rtag pa rgyun gyi 'khor lor bstan par mdzad cing /
NK120(e)001:7237: de bzhin du byang sems sa dgu pa la snang ba'i 'og min tsam po ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7238: sa brgyad pa la snang ba'i 'og min btags pa
NK120(e)001:7239: ba rnams su'ang tshul de dang 'dra bar gsungas shing
NK120(e)001:7240: / de'i tshe gdul bya gdug pa can rnams kyi
NK120(e)001:7241: ngor dpal he ru ka'i rnam par snang bas khro
NK120(e)001:7242: bo'i dkyil 'khor rab 'byams sprul bshad kyis don mdzad
NK120(e)001:7243: / pa dang / gzhan yang rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing khams lnga dang /
NK120(e)001:7244: dag ma dag gi 'jig rten gyi khams rnams su
NK120(e)001:7245: 'gro 'dul sprul pa'i rnam pa tshad med par snang
NK120(e)001:7246: bas de dang der gnas pa'i gdul bya rang rang
NK120(e)001:7247: gi mos pa dang mthun par 'dul byed kyi thabs
NK120(e)001:7248: tshul dpag tu med pas don mdzad do //
NK120(e)001:7249: de lta bu'i rgyud sde rnams rdo rje 'chang gi
NK120(e)001:7250: thugs kyi rnam par 'phrul pa rigs gsum sems dpas
NK120(e)001:7251: lha klu gnod sbyin gyi yul rnams su bstan nas
NK120(e)001:7253: khyad par mi yul sogs su ji ltar byung ba'i
NK120(e)001:7254: tshul la mchog gi sprul sku'i rnam par snang ba
NK120(e)001:7255: bdag cag gi ston pa 'di nyid dka' thub la
NK120(e)001:7256: gnas pa'i tshe thugs 'og min du sangs rgyas nas
NK120(e)001:7257: rim bzhin ri rib kyi rtse dang /
NK120(e)001:7258: rgya mtsho'i 'gram la sogs par gsang sngags kyi chos
NK120(e)001:7259: du ma bstan te slar btags pa'i lus la zhugs
NK120(e)001:7260: te 'tshang rgya tshul sogs bstan par bzhed pa dang
NK120(e)001:7261: / spyir gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rgyud rnams phyag na rdo rjes bsdus te /
NK120(e)001:7266: kla klo'i skad la sogs pa skad rigs dang yig
NK120(e)001:7267: rigs sna tshogs pas glegs bam la bkod par bshad
NK120(e)001:7268: de / ye shes thig le'i rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:7269: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su gsang ba'i rgyud skal ba
NK120(e)001:7270: dang ldan pa'i sems can la sus 'chad par byed
NK120(e)001:7272: phyag na rdo rje mgon pos bshad par byed do //
NK120(e)001:7274: de nas yang o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu
NK120(e)001:7275: tis ston pa'i nyan thos mkha' la 'phur te 'gro
NK120(e)001:7276: 'ong byed pa gzigs pa na thag ring bas cha
NK120(e)001:7277: ma phyed de / blon po la bya dmar po'i khyu 'di dag ci yin dris pas /
NK120(e)001:7280: sangs rgyas kyi nyan thos lags so byas pas /
NK120(e)001:7281: rgyal po sangs rgyas blta 'dod nas gsol ba btab pas /
NK120(e)001:7282: nangs par w+aa ra n+aa si nas bcos ldan 'das
NK120(e)001:7283: 'khor dgra bcom pa lnga brgya dang bcas pa rdzu
NK120(e)001:7284: 'phrul gyis byon / der rgyal pos mchod nas 'tshang rgya ba'i thabs zhus pas /
NK120(e)001:7285: rab tu byung la bslab pa gsum rgyud la brten cig gsungs pas /
NK120(e)001:7286: dzam+bu'i tshal ni nyams dga' bar //
NK120(e)001:7287: wa skyes nyid du gyur kyang sla'i //
NK120(e)001:7288: 'dod yon spangs pa'i thar pa ni //
NK120(e)001:7289: nam yang mi 'dod goo ta ma //
NK120(e)001:7291: skad cig la nyan thos kyi tshogs rnams mi snang bar gyur te /
NK120(e)001:7292: 'di na gang zag brgyad med cing //
NK120(e)001:7293: nyan thos rang rgyal 'ga' yang med //
NK120(e)001:7294: byang chub sems dpa' rdzu 'phrul che //
NK120(e)001:7295: de dag de yis gzugs su sprul //
NK120(e)001:7296: zhes nam mkha' nas sgra byung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7297: der ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor sprul nas rgyal po la dbang bskur bas /
NK120(e)001:7298: de nyid du zung 'jug gi sku 'grub ste /
NK120(e)001:7299: de la ston pas rgyud thams cad gtad par bzhed do //
NK120(e)001:7300: gzhan yang ri bo bya rkang can dang /
NK120(e)001:7302: lang+ka'i bdag po sgra sgrogs kyi gnas la sogs par
NK120(e)001:7303: ston pa nyid dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po'i rnam par
NK120(e)001:7304: bsgyur ba'am / ma bsgyur ba chags bral gyi rnam
NK120(e)001:7305: pa ci rigs pas rgyud sde mang du gsungs pa
NK120(e)001:7306: bsgyur ba'am / ltar yin la / de yang dus
NK120(e)001:7307: 'khor ba rnams ni sngar bstan pa'i rgyud sde rnams
NK120(e)001:7308: ston pas zhing 'dir theg gsum bstan pa'i phyis nas
NK120(e)001:7309: dpyid 'bring nag pa'i nya la dpal ldan 'brasa spungsa
NK120(e)001:7310: kyi mchod rten du 'og tu chos dbyings gsungs dbang
NK120(e)001:7311: bsgyur ba'am / ltar yin la / dang / steng
NK120(e)001:7312: du dpal ldan rgyu skar gyi dkyil 'khor sprul te
NK120(e)001:7313: 'dus pa'i 'khor la dbang bskur nas rnal 'byor dang
NK120(e)001:7314: rnal 'byor ma'i rgyud sde mtha' dag bstan pa dang
NK120(e)001:7315: bsgyur ba'am / ltar yin la / dang / /
NK120(e)001:7316: gzhan yang chags bral gyi rnam pas bya spyod kyi
NK120(e)001:7318: o rgyan gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu ti la gsang ba 'dus pa'i rgyud dang /
NK120(e)001:7319: rdo rje snying po la kyee rdor gyi rgyud sogs
NK120(e)001:7320: de dang de'i dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo'i skur bzhengs
NK120(e)001:7321: nas gsungs pa sogas sngar 'og min du gsungs pa
NK120(e)001:7322: so so'i gnas su slar yang bzlasa te bstan pa'ang
NK120(e)001:7324: gnyis pa de ltar byung ba'i bstan pa bsdus nas bshad sgrub kyis ji ltar bzung tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:7325: phyag rdor dang ni zhu ba'i 'khor gyis bsdus //
NK120(e)001:7326: grub chen brgyad sogs rgya bod mkhas pas bkral //
NK120(e)001:7328: de yang bka' bsdu sogs kyis bstan pa spel ba'i
NK120(e)001:7329: tshul ni ri rab kyi byang shar lcang lo can
NK120(e)001:7330: gyi pho brang du byang chub sems dpa' bye ba
NK120(e)001:7331: phrag dgu bcu rtsa drug 'dus pa la phyag rdora
NK120(e)001:7332: gyis bka' bsdu ba'i tshul du rgyud sde ma lus
NK120(e)001:7334: dus 'khor rtsa rgyud zla ba bzang pos dang /
NK120(e)001:7335: brtag gnyis rdo rje snying pos dang /
NK120(e)001:7336: rdo rje mkhas 'gro phag mos bsdus pa sogs zhu ba po'i 'khor gyis bsdus pa'ang yod la /
NK120(e)001:7337: de ston pa dang sdud pa po tha dad du snang yang don la tha dad med de /
NK120(e)001:7339: rgyud 'chad pa de thugs rdo rje //
NK120(e)001:7340: 'chad pa po de sdud pa'ang de //
NK120(e)001:7342: 'o na mdo sde gdams ngag 'bogs pa'i rgyal po las /
NK120(e)001:7343: 'dren pa'i theg pa gsum po dag /
NK120(e)001:7344: bcom ldan nges par gsungs lags na //
NK120(e)001:7345: rgyu 'bras lhun grub tu spyod cing //
NK120(e)001:7346: sangs rgyas gzhan nas mi 'tshol ba'i //
NK120(e)001:7347: nges pa'i theg pa cis ma gsungs //
NK120(e)001:7349: rgyu la mos pa rgyu chos kyi //
NK120(e)001:7350: 'khor lo rab tu bskor byas nas //
NK120(e)001:7351: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam zhig /
NK120(e)001:7354: lung bstan pa tsam las dngos su ma gsungs pa ma yin nam zhe na /
NK120(e)001:7355: de ni re zhig gsang sngags kyi sgra mi yul
NK120(e)001:7356: du khyab brdal du ma grags pa tsam la bshad
NK120(e)001:7357: kyi gtan nas ma gsungs pa ni ma yin te
NK120(e)001:7358: sngar bshad pa dag gis kyang shes la /
NK120(e)001:7359: phyis 'byung bar lung bstan pa ni yongs su grags pa la dgongs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7360: de yang snga 'gyur ba rnams ltar na rgyud sde dang /
NK120(e)001:7361: sgrub sde gnyis su dbye ba las /
NK120(e)001:7362: rgyud sde rnams mi yul du dar tshul ni //
NK120(e)001:7364: nga ni 'di nas mi snang nas //
NK120(e)001:7365: lo ni brgyad dang bcu gnyis na //
NK120(e)001:7366: lha gnas gsum du grags pa yi //
NK120(e)001:7367: bstan pa'i snying po dam pa zhig /'dzam gling shar gyi phyogs mtshams kyi //
NK120(e)001:7368: mi las skal ldan rigs can te //
NK120(e)001:7369: rgyal po dzahzhesa bya ba la //
NK120(e)001:7370: sngon du ltas snang snang gyur te //
NK120(e)001:7371: drag shul can zhes bya ba'i rtser //
NK120(e)001:7372: grogs kyi sems dpa' dman pa'i lus //
NK120(e)001:7373: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs la //
NK120(e)001:7374: lag na rdo rjes snang bar 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:7375: zhes pa ltar thub pa'i dbang po mya ngan las
NK120(e)001:7376: 'das nas lo nyi shu rtsa brgyad na dam pa'i
NK120(e)001:7377: rigs can lha grags ldan mchog skyong /
NK120(e)001:7380: srin po blo gros thabs ldan /
NK120(e)001:7381: mi'i rig 'dzin li tsa b+ai dri ma med par
NK120(e)001:7382: grags pa ste d+r+wa ma lnga po lang+ka'i yul gyi
NK120(e)001:7383: ri ma la ya'i rtser rang rang gi mngon shes
NK120(e)001:7384: dang rdzu 'phrul gyis 'dus te gdung tshig nyer gsum
NK120(e)001:7385: bton pas / gsang bdag mngon sum du byon nas
NK120(e)001:7386: rigs can d+r+wa ma lnga sogs rig 'dzin 'dus pa
NK120(e)001:7387: phal mo che la sngon 'og min dang /
NK120(e)001:7389: sum cu rtsa gsum rnams su grags pa'i gsang ba'i theg pa nyid ston par mdzad cing /
NK120(e)001:7390: de rnams srin po blo gros thabs ldan gyi gser
NK120(e)001:7391: gyi glegs bam la bee d+aur+ya'i zhun mas bris nas
NK120(e)001:7392: dgongs pa'i rtsal bdun gyis nam mkha' la sbas so
NK120(e)001:7393: // de'i tshe de'i byin rlabs kyis sa ho ra'i
NK120(e)001:7394: rgyal po dzahl rmis ltas ngo mtshar ba bdun rmis
NK120(e)001:7395: pa la brten nas sgrub pa mdzad pas /
NK120(e)001:7396: rmi ltas dang mthun par rgyud sde'i glegs bam rnams mi yul du dngos su babs te /
NK120(e)001:7397: ma h+aa yo ga'i rgyud sde'i glegs bam rnams pho brang gi steng du babs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7398: kri ya'i rgyud rnams w+aa ra n+aa si /
NK120(e)001:7399: yo ga rnams me ri 'bar ba'i rtse mor /
NK120(e)001:7400: a nu yo ga rnams lang+ka'i yul du grags pa
NK120(e)001:7401: sing+ga la'i gling gi nags tshal du babs pa nas
NK120(e)001:7402: rgya bal bru sha'i yul rnams la rim gyis dar
NK120(e)001:7403: ba las / phyis su yul de dag gi lo
NK120(e)001:7404: pan las gnubs chen gyis gsan te bod du dar
NK120(e)001:7405: ba las / ro // a ti yo ga rnams
NK120(e)001:7406: ni nub phyogs o di ya na'i yul du slob
NK120(e)001:7407: dpon dga' rab rdo rjes rdo rje sems dapa'am phyag
NK120(e)001:7408: na rdo rje las dngos su gsan pa ltar bsdu
NK120(e)001:7409: bar mdzad de glegs bam la bkod de 'jam dpal
NK120(e)001:7412: des o rgyan sangs rgyas gnyis pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7413: pan chen bi ma la mi tra /
NK120(e)001:7414: lo chen bee ro tsa na gsum la gnang ba las rgya cher 'phel lo //
NK120(e)001:7415: sgrub sde rnams ni sngon 'og min gsang ba mchog
NK120(e)001:7416: gi gnas su che mchog he ru kas chos nyid
NK120(e)001:7417: kyi rang sgras gsungs pa gsang bdag rdo rje chos
NK120(e)001:7418: kyis rang nyid tshom bu dgu yi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK120(e)001:7419: nang du snang bar mdzad nas thog mar ngag tu
NK120(e)001:7420: bsdus / de nas glegs bam du bkod cing /
NK120(e)001:7421: de'i dgongs 'grel du lung lnga thugs rje dpyangs thag gnas kyi lung /
NK120(e)001:7422: mdzad pa cho 'phrul lha yi lung /
NK120(e)001:7423: phrin las mthar phyin sgrub pa'i lung /
NK120(e)001:7424: gsang sngags nges pa don gyi lung /
NK120(e)001:7425: gsang ba sgo 'byed sgron ma'i lung /
NK120(e)001:7428: re zhig mi'i yul du bstan pa'i yul ma gzigs
NK120(e)001:7429: nas mkha' 'gro ma las kyi dbang mo che la
NK120(e)001:7430: gtad / des sgrub pa bka' brgyad kyi spyi rgyud
NK120(e)001:7431: lnga sgos rgyud bcu rnams rin chen sna brgyad kyi
NK120(e)001:7432: gtad / sgrom bur bcug / sgos rgyud rnams rin
NK120(e)001:7433: po che tha dad pa'i sgrom bur bcug nas dur
NK120(e)001:7434: khrod bsil ba'i tshal gyi mchod rten bde byed brtsegs
NK120(e)001:7435: pa'i tshal du mi snang bar rgyas btab /
NK120(e)001:7436: dus phyis grub pa'i slob dpon brgyad kyis mngon shes
NK120(e)001:7437: kyis mkhyen nas gnas der 'dus shing dgongs pa ting
NK120(e)001:7438: nge 'dzin gyi mthus bskul bas mkha' 'gro ma las
NK120(e)001:7439: kyi dbang mo che mngon sum du byon nas sgrom
NK120(e)001:7441: che mchog gi bse sgrom bi ma la /
NK120(e)001:7442: yang dag gi dngul sgrom h'u ka ra /
NK120(e)001:7443: gshin rje'i lcags sgrom 'jam dpal bshes gnyen /
NK120(e)001:7444: rta mgrin gyi zangs sgrom n+aa ga rdzu na /
NK120(e)001:7445: phur pa'i g.yu sgrom pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK120(e)001:7446: ma mo'i bse sgrom d+ha na sam skri ta /
NK120(e)001:7447: mchod bstod kyi mchong sgrom ram bu gu h+ya /
NK120(e)001:7448: drag sngags kyi gzi sgrom sh+ain+tam gar+b+ha rnams la so
NK120(e)001:7449: sor gtad pa bzhin rang rang la bka' babs pa'i
NK120(e)001:7450: don la mkhas shing sngags kyi dngos grub brnyes par
NK120(e)001:7451: gyur / rin po che sna brgyad kyi sgrom bu
NK120(e)001:7452: las bde gshegs 'dus pa'i tshom bu gcig tu 'dus
NK120(e)001:7453: pa'i rgyu dang man ngag gi bka' rnams byung ba
NK120(e)001:7454: skabs der rgya ma 'khrol bas slar de nyid du
NK120(e)001:7455: gyur / sbas shing / phyis su kun 'dus rig
NK120(e)001:7456: 'dzin slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam+b+ha wa la bka'
NK120(e)001:7457: babs pa bzhin bod du las can rje 'bangs snying
NK120(e)001:7458: gi bu dgu rnams thog mar dbang gis smin par
NK120(e)001:7459: mdzad nas gdams pa yongs rdzogs legs par stsal zhing
NK120(e)001:7460: gyur / sbas shing / / gzhan yang skal ldan
NK120(e)001:7461: 'bangs rigs nyer lnga sogs la'ang ci rigs par stsal
NK120(e)001:7462: gyur / sbas shing / / / dpe rgyun rnams
NK120(e)001:7463: zab mo'i gter du gtams pa bstan zhabs gter gyis
NK120(e)001:7464: skyong ba'i thugs bskyed bla na med par go zhing
NK120(e)001:7466: rgyud sde dang sgrub sde'i skor sogsa la rgya boda
NK120(e)001:7467: kyi makhasa pa dang dngos grub brnyes pa'i slob dpon
NK120(e)001:7468: rnams kyis so so'i dgongs pa ma nor bar bkrala
NK120(e)001:7469: zhing spel bar mdzad pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:7470: gsum pa de ltar bzung ba'i brjod bya skabs don gtan la dbab pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:7473: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7474: snga 'gyur ring lugs bka' gter grags pa dang //
NK120(e)001:7475: gsar ma'i bzhed srol dpag tu med na yang //
NK120(e)001:7476: rgyud sde spyi yi dam tshig 'dir 'chad do //
NK120(e)001:7478: de ltar gsang sngags snga 'gyur ba rnams kyi ringa lugsa la /
NK120(e)001:7480: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar gtad //
NK120(e)001:7481: rgyal ba sems dpa' rnal 'byor pa //
NK120(e)001:7482: gang la thug gi bar du'o //
NK120(e)001:7486: gnyis ka'i thun mong gi brgyud khungs rgyal ba dgongs brgyud /
NK120(e)001:7488: gang zag snyan brgyud gsum po'i steng du /
NK120(e)001:7489: gter ma'i phyogs su bka' babs lung bstan /
NK120(e)001:7491: mkha' 'gro gtad rgya ste de gsum bsnan pas brgyud
NK120(e)001:7492: tshul drug gi sgo nas bzung ba'i tshul sogs yongs
NK120(e)001:7494: phyi 'gyur gasra ma ba'i bzheda srola la o rgyan
NK120(e)001:7495: gyi rgyal po in+d+ra b+hu tis rgyud rnams glegs bam
NK120(e)001:7496: du byas shing yul de'i skye bo thams cad la
NK120(e)001:7497: bstan pas yul de'i srog chags phra mo yan chad
NK120(e)001:7498: kyis dngos grub thob ste 'ja' lus su song /
NK120(e)001:7499: slar yul de mtshor gyur pa klu rnams kyis gang ba na /
NK120(e)001:7500: phyag rdor gyis klu rnams smin par mdzad pas /
NK120(e)001:7501: de dag kyang rim gyis mir gyur nas mtsho 'gram
NK120(e)001:7502: du grong bcas te nyams su blangs pas thams cad
NK120(e)001:7504: bu dang bu mo rnams mkha' 'gro dang mkha' 'gro
NK120(e)001:7505: mar gyur pas o rgyan mkha' 'gro'i gling zhes grags
NK120(e)001:7506: / mtsho de'ang skam ste he ru ka'i lha khang
NK120(e)001:7507: rang byung bas de'i dkor mdzod du rgyud sde thams
NK120(e)001:7508: cad kyi glegs bam bzhugs pa las /
NK120(e)001:7509: phyis rgyal po bi pu ka wa /
NK120(e)001:7514: grub chen te lo pa sogs nas rim gyis spyan drangs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7515: de bzhin du sham+b+ha la sogs yul gzhan dag nas kyang spyan drangs pa bcas /
NK120(e)001:7516: de dag kyang grub chen brgyad dang grub thob brgyad
NK120(e)001:7517: cu sogs mkhas grub mang pos don la rton pa'i
NK120(e)001:7518: dgongs 'grel gyis bkral zhing bshad sgrub kyis bzung tshul
NK120(e)001:7519: sogs lo rgyus rnam gzhag dapaga tu med pa zhig
NK120(e)001:7520: yod na yanga / 'di dag gi byung tshul zhib
NK120(e)001:7521: tu rtogs par 'dod na gzhan las shes par bya
NK120(e)001:7522: yod na yanga / zhing / 'dir skabs su babs pa phyi rgyud rnams phyogs tsam dang /
NK120(e)001:7523: nang rgyud yo ga sde gsum spyi yi dam tshiga
NK120(e)001:7524: rnams zab don nyams su len pa'i skal pa can
NK120(e)001:7525: gyi phyir bsrung bya'i rnam grangs zhib tu bstan par
NK120(e)001:7526: bzhed nas skabs 'dira de 'achada par mdzad do //
NK120(e)001:7527: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bdun /
NK120(e)001:7530: ma thob pa thob par byed pa /
