NK120(e)001:7531: thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba /
NK120(e)001:7534: bsrung ba'i phan yon bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7535: dang po sngags sdom gyi ngo bo ni /
NK120(e)001:7536: ngo bo sgo gsum thabs shes kyis zin par //
NK120(e)001:7537: sdom pa'i tshul khrims so so'i ring lugs bzhin //
NK120(e)001:7539: de la sngags sdom gyi ngo bo gang zhe na /
NK120(e)001:7540: bsdam bya sgo gsuma phra ba'i bag chags mtshan 'dzin gyi rtog pa dang bcas pa /
NK120(e)001:7541: sdom byed thabas shesa khyad par can rnams kyis zina
NK120(e)001:7542: pa'i bde ba chen po'i ye shes kyis bsdoma par
NK120(e)001:7543: byas pa'i sems dpa' sa bon dang bcas pa gang
NK120(e)001:7544: zhig rang rgyud dbang bskur ba las gsar du thob
NK120(e)001:7546: de yang bltas pa'i bde ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7549: gnyis sbyor gyi bde ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7550: de dag par byed pa'i ye shes rang rgyud la
NK120(e)001:7551: 'dzin pa'i khyad par ni rgyud sde bzhi po so
NK120(e)001:7553: gnyis pa dbye ba la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:7554: rgyud sde bzhi'i lugs spyir dbye ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7555: bla med kyi lugs bye brag tu dbye ba'o //
NK120(e)001:7556: dang po rgyud sde bzhi'i lugs spyir dbye ba ni /
NK120(e)001:7557: dbye ba bya spyod rnal 'byor bla med bzhir //
NK120(e)001:7558: rtsa ltung bcu bzhi so sor grangs nges par //
NK120(e)001:7559: dus kyi 'khor lor bshad pas gzhan du blta //
NK120(e)001:7561: de la dbye ba byas na bya spyod rnal 'byor
NK120(e)001:7562: bla meda kyi rgyud bzhira rtsa ltung bcu bzhi so
NK120(e)001:7563: sora grangsa ngesa para dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor lo'i
NK120(e)001:7564: 'grel para bashada pasa gzhan du blta zhes zhal 'phangs
NK120(e)001:7565: pa ste / 'dir ming tsam smos na /
NK120(e)001:7567: dkon mchog la dad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7570: bla ma dang mched la gus pa /
NK120(e)001:7571: 'das ma 'das kyi lha gzhan la mi sdang ba /
NK120(e)001:7572: rang gi lha dus dus su mchod pa /
NK120(e)001:7574: glo bur ba'i mgron mchod pa /
NK120(e)001:7576: sems can gyi don la brtson pa /
NK120(e)001:7578: dam tshig gzhan yang ci nus bsrungs pa /
NK120(e)001:7579: snod min la sngags rgya mi sbyin pa /
NK120(e)001:7580: rang gi sngags rgyud srung zhing de'i don rtogs par byed pa rnams te /
NK120(e)001:7581: de dag bzlog na rtsa ltung du 'gyur ba yin no //
NK120(e)001:7585: de la rtsa ba bzhi ni dam pa'i chos spong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7586: byang chub kyi sems spong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7587: ser snas mi sbyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7588: sems can la gnod pa bya ba'o //
NK120(e)001:7589: rnal 'byor rgyud la rigs lnga'i sdom bzung ltar /
NK120(e)001:7590: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la skyabs gsum 'dzin pa ste gsum /
NK120(e)001:7591: rdo rje'i rigs la rdor dril phyag rgya slob dpon bzung ba bzhi /
NK120(e)001:7592: rin chen rigs la sbyin pa rnam bzhi gtong ba bzhi /
NK120(e)001:7593: pad+ma'i rigs la dam chos ma lus 'dzin pa ste gcig /
NK120(e)001:7594: las rigs la sngar gyi sdom pa rnams 'dzin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7595: mchod pa'i las la 'bad pa ste gnyis bcas bcu bzhi bsgrub pa'i bslab bya dang /
NK120(e)001:7596: de las bzlog pa rtsa ltung bcu bzhi'o //
NK120(e)001:7597: bla med kyi rtsa ltung ni 'chad par 'gyur bas shes so //
NK120(e)001:7598: gnyis pa bla med kyi lugs bye brag tu dbye ba ni /
NK120(e)001:7599: bla med lugs la brtul zhugs nyi shu lnga //
NK120(e)001:7600: rigs lnga'i sdom pa rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang //
NK120(e)001:7601: sbom po dang ni rdzogs pa chen po'i srol //
NK120(e)001:7603: 'dir gtso bo bla med kyi lugsa kyi sdom pa
NK120(e)001:7604: bshad pa la brtul zhugsa nyi shu rtsa lnga thun
NK120(e)001:7605: mong dang / khyad par rigas lnga'i sdom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7606: rgyud sde spyi la grags pa'i rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:7607: de'i yan lag sbom po'i brgyad dang ni rdzogas pa
NK120(e)001:7608: chen po'i srola gyi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi
NK120(e)001:7609: dam tshig rnams te rim bzhin 'chad par 'gyur ro
NK120(e)001:7610: // gsum pa sngags sdom ma thob pa thob par byed pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:7613: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7614: dang po ma thob thob pa'i tshul bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:7616: 'dir cung zad zhib tu smos na /
NK120(e)001:7617: de'ang nang gses su dang po ma thoba pa la gsar du bskur ba ni rgyu'i dbang yin la /
NK120(e)001:7618: de nas bla mas bskur ba dang rang gis bdag
NK120(e)001:7619: 'jug len pa sogs la lam dbang zhes bya zhing
NK120(e)001:7620: / rgyun mthar longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i dbang bskur
NK120(e)001:7621: bas bag chags phra ba dag nas ston 'khor dbyer
NK120(e)001:7622: med du gyur pa ni 'bras bu'i dbang yin pas
NK120(e)001:7623: na rgyu lam gnyis kyi dbang ji ltar thoba pa'i
NK120(e)001:7624: tshul bashada pa ni 'di lta ste zhes so //
NK120(e)001:7625: 'di las 'phros pa dbang bskur ba po rdo rje slob dpon ni /
NK120(e)001:7627: brtan zhing dul la g.yo sgyu med //
NK120(e)001:7628: gsang sngags rgyud kyi sbyor ba shes //
NK120(e)001:7629: dkyil 'khor bri ba'i las la mkhas //
NK120(e)001:7630: de nyid bcu ni yongs shes shing //
NK120(e)001:7631: sems can rnams la mi 'jigs sbyin //
NK120(e)001:7632: theg pa che la rtag dga' ba //
NK120(e)001:7633: de ni slob dpon yin par gsungs //
NK120(e)001:7635: rdo rje snying po rgyan gyi rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:7636: phyir bzlog gnyis kyi cho ga dang //
NK120(e)001:7637: gsang dang shes rab ye shes dang //
NK120(e)001:7638: kha sbyor 'byed pa'i cho ga dang //
NK120(e)001:7639: gtor ma rdo rje'i bzlas pa dang //
NK120(e)001:7640: drag shul sgrub pa'i cho ga dang //
NK120(e)001:7641: rab tu gnas dang dkyil 'khor sgrub //
NK120(e)001:7642: gsang ba'i de nyid bcu yin no //
NK120(e)001:7644: stangs stabs 'dug stangs bzlas brjod dang //
NK120(e)001:7645: sbyin sreg mchod pa las sbyor dang //
NK120(e)001:7646: slar yang sdud pa'i rnam pa ni //
NK120(e)001:7647: phyi yi de nyid bcu yin no //
NK120(e)001:7648: zhes pa la sogs pa rgyud las gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid dang ldan pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7649: gtso bo rang gi bla ma rdo rje slob dpon
NK120(e)001:7650: la mchog tu gus pas dam tshig la nyams skyon
NK120(e)001:7651: med pa dang / gdul bya blos mi gtong ba'i byams snying sems bskyed che zhing /
NK120(e)001:7652: bstan pa'i rgyud yal bar mi dor ba'i lhag bsam
NK120(e)001:7653: nus shugs dang ldan pa ni dbang bskur ba po
NK120(e)001:7654: slob dpon gyi mtshan nyid yid la /
NK120(e)001:7655: des gang la dbang bskur ba'i yul slob ma ni /
NK120(e)001:7657: dad brtson shes rab gtong phod che //
NK120(e)001:7658: sgom sgrub dam tshig la yid rton //
NK120(e)001:7659: sgrub dang sgom la dga' ba dang //
NK120(e)001:7660: rtag tu bla ma la gus shing //
NK120(e)001:7661: dus gsum bla ma mchod byed pa //
NK120(e)001:7662: yon tan dang ldan slob ma yin //
NK120(e)001:7663: zhes sogs kyi mtshan nyid tshang ba'i slob ma la /
NK120(e)001:7664: ji ltar bskur ba'i tshul mthong brgyud kyis gtan la
NK120(e)001:7665: phab pa'i don bzhin ma nor ma 'khrugs par bskur
NK120(e)001:7666: bar bya'o // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:7672: dang po dkyil 'khor gyi rnam gzhag ni //
NK120(e)001:7673: rdul tshon dang ni de bzhin b+ha ga dang /
NK120(e)001:7674: kun rdzob don dam byang sems dkyil 'khor bzhir //
NK120(e)001:7676: dbang dang po bum dbang ni phyi mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor la bsten dgos pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:7679: blo tha ma la rdul tshona gyi dkyil 'khor lhag
NK120(e)001:7680: pa'i lha gang yin gyi gzhung dang mthun pa dang
NK120(e)001:7681: ni de bzhina khyad par dbang gnyis pa la sngags
NK120(e)001:7682: kyi de kho na nyid yi ge b+ha ga'i dang
NK120(e)001:7683: / dbang gsum pa la lha'i de kho na nyid kun rdzob byang chub sems kyi dang /
NK120(e)001:7684: dbang bzhi pa la ye shes kyi de kho na
NK120(e)001:7685: nyid dona dama byang chub semas snying po ye shes
NK120(e)001:7686: rlung gi dkyil 'khor te de bzhira brten nas dbang
NK120(e)001:7687: bskur bar bya'o // gnyis pa ji ltar bskur ba'i dbang bzhi'i rnam gzhag ni /
NK120(e)001:7688: bum pa gsang ba shes rab bzhi pa'i dbang //
NK120(e)001:7689: mtshan nyid ldan pa'i slob bur rim par bskur //
NK120(e)001:7695: slob ma sta gon sogs sngon du song nas /
NK120(e)001:7696: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas slob ma snod
NK120(e)001:7697: du rung bar bya ba'i phyir dkyil 'khor du 'jug
NK120(e)001:7698: par byas nas dam tshig dang sdom pa 'dzin du
NK120(e)001:7699: bcug la / de nas dbang dngos gzhi bskur ba
NK120(e)001:7700: ni slob dpon sku rdo rje sprul sku'i ngo bo
NK120(e)001:7701: dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang gnyis su med par bzhugs
NK120(e)001:7702: la de las sprul pa'i lha dang rang bzhin gyi
NK120(e)001:7703: gnas nas spyan drangs pa'i lha ste de thams cad
NK120(e)001:7704: kyang gdan gsum tshang ba'i rnam par bzhugs pa rnams
NK120(e)001:7705: bcug la / kyis / slob ma dbang rdzas dang
NK120(e)001:7706: bcas pa lhar bskyed de ye shes pa bcug la
NK120(e)001:7707: dbang rdzas kyi lha rnams 'od du zhu nas dbang
NK120(e)001:7708: rdzas so so'i rnam par gyur pa thogs te rig
NK120(e)001:7710: thabs rdo rje rtul zhugs kyi dbang ste slob ma'i dbang drug dang /
NK120(e)001:7711: thabs byung rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang ste bum pa'i dbang dngos gzhi bdun dang /
NK120(e)001:7712: de'i yan lag mtha' rten dang bcas pa bskur bas
NK120(e)001:7713: snang stong gnyis su med pa'i ye shes nyams su
NK120(e)001:7714: myong ba dang / slob dpon gsung rdo rje longs
NK120(e)001:7715: spyod rdzogs sku'i ngo bor yab yum snyoms par zhugs
NK120(e)001:7716: te sangs rgyas thams cad spyan drangs pa bstims nas
NK120(e)001:7717: rjes chags kyis zhu ba bdud rtsi byang chub kyi
NK120(e)001:7718: sems dkar dmar gyi ngo bo gsang dkyil du gnas
NK120(e)001:7719: pa de gsang rtse gnyis gang rung nas slob bus
NK120(e)001:7720: myong ba dang / len pa'am / ma nus na
NK120(e)001:7721: me long yu ba can gyis blangs te bdud rtsi
NK120(e)001:7722: dang sbyar nas slob ma'i lce la bzhag pa snying
NK120(e)001:7723: gar bstims te gasnga ba'i dbang bskur bas gsal stong
NK120(e)001:7724: brjod bral gyi ye shes nyams su myong ba dang
NK120(e)001:7725: myong ba dang / len pa'am / / rdo rje
NK120(e)001:7726: slob dpon thugs rdo rje chos kyi sku'i ngo bor
NK120(e)001:7727: bzhugs te slob ma yab yum snyoms par zhugs pa
NK120(e)001:7728: la brten nas shesa raba ye shes kyi dbang bskur
NK120(e)001:7729: ba ni ye shes pa bstims nas yas bab dga'
NK120(e)001:7730: bzhi'i 'gros kyis phyin pa rdo rje nor bu'i bum
NK120(e)001:7731: par 'dzag med du bzung bas bde stong gnyis su
NK120(e)001:7732: med pa'i ye shes nyams su myong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7733: slob dpon ye shes rdo rje ngo bo nyid sku'i
NK120(e)001:7734: ngo bor bzhugs la gsum pa'i dus kyi dga' bzhi
NK120(e)001:7735: rdzogs nas thabs kyis ldog pa las mas brtan gyi
NK120(e)001:7736: dga' ba bcu drug mthar phyin pa'i tshe lhan cig
NK120(e)001:7737: skyes pa'i ye shes nyams su myong ba ni bzhi
NK120(e)001:7739: de la yang tshig tsam gyis ye shes ngo sprod pa tshig gi dang /
NK120(e)001:7740: bde ba chen po'i ye shes mchog gi ting nge 'dzin rgyud la skyes pa don gyi dang /
NK120(e)001:7741: las rgya la brten nas nyams myong 'dren pa rten can gyi dang /
NK120(e)001:7742: de goms par byed pa lam gyi dang /
NK120(e)001:7743: de mthar phyin pa 'bras bu'i bzhi pa ste lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:7744: gang la bskur na rang don nus pa'i dad pa can dang /
NK120(e)001:7745: gzhan don nus pa'i brtson 'grus can dang /
NK120(e)001:7746: bdud rtsi lnga sogs dam tshig gi rdzas khyad par
NK120(e)001:7747: can la spong len med par spyod nus shing rang
NK120(e)001:7748: byin gyi rlob pa'i lam bsgom nus pa'i brtul zhugs
NK120(e)001:7749: can dang / rtsa thig rlung gsum las su rung
NK120(e)001:7750: nas phyag rgya brten nus pa rig ma'i brtul zhugs
NK120(e)001:7751: can dang / can dang / dbyer med blang dor
NK120(e)001:7752: dang bral bar 'jog nus pa'i mnyam pa'i brtul zhug
NK120(e)001:7753: can te matshana nyid dang ldana pa'i slob bur dbang
NK120(e)001:7754: bzhi po go rim ma 'chol bar dum bu'i lugs
NK120(e)001:7755: sam mthar chags kyi lugs gang rung gis rima para
NK120(e)001:7758: dad brtson brtul zhugs rab rtogs na //
NK120(e)001:7759: phan pa'i dbang sbyin nus pa'i dbang //
NK120(e)001:7760: rim pa bzhin du sbyin par bya //
NK120(e)001:7761: snying rjes chud ma zos par bzung //
NK120(e)001:7763: gsum pa bral thob kyi rnam gzhag ni /
NK120(e)001:7764: sad rmi gnyid 'thug snyoms 'jug gnas skabs bzhis //
NK120(e)001:7765: bskyed pa'i sgo gsum shes bya'i dri ma sbyangs //
NK120(e)001:7766: bskyed rim gtum mo dpe don ye shes gnyis //
NK120(e)001:7767: sgom dang sku bzhi thob pa'i nus rung bya //
NK120(e)001:7769: de ltar dbang bzhi bskur bas rim pa bzhin sada pa'i gnas skabs kyi snang ba rags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7770: rmi lam gyi gnas skabs thig le rlung gis bskyod pa las snang ba phra ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7771: gnyid 'thuga gi gnas skabs ci yang mi rtog pa'i yid kyi thig le kho na dang /
NK120(e)001:7772: snyomsa 'juga gi gnas skabs bde ba'i ngang du rtog tshogs thams cad 'gag pa ste /
NK120(e)001:7773: de ltar gansa skabsa bzhisa bskyed pa'i rags pa lus dang /
NK120(e)001:7775: shin tu phra ba yid de sgo gsuma dang /
NK120(e)001:7776: ches shin tu phra ba kun gzhi tsam ste shes bya'i dri ma rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:7777: gzhan yang rim pa bzhin du phung po'i bdud dang /
NK120(e)001:7780: yul la zhen pa lha'i bu'i bdud rnams bcom ste /
NK120(e)001:7784: shes sgrib phra ba 'pho ba'i bag chags kyi sgrib
NK120(e)001:7785: pa rnams sbyangsa shing dag pa'i nus pa 'jog go
NK120(e)001:7786: // de rnams ni gtso bor sbyangs bya gzhi dang sbyar ba yin la /
NK120(e)001:7787: sbyong byed lam dang sbyar na /
NK120(e)001:7788: bum dbang gis gtso bor bskyed rima dang /
NK120(e)001:7789: gsang dbang gis gtum mo dang /
NK120(e)001:7790: shes dbang gis dpe'i ye shes dang /
NK120(e)001:7791: tshig dbang gis dona gyi ye shesa te /
NK120(e)001:7792: dbang phyi ma gnyis kyis dpe don gyi ye shes gnyis sgom pa la dbang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7797: tshig dbang gis ngo bo nyid sku ste sku bzhi
NK120(e)001:7798: thoba pa'i nus pa rgyud la bzhag pas na mthar
NK120(e)001:7799: thug sku bzhi mngon du 'gyur rung du bya ba
NK120(e)001:7800: yin no // bzhi pa thob mtshams kyi rnam gzhag ni /
NK120(e)001:7801: dang po gnas gsum rdo rje gsum bskyed nas //
NK120(e)001:7802: tha ma dbang bzhi yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshe //
NK120(e)001:7805: de nas sngags sdom thob mtshams ngos bzung ba la /
NK120(e)001:7806: dang po slob ma'i gansa gsuma du rdo rje gsuma
NK120(e)001:7807: gyi lha'am yig 'bru bskyed nasa sgo gsum byin gyis
NK120(e)001:7808: brlabs pa'i dus de nas 'go brtsam ste /
NK120(e)001:7809: dngos gzhi bum pa'i dbang dang mchog dbang gsum bcas rim par bskur zhing thob pa las /
NK120(e)001:7810: tha ma dabnga bzhi yongas su rdzogas pa'i tshe na
NK120(e)001:7811: riga pa 'dzina pa'i sdoma pa mtha' dag thoba zin
NK120(e)001:7812: pa yin cing / de ltar thob ma thag pa
NK120(e)001:7813: nas bslab bya'i gnas rnams la slob pa'i 'du shes
NK120(e)001:7814: bskyed pa la nan tan du bya'o //
NK120(e)001:7815: lnga pa rjes kyi rnam gzhag ni /
NK120(e)001:7817: khas blangs sdom dang dam tshig bslab la 'bad //
NK120(e)001:7819: de ltar snod dang 'tshams par dbang bzhi mtha' rten
NK120(e)001:7820: dang bcas pa bskur thob zin pa de yi rjesa
NK120(e)001:7821: su slob dpon gyis dam tshig gi rnam gzhag rgyas
NK120(e)001:7823: slob mas bsdus te khasa blangsa pas bzung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7824: bzung nas kyang gsang sngags rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdoma
NK120(e)001:7825: pa dang dama tshiga gi tshul la blang dor ma
NK120(e)001:7826: nor bar bslab pa la 'abda par bya dgos so
NK120(e)001:7827: // bzhi pa thob pa mi nyams par bsrung ba la gsum /
NK120(e)001:7831: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7832: bar du mi nyams bsrung ba'i thabs bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:7834: de ltar sngags sdom ma thob pa nyid thob pa tsam kho nas mi chog ste /
NK120(e)001:7835: bar du thob pa'i rgyun de mi nyamsa par bsrung
NK120(e)001:7836: ba'i lhag bsam khyad par can gyis bsrung bar bya
NK120(e)001:7837: dgos la / dam tshig dang sdom pa ni sngags
NK120(e)001:7838: kyi bslab pa ma lus pa'i gzhi rten yin pas
NK120(e)001:7839: dgos la / / de nyams na bslab pa thams cad don med par 'gyur ba'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:7840: dper na srog gi dbang po 'gag na dbang po thams cad 'gag par 'gyur ba bzhin /
NK120(e)001:7841: des na bsrung thabs shes pa la rags las pas na 'dir de'i tshul bashada pa la zhes so //
NK120(e)001:7842: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:7845: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi /
NK120(e)001:7846: yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba /
NK120(e)001:7847: khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7851: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7852: thog ma'i brtul zhugs dus kyi 'khor lo las //
NK120(e)001:7854: thoga mara sngags kyi bslab pa thams cad kyi rten
NK120(e)001:7855: gzhi rdo rje sems dpa'i dam tshig gi yan lag
NK120(e)001:7856: brtul zhugsa nyer lnga po dpal ldan dus kyi 'khor
NK120(e)001:7857: lo lasa gsungs pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:7858: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:7863: mi zhen pa lnga rnams su yod pa las /
NK120(e)001:7864: dang po spang ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:7865: gsod rdzun rku dang 'dod log chang 'thung ba //
NK120(e)001:7866: spang bya bslab pa'i gzhi lnga spang zhes gsungs //
NK120(e)001:7868: srog chags phra mo gcig yan chad gsod par byed pa lta ci /
NK120(e)001:7869: skad cig tsam yang mnar sems kyis 'tshe ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7870: rang 'dod kyis gzhan bslu bsam pa'i rdzuna smra ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7871: dud 'gro bdag tu bzung ba yan chad kyi gzhan nor brku ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7872: gzhan gyi bud med la 'doda pa'i loga par g.yem pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7873: nyes pa bskyed pa'i gzhi changa 'thunga basa myos pa ste /
NK120(e)001:7874: de lnga'i phyogs mthun char gtogs dang bcas pa spang bar bya dgos te /
NK120(e)001:7875: 'khor ba'i gnas su 'ching byed dam po rdo rje'i zhags pa dang mtshungs shing /
NK120(e)001:7876: rang gzhan gyi dge ba thams cad 'joms par byed pas na /
NK120(e)001:7877: 'di rnams brtul zhugs phyi ma thams cad kyi rten
NK120(e)001:7878: gzhi yin pas spang bya bslab pa'i gzhi lnga 'di
NK120(e)001:7879: dag kun spanga zhesa gsungas pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:7880: gnyis pa mi bya ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:7881: cho lo kha na ma tho'i zas za dang //
NK120(e)001:7882: ngan tshig 'byung po lha min chos bslab pa //
NK120(e)001:7883: rnam pa lnga ni bya ba min lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:7885: shwa dang mig mang rgyal blon sogs cho lo rtse ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7886: rang gis bsad pa'i sha ma gtogs las kyis shi
NK120(e)001:7887: ba'i sha mi za ba sogs kha na ma tho'i
NK120(e)001:7889: ngana tshiga gi bstan bcos dmag 'khrug gi lo rgyus sgrung gtam sogs smra ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7890: 'byung po'i chos phyugs kyi mchod sbyin bya ba sogs mu stegs pa'i lugs dang /
NK120(e)001:7891: bya gag gi btung ba 'ba' zhig bsten pa sogs
NK120(e)001:7892: lha mina gyi chosa zhes kla klo'i chos lugs la
NK120(e)001:7893: bslaba pa ste rnama pa lnga ni dge ba'i phyogs
NK120(e)001:7894: nyams par byed pa'i nye ba'i sdig pa lnga zhes
NK120(e)001:7895: grags la bya ba mina pa lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:7896: gsum pa gsod pa lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:7897: ba lang byis pa skyes pa bud med dang //
NK120(e)001:7898: mchod rten bsnun pa gsod pa lnga ru grags //
NK120(e)001:7900: spyir rkang pa dang po'i gsod pa bzhi sngar bshad pa'i gsod pa'i nang du 'du na'ang /
NK120(e)001:7901: mu stegs pa rnams kyis spyir 'tshe ba sdig pa yin kyang /
NK120(e)001:7902: mtho ris kyi ched du mchod sbyin bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7903: ma mo mchod pa dang skyes pa dang bud med thob pa'i ched du rim pa bzhin /
NK120(e)001:7907: bud meda gsod pa la dge bar 'dod pas de
NK120(e)001:7908: dgag pa'i ched du 'dir dmigs kyis bkar nas gsungs
NK120(e)001:7909: pa dang / yang kla klo rnams kyis lha mi'i
NK120(e)001:7910: bla ma gsod pa zhes sku gsung thugs rten mchoda
NK120(e)001:7911: rten la bsnun te bshigs pa bsod nams su 'dod
NK120(e)001:7912: pa de dag la gsoda pa lnga ru gragas pa
NK120(e)001:7914: bzhi pa mi 'khu ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:7915: dge grogs rje bo sangs rgyas dge 'dun dang //
NK120(e)001:7916: bla mar khong khro bsgom rnams 'khu ba lnga //
NK120(e)001:7918: chos dang 'jig rten gang rung gis sbrel ba'i mnyam por dge bar 'grogs pa'i grogas po dang /
NK120(e)001:7919: rang las rgan pa'i rje bo bkur bar 'os pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7920: lha mi'i bla ma sangsa rgyas dang /
NK120(e)001:7922: yid brtan par 'os pa'i mkhan slob bla ma ste
NK120(e)001:7923: yul de dang der khonga khro bsgoma zhing 'khang ba
NK120(e)001:7924: rnams 'khu ba lnga ste spang bar bya'o //
NK120(e)001:7925: lnga pa mi zhen pa lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:7926: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya yul lnga la //
NK120(e)001:7927: mig dang rna ba sna lce lus dbang lngas //
NK120(e)001:7928: zhen par mi byed brtul zhugs nyer lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:7930: de yang gzugas sgra dri ro rega bya ste yul lnga po de la /
NK120(e)001:7931: miga dang rna ba dang sna dang lce dang lus
NK120(e)001:7932: kyi dabnga po ste yul can de la brten pa'i
NK120(e)001:7933: shes pa lngasa zhena cing chags para mi byed de
NK120(e)001:7934: / yang srid 'phen nus kyi las su rdzogs pas na /
NK120(e)001:7935: bskyed rim gyis dbang yul lhar bsgyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:7936: rdzogs rim so sor sdud pa'i rnal 'byor gyis 'jug
NK120(e)001:7937: pa gcod pa sogs dran shes kyi gnyen po bsten
NK120(e)001:7939: de dag la rdo rje sems dpa'i brtul zhugsa nyer lnga zhes bya'o //
NK120(e)001:7940: gnyis pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:7946: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7947: thun mong gyur pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa lnga //
NK120(e)001:7949: 'di rnams rnal 'byor phyi pa'i gzhung du bshad pa las don 'phags kyang sgrar mthun pa 'byung zhing /
NK120(e)001:7950: der ma zad smon 'jug gi sems bskyed dang tshul
NK120(e)001:7951: khrims gsum sogs theg chen spyi'i bslab bya dang 'dra
NK120(e)001:7952: bas thuna monga du gyur pa zhes bya ste /
NK120(e)001:7953: gzhi de las 'dir rdo rje theg pa mchog gi dgongs pa ltar 'chad de /
NK120(e)001:7954: de la rigs bye brag gi rnal 'byor pas kyang rigs lnga ka'i sdom pa bsrung dgos mod kyang /
NK120(e)001:7955: rang rigs gang yin gyi sdom pa gtso bor bslab dgos pas /
NK120(e)001:7956: rigas lnga so so'i sdom pa'am dam tshig lnga zhes grags so //
NK120(e)001:7957: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:7958: smon 'jug gnyis dang tshul khrim sa rnam pa gsum //
NK120(e)001:7959: slob pa sangs rgyas rnal 'byor sdom pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7960: rdor dril phyag rgya bla mar bzung rdo rje //
NK120(e)001:7961: nor chos mi 'jigs byams sbyin rin chen 'byung //
NK120(e)001:7962: phyi nang gsang pa'i theg 'dzin pad+ma'i rigs //
NK120(e)001:7963: mchod gtor las rim 'dzin pa las kyi'o //
NK120(e)001:7965: de rnams rim pa bzhin 'chad pa'i dang po ni /
NK120(e)001:7967: smon pa dang 'juga pa'i sems gnyis bskyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7968: sdom sdud don byed kyi tshul khrimsa rnama pa gsuma
NK120(e)001:7969: po so so'i mtshan nyid tshang bar brtan por bzung
NK120(e)001:7970: zhing / de thams cad kyi rten du thun mong
NK120(e)001:7971: min pa'i mchog gsum la skyabs su 'gro bar slob
NK120(e)001:7972: zhing / pa dang / sbas don ltar na bde
NK120(e)001:7973: stong dbyer med kyi byang sems dang sems nyid gdod
NK120(e)001:7974: nas dag pa mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin du bzung
NK120(e)001:7975: zhing / pa dang / ba'o // de yang sangsa
NK120(e)001:7976: rgyas rnal 'byor te rnam par snang mdzad ni gtso
NK120(e)001:7978: sku ni 'bras chos thams cad kyi rten yin pa
NK120(e)001:7979: ltar tshul khrims ni yon tan kun gyi rten dang
NK120(e)001:7980: / de'i rten ni skyabs 'gro yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:7981: rigs de'i sdom par bzhag pa'o //
NK120(e)001:7983: dngos bstan ltar na phyi mtshan ma rdzas kyi rdor
NK120(e)001:7984: drila bzung nas rang nyid lha sku phyag rgya chen
NK120(e)001:7985: por bskyed nas dag dran bya ba ste /
NK120(e)001:7987: de nyid kyis ni rdo rje bzung //
NK120(e)001:7988: chos kyi dril bu dkrol bar bya //
NK120(e)001:7989: dam tshig gis ni phyag rgya cher //
NK120(e)001:7990: byin gyis brlabs nas snying po bzla //
NK120(e)001:7992: sbas don ltar na nang gi rdo dril ni /
NK120(e)001:7993: thabs yab kyi nor bu rdo rje dang /
NK120(e)001:7994: shes rab yum gyi pad+ma dril bu ste /
NK120(e)001:7995: phyag rgya ni phan tshun rgyas btab nas mnyam par sbyor ba'o //
NK120(e)001:7996: gsang ba khams dkar dmar gnyis 'bar 'dzag gis zung du 'jug pa dang /
NK120(e)001:7997: de kho na nyid mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen dang /
NK120(e)001:7998: rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid dbyer med du bsgom pa ste /
NK120(e)001:7999: de dag zung du 'jug pa'i ye shes ni phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK120(e)001:8000: de dag gi de kho na nyid ston par mdzad
NK120(e)001:8001: pa'i bla ma yang bsnyen bskur la sogs pas yang
NK120(e)001:8002: dag par bzunga zhing brten par bya ba rnams ni
NK120(e)001:8003: rdo rje mi bskyod pa gtso bor thugs kyi rigs
NK120(e)001:8004: yin la thabs shes gnyis med kyi thugs mtshon par
NK120(e)001:8005: byed pa mtshan ma rdzas kyi dang /
NK120(e)001:8006: nang gsang de kho na nyid kyi rdor dril rnams
NK120(e)001:8007: mtshon bya thugs kyi ngo bo yin pas rigs de'i
NK120(e)001:8010: dngos bstan ltar na zang zing nora gyi sbyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8012: mi 'jigas pa skyabs kyi sbyin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8013: de'i rtsa ba byamsa pa chen po'i sbyin pa bzhi
NK120(e)001:8014: po nyin re bzhin dus drug tu bya ba dang
NK120(e)001:8015: / sbas don ltar na rjes chags kyi mes byang
NK120(e)001:8016: sems dbab ldog gi dga' bzhi'i ye shes sbyin pa
NK120(e)001:8017: / ste / de yang rina chena 'byung ldan ni
NK120(e)001:8018: yon tan kun gyi 'byung gnas rin po che'i rigs
NK120(e)001:8019: / ste / yin la / sbyin pa yang dgos
NK120(e)001:8020: 'dod ster ba'i ngo bo yin pas de'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:8021: / ste / yin la / tu bzhag go // bzhi pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8022: dngos bstan ltar na phyi mtshan nyid sde gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:8023: nanga kri yog sde gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:8024: gasnga ba nang rgyud sde gsum po'i thega pa kun gyi tshig don 'dzin zhing /
NK120(e)001:8025: sbas don ltar na rlung dbu mar bcings pas gzho ma med kyi gsung sgrub pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8026: de yang 'od dpag med gsung pad+ma'i rigas yin pa ltar /
NK120(e)001:8027: chos kyang gsung gi ngo bo yin pa'i phyir de'i dam tshig tu bzhag go //
NK120(e)001:8029: dngos bstan ltar na sdom pa de thams cad dang
NK120(e)001:8030: ldan pa'i steng du phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa
NK120(e)001:8032: sbyin sreg sogs lasa bzhi'i rima pa thams cad ci nus su 'dzin par byed cing /
NK120(e)001:8033: sbas don ltar na de thams cad zung 'jug e wam gyi sdom pas rgyas 'debs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8034: zhu bdes phung khams dbang yul gyi lha rnams tshim par mchod pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8035: de yang don yod grub pa ni las thams cad
NK120(e)001:8036: pa'i bdag nyid yin pa ltar 'di dag kyang gtso
NK120(e)001:8037: bo lasa kyi ngo bo yin pas de'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:8038: tu bzhag pa'o // gnyis pa khyad par gyi rigs lnga'i sdom pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8039: khyad par srog gcod rdo rje'i rigs yin te //
NK120(e)001:8040: zhing bcu tshang dang rlung dang rtog pa yin //
NK120(e)001:8041: rin chen rigs la ma byin len pa ni //
NK120(e)001:8042: nor dang bud med theg chen zab mo'i chos //
NK120(e)001:8043: rang dang gzhan don sgrub la dgongs pas sungs //
NK120(e)001:8044: pad+ma'i rigs la las chos dam tshig dang //
NK120(e)001:8045: phyag rgya che ste bud med bsten par gsungs //
NK120(e)001:8046: las kyi rigs la rdzun du smra gsungs pa //
NK120(e)001:8047: bdag dang sems can mi dmigs bden med ston //
NK120(e)001:8048: 'khor lo'i rigs la chang dang sha lnga dang //
NK120(e)001:8049: yul kun bsten gsungs phyi nang gsang ba'i theg /
NK120(e)001:8050: rim par ma nyams spyod pa bla med lugs //
NK120(e)001:8052: thun mong ma yin pa rigs lnga'i sdom pa 'di
NK120(e)001:8053: ni bsad pa gso nus pa sogs rnal 'byor pa
NK120(e)001:8054: rtogs goms kyi gding dang ldan pa /
NK120(e)001:8055: lha dang bla mas gnang ba thob pa /
NK120(e)001:8056: snying rje'i kun slong khyad par can gyis zin pa
NK120(e)001:8057: yin na gzhan don du sgra ji bzhin par spyod
NK120(e)001:8058: pa drang don bskyed rim gyi dam tshig dang /
NK120(e)001:8059: de ltar min na sgra bsgyur te dgongs gzhi'i don
NK120(e)001:8060: de nyid blangs nas dbang gong ma'i dam tshig dang
NK120(e)001:8061: sdom pa rdzogs rim la sbyar bar bya ba yin
NK120(e)001:8062: pas na khyad para zhes bstan te /
NK120(e)001:8063: dang po sroga gcod pa ni zhe sdang rnam par
NK120(e)001:8064: dag pa rdo rje'i rigas mi bskyod pa'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:8065: yina te / drang don ltar na zhing bcu tshanga
NK120(e)001:8066: ba'i dgra bo drag po'i las kho nas ma gtogs
NK120(e)001:8067: 'dul bar mi nus pa rnams kyi las ngan rgyun
NK120(e)001:8068: gcod phyir mngon spyod kyi las kyis sgrol bar bya
NK120(e)001:8069: yina te / ba dang / de yang rang nyid
NK120(e)001:8070: la nyes par mi 'gyur bar ma zad don yang
NK120(e)001:8071: yina te / ba dang / che ste / gsang snying las /
NK120(e)001:8072: yod med dbu ma'ang mi dmigs shing //
NK120(e)001:8073: sgyu ma mig g.yor lta bu'i tshul //
NK120(e)001:8074: srog med srog kyang bcad du med //
NK120(e)001:8075: srog dang skyes bu log rtog tsam //
NK120(e)001:8078: sangs rgyas bstan pa gnod byed dang //
NK120(e)001:8079: bla mar smod brtson ma rung dang //
NK120(e)001:8080: rtag tu sems can gnod brtson pa //
NK120(e)001:8081: mkhas pas bsgrims te bsad par bya //
NK120(e)001:8083: nges pa'i don du srog ni ro rkyang gi rlung yin la /
NK120(e)001:8084: de bcad pa'i thabs kyis bkag pas dbu mar 'dzud cing gtsug tor du brtan pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8085: yang na srog ni rnam par rtog pa dang bcas pa'i sems yina la /
NK120(e)001:8086: de bcad pa ni de'i rgyun skye med kyi dbyings su dag par bya ba'o //
NK120(e)001:8087: gnyis pa nga rgyal rnam par dag pa rina cheena
NK120(e)001:8088: rigas kyi dam tshig la ma byin pa leen par
NK120(e)001:8089: bshad pa ni / drang don ltar na gzhan gyi tshogs rdzogs pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8090: sbyin yul gyi dbul ba sel ba sogs phan par
NK120(e)001:8091: 'gyur na sngags kyi mthus gzhan nora blang ba dang
NK120(e)001:8092: / des mchod sbyin sogs byas na nyes par mi 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:8094: bden pa gnyis ka dbyer med pa //
NK120(e)001:8095: 'phrul dag'i tshul te tha dad min //
NK120(e)001:8096: gzhan dang ma byin med pa'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:8097: blang med thams cad nyid kyi dbyings //
NK120(e)001:8099: nges don du sngags kyi ye shes sgrub phyir pha
NK120(e)001:8100: rol gyi bud meda dgug pa'i thabs kyis 'phrog nas
NK120(e)001:8101: de'i byang sems rlung stobs kyis len pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8102: yang na don dam pa'i btsun mo thega chen gyi dgongs don gtong pa nyid yin la /
NK120(e)001:8103: de'i khu ba zaba mo'i chosa gnyis med kyi ye shes nyid goms stobs kyis blangs te /
NK120(e)001:8104: ranga dang gzhan gyi doon gnyis bsgrub pa la mnga' dbang 'byor ba la dgongas pasa gsungas te /
NK120(e)001:8106: gang phyir theg pa chen po 'di //
NK120(e)001:8107: gang gis kyang ni byin ma lags //
NK120(e)001:8108: de nyid rtogs pas ma byin blangs //
NK120(e)001:8110: gsum pa 'dod chags rnam par dag pa pad+ma'i rigas
NK120(e)001:8111: kyi dam tshig la rtogs goms kyi gding dang ldan
NK120(e)001:8112: pa'i gang zag gis gnyis med du shes pa'i lta
NK120(e)001:8113: ba dang / yab yum lha'i 'du shes /
NK120(e)001:8114: mkha' gsang gnyis rdo rje dang pad+ma'i 'du shes /
NK120(e)001:8115: bde chen ye shes la chos kyi 'du shes te /
NK120(e)001:8116: 'du shes gsum ldan gyi sgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8117: thabs kyi spyod pa gsum gyis zin pas /
NK120(e)001:8118: dngos rig lasa kyi phyag rgya la bsten pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8120: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK120(e)001:8121: chags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK120(e)001:8122: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK120(e)001:8123: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK120(e)001:8125: de bzhin du yid rig chosa kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK120(e)001:8126: gtum mo dama tshiga gi phyag rgya dang gnyis bsten
NK120(e)001:8127: pa ste de gsum gyis zhu bde dpe'i ye shes
NK120(e)001:8128: sgrub pas / drang nges gnyis ka'i cha yod cing /
NK120(e)001:8129: nges don du rnam kun mchog ldan gyi stong nyid
NK120(e)001:8130: dang mi 'gyur ba'i bde chen kha sbyor las bde
NK120(e)001:8131: stong phyag rgya chena po don gyi ye shes sgrub
NK120(e)001:8132: pa ste de dag la bud meda kyi sgras bstan
NK120(e)001:8133: nas bsten para gsungas pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:8134: bzhi pa phrag dog rnam par dag pa lasa kyi
NK120(e)001:8135: rigas kyi dam tshig la rdzun du smra bar gsungas
NK120(e)001:8136: pa ni / drang don du gzhan la phan par 'gyur na rdzun du smra bar bya ste /
NK120(e)001:8138: sems can rnams la phan spyod pa //
NK120(e)001:8139: rtag tu dam tshig bla ma'i nor //
NK120(e)001:8140: sems can srog ni bsrung ba'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:8141: rdzun du yang ni smra bar bya //
NK120(e)001:8143: nges don du sgrol ba po badga dang /
NK120(e)001:8144: bsgral bya semas can gang du'ang mi dmigas pa'i ngang
NK120(e)001:8145: nas sems can thams cad bdena med 'khor ba las
NK120(e)001:8146: bsgral bar bya'o zhes pa'i don ston te /
NK120(e)001:8147: de ltar yang gsang snying las /
NK120(e)001:8148: chos rnams sgyu ma lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:8149: ming dang tshig tu btags pa rdzun //
NK120(e)001:8150: rdzun nyid la ni rdzun spyod pas //
NK120(e)001:8151: rdzun zhes btags tsam yod ma yin //
NK120(e)001:8153: yang na snying ga'i 'khor lor rlung thim pas gzhom
NK120(e)001:8154: med kyi sgra rnam pa thams cad par shar ba
NK120(e)001:8156: de las gzhan snang du sems can rnams la chos
NK120(e)001:8157: sgo sna tshogs pa gcig car du ston pa drang
NK120(e)001:8158: don du gsungs pa'ang yod de /
NK120(e)001:8160: gang gis srog rlung bros pa na //
NK120(e)001:8161: gcig car 'gro kun skad kyis ni //
NK120(e)001:8162: gang dang gang la de dang de //
NK120(e)001:8163: mthun pa'i chos ston rdzun pa'i tshig /
NK120(e)001:8165: lnga pa gti mug rnam par dag pa 'khor lo'i rigas rnam snang gi dam tshig la /
NK120(e)001:8166: drang don du smyos pa'i skyon med na changa btung
NK120(e)001:8167: ba dang rigs kyis dregs shing nga rgyal dang gtsang
NK120(e)001:8168: rme'i rtog pa gzhig pa'i slad du yul dbus su
NK120(e)001:8169: bza' ba'i don du gsod par mi byed pa'i sha
NK120(e)001:8170: lnga gnang ba ltar rang gi las kyis shi ba'i
NK120(e)001:8171: sha rnams dam tshig gi rdzas su bza' ba dang
NK120(e)001:8172: / de bzhin du bdud rtsi lnga dang gzugs sogs
NK120(e)001:8173: yul kuna ci dgar spyod pa'i bde ba bsten par
NK120(e)001:8174: / gsungas pa dang / nges don du sha lnga bza' ba ni dbang lnga'i dwangs ma 'ching ba /
NK120(e)001:8175: chang 'thung ba ni yas babs kyi lhan du skyes zhu bde 'dzag med du 'ching ba /
NK120(e)001:8176: bdud rtsi lnga ni 'byung lnga'i dwangs ma bcings pa
NK120(e)001:8177: las zhu ba'i thig le rdul phra rab kyi tshogs
NK120(e)001:8179: yul ni gshang gci khu ba'i dwangs ma lte bar lugs ldog tu brten pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8180: yang na de dag bsten pa de ni rnam par
NK120(e)001:8181: rtog pa thams cad mnyam pa nyid kyi dbyings su
NK120(e)001:8183: de ltar dam tshig dang sdom pa de rnams kyi go rim yang /
NK120(e)001:8184: thog mar brtul zhugs nyer lnga bstan te de'i lnga
NK120(e)001:8185: tshan dang po sems can la gnod pa shas che
NK120(e)001:8186: ba dang / lnga pa yul la dbang po zhen
NK120(e)001:8187: pa'ang nyon mongs pa skye ba'i rgyu yin pas phyi
NK120(e)001:8188: mtshan nyid dang nanga kri yog sde gsum gyi theg
NK120(e)001:8189: pas kyang don la spang dgos pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:8190: de nas rigs lnga'i dam tshig thun mong ba bstan te /
NK120(e)001:8191: de'i dngos bstan rnams rnal 'byor gyi rgyud kyi dam tshig dang sgra mthun pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:8192: de nas khyad par rigs lnga'i dam tshig bstan te /
NK120(e)001:8193: de'i drang nges gnyis ka gasnga ba bla na med pa'i theg pa'i khyad chos yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:8194: des na gdul bya rnams 'jug pa'i rima pa ma
NK120(e)001:8195: nyamsa pa'i sgo nas bkri zhing spyod pa ni bla
NK120(e)001:8196: meda kyi lugas su shes par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:8197: gsum pa rtsa ba'i ltung ba bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8200: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8201: rtsa ba'i ltung ba bcu bzhi bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8203: rtsa ba'i ltung ba zhes pa /
NK120(e)001:8204: dper na ljon shing rtsa ba dang 'dra ste /
NK120(e)001:8205: brtan na yal ga lo 'dab thams cad rgyas la /
NK120(e)001:8206: nyams na rtsa ba nas 'gyel ba ltar /
NK120(e)001:8207: 'di yang bsrung na lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan thams cad bskyed pa'i rtsa ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8208: nyams na mnar med ya nga ba'i gnas su ltung
NK120(e)001:8209: nas thar pa'i go skabs med par sdug bsngal thams
NK120(e)001:8210: cad kyi rtsa bar yang 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:8211: de la grangs bcu bzhira nges pa rnams bstan pa ni zhes so //
NK120(e)001:8212: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la bcu bzhi las /
NK120(e)001:8213: dang po slob dpon smod pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8214: slob dpon rnam gsum snying nas smod pa dang //
NK120(e)001:8215: brnyas dang thugs dkrugs ltung ba'i sgo kun las //
NK120(e)001:8216: shin tu lci phyir 'di nyid dang por bshad //
NK120(e)001:8218: de la spyir bla ma ru bzung nas dam pa'i
NK120(e)001:8219: chos kyis 'brel phan chad bla slob kyi 'du shes
NK120(e)001:8220: go ma log pa zhig dgos pa gzhir bcas na'ang
NK120(e)001:8221: / 'dir khyad par gyi slob dpona rnam pa gsuma
NK120(e)001:8222: ste bde 'dus zhi ba 'dus pa rtsa ba'i rgyud
NK120(e)001:8223: / las / rgyud dgrol dbang bskur de nyid bstan //
NK120(e)001:8225: rang nyid la dbang bskur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8227: man ngag ston pa'i slob dpon te /
NK120(e)001:8230: gcig ldan gang rung la snying thag pa nasa sma
NK120(e)001:8231: 'bebs par 'dod pas ngag gis 'khu zhing 'phya ba'i
NK120(e)001:8232: sgo nas lkog tu smoda pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8233: dngos su lus ngag gis mi dge ba'i rnam 'gyur bstan nas brnyas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8234: rang nyid kyi bya ba ma yin pa la spyod pa'am /
NK120(e)001:8235: bla ma'i 'khor la 'tshe ba sogs kyis thugsa dkrugsa
NK120(e)001:8236: pa sogs mi mnyes par byas pa de ni ltung
NK120(e)001:8237: ba'i sgo kun lasa kyang shina tu lci ba yin
NK120(e)001:8238: te / rdo rje slob dpon ni sangs rgyas thams
NK120(e)001:8239: cad kyi ngo bo yin pas yul gnyan par ma
NK120(e)001:8240: zad rang nyid kyi lam dang 'bras bu'i yon tan
NK120(e)001:8241: thams cad de nyid mnyes pas rjes su bzung ba
NK120(e)001:8242: la rag las pa'i phyir 'di nyid dang pora bashada
NK120(e)001:8243: te / pas / gal srid 'di las nyams na
NK120(e)001:8244: de nas bzung ste sgom sgrub ci byas pa thams
NK120(e)001:8245: cad ru dra'i rgyu 'ba' zhig pa yin pas shin
NK120(e)001:8246: tu nas kyang gzab par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:8247: gnyis pa bde gshegs bka' 'das ni /
NK120(e)001:8248: blang dor gnas ston bde bar gshegs pa'i bka' //
NK120(e)001:8249: bla mas gsungs shing rang gis go bzhin du //
NK120(e)001:8250: khyad gsod mi mthun spyod 'brel bka' 'das gnyis //
NK120(e)001:8252: gdul bya la blang dora gyi gansa ston pa sde
NK120(e)001:8253: snod gsum dang rgyud sde bzhis bsdus pa bde bar
NK120(e)001:8254: gshegas pa'i bka'a las gsungs pa'i don rnams bla mas
NK120(e)001:8255: gsungas shinga ranga gisa kyang de'i don go bzhina du
NK120(e)001:8256: / khyada du gsoda nas sdom pa gsum gang yang
NK120(e)001:8257: rung ba'i bslab pa dang mi mthuna par spyod pa'am
NK120(e)001:8258: / / de dang 'brela ba gzhan la bstan kyang
NK120(e)001:8259: rung ste bde bar gshegs pa'i bka'a las 'adsa pa
NK120(e)001:8260: yin pas rtsa ltung dang po'i 'og nas 'di nyes
NK120(e)001:8261: pa che bas na gnyisa par bzhag go //
NK120(e)001:8262: gsum pa mched la 'khu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8263: spyi ring nye dang nang 'dres spun la khros //
NK120(e)001:8264: 'khon 'dzin phrag dog brnyas sogs gsum pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8266: spyi'i mched sems can thams cad /
NK120(e)001:8267: ringa ba'i mched sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la zhugs so cog /
NK120(e)001:8268: nye ba'i mched sngags kyi theg par zhugs pa rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:8269: de las kyang khyad par nanga 'dresa pa'i mched bla
NK120(e)001:8270: ma gcig gis bsdus pa pha gcig pa'i spun dang
NK120(e)001:8271: / de'i shugs kyis dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus pa ma gcig pa'i spun dang /
NK120(e)001:8272: gnyis kas bsdus pa pha ma gnyis ka gcig pa'i spun te /
NK120(e)001:8273: de'ang dbang thob pa snga phyi yod na spun rgan gzhon dang /
NK120(e)001:8274: dus mnyam du thob na mtshe ma lta bu yin pas /
NK120(e)001:8275: spun de dag snga ma snga ma las phyi ma
NK120(e)001:8276: phyi ma shin tu nye ba yin pas na spun
NK120(e)001:8277: de rnams la yid kyis khros shing 'khona zhe la
NK120(e)001:8278: 'dzina pa dang / phraga doga gi bsam pas sbyor ba lus ngag gi brnyas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8279: ngag gi tshig rtsub skyon brjod pa la sogas pas de'i sems sun phyung na rtsa ltung gsuma pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8280: de'ang nang 'dres pa'i spun la 'thab pa sogs ni
NK120(e)001:8281: rdo rje'i nang dme yin pas shin tu lci zhing
NK120(e)001:8282: nyes pa sbyong dka' bas gzab par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:8283: bzhi pa byams pa 'dor ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8284: sems can bde ba kun dang bral na bsam //
NK120(e)001:8285: snying nas byams pa btang ba bzhi pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8287: yul semsa can gang yang rung ba gcig gam 'ga' la dmigs nas /
NK120(e)001:8288: 'di bde ba kuna dang brala zhing sdug bsngal dang
NK120(e)001:8289: 'phrad na ci ma rung snyam du khro bo'i bsam
NK120(e)001:8290: pas snying thag pa nasa byamsa pa btang ba ni
NK120(e)001:8292: lnga pa byang sems 'dor ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8293: 'dod chags sems kyis gnas skabs ma yin par //
NK120(e)001:8294: bsam bzhin khu ba 'byin dang sems can la //
NK120(e)001:8295: byang chub sems bskyed btang ba lnga ba yin //
NK120(e)001:8298: gsang ba'i dbang dang gsum pa dang //
NK120(e)001:8299: ro mnyam pa dang lha mchod dang //
NK120(e)001:8300: rigs brgyud spel dang ril bu dang //
NK120(e)001:8301: 'chi ltas brtag pa'i dus yin te //
NK120(e)001:8302: zhes pa ltar 'dod chagas kyi semsa kyis gnang ba'i
NK120(e)001:8303: gansa skabas bdun ma yina para bslab pa khyad gsod
NK120(e)001:8304: kyi mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba la ma dad cing
NK120(e)001:8305: / zhu bde 'gyur med la dgos pa med par
NK120(e)001:8306: bltas nas bsam bzhina du khu ba 'byin pa dang
NK120(e)001:8307: / / spyir bskyed rim pas semsa can la smon
NK120(e)001:8308: pa byang chub kyi semsa bskyed btang pa'am 'jug pa'i
NK120(e)001:8309: rtsa ltung thun mong ba spyad pas 'jug sems btang
NK120(e)001:8310: ba rtsa ltung lnga pa yina no //
NK120(e)001:8311: drug pa grub mtha' smod pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8312: lam 'tshol mu stegs lam zhugs nyan rang dang //
NK120(e)001:8313: lam chen theg chen grub mthar smod na drug /
NK120(e)001:8315: ngan 'gro las thar pa'i thabs kyi lam 'tshola ba mu stegsa kha cig dang /
NK120(e)001:8316: 'khor ba las nges par 'byung ba'i lam la zhugas pa nyan ranga gnyis dang /
NK120(e)001:8317: mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung ba'i lam chen po
NK120(e)001:8318: la zhugs pa thega pa chen po'i grub matha'a la
NK120(e)001:8319: / lam gong ma la drang pa sogsa kyi dgos
NK120(e)001:8320: pa med par sdang sems kyis smod na rtsa ltung
NK120(e)001:8321: / druga pa'o // bdun pa gsang ba sgrog pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8322: snod dang cho ga ma byas ma rdzogs dang //
NK120(e)001:8323: nyams dang zab mos 'jigs lngar gsang sgrog bdun //
NK120(e)001:8325: snod kyis ma smin pa ni log sred can te rgyus ma smin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8326: cho ga ma byas pas ma smin pa ni bum dbang ma thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8327: cho ga ma rdzogas pas ma smin pa ni dbang gong ma gsum ma thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8328: dbang thob kyang rtsa ltung byung bas nyamsa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8329: chos zaba mosa 'jigas pa nyan rang sogs ni rkyen gyis ma smin pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8330: yul lnga po der gsang sngags kyi thun mong ma yin pa'i rdzas dang /
NK120(e)001:8332: zab don gyi gasnga ba sgrogsa pas des kyang go
NK120(e)001:8333: bzhin ma dad pa skyes na rtsa ltung bduna pa'o
NK120(e)001:8334: // brgyad pa phung por smod pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8335: phung lnga sangs rgyas lnga la brnyas pa yis //
NK120(e)001:8336: smod dang gdung ba bskyed na brgyad pa yin //
NK120(e)001:8338: phung po lnga ni sangsa rgyas rigs lnga yin pa
NK120(e)001:8339: ltar dbang dus su ngo sprad nas de 'dod yon
NK120(e)001:8340: gyis mnyes par mchod pas rten bde ba 'phel /
NK120(e)001:8341: des brten pa ye shes mngon du 'gyur ba yin
NK120(e)001:8342: pa la de mi shes pa kun 'byung gi gtsor
NK120(e)001:8343: bor bzung ste ngag gis brnyas pa yisa smod pa
NK120(e)001:8344: dang yan lag gcod pa sogs dang /
NK120(e)001:8345: dka' thub kyis lus la gdunga ba bskyed par byas na rtsa ltung brgyad pa yina no //
NK120(e)001:8346: dgu pa chos la the tshom za ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8347: gzhi lam 'bras bu'i rang bzhin dag pa la //
NK120(e)001:8348: dkri bar the tshom za ba dgu par bshad //
NK120(e)001:8350: gzhi lam 'brasa bu'i chos thams cad ranga bzhina gyis
NK120(e)001:8351: rnam par dag pasa dbyer mi phyed pa'i zung 'jug
NK120(e)001:8352: 'od gsal byang chub kyi sems bde bar gshegs pa'i
NK120(e)001:8353: snying po gdod ma'i gnas lugs su bzhugs par bshad
NK120(e)001:8354: pa ni / lam la dkri bar bya ba'i ched
NK120(e)001:8355: du spro ba bskyed pa tsam las don la de
NK120(e)001:8356: ltar ma yin snyam du the tshoma za basa yid
NK120(e)001:8357: ma ches te ma dad na rtsa ltung dgu para
NK120(e)001:8358: pa ni / bashada do // bcu pa zhing bcu mi sgrol ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8359: bsgral ba'i zhing bcu tshang ba nus bzhin du //
NK120(e)001:8360: mi sgrol ba dang byams par byed na bcu //
NK120(e)001:8362: de'ang spyir bstan pa la gnod pa dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra dang /
NK120(e)001:8363: khyad par rang nyid kyi bla ma'i sku dgra /
NK120(e)001:8364: sngags kyi dam tshig nyams pa gso bar mi byed pa /
NK120(e)001:8365: sngags kyi lta spyod la zhugs nas de la log lta skyes nas spangs pa /
NK120(e)001:8366: bla ma dang mched la zhe sdang zhing 'khu ba /
NK120(e)001:8367: sngags spyod la 'du bar mi dbang bar rku thabs kyis 'du nas nang du 'ong ba /
NK120(e)001:8368: sems can yongs la gnod pa /
NK120(e)001:8369: dam tshig dang ldan pa'i dgrar gyur na /
NK120(e)001:8370: mi dge ba kho nar spyod pa ngan pa'i ngang
NK120(e)001:8371: tshul can te snying rjes bsgral ba'i zhing sdug bsngal
NK120(e)001:8372: gyi rgyu la spyod pa dgu dang /
NK120(e)001:8373: sdug bsngal dngos la spyod pa ngan song gsum gcig tu bsdoms pas bcu ste /
NK120(e)001:8374: de dag gang rung tshanga ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8375: khyad par bla ma dang bstan 'gror 'tshe ba'i gdug
NK120(e)001:8376: pa can de dag mngon spyod kyi las kyis sgrol
NK120(e)001:8377: bar nus bzhina du yal bar dor nas mi sgrol
NK120(e)001:8378: ba dang / log pa'i sred pas mdza' bor byas
NK120(e)001:8379: nas tha mal ba'i byamsa pa dang lus ngag gi
NK120(e)001:8380: spyod lam mthun para byed na rtsa ltung bcu pa'o
NK120(e)001:8381: ba dang / // de dag la yang yid kyi
NK120(e)001:8382: byams pa btang na rtsa ltung bzhi par 'gyur ro
NK120(e)001:8383: ba dang / // // bcu gcig pa chos la tshad mas gzhal ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8384: mig sogs bral la dngos dang dngos med rtog /
NK120(e)001:8385: rtog ges 'jal bar byed na bcu gcig pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8387: minga dang barda'am mtshan ma sogas spros pa'i mtha' thams
NK120(e)001:8388: cad dang brala ba don dam stong pa nyid kyi
NK120(e)001:8389: gnas lugs la dngosa po dang dngosa med kyi mtha'
NK120(e)001:8390: gang rung zhig tu rtog cing zhen nas rtog gesa
NK120(e)001:8391: rig pa'i sgro skur gyis 'ajala bar byed na rtsa
NK120(e)001:8393: bcu gnyis pa dad ldan sems sun 'byin pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8394: dad gsum ldan pa'i sems can don mi byed //
NK120(e)001:8395: sems mi bsrung dang bslu ba bcu gnyis pa //
NK120(e)001:8397: bla ma dang dkon mchog gi yon tan la spro ba dang ba'i dad pa /
NK120(e)001:8398: de don du gnyer ba 'dod pa'i dad pa /
NK120(e)001:8399: de dang des bstan pa'i chos la the tshom dang
NK120(e)001:8400: bral bas yid ches pa'i dada pa gsuma dang ldana
NK120(e)001:8401: pa'i semas cana chos 'dod cing sbyin du rung ba
NK120(e)001:8402: la rang la nus pa yod bzhin chos ston pa
NK120(e)001:8403: sogs de'i dona mi byed par ma zad de'i semsa
NK120(e)001:8404: mi bsrung bar tshigs barlanga por brjod pa'am /
NK120(e)001:8405: rang gi spyod ngan bstan pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8406: g.yo sgyus bslu ba rnams gang yang rung bas de'i
NK120(e)001:8407: sems sun phyung bas dad 'dun log na rtsa ltung
NK120(e)001:8408: bcu gnyis pa'o // bcu gsum pa dam rdzas ji bzhin mi bsten pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8409: skabs bab yo byad longs spyod dam tshig rdzas //
NK120(e)001:8410: dus tshod 'brel kyang mi bsten bcu gsum pa //
NK120(e)001:8412: sngags kyi spyod pa'i skabsa su bab pa tshogs kyi
NK120(e)001:8413: 'khor lo'am dpa' bo dang dpa' mo'i dga' ston sogs
NK120(e)001:8414: kyi tshe rdor dril gos rgyan sogs bcang bar 'os
NK120(e)001:8416: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga chang sogs longas spyod par 'os pa'i dama tshiga gi rdzas dang /
NK120(e)001:8417: bro gar glu tshig sogs dam tshig gi spyod pa
NK120(e)001:8418: dus tshoda dang 'brela kyang nyan thos kyi bslab pa
NK120(e)001:8419: la 'chal nas mi gtsang ba dang nyes dmigs kyi
NK120(e)001:8420: bsam pas mi bsten pa rtsa ltung bcu gsuma pa'o
NK120(e)001:8421: // bcu bzhi pa shes rab mar smod pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8422: spyi dang bye brag la ltos shes rab mar //
NK120(e)001:8423: ngos lkog snying tshim smad go bcu bzhi pa //
NK120(e)001:8425: bud med kyi rigs 'di rnams g.yo sgyu che'o zhes
NK120(e)001:8426: pa lta bu spyi la ltos nas smod pa dang
NK120(e)001:8427: / bye brag la ltos pa rang gi brten byar
NK120(e)001:8428: 'os pa'i shesa raba ma sogs la ngosa nas sam
NK120(e)001:8430: de dag gi skyon brjod pa'i sgo nas snying tshima
NK120(e)001:8431: par smad pa yul de goo na rtsa ltung bcu
NK120(e)001:8432: bzhi pa'o // de yang bla med kyi sdom pa dang mi ldan pa zhig dgos te /
NK120(e)001:8433: de ltar min na rtsa ltung dang po'i gsum par 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:8434: de dag gi go rim kyang gnyen po'i sngags kyi
NK120(e)001:8435: go rim dang snga ma snga ma las phyi ma
NK120(e)001:8436: phyi ma yang bas lci yang gi sgo nas de
NK120(e)001:8437: ltar bzhag la / dbang bzhi so so'i sdom pa'i
NK120(e)001:8438: rtsa ltung du 'gyur tshul gtso che ba'i dbang du
NK120(e)001:8439: byas na bcu gsum pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8440: lnga pa rgyu 'bras bu byas nas gsang dbang gi dang /
NK120(e)001:8441: bcu bazha pa khyad par sher dbang gi dang /
NK120(e)001:8442: dgu pa dang bcu gcig pa dbang bzhi pa'i dang /
NK120(e)001:8443: lhag ma dgu po bum dbang dang 'gal ba'i rtsa ltung yin zhing /
NK120(e)001:8444: dbang phyi ma phyi ma'i tshe na snga ma snga ma thun mong dang /
NK120(e)001:8445: dbang rang skal gyi de nyid thun min du 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:8446: des na bum dbang tsam thob pas rang 'gal ba'i dgu po spyad na rtsa ltung du 'gyur gyi /
NK120(e)001:8447: de las gzhan pa lnga la spyad kyang rtsa ltung dngos su mi 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:8448: de spong ba'i sdom pa ma thob pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:8449: bzhi pa yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba bshad pa la gsum /
NK120(e)001:8453: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8454: da ni yan lag sbom po'i ltung ba bshad //
NK120(e)001:8456: da ni rtsa ba dang rjes su mthun pa'i yan
NK120(e)001:8457: lag sdo ma pa gtong byed kyi rgyu ma yin
NK120(e)001:8458: kyang dngos grub myur du 'grub pa la gegs byed
NK120(e)001:8459: pa'i nyes pa lci bas na sbom po zhes bya
NK120(e)001:8460: ste / dper na ljon shing gi yal ga rags
NK120(e)001:8461: pa chad pa ltar nyams skyon che bas na sbom
NK120(e)001:8462: po'i ltung ba'i rnam grangs bashada par bya ste zhes
NK120(e)001:8463: ste / so // gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8464: sbom po brgyad bshad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8466: dang po sbom po brgyad bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8467: dbang dang dam tshig ma smin rig ma bsten //
NK120(e)001:8468: tshogs kyi 'khor lo'i dus su lus ngag rtsod //
NK120(e)001:8469: ma gsungs rig mar rang stobs bdud rtsi len //
NK120(e)001:8470: snod ldan slob mar gsang sngags mi ston dang //
NK120(e)001:8471: dad ldan chos 'dri ba la chos gzhan ston //
NK120(e)001:8472: nyan thos nang du zhag bdun longs par bsdad //
NK120(e)001:8473: rnal 'byor ye shes mi ldan sngags par rlom //
NK120(e)001:8474: snod min la bshad yan lag ltung ba brgyad //
NK120(e)001:8476: dabnga ma thob pa dang dama tshiga dang mi ldan
NK120(e)001:8477: pa rgyud ma smin pa'i riga ma bsten pa tsam
NK120(e)001:8478: 1dang / tshogas kyi 'khor lo la sogs pa'i dus
NK120(e)001:8479: su rdo rje'i spun la mnar sems med kyang lus
NK120(e)001:8480: ngaga gis rtsod brdeg dang kha shag tsam byas pa
NK120(e)001:8481: 1dang / 2dang / mtshan nyid ma tshang bas rgyud
NK120(e)001:8482: las bsten byar ma gsungas pa'i riga ma phal par
NK120(e)001:8483: ril bu'am bde ba'i rgyur sngags kyi cho ga bzhin
NK120(e)001:8484: du ma yin par ranga gi rlung stobsa tsam gyis
NK120(e)001:8485: ril bu sogs kyi rgyu bduda rtsi lena pa 3dang
NK120(e)001:8487: ldana zhing don gnyer can gyi slob mara gsang sngags
NK120(e)001:8488: kyi chos dpe mkhyud kyis mi ston pa 4dang /
NK120(e)001:8489: dada pa dang ldana cig chos don du gnyer ba'i
NK120(e)001:8490: slob mas tshig don 'dri ba la de mi ston
NK120(e)001:8492: sngags kyi lta spyod la skur pa 'debs pa'i nyan
NK120(e)001:8493: thosa dngos sam de dang 'dra ba rtog ge ba'i
NK120(e)001:8494: nanga du zhaga bduna longsa para bsdada pa 6dang /
NK120(e)001:8495: rnala 'byor pa rang nyid de kho na nyid kyi
NK120(e)001:8496: ye shesa dang mi ldana bzhin du nga ni sngagas
NK120(e)001:8497: 'chang rdo rje 'dzin pa yin para smra zhing rlom
NK120(e)001:8498: pa 7dang / tshogs bshad tsam las man ngag slob
NK120(e)001:8499: bshad ston pa'i snod mina pa la zab don rjen
NK120(e)001:8500: par bashada pa ste de rnams ni yan lag gi
NK120(e)001:8502: gnyis pa rnam grangs gzhan bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8503: bsnyen sogs ma byas dbang rab las la 'jug /
NK120(e)001:8504: phyi chos mos la lus kyi phyag rgya bstan //
NK120(e)001:8505: sdom pa gnyis kyi bcas las dgos med 'da' //
NK120(e)001:8507: de'ang rang gi bsnyen sgrub sogas ma byas par slob ma la dabnga bskur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8508: rten la raba gnas byas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8509: sbyin sreg gi lasa sogs la bsam pas 'juga par
NK120(e)001:8510: rtsom zhing sbyor bas dngos su lag len la zhugs
NK120(e)001:8511: pa dang / sngags kyi zab don la skrag pa'i
NK120(e)001:8512: rigs can ma yin kyang phyi mtshan nyid theg pa'i
NK120(e)001:8513: chosa la mosa pa che ba'i gang zag la dgos
NK120(e)001:8514: pa med par lus kyi phyag rgya 'khrul 'khor sogs
NK120(e)001:8515: pa dang / bstan pa dang / sdom pa 'og
NK120(e)001:8516: ma so byang gnyis thob pa'i sngags pas chang 'thung
NK120(e)001:8517: ba dang phyi dro'i kha zas bza' ba sogs so
NK120(e)001:8518: byang gnyis kyi bacasa pa lasa tshogs 'khor dang nang
NK120(e)001:8519: gi sbyin sreg sogs dgosa pa khyad par can med
NK120(e)001:8520: bzhin du 'ad'a bar byed pa ni sbom po'o //
NK120(e)001:8521: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8522: zhes sogs sbom po'i ltung ba du ma rnams //
NK120(e)001:8523: yod kyang nyes pa chung zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK120(e)001:8525: zhesa bshad pa la sogas pa'i sbom po'i ltung ba ngos 'dzin dang /
NK120(e)001:8528: yan lag gang rung ma tshang ba'i nyes byas sogs
NK120(e)001:8529: du ma rnams yoda kyang nyesa pa chung ba'i tshul
NK120(e)001:8530: ji skad du / ltung ba sbom po rnams ni du ma te /
NK120(e)001:8531: de rnams la chad pa shin tu chung bar 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:8532: zhesa dus 'khor 'grel chen las bashada pas 'dir btang snyoms su byas so //
NK120(e)001:8533: de yan chad kyis gsar rnying thun mong ba'i dam tshig rnams bstan te /
NK120(e)001:8534: lnga pa khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i lugs bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8537: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8538: khyad par snga 'gyur rdzogs pa chen po'i srol //
NK120(e)001:8540: gsar ma'i rgyud gzhung rnams su ma grags pas na khyad para ba ste /
NK120(e)001:8541: snga 'gyur rdzogas pa chena po gtso bor byas pa'i
NK120(e)001:8542: rgyud sde rnams su gsungs pa'i lugs srol 'chad pa
NK120(e)001:8543: las / spyir dam tshig la sgra don gyi dbang
NK120(e)001:8544: du btang na sa ma ya'i sgra dngos su yal
NK120(e)001:8545: gam bcas pa'i tha tshig la 'jug pas ji ltar
NK120(e)001:8546: dam bcas pa las 'da' bar bya ba ma yin
NK120(e)001:8548: 'da' dka' rdo rje'i dam tshig gtan gyi gnyer //
NK120(e)001:8550: de la bsrung ma bsrungs kyi khe nyen gyi dam tshig tu bzhag pa'ang yod de /
NK120(e)001:8551: he ru ka 'dus pa'i rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:8552: mi 'da' da ma pa mchog gyur pa //
NK120(e)001:8553: 'das par gyur na tshig par bshad //
NK120(e)001:8555: dbye na snga 'gyur gyi rgyud sde thun mong ma
NK120(e)001:8556: yin pa rnams rgyud lung man ngag gsum du 'du
NK120(e)001:8557: zhing / de rnams su spyi dang /
NK120(e)001:8559: lhag pa'i dam tshig gsum du bshad pa las /
NK120(e)001:8560: dang po spyi'i dam tshig ni /
NK120(e)001:8561: so byang dang phyi rgyud kyi sdom pa'i bsrung mtshams su grags pa'i dam tshig rnams te /
NK120(e)001:8563: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK120(e)001:8564: bya spyod rnal 'byor rgyud rnams las //
NK120(e)001:8565: bsrung bar bya ba gang gsungs pa //
NK120(e)001:8566: thun mong spyi yi dam tshig yin //
NK120(e)001:8568: gnyis pa khyad par gyi dam tshig ni /
NK120(e)001:8569: rgyud thams cad kyi gzhi mar gyur pa sgyu 'phrul
NK120(e)001:8570: rtsa rgyud las ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga dang
NK120(e)001:8571: / yan lag gi dam tshig bcur bshad pa las /
NK120(e)001:8572: snga ma ni 'dir bshad pa'i rtsa ba'i dam tshig gi nang du 'du la /
NK120(e)001:8573: phyi ma 'di'i yan lag gi dam tshig nyer lnga'i nang tshan mi spang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8574: dang blang gnyis las gzhan med cing /
NK120(e)001:8575: lung thams cad kyi rtsa ba spyi mdo dgongs pa
NK120(e)001:8576: 'dus pa las rtsa ba'i dam tshig gsum dang yan
NK120(e)001:8577: lag nyer lnga bshad pa las snga ma'ang 'dir bshad
NK120(e)001:8578: par 'du zhing / phyi ma'ang nyer lnga po 'dir
NK120(e)001:8579: bshad pa dang don gcig pa des na bstan bcos
NK120(e)001:8580: 'dir ni man ngag a ti yo ga'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:8581: par 'du zhing / rnams bstan to // gsum pa
NK120(e)001:8582: lhag pa'i dam tshig ni 'og tu 'chad par 'gyur
NK120(e)001:8583: par 'du zhing / rnams bstan to // la / gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8586: dang po rtsa ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK120(e)001:8587: rdzogs pa chen po'i dam tshig de la'ang bsrung du med pa gcig car ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK120(e)001:8588: bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i dam tshig gnyis su dbye ba las /
NK120(e)001:8589: dang po gcig car ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK120(e)001:8591: de dus bsrung ba'i mtshams 'das pas //
NK120(e)001:8592: dam tshig lhun grub chen po dang //
NK120(e)001:8593: med dang gcig pu phya ba yin //
NK120(e)001:8596: chos thams cad ye nas blang dor rgyu 'bras bsrung
NK120(e)001:8597: bya srung byed bsrung mtshams las 'das pa 'khor 'das
NK120(e)001:8598: mnyam nyid bde ba chen po'i klong du mnyam brdal
NK120(e)001:8599: gyi dgongs pa zab mo mngon du gyur pa cir
NK120(e)001:8600: snang ye shes chen po'i rol pa 'ba' zhig tu
NK120(e)001:8601: 'char ba ni bsrung du med pa gcig car ba'i
NK120(e)001:8602: dam tshig gi tha snyad du bzhag pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8603: gnyis pa bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK120(e)001:8604: de lta bu'i gdams ngag zab mo thob kyang nyams
NK120(e)001:8605: len gyi ngos nas rtogs goms kyi gding tshad ma
NK120(e)001:8606: longs pa'i gang zag dad brtson shes rab can thun
NK120(e)001:8607: mong gi 'jug sgor bsrung mtshams can rim gyis pa'i
NK120(e)001:8608: dam tshig gi rnam gzhag dam tshig rnam par bkod
NK120(e)001:8609: pa'i rgyud las gsungs pa bzhin 'chad pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8610: rtsa ba bla ma'i sku gsung thugs gsum la //
NK120(e)001:8611: dgu dgur phye ba nyi shu rtsa bdun dang //
NK120(e)001:8613: rtsa ba'i dam tshig ni rang gi sgo gsum sangs
NK120(e)001:8614: rgyas kun 'dus bla ma'i sku gsunga thugas rdo rje
NK120(e)001:8615: gsuma dang dbyer mi phyed par bsdoms pas sam /
NK120(e)001:8616: yang na gu ru'i sgra las lci ba ste nyams
NK120(e)001:8617: na sbyangs dka' ba'i don gyis de skad ces bya
NK120(e)001:8618: la / de la dbye na sku gsung thugs gsum
NK120(e)001:8619: re re la phyi nang gsang ba gsum gsum du
NK120(e)001:8620: phye bas dgu dgur phye ba las /
NK120(e)001:8621: dang po sku'i dam tshig gsum tshan gsum ni /
NK120(e)001:8622: rim par ma byin par len pa /
NK120(e)001:8624: srog gcod pa gsum spong ba sku'i phyi'i gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:8625: pha ma spun sring dang rang lus la smod pa /
NK120(e)001:8626: chos dang gang zag la smod pa /
NK120(e)001:8627: rang lus la brdeg btsogs dang dka' thub kyis brnyas
NK120(e)001:8628: shing gdung ba rnams spang ba sku'i nang gi gsum
NK120(e)001:8629: dang / rdo rje spun sring gi lus la brdeg gam brdeg par gzas shing rgyan la smod pa /
NK120(e)001:8630: bla ma'i yum la gtses pa /
NK120(e)001:8631: bla ma'i sku'i grib mar 'gongs pa dang spyan sngar
NK120(e)001:8632: lus ngag gi spyod pa bag med pa rnams spong
NK120(e)001:8633: ba sku'i gsang ba'i dam tshig go //
NK120(e)001:8634: gnyis pa gsung gi dam tshig gsum tshan sum ni /
NK120(e)001:8637: tshig rtsub smra ba rnams spong ba gsung gi phyi'i gsum dang /
NK120(e)001:8640: gnas lugs sgom pa rnams la gshe skur 'debs pa spong ba rnams gsung gi nang gi dang /
NK120(e)001:8641: rdo rje spun sring gi tshig /
NK120(e)001:8642: bla ma'i phyag rgya dang nye 'khor gyi tshig /
NK120(e)001:8643: bla ma'i gsung rnams la brnyas shing gcog par byed
NK120(e)001:8644: pa rnams spong ba gsung gi gsang ba'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:8645: go // gsum pa thugs kyi dam tshig gsum tshan gsum ni /
NK120(e)001:8648: log lta gsum spong ba thugs kyi phyi'i dang /
NK120(e)001:8649: spyod pa log pa bag med dang tho co //
NK120(e)001:8650: sgom pa log pa bying rgod dang gol sgrib /
NK120(e)001:8651: lta ba log pa rtag chad dang mthar 'dzin spangs pa rnams thugs kyi nang gi dang /
NK120(e)001:8652: nyin zhag gi thun re re bzhin lta bzhin lta sgom spyod gsum yid la ma byas pa /
NK120(e)001:8653: yi dam gyi lha yid la ma byas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8655: mched lcam la brtse gdung yid la ma byas pa
NK120(e)001:8656: rnams spang ba thugs kyi gsang ba'i dam tshig ste
NK120(e)001:8659: gnyis pa yan lag gi dam tshig bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8662: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8663: yan lag dam tshig nyi shu rtsa lnga ni //
NK120(e)001:8665: rtsa ba'i dam tshig de dag bsrung ba'i thabs sam
NK120(e)001:8666: grogs su gyur pas na yan lag gi dama tshiga
NK120(e)001:8667: ste dbye na grangs lnga tshan lnga ste nyi shu
NK120(e)001:8668: rtsa lnga bshad pa ni zhes so //
NK120(e)001:8669: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la lnga /
NK120(e)001:8675: dang po spyad par bya ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:8676: ta na ga na ma byin len dang rdzun //
NK120(e)001:8677: ngag 'khyal rnams ni spyad par bya ba lnga //
NK120(e)001:8679: 'di dag la rang 'dod kyi zhen 'khris med cing
NK120(e)001:8680: rtogs goms kyi gding rnyed na gzhan don du spyad
NK120(e)001:8682: dngos bstan ta na sgrol ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8684: ma byin pa lena pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8685: rdzun du smra ba rnams sngar ltar la /
NK120(e)001:8686: gdul bya ma rung ba'i rgyud 'chos pa'i phyir zhe
NK120(e)001:8687: gcod kyi barlanga tshig ngaga 'khyal smra ba rnams dang
NK120(e)001:8688: / sbas don du rlung rtog dbu mar gsod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8689: kha sbyor las zhu bde 'gyur med du sgrub pa'i 'dod spyod dang /
NK120(e)001:8690: btsun mo'i shu tra ma byin par len pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8691: 'khor ba med snang las sgrol ba'i rdzun tshig dang /
NK120(e)001:8692: brjod med rtog pas gab sbas med par smra ba'i ngag 'khyal rnams ni spyad para bya ba lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:8693: gnyis pa mi spang ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:8694: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug nga rgyal dang /
NK120(e)001:8695: phrag dog lnga ni mi spang dam tshig lnga //
NK120(e)001:8702: dngos bstan log pa'i dug lnga po de ni nyan
NK120(e)001:8703: thos pa ltar dgrar bltas nas spang mi dgos te
NK120(e)001:8704: / chos thams cad rang rang gi ngo bos stong
NK120(e)001:8705: pas spang bya'i rdzas ma grub pa'i phyir smig sgyu
NK120(e)001:8706: la chu rags mi dgos pa bzhin te /
NK120(e)001:8708: nyon mongs rnams ni sgyu 'dra ngo bos stong //
NK120(e)001:8709: rang gi ma rig rang bzhin shes pas sgrol //
NK120(e)001:8711: thabs kyis zin na spyad kyang mi 'ching bar ma
NK120(e)001:8712: zad rnam par grol ba'i myur lam yin pas kyang
NK120(e)001:8713: mi spang ste / rna bar chu zhugs pa chus 'gugs pa bzhin te /
NK120(e)001:8715: nyon mongs lam ni dag pa che //
NK120(e)001:8716: thabs kyi 'dod yon rgyan gyi mchog /
NK120(e)001:8717: thams cad thams cad rol pa yis //
NK120(e)001:8718: myur du he ru ka dpal 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:8720: nyon mongs pa lnga ye nas rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas kyang mi spang ste /
NK120(e)001:8721: snum 'dod pas til 'bru sgrub pa bzhin te /
NK120(e)001:8722: thabs zhags kyi 'grel par slob dpon chen po pad+mas /
NK120(e)001:8723: gti mug ni rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam tshig ste /
NK120(e)001:8725: ma rig pa ni spang du med /
NK120(e)001:8726: rig pa ni sgrub du med de chos kyi dbyings su ro gcig pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:8728: sbas don yang dag pa'i dug lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:8729: chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs pas lta ba la phyogs ris dang /
NK120(e)001:8730: spyod pa la blang dor gyis 'byed pa med pa'i gti mug /
NK120(e)001:8731: de ltar ma rtogs pa la dmigs pa med pa'i snying rjes rjes su chags pa'i 'dod chags /
NK120(e)001:8732: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis log rtog 'joms pa'i zhe sdang /
NK120(e)001:8733: mnyam nyid rtogs pa'i lta ba gshongs su mi 'bebs pa'i nga rgyal /
NK120(e)001:8734: gnyis 'dzin gyi lta spyod mnyam nyid kyi klong du
NK120(e)001:8735: mi shong ba'i phrag dog rnams rtogs goms kyi thabs
NK120(e)001:8737: de dag ni mi spang ba'i dam tshiga lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:8738: gsum pa dang du blang ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:8739: dri chen dri chu rak+ta m+aam sa dang //
NK120(e)001:8740: rdo rje zil pa dang du blangs pa lnga //
NK120(e)001:8747: rdo rje zil pa ste bdud rtsi lnga po de nyid chos nyid ngo bos grub /
NK120(e)001:8748: chos can rang bzhin gyis grub /
NK120(e)001:8750: byin gyis rlabs kyis grub pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8752: nad lnga sel pa'i sman yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8753: mchog thun dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8759: rdo rje zila pa mi bskyod pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8760: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin yin pas na /
NK120(e)001:8761: yin pa gsum gyi tshul ji lta ba bzhin shes nas bsten pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8762: sbas don du phung po lnga'i dwangs ma 'dzag med
NK120(e)001:8763: du 'ching ba ste de rnams ni dang du blang
NK120(e)001:8764: ba lnga'o // bzhi pa shes par bya ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:8765: phung lnga 'byung lnga yul lnga dbang po lnga //
NK120(e)001:8766: kha dog lnga rnams lha ru shes pa lnga //
NK120(e)001:8768: chos thams cad ye nas sangs rgyas pas /
NK120(e)001:8769: phung po lnga de bzhin gshegs pa yab lnga /
NK120(e)001:8772: dabnga po lnga dang dbang shes lnga sems dpa'/
NK120(e)001:8773: kha doga lnga rigs lnga ye shes lnga sogs lnga
NK120(e)001:8774: tshan gyi rtog tshogs rnams kyi rang bzhin lha ru
NK120(e)001:8775: dag pas sku dang ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor du
NK120(e)001:8776: shes rab kyis sgro 'dogs bcad nas shesa par byed
NK120(e)001:8777: pa ste / de dag ni shes bya lta ba'i dam tshig lnga'o //
NK120(e)001:8778: lnga pa bsgrub par bya ba lnga ni /
NK120(e)001:8779: de bzhin gshegs dang rdo rje rin po che //
NK120(e)001:8780: pad+ma las rigs bsgrub bya lnga rnams ni //
NK120(e)001:8781: dus tshod 'brel ba'i spyod pas dgongs pa blangs //
NK120(e)001:8783: shes par bya ba'i dam tshig rnams lta bu'i nges
NK120(e)001:8784: pa rnyed pa na rtogs goms kyi sbyor bas de
NK120(e)001:8789: lasa kyi rigas te lnga po rang rgyud la tshul
NK120(e)001:8790: bzhin nyams su blangs nas bsgrub par bya ba lnga
NK120(e)001:8791: ste / de rnams ni las dang po pa dang
NK120(e)001:8792: nyams myong cung zad skyes pa sogs lta dgongs kyi
NK120(e)001:8793: ste / gding dang / tshogs dang dben pa la sogs pa'i yul dang /
NK120(e)001:8794: dus tshod kyi gnas skabs brtsis nas de dang 'brela
NK120(e)001:8795: ba'i sgo nas spyod dgos pasa de dag dngos bstan
NK120(e)001:8796: dang / gzhan yang sbas don gyi tshul du gsungs
NK120(e)001:8797: pa'i dgongas pa blangsa te spyad pa la mkhas par
NK120(e)001:8798: dang / bya'o // gsum pa lhag pa'i dam tshig ni /
NK120(e)001:8799: spyi dang khyad par gyi dam tshig la gnas pa'i
NK120(e)001:8800: rnal 'byor pas sgrub pa la sogs pa'i skabs su
NK120(e)001:8801: bsrung bya lhag par bstan pa'i dam tshig nyi shu
NK120(e)001:8802: ldems dgongs kyi sgras bshad pa ste /
NK120(e)001:8804: gzhung don lhag pa'i dam tshig ni //
NK120(e)001:8805: rab tu lhag par bsrung bar bya //
NK120(e)001:8806: gcan gzan rgyal po'i khri mi gzhig /
NK120(e)001:8807: ces rdo rje slob dpon gyi sku la mi 'tshe zhing bka' mi gcog pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8808: za ma tog tu dug mi blug /
NK120(e)001:8809: ces bla ma'i yum la mi spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8810: rin chen lcug phran mi 'brag cing //
NK120(e)001:8811: zhes dad pa can gyi tshogs mi bcag pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8812: zhun khol lta bu mi btung ste //
NK120(e)001:8813: zhes dkon mchog dang mkhas pa'i dkor la mi 'bag cing chang myos par mi 'thung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8815: zhes rdo rje spun gyi yum la mi spyood pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8816: bug rdol snod du bcud mi blug /
NK120(e)001:8817: ces mtshan ngan gyi gzungs ma mi bsten pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8818: don dang mi ldan rdzas mi bsten //
NK120(e)001:8819: zhes mtshan nyid dang mi ldan pa'i dam rdzas mi bsten pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8820: shel sgong 'dam du bsub mi bya //
NK120(e)001:8821: zhes mkhas pa'i yon tan la mi smod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8822: ma dag snod du dag pa min //
NK120(e)001:8823: zhe snod min la gsang chos mi ston pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8824: yid bzhin nor bu mi 'breg ste //
NK120(e)001:8825: zhes mtshan ldan gyi gzungs ma dang snod ldan gyi slob ma mi spang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8826: khyung chen gshog pa ya mi 'bral //
NK120(e)001:8827: zhes don bde stong dang rtags yab yum mi 'bral ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8828: gnam lcags ngur mo'i mtshon mi rdeg /
NK120(e)001:8829: ces mched la kyal ka tsam du'ang nang 'thab mi byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8830: gcan gzan rol pa'i lhag mi spyad //
NK120(e)001:8831: ces gzhan gyis spyad pa'i lhag mi spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8832: rdo rje brag chen mi gzhig cing //
NK120(e)001:8833: zhes bla ma'i gdan sa mi rlom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8834: ra ba d+r+wa ba'i mtshams mi 'dral //
NK120(e)001:8835: zhes rang gzhan gyi mtshams mi 'dral ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8836: sgron me rlung gi bsad pa min //
NK120(e)001:8837: zhes ting nge 'dzin bying rgod kyi dbang du mi gtong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8838: ye shes chu rgyun gcod pa spang //
NK120(e)001:8839: zhes bzlas brjod dang cho ga mi tshig gis bar mi gcod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8840: bka' rtags phyag rgya mi dbye zhing //
NK120(e)001:8841: zhes dbang rtags kyi phyag rgya las mi 'da' zhing brda mi brjod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8842: rdo rje pha lam mkhar mi ldog /
NK120(e)001:8843: ces rnal 'byor pa'i dkyil 'khor mi dkrugs shing skye bo'i mthu zlog mi byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8844: gtsug gi nor bu sma mi dbab //
NK120(e)001:8845: ces slob dpon gtsug tu khur ba las nyams par mi bya ba'o //
NK120(e)001:8846: 'di dag bsrung bar bya ba ste //
NK120(e)001:8847: lhag par gces pa'i dam tshig yin //
NK120(e)001:8849: gsum pa don bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:8850: de sogs dam tshig rnam gzhag mang gsungs pa //
NK120(e)001:8851: rtsa ba yan lag bcas 'dir ma 'dus med //
NK120(e)001:8852: mdor na rang lus rdo rje gsum shes na //
NK120(e)001:8853: sngags kyi dam tshig sa ya 'bum sde 'dus //
NK120(e)001:8855: gong du ji skad bshad pa desa mtshon te sogas
NK120(e)001:8856: khongs nas sngar bshad pa'i sgyu 'phrul gyi rtsa ba
NK120(e)001:8857: dang yan lag gi dam tshig bco lnga las rnam
NK120(e)001:8858: grangs sum brgya drug cur spros pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8859: bshad rgyud rgyas par dam tshig dgu bcu rtsa bdun dang /
NK120(e)001:8860: spyi mdor gal mdo nges pa'i dam tshig bzhi /
NK120(e)001:8861: thun mong gi dam tshig nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK120(e)001:8868: lta ba'i dam tshig ste dgur phye ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8869: gzhan yang rgyud sde so sor rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i bsrung ba'i dam tshig dang /
NK120(e)001:8873: mi 'bral ba'i yo byad kyi dama tshiga sogs rnam
NK120(e)001:8874: gazhaga manga po zhig gsungas pa yod na'ang de thams
NK120(e)001:8875: cad rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig dang
NK120(e)001:8876: bacasa pa 'dira ma 'dusa pa meda do //
NK120(e)001:8877: gang spyad na sngags sdom gtong ba'i rigs dang /
NK120(e)001:8878: mi gtong na'ang yan lag nyams par byed pa'i rigs gnyis su 'dus pa'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:8879: 'o na gsar rnying thun mong ba'i rtsa ltung bcu bzhi dang /
NK120(e)001:8880: snga 'gyur ba'i khyad par gyi dam tshig sngar bshad pa rnams mi 'gal lam snyam na /
NK120(e)001:8881: bcu bzhi po khyad par gyi rtsa ba'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:8882: de dag gi khongs su 'dus pas 'gal ba med
NK120(e)001:8883: do // de thams cad kyang mdora bsdu na ranga
NK120(e)001:8884: gi lus gnyug ma'i rtsa rlung thig le ye shes
NK120(e)001:8885: dang bcas pa gdod ma nas sku gsung thugs rdo
NK120(e)001:8886: rje gsuma dbyer med pa'i ye shes rdo rje'i bdag
NK120(e)001:8887: nyid du bzhugs pa nyid shes rab kyis sgro 'dogs
NK120(e)001:8888: bcad de shesa nasa gsang sngagsa kyi dama tshig sa
NK120(e)001:8889: ya 'buma sde ji skad gsungs pa thams cad der
NK120(e)001:8890: lhun gyis grub par 'dusa shing skyon rnam par dag
NK120(e)001:8892: lnga pa sdom pa skye ba'i rten bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8893: skye ba'i rten ni nyin bzhin bram ze gsod //
NK120(e)001:8894: mtshams med lnga byed la sogs kun la'o //
NK120(e)001:8896: de lta bu' rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom pa de
NK120(e)001:8897: skye ba'i rten ni gtso bor khams drug ldan gyi
NK120(e)001:8899: dper na mtshon rtul pos shing sdong gcod pa la
NK120(e)001:8900: yun ring thogs pa de rnon pos skad cig la
NK120(e)001:8901: gcod pa ltar mtshan nyid theg pas tshe rabs mang
NK120(e)001:8902: por tshogs bsags nas bsgrub dgos pa'i 'bras bu de
NK120(e)001:8903: sngags kyi theg pa 'dir zhugs na tshogs gnyis kyi
NK120(e)001:8904: bsags pa sngon du 'gro mi dgos par ma zad
NK120(e)001:8905: / theg pa gzhan du spangs pa'i gdul bya nyin bzhina bram ze gsoda pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8906: matshamas meda pa lnga byed pa la sogas pa'i sdig
NK120(e)001:8907: pa tshab po che'i las byed bzhin pa zhig yin
NK120(e)001:8908: kyang / dbang rnon sems stobs chen po dang ldan cing /
NK120(e)001:8909: mos 'dun bzlog tu med pa zhig yod phyin skye
NK120(e)001:8910: ba 'di las sangs rgyas nyid 'grub ste thabs zab
NK120(e)001:8911: cing yangs pa'i gnad kyis so //
NK120(e)001:8912: gzhan yang skal ldan las 'phro can bsags pa yang
NK120(e)001:8913: rab yin na mi'i rten kho na dgos pa'i nges
NK120(e)001:8914: pa med de / rgyud sde rnams las lha dang
NK120(e)001:8915: lha min sogs rgyud mnyan pa'i snod du bsdus pa
NK120(e)001:8916: pa med de / dang / gsang bdag gis sngags
NK120(e)001:8917: kyi theg pa gsungs pa'i gdul bya'i gtso bo d+r+wa
NK120(e)001:8918: ma lnga las bzhi mi ma yin pa'i rten can
NK120(e)001:8919: pa med de / dang / yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8920: o rgyan gyi gnas su klu rnams sngags lam gyis
NK120(e)001:8921: pa med de / dang / yin pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8922: grol ba dang / dgra bcom lhag med rnams sngags
NK120(e)001:8923: kyi theg par 'jug pa yod dgos pa la sogs
NK120(e)001:8924: pa'i phyir skal ba dang ldan pa'i 'gro ba kun
NK120(e)001:8925: la sngags kyi snod rgyu yod par bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:8926: drug pa nyams pa gso ba'i tshul la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8929: dang po mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8930: tha mar nyams na gso ba'i tshul bshad pa //
NK120(e)001:8932: de lta bu'i dam tshig rnams ma nyams par bsrung ba la 'bad cing /
NK120(e)001:8933: gal te ltung ba 'byung ba'i rgyu'i dbang gis tha
NK120(e)001:8934: mara nyamsa par gyur na slar gso ba'i tshul bashada
NK120(e)001:8936: gnyis pa rgyas par bshad pa la gnyis /
NK120(e)001:8939: dang po phyir bcos bya tshul la lnga /
NK120(e)001:8940: ltung ba'i rgyu gnyer po bcas bshad pa /
NK120(e)001:8941: ltung ba lci yang gi ldang tshad /
NK120(e)001:8944: phyir bcos bya tshul dngos so //
NK120(e)001:8945: dang po ltung ba'i rgyu gnyer po bcas bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:8946: ltung mtshams mi shes bla ma sogs mi gus //
NK120(e)001:8947: bag med spyod cing nyon mongs mang ba bzhi //
NK120(e)001:8948: ltung ba 'byung ba'i sgo bzhi thogs med bzhed //
NK120(e)001:8949: de yi gnyen por bslab byar bslab pa dang //
NK120(e)001:8950: kun la gus bskyed rtag par dran shes bsten //
NK120(e)001:8951: nyon mongs gang che'i gnyen por 'bad de bslab //
NK120(e)001:8952: spang bya bzhi'i steng brjed ngas dran mi gsal //
NK120(e)001:8953: gnyis bsnan dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu drug ces //
NK120(e)001:8954: dpal ldan sdom pa'i rgyud las gsal bar gsungs //
NK120(e)001:8956: dam tshig la bslab par 'dod kyang ltung ba so so'i blang dor gyi matshamas mi shes pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8958: des 'doms pa'i bslab bya la sogas pa la mi gus pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8959: spyir gus kyang nyes dmigs ma mthong ba'am dran shes
NK120(e)001:8960: med pas gzob par mi byed pas baga meda par
NK120(e)001:8961: spyod cinga / des nyes pa 'byung ba'i rgyu byed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8962: 'dzem bag cung zad skyes kyang nyon mongas shas che
NK120(e)001:8963: zhing manga ba ste bzhi ni ltung ba 'byung ba'i
NK120(e)001:8964: sgo bzhira rgyal sras thogas med kyi bzheda la /
NK120(e)001:8965: bzhi bo de yi gnyen pora blang dor rnams shes par byas nas bslab byar bslab pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8966: phan yon la brod pa bskyed nas bla ma dang bslab pa kuna la gus pa bskyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8967: dgra che sar zon byed pa ltar nyes dmigs la
NK120(e)001:8968: 'jigs nas sems bsgrims te rtag para drana shesa dang
NK120(e)001:8970: rang rgyud la nyon mongas ganga shas che ba de'i gnyen pora 'abda de bslaba pa dang bzhi'o //
NK120(e)001:8971: spanga bya rgyu bzhi po de'i steng bslab bya'i mtshams brjed ngas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8972: shes bzhin med pas dran pa mi gasla ba gnyis
NK120(e)001:8973: bsnan te dama tshiga nyamsa pa'i rgyu drug cesa dapala
NK120(e)001:8974: ldana sdoma pa'i rgyud lasa gasla bar gsungas te /
NK120(e)001:8976: mi shes pa dang bag med dang //
NK120(e)001:8977: nyon mongs mang dang ma gus dang //
NK120(e)001:8978: brjed ngas dran pa mi gsal ba //
NK120(e)001:8979: 'di drug dam tshig nyams pa'i rgyu //
NK120(e)001:8981: phyi ma gnyis kyi gnyen po gnang bkag gi mtshams mi brjed pa'i dran pa dang /
NK120(e)001:8982: dam tshig las 'das ma 'das dpyod pa'i shes bzhin no //
NK120(e)001:8983: gzhan yang nyams na bdag nyid ngan no snyam du
NK120(e)001:8984: rang la brten nas 'dzem pa'i ngo tsha shes pa
NK120(e)001:8985: dang / gzhan gyis khrel nas smad pa'i gnas su 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:8986: rgyal ba sras bcas rnams dang drin ldan bla ma
NK120(e)001:8987: rnams kyi zag pa med pa'i mngon shes kyis dgongs
NK120(e)001:8988: par 'gyur ba ni gdon mi za bas na nyes
NK120(e)001:8989: spyod la 'dzem par bya dgos snyam du gzhan la
NK120(e)001:8990: brten pa'i khrel yod sogs kyi sgo nas 'bad pas
NK120(e)001:8993: ji stee dngos grub mchog 'dod na //
NK120(e)001:8994: srog ni yongs su gtong yang sla //
NK120(e)001:8995: 'chi ba'i dus la bab kyang sla'i //
NK120(e)001:8996: rtag tu dam tshig bsrung bar bya //
NK120(e)001:8998: gnyis pa ltung ba lci yang gi ldang tshad ni /
NK120(e)001:8999: kun la yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug gam //
NK120(e)001:9000: kun slong nyon mongs gang 'gal der shes dang //
NK120(e)001:9001: lus ngag sbyor byas dngos gzhi bar chod pa //
NK120(e)001:9002: ma 'khrul spyad dang 'gyod med bshags tshad 'das //
NK120(e)001:9003: pham pa zhes brjod dngos gzhi ma tshang na //
NK120(e)001:9004: thun 'das ltung ba zhes brjod lhag ma ltar //
NK120(e)001:9005: rim pas dman na sbom po ltung byed dang //
NK120(e)001:9006: nyes byas ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan shes par bya //
NK120(e)001:9008: de nas ltung ba dang ltung med kyi tshul shes par bya ba la /
NK120(e)001:9009: ltung ba kuna la yan lag bzhi ldan nam bdud ldan te /
NK120(e)001:9010: de yang gang la brten nas ltung ba 'byung ba'i yul dang /
NK120(e)001:9011: der 'du shes pa'i bsam pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9012: las lam la 'jug pa'i sbyor ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9013: sgo gsum gang gis grub pa'i las lam rdzogs nas
