NK120(e)001:9014: mathara thug pa ste yan lag bzhi ldan dag gama
NK120(e)001:9015: / yang na kun slonga nyon mongsa drag pos bslang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9016: ganga la brten nas dam tshig dang 'gal bar 'gyur ba'i yul de la der shesa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9017: kun+da 'dor ba lta bu lus dang /
NK120(e)001:9018: gsang sgrog lta bu ngaga gi sbyor bas grogs la
NK120(e)001:9019: ltos ba'i bya ba de byas zin na rtsa ltung
NK120(e)001:9021: yid kyis grub pa rnams nyin mtshan gyi drug cha'i
NK120(e)001:9022: nang du gnyen pos ma slebs par thun tshod kyis
NK120(e)001:9024: yang sgo gsum gyis bskyed pa'i ltung ba gang yin yang /
NK120(e)001:9025: ltung ba gcig tsam la yan lag bdun ka tshang dgos pa'i dbang du byas na /
NK120(e)001:9026: bar chod pa zhes pa 'di de ltar 'grel na
NK120(e)001:9027: thun tshod 'das zhes pa dang gcig tu 'gyur bas
NK120(e)001:9028: srog gcod lta bus mtshon te gong du bshad pa'i
NK120(e)001:9029: bsam sbyor de dang ldan pas dngos gzhir grub pa
NK120(e)001:9030: ni / bar du srog gcod pa na bya ba de rdzogs nas srog gcod pa na zhes pa'am /
NK120(e)001:9031: yang na dngos gzhi'i ltung ba bskyed pa la mthar ma phyin gong /
NK120(e)001:9032: bar du gnyen pos chod pa min pa zhes 'grel na'ang rung ngam snyam du sems so //
NK120(e)001:9033: smyos pa la sogs pa 'du shes ma 'khrula bas spyad pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9034: des mgu bas 'gyod pa meda pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9035: bashagas pas ma zin par thun tshod las 'adsa pa ste /
NK120(e)001:9036: de ltar yan lag bdun tshang bar spyood na sngags
NK120(e)001:9037: sdom gtong bas shin tu lci zhing mi mthun phyogs
NK120(e)001:9038: kyis gnyen po bcom pas phas phama pa zhesa brjod
NK120(e)001:9039: cing / gal te rtsa ltung gang rung gnyen po
NK120(e)001:9040: dang spel nas skyes pa lta bu dngosa gzhi 'grub
NK120(e)001:9041: byed kyi yan lag gang rung ma tshanga nasa ma
NK120(e)001:9042: bshags par thuna tshod 'adsa na thun 'das kyi ltung
NK120(e)001:9044: so thar gyi dge 'dun lhag ma ltar pham pa'i 'og nas nyes pa lci ba yin la /
NK120(e)001:9045: de bzhin du rima pasa nyes pa damna na 'di
NK120(e)001:9046: ltar pham pa'i sder gtogs pa yan lag ma tshang
NK120(e)001:9047: ba nyon mongs pa can ni sboma po dang /
NK120(e)001:9048: yan lag gi ltung ba gzhan thams cad ni ltung byed lta bu dang /
NK120(e)001:9049: phyogs mthun gyi nyes pa phra mo rnams ni nyes byas dang 'dra'o //
NK120(e)001:9050: gal te rdo rje'i mched la phan sems kyis khros
NK120(e)001:9051: pa lta bu ni ltung ba'i gzugas brnyan te don
NK120(e)001:9052: la ltung med du shesa par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:9053: gsum pa ltung med kyi rgyu bshad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:9054: na dang dab nga nyams bya ba gzhan gyis dang //
NK120(e)001:9055: don chen skye med brtan dang dgos ldan dang //
NK120(e)001:9056: nus rnyed gnang dang bka' bsgo bar chad las //
NK120(e)001:9057: nyes pa med ces snying po rgyan las gsungs //
NK120(e)001:9059: de dag thams cad la rang nyid na ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9060: gzhan dbang du song bas rang dbang nyamsa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9061: bya ba de las che ba'i bya ba gazhana gyis brel ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9062: gzhan dona du 'gyur nges pa'i don chena po mthong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9063: rang rgyud la skye ba meda pa'i don skyes nas brtan pa thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9064: gzhan drang ba la sogs pa'i dgosa pa chen po dang ldan pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9065: rtogs goms kyi nus pa rnyed pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9066: lhag pa'i lha lta bu'i yul khyad par can gyis gannga ba thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9067: rang gi bla mas 'di lta bu zhig gyis shig ces bka'a bsgo ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9068: don des rang gi srog la bar chad du 'gyur
NK120(e)001:9069: ba lasa ltung ba de dag byas kyang nyes pa
NK120(e)001:9070: meda cesa snying po rgyan lasa gsungas te /
NK120(e)001:9072: na dang dbang nyams bya ba ni //
NK120(e)001:9073: gzhan gyi don dang don chen dang //
NK120(e)001:9074: skye med brtan dang dgos ldan dang //
NK120(e)001:9075: nus pa rnyed dang gnang ba dang //
NK120(e)001:9076: bka' bsgo ba dang bar chad las //
NK120(e)001:9077: nyes pa med par shes par bya //
NK120(e)001:9079: bzhi pa bshags tshad las 'das pa bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:9080: de ltar nyin mtshan thun la lan drug tu //
NK120(e)001:9081: spang blang dam tshig gnas la bsgrims te dpyad //
NK120(e)001:9082: drug cha 'das na thun tshod 'das zhes bya //
NK120(e)001:9083: zhag gcig zla gcig lo gcig lo gnyis 'das //
NK120(e)001:9084: 'gal nyams 'das ral zhes brjod de dag kyang //
NK120(e)001:9085: snying nas bshags na gsor rung phyi rim lci //
NK120(e)001:9086: lo gsum 'das na gsor mi rung ba yin //
NK120(e)001:9088: de ltar nyin mtshan gyi thun la nyin lan gsum /
NK120(e)001:9089: mtshan lana gsum ste drug tu thun re re bzhin
NK120(e)001:9090: spanga blang dama tshiga gi gnas la 'gal ma 'gal
NK120(e)001:9091: sems legs par bsgrimsa te brtags shing dpyad pas dus
NK120(e)001:9092: drug cha'i nang du gnyer pos ma slebs par 'adsa
NK120(e)001:9093: na thun tshod las 'adsa pa zhes bya ba dang
NK120(e)001:9094: / de bzhin du ltung ba byung nas ma bshags par zhaga gciga dang /
NK120(e)001:9097: lo gnyis rnams 'adsa na 'agla ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9101: de dag kyang snying thag pa nasa bashagas na gsora rung yang phyi rim rnams nyes pa lci'o //
NK120(e)001:9102: gal te lo gsum 'adsa par gyur na gsora mi rung ba yina te /
NK120(e)001:9103: dam tshig bkod pa'i rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:9104: log gsum dag las 'das pa na //
NK120(e)001:9105: de nas gso ru mi rung ste //
NK120(e)001:9106: gal te blangs ni gnyis ka 'tshig /
NK120(e)001:9107: nges par sa spyod sdug bsngal la //
NK120(e)001:9108: rgyun du spyod pa kho na'o //
NK120(e)001:9110: de yang ngo bo la ltos pa rtsa ba dang yan lag nyams pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9111: dus la ltos pa thun 'das zhes 'gal nyams sogs kyis bshags bya'i lci yang shes par bya'o //
NK120(e)001:9113: nyams par gyur pa gang zhe na //
NK120(e)001:9114: kun tu nyams pa chen po dang //
NK120(e)001:9115: rtsa ba nyams dang yan lag nyams //
NK120(e)001:9116: de bzhin zlas nyams zhar nyams lnga //
NK120(e)001:9118: kun tu nyams pa'i yul ches gnyan pa la kun dkris drag pos spyad pa'am /
NK120(e)001:9119: lan grangs mang du byung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9120: dus 'das ral ba la sogs pa yun ring por lon pa yin la /
NK120(e)001:9121: zlas nyams ni nyams pa dang 'grogs pa'i nyes pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9122: zhar nyams ni gzhan gyi ngo dgar thal ba la sogs pa'o //
NK120(e)001:9123: lnga pa phyir bcos dngos la bzhi /
NK120(e)001:9124: dbang bzhi la ltos pa'i gso thabs /
NK120(e)001:9125: dus 'das la ltos pa'i gso thabs /
NK120(e)001:9126: snying po rgyan las bshad pa'i phyir bcos nyer lnga /
NK120(e)001:9127: yo ga gsum gyi rnal 'byor spyi khrus kyis gso ba'o //
NK120(e)001:9128: dang po dbang bzhi la ltos pa'i gso thabs ni //
NK120(e)001:9129: dbang bdun thob la lha grangs re re la //
NK120(e)001:9130: bzlas pa sum khri drug stong byas pas sbyangs //
NK120(e)001:9131: bum gsang thob nyams sngon du chad las sbyang //
NK120(e)001:9132: de rjes dkyil 'khor zhugs la dbang bzhi len //
NK120(e)001:9133: sher dbang tshig dbang thob nyams bskyed rim dang //
NK120(e)001:9134: 'pho med tshul khrims rdzogs pa'i rim pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9135: rang rgyud byin rlabs ma gtogs gzhan mi 'dag /
NK120(e)001:9137: de yang dbang thob mtshams tha dad pa'i dbang gis
NK120(e)001:9138: ltung ba sbyor ba'i thabs kyang tha dad pa dus
NK120(e)001:9140: 'di ltar bum dabnga bduna tsam thob pa'i nyes ltung gi gnyen po la /
NK120(e)001:9141: dkyil 'khor gyi lha grangas re re la'am gtso bo'i
NK120(e)001:9142: bzlas pa sum khri drug stong byas pasa sbyang ba
NK120(e)001:9143: dang / bum gasnga thob pas ni nyamsa pa'i nyes
NK120(e)001:9144: pa byung na bshad ma thag pa'i sbyang thabs de'i
NK120(e)001:9145: steng bshags pa'i sngona du slob dpon gyis 'di gyis
NK120(e)001:9146: zhes gsungs pa'i chad lasa kyi brtul zhugs spyad pas
NK120(e)001:9147: dang / sbyang ba / dbang bzhi rdzogs par thob
NK120(e)001:9148: pa zhig yin na nyams pa'i nyes pa bshags shing
NK120(e)001:9149: dag pa'i mtshan ma mthong na de'i rjesa su dkyil
NK120(e)001:9150: 'khor du zhugsa la bla ma las sam bdag 'jug
NK120(e)001:9151: gis dabnga bzhi lena pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9152: khyad par du shera dabnga dang tshiga dabnga thoba pa
NK120(e)001:9153: las nyamsa na dben pa'i gnas su bskyed rdzogs kyi
NK120(e)001:9154: rima pa gnyis zung 'jug tu bsgom pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9155: 'pho meda kyi tshul khrimsa thun mong ma yin pa'i rdzogas pa'i rima pa mtshan bcas dang /
NK120(e)001:9156: mtshan med sogs ranga rgyud byin gyis brlabs pa'i lam
NK120(e)001:9157: ma gtogas bzlas pa tsam la sogs pa gazhana gyi
NK120(e)001:9158: mi 'adga go // de thams cad kyang dag pa'i
NK120(e)001:9159: mtshan ma mthong ba na slar dkyil 'khor du zhugs
NK120(e)001:9160: te sdom pa bzung zhing dbang blang bar bya ba
NK120(e)001:9161: mi 'adga go // yin la / de'i tshe sngar
NK120(e)001:9162: gyi dbang thob pa'i bslab gral dang rnyed bkur len
NK120(e)001:9163: pa sogs mi bya bar gsungs so //
NK120(e)001:9164: gnyis pa dus 'das la ltos pa'i gso thabs ni /
NK120(e)001:9165: 'gal na tshogs 'khor nyams na bdog pas bskang //
NK120(e)001:9166: 'das na bu dang chung ma nor sogs dang //
NK120(e)001:9167: ral na rang gi srog gis gso bar bshad //
NK120(e)001:9169: 'agla ba'i nyes pa 'byung na tshogas kyi 'khor lo
NK120(e)001:9170: phul zhing dpa' bo dang dpa' mo'i dga' ston byas
NK120(e)001:9172: nyamsa pa'i nyes pa byung na rang gi bdoga pa'i
NK120(e)001:9173: dngos po gang bzang bla ma la sogs pa'i phyogs
NK120(e)001:9174: su phul nas bshags pa byas pasa bskanga ba dang
NK120(e)001:9175: / 'adsa pa'i nyes pa byung na bu dang chung
NK120(e)001:9176: ma dang nora gyi nang nas gser la sogas pa'i
NK120(e)001:9177: rin po che du mas dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang
NK120(e)001:9178: bla ma la mchod de bshags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9179: rala ba'i nyes pa byung na ranga gi srogas la'ang
NK120(e)001:9180: mi lta bar bla ma dang bstan pa'i don du
NK120(e)001:9181: rang srog blos btang gi brtson pa drag pos bshags
NK120(e)001:9182: shing gso dgos par dam tshig rnam para bkod pa'i
NK120(e)001:9184: tshogs 'khor bdog pa sogs ni gang las ltung ba
NK120(e)001:9185: byung ba'i yul dngos bzhugs na de la phul nas
NK120(e)001:9186: bshags dgos so // gsum pa snying po rgyan las bshags pa'i phyir bcos ni /
NK120(e)001:9187: snying po rgyan las gso ba'i cho ga ni //
NK120(e)001:9188: tshogs zhing la bshags dral ba'i sngags rgya dang //
NK120(e)001:9189: bkru ba'i rim pa gtum mo'i mes sreg dang //
NK120(e)001:9190: mi dmigs bsgom dang dbang bzhi blang ba dang //
NK120(e)001:9191: tshogs su zhu dang rten la smra ba dang //
NK120(e)001:9192: man+dala phul dang mchod rten bya ba dang //
NK120(e)001:9193: me la sbyong dang gtor ma gtong ba dang //
NK120(e)001:9194: gsang sngags bzla dang zab mo'i bsam gtan dang //
NK120(e)001:9195: srog skyob bka' klog bla ma bsten pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9196: bdag 'jug rgyal ba'i yig brgya dus bzang bzla //
NK120(e)001:9197: phung po gsum pa rdor sems bla ma dang //
NK120(e)001:9198: thig le phra mo'i rnal 'byor bsgoms pas gso //
NK120(e)001:9200: de nas snying po rgyan lasa nyams pa slar gso
NK120(e)001:9201: ba'i thabs su gsungs pa'i cho ga bshad pa ni
NK120(e)001:9202: / tshogas zhing spyan drangs la de'i drung du stobs bzhi tshang bas bashagas sdom bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9203: yo ga nas bshags pa drala ba'i sngagas rgya gnyis te ltung ba lhonga ba'i phyag rgya dang /
NK120(e)001:9204: de'i sngags kyi rim pa la brten nas ngan 'gro dgug bral dang /
NK120(e)001:9205: de bzhin du rdo rje yang tog gi rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:9206: yig 'bru sngags kyis sbyang ba ni //
NK120(e)001:9207: rkang mthil nyis su yam gnyis bsam //
NK120(e)001:9208: gsang ba'i sgo ru ram bsam mo //
NK120(e)001:9209: lte bar rigs drug yig 'bru bsam //
NK120(e)001:9210: snying gar phata kyi gdan dag la //
NK120(e)001:9211: sku gsung thugs kyi snying po bsam //
NK120(e)001:9212: yam las ye shes rlung byung ste //
NK120(e)001:9213: ram las ye shes me 'bar nas //
NK120(e)001:9214: rigs drug bag chags thams cad bsregs //
NK120(e)001:9215: sgo gsum sku gsung thugs su gyur //
NK120(e)001:9216: phata kyis chos nyid dbyings su 'phang //
NK120(e)001:9217: zhes pa'ang man ngag shin tu zab bo //
NK120(e)001:9218: bam las chu m+aa ma k+ai'i bdag nyid du mos
NK120(e)001:9219: la sbyong ba'i brtul zhugs kyis lus bkru ba dang
NK120(e)001:9220: / so skyes nas slob lam gyi nyes byas thams
NK120(e)001:9221: cad grib tu mi gyur ba med pas rnam 'joms
NK120(e)001:9222: sogs gzungs sngags kyis sgrub pa'i bum chus dngos su
NK120(e)001:9223: / bkru ba dang / mkha' dbyings su shar ba'i
NK120(e)001:9224: dbang lha las rig pa'i dbang lnga blangs nas bkru
NK120(e)001:9226: lte bar kam yig dang snying gar sha za'i gzugs
NK120(e)001:9227: kyi rnam par bsam pa'i sdig sgrib rnams gtum mo'i
NK120(e)001:9229: 'khor gsum mi dmigas pa'i shes rab bsgoma pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9230: bla ma las sam bdag 'jug gi dabnga bzhi blang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9231: tshogas 'khor ram dpa' bo dpa' mo ston mos mchod nas de rnams su zhu zhing bshags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9232: rten khyad par can rab gnas can gyi drung du
NK120(e)001:9233: 'dug la yan lag bdun pa sngon du 'gro bas
NK120(e)001:9234: smre sngags kyis bshags pa bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9235: man+dal gyis mtshon lus srog longs spyod dge tshogs thams cad 'bula ba dang bcas bshags pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9236: mchod rten tshad ldan bzhengs par bya ba'am s+aats+tsha gdab pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9237: zhi ba'i bsreg blugs rgyas pa bya ba'am za byed
NK120(e)001:9238: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i sbyin sreg lta bu me la
NK120(e)001:9239: sbyong ba dang / gtor ma sbyangs rtog sbar gsum
NK120(e)001:9240: gyi byin gyis brlabs pa 'khor 'das thams cad 'khor
NK120(e)001:9241: lo'i dbang phyug gi rnam par sad pa la gtonga
NK120(e)001:9243: rang gi lhag pa'i lha'i gasnga sngagas bzla ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9244: zaba mo'i bsam gtan zhi lhag gi ting nge 'dzin bsgoms pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9245: nye'u 'don chu mig lteng ka nas srog chags skyob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9248: rngon pa la barngana ster ba /
NK120(e)001:9249: nad pa la phan gdags pa /
NK120(e)001:9250: mtshon cha'i 'og nas thar bar bya ba sroga sogs skyob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9251: sdig sgrib kyi gnyen por basngagasa pa'i thar pa chen po'i mdo dang /
NK120(e)001:9252: dri med bshags pa'i rgyud sogs bka'a zab mo klog pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9253: bla ma gtsug gi nor bu ltar bsten pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9254: snying gar dam tshig rdo rje don grub yab yum
NK120(e)001:9255: bsgom pa'i thugs ka'i sa bon las bdud rtsi'i rgyun
NK120(e)001:9256: babs pas sdig sgrib sbyong bar bsam la +aahkham h'u
NK120(e)001:9257: zhes pa'i bsnyen pa sngon du 'gro bas lus dkyil
NK120(e)001:9258: lam phyi dkyil gang rung du badga 'juga blang ba
NK120(e)001:9259: dang / rten byin can la bskor ba byed pa'am
NK120(e)001:9260: drung du 'dug nas dus gsum rgyala ba'i thugs kyi
NK120(e)001:9261: yang snying yiga brgya lnga stong sogs bzla ba dang
NK120(e)001:9262: dang / / yar ngo brgyad dang bco lnga sogs
NK120(e)001:9263: dus bazanga por sdig sbyong la basngagasa pa'i gzungs sngags
NK120(e)001:9265: nyin mtshan dus drug tu phunga po gsuma pa'i mdo 'don pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9266: spyi bor bla ma rdora semsa kyi rnam par bsgoms
NK120(e)001:9267: la sdig sgrib bkru ba'i dmigs pas yi ge brgya
NK120(e)001:9269: rang gnyug ma'i lhar gsal ba'i spya bor bla ma
NK120(e)001:9270: rdo rje 'chang gi rnam par bsgom pa'i gnas gsum
NK120(e)001:9271: 'bru gsum gsal ba yid bzlas bya ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9272: rang lhar gsal la rtsa 'khor gsal btab ste 'bar 'dzag bsgom pa thiga le'i rnal 'byor dang /
NK120(e)001:9273: rtsa 'khor lnga'i lte bar rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan phra
NK120(e)001:9274: mo gsal ba la sems bzung ste mgon po lnga'i
NK120(e)001:9275: rlung gcun pa phra mo'i rnal 'byor bsgoma pasa gso
NK120(e)001:9276: ba rnams so // bzhi pa yo ga gsum gyi rnal 'byor spyi khrus kyis gso ba ni /
NK120(e)001:9277: glang chen rab 'bogs rgyud las gsungs pa yi //
NK120(e)001:9278: rnal 'byor spyi khrus 'gyod tshangs dong sprug gi //
NK120(e)001:9279: bshags pas mi 'dag med phyir nyams su blangs //
NK120(e)001:9281: gzhan yang glang chena rab 'boga gi rgyud las rtog
NK120(e)001:9282: pa gcig khol du phyung ba kalpa dum bu'i rgyud
NK120(e)001:9283: dri med bshags rgyud las ji skad gsungas pa yi
NK120(e)001:9284: yo ga rnam pa gsum gyi sgor zhugs pa'i rnal
NK120(e)001:9285: 'byor pa rnams kyi nyams chag skong zhing rtog sgrib
NK120(e)001:9286: sbyong ba'i spyi khrus rmad du byung ba 'gyod tshangsa
NK120(e)001:9287: thams cad kyi rgyal po na raka donga sprug gi
NK120(e)001:9291: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi bskang bshags gsum nya stong tshes brgyad sogs la byas na /
NK120(e)001:9292: de tshun chad kyi nyams chag thams cad 'dag par gsungs shing /
NK120(e)001:9293: de tsam ma grub na'ang phyag gi bkol byang tsam
NK120(e)001:9294: rgyun du yi dam du bgyis nas bashagas pasa kyang
NK120(e)001:9295: nyams chag thams cad mi 'adga pa med par gsungs
NK120(e)001:9296: pa'i phyir na ci nas 'bad pas nyamsa su blangsa
NK120(e)001:9297: par bya ste / ji skad du /
NK120(e)001:9298: gang gis sgyu 'phrul zhi khro yi //
NK120(e)001:9299: dkyil 'khor lha la phyag btsal na //
NK120(e)001:9300: nyams chag kun kyang byang 'gyur te //
NK120(e)001:9301: mtshams med lnga yi sdig kyang 'byang //
NK120(e)001:9302: na raka gnas kyang dor sprugs te //
NK120(e)001:9303: rig 'dzin rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK120(e)001:9305: gang gis dkyil 'khor gyi lha de rnams kyi mtshan
NK120(e)001:9306: rnal 'byor pho mo rnams kyis thos pa tsam gyis
NK120(e)001:9307: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams chag
NK120(e)001:9310: de ltar bshags pa yang mdor na rmi lam du bla ma dang lhas legs so ster ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9313: ri bo chen po'i rtser 'dzegs pa /
NK120(e)001:9314: nyi zla shar ba sogs sdig ltung dag pa'i rtags
NK120(e)001:9315: ma byung gi bar de srid du stobs bzhi tshang
NK120(e)001:9316: ba'i bshags pa la 'bad par bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:9317: de yang yan lag tshang ba'i rtsa ltung ni bshags
NK120(e)001:9318: pas dag pa'i rtags byung ba dang slar dkyil 'khor
NK120(e)001:9319: du zhugs nas dbang blang bar bya ba khyad par
NK120(e)001:9320: ro // gnyis pa phyir bcos ma byas pa'i nyes dmigs ni /
NK120(e)001:9321: ma bshags tshe 'dir yid mi 'ong bas mnar //
NK120(e)001:9322: phyi ma rdo rje'i dmyal ba zhes bya ba //
NK120(e)001:9323: mnar med do zla med pa'i gnas su skye //
NK120(e)001:9325: de ltar nyes pa byung ba tshul bzhin du ma
NK120(e)001:9326: bashagas pa'i nyes dmigs ni bsam gyis mi khyab ste
NK120(e)001:9327: / rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams na sgrub pa thams cad phyin ci log tu 'gyur zhing /
NK120(e)001:9328: sku'i dam tshig nyams pas lus la nad sna tshogs 'byung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9329: gsung gi dam tshig nyams pas ngag dig lkug sogs su 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9330: thugs kyi dam tshig nyams pas yid smyo 'bogs su 'gyur ba ste /
NK120(e)001:9331: tshe 'dira yida du mi 'onga ba'i dngos po sna
NK120(e)001:9332: tshogs khab len la lcags bzhin du 'du basa manra
NK120(e)001:9334: rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK120(e)001:9335: sgrub pa thams cad log par 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:9336: yid du mi 'ong sna tshogs pa'i //
NK120(e)001:9339: yan lag gi dam tshig nyams par gyur na dngos
NK120(e)001:9340: grub rnam pa gnyis thob pa'i gegs su 'gyur zhing
NK120(e)001:9341: / de gnyis kas phyi ma rdo rje'i dmyal ba
NK120(e)001:9342: zhesa bya ba sdug bsngal gyi manra ba la de
NK120(e)001:9343: bas che ba med pas do zla med pa'i gnas
NK120(e)001:9344: su 'jig rten gyi khams brgyud cing skye bar 'gyur
NK120(e)001:9346: yan lag dam tshig nyams gyur na //
NK120(e)001:9347: 'bras bu med cing ngan song ltung //
NK120(e)001:9350: rtsa kun nyams pa'i 'chal ba dag /
NK120(e)001:9351: gso la nye bar mi brtson pa //
NK120(e)001:9352: rdo rje dmyal bar de ltung ste //
NK120(e)001:9353: dmyal ba phal pa thams cad kyi //
NK120(e)001:9354: sdug bsngal gcig tu bsdoms pas ni //
NK120(e)001:9355: de yi 'bum gyi char mi phod //
NK120(e)001:9357: de lta bu'i skye bo sdig po che rtsa ltung
NK120(e)001:9358: can des ni rang nyid nyams par ma zad gzhan
NK120(e)001:9359: la'ang zlas nyams kyi nyes pa ster bar byed de
NK120(e)001:9361: ji ltar 'o ma rul ba dag /
NK120(e)001:9362: rul bas 'o ma kun rul ltar //
NK120(e)001:9363: rnal 'byor nyams gyur gcig gis ni //
NK120(e)001:9364: rnal 'byor can kun ma rung byed //
NK120(e)001:9366: der ma zad rmi lam du nyes pa byas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9367: gzhan ci zer brtag pa'am gzhan gyi ngo dgar thal
NK120(e)001:9368: ba'i zhor nyams byung yang de ma thag ma bshags
NK120(e)001:9369: na nyes pa chen por 'gyur te /
NK120(e)001:9371: bla ma dang ni nye ba'i 'khor //
NK120(e)001:9372: rdo rje spun dang sring mo la //
NK120(e)001:9373: ngan smras tshig gi zung tsam yang //
NK120(e)001:9374: barda'am dngos por brjod mi bya //
NK120(e)001:9375: gal te rmi lam dag tu yang //
NK120(e)001:9376: byung na yid kyis bshags par bya //
NK120(e)001:9377: dngos dang zhe yis byas pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9378: gal te dran pas ma zin par //
NK120(e)001:9379: thal bar gyur kyang ma bshags na //
NK120(e)001:9380: mthur du bltas te dmyal bar 'gro //
NK120(e)001:9383: de las sngags pas yongs 'das na //
NK120(e)001:9386: bstir med spyi'u tshugs dmyal bar 'gro //
NK120(e)001:9387: sbom po'i ltung byed nyes dmigs kyang //
NK120(e)001:9388: de dang 'dra bar shes par bya //
NK120(e)001:9389: zhes rtsa ba dang yan lag gi ltung ba gnyis
NK120(e)001:9390: kas dmyal bar skye ba 'dra ba lta bur gsungs
NK120(e)001:9391: na'ang / sdug bsngal che chung dang mnar yun ring thung gi khyad par che'o //
NK120(e)001:9392: bdun pa dam tshig ma nyams par tshul bzhin bsrung ba'i phan yon ni //
NK120(e)001:9393: ma nyams ring mtha' skye ba bcu drug gam //
NK120(e)001:9394: myur na tshe 'adi'am 'chi kha bar do ru //
NK120(e)001:9395: thun mong grub pa brgyad dang dbang phyug brgyad //
NK120(e)001:9396: mchog gi dngos grub kha sbyor bdun ldan thob //
NK120(e)001:9397: de phyir rang gzhan don gnyis lhun gyis grub //
NK120(e)001:9399: spyir dam tshig ni yon tan thams cad skye ba dang gnas pa'i gzhi rten du gyur pa ste /
NK120(e)001:9401: ji ltar sa gzhi gshin pa la //
NK120(e)001:9402: brten nas sa bon btab pa las //
NK120(e)001:9403: 'bras bu smin par gyur pa yis //
NK120(e)001:9405: chos rnams kun gyi gzhir gyur pa //
NK120(e)001:9406: dam tshig 'di la gnas pa na //
NK120(e)001:9407: bla med byang chub rnam smin pas //
NK120(e)001:9410: khyad par gnas skabs su'ang bsam pa'i don thams cad ji lta ba bzhin du 'grub pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9411: kun gyi yid du 'ong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9412: 'jig rten gyi lha chen po rnams kyi bkur gnas thob pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9413: sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa' dpa' bo rnal
NK120(e)001:9414: 'byor ma rnams kyis sras dang spun du dgongs pas
NK120(e)001:9416: de bzhin gshegs pa nyid kyi spyod yul la zhugs
NK120(e)001:9417: pas rig pa 'dzin pa'i sa la rim gyis sbyor
NK120(e)001:9420: rgyal ba'i rig mchog 'dzin pa de //
NK120(e)001:9422: dam pa mchog dang dam pa yi //
NK120(e)001:9423: sras dang spun dgongs byin gyis brlab //
NK120(e)001:9424: bde gshegs nyid kyi yul la zhugs //
NK120(e)001:9425: 'jigs med kun tu bzang por sbyor //
NK120(e)001:9428: gsang sngags rdo rje'i dam la gnas //
NK120(e)001:9429: de yi smon pa kun 'grub cing //
NK120(e)001:9430: lha rnams kyis kyang rtag tu bsrung //
NK120(e)001:9431: rgyal ba rgyal mchog sras bcas kyis //
NK120(e)001:9432: bu bzhin dgongs pa dam pa mdzad //
NK120(e)001:9433: ting 'dzin yon tan dpag yas shing //
NK120(e)001:9434: kun bzang rigs kyi dam pa 'grub //
NK120(e)001:9436: gal te tshe 'dir rim gnyis kyi lam la brtson
NK120(e)001:9437: ma nus kyang dam tshig ma nyamsa na ji ltar
NK120(e)001:9438: 'gor yang ringa matha'a skye ba bcu drug gama /
NK120(e)001:9439: skye ba bdun na rim gnyis kyi lam dang 'phrad nas grol bar 'gyur la /
NK120(e)001:9440: shin tu myur ba'i dbang du byas na dam tshig
NK120(e)001:9441: rnam par dag cing lam rim la 'bad pas dbang
NK120(e)001:9442: po rnon po tshe 'dira zung 'jug rdo rje 'chang
NK120(e)001:9444: dbang po 'bring rnams ni tshe 'dir dpe'i 'od gsal
NK120(e)001:9445: mngon du gyur pa zhig yin na 'chi kha don
NK120(e)001:9446: gyi 'od gsal du gyur nas slob pa'i zung 'jug
NK120(e)001:9448: gal te don gyi 'od gsal mngon du gyur pa zhig yin na /
NK120(e)001:9449: 'chi srid gzhi dus kyi 'od gsal dang 'dres pas
NK120(e)001:9450: yang dag pa'i mtha' mngon du byas te mi slob
NK120(e)001:9451: pa'i zung 'jug gi skur ldang zhing /
NK120(e)001:9452: 'bring gi tha mas kyang srid pa bar do ru
NK120(e)001:9453: rang gi nyams len dang bla ma la mos gus
NK120(e)001:9454: dang dag pa'i zhing yid la byas pas rang bzhin
NK120(e)001:9455: sprul sku'i zhing du dbugs dbyung ste grol bar 'gyur
NK120(e)001:9456: ro // de dag gi tshe thob bya'i yon tan
NK120(e)001:9457: mtha' yas pa yod na'ang thun mchog gi dngos grub
NK120(e)001:9459: thuna monga gi dngos grub chung ngu ni las chen brgyad thob ste /
NK120(e)001:9460: dgyes rdor las gsungs pa sdom du byas na /
NK120(e)001:9461: dbang dang mngon spyod dgra sde 'jig /
NK120(e)001:9462: bskrad dang bsad dang dgug dang zhi //
NK120(e)001:9467: gang phyir des ni dka' ba min //
NK120(e)001:9468: mig sman dang ni rkang mgyogs dang //
NK120(e)001:9469: ral gri dang ni sa 'og grub //
NK120(e)001:9470: ril bu grub dang mkha' spyod nyid //
NK120(e)001:9471: mi snang ba dang bcud kyis len //
NK120(e)001:9472: gang phyir des ni rdo rje 'dzin //
NK120(e)001:9473: mnyes par byas las myur du thob //
NK120(e)001:9475: chen po ni dabnga phyug gi yon tan brgyad de /
NK120(e)001:9477: gzugs phra rags pa yangs pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9478: khyab pa yang dag thob pa nyid //
NK120(e)001:9479: rab tu gsal ba nyid brtan pa //
NK120(e)001:9480: dbang phyug nyid dang 'dod rgur bsgyur //
NK120(e)001:9482: 'di dag ni bskyed rim kho nas kyang 'grub nus pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:9483: thun mong zhes pa'i don ni yon tan 'di dag
NK120(e)001:9484: phyi rol pa la'ang yod pas 'jig rten pa dang
NK120(e)001:9485: 'das lam gnyis ka'i thun mong ba dang bskyed rdzogs
NK120(e)001:9486: gnyis ka'i thun mong gi yon tan yin pas kyang
NK120(e)001:9489: sku bzhi ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid mi slob pa'i zung 'jug mngon du brnyes pa'o //
NK120(e)001:9490: de yang ldog chas dbye na kha sbyor yan lag bduna ldana thob par gyur ba ste /
NK120(e)001:9491: gsung rnam pa thams cad pa theg pa chen po'i
NK120(e)001:9492: chos la longs spyod pas na longs spyod rdzogs pa
NK120(e)001:9493: 1dang / sku shes bya'i snang brnyan yod rgur 'char ba ni kha sbyor 2dang /
NK120(e)001:9494: mi 'gyur ba'i bde ba chen po 3dang /
NK120(e)001:9495: rang bzhin gyis med pa ni spros pa thams cad las 'das pa'i stong nyid 4dang /
NK120(e)001:9496: snying rjes yongs gang ni dmigs pa med pa'i thugs rje chen po 5dang /
NK120(e)001:9497: rgyun mi chad pa'i thugs rje de nyid nam du'ang rgyun chad med par 'jug pas rtag pa 6dang /
NK120(e)001:9498: 'gog pa med pa ni sems can so so'i mos
NK120(e)001:9499: pa ltar sku dang chos sgo mtha' yas par 'char
NK120(e)001:9500: ba 7dang / de yang dang po bzhis rang don dang /
NK120(e)001:9501: phyi ma gsum gyis gzhan don phun tshogs bstan pa bcas /
NK120(e)001:9502: de'i phyir na ranga gzhan gyi dona gnyis lhun gyis grub par 'gyur ro //
NK120(e)001:9504: gsang sngags rig 'dzin sdom pa'i rim par phye ba ste bzhi pa'o //
NK120(e)001:9506: rdo rje theg pa thun mong ma yin pa'i bstan
NK120(e)001:9507: pa'i nyams len gasnga sngagas riga pa 'dzina pa'i sdoma
NK120(e)001:9508: pa'i don rnam par gzhag pa bslab bya dang bcas
NK120(e)001:9509: pa bshad pa'i rima para phye ba ste le'u bzhi
NK120(e)001:9510: pa'i 'grel pa'o //// gsum pa sdom pa gsum gang
NK120(e)001:9511: zag gcig gi rgyud la 'gal med du nyams su
NK120(e)001:9512: len tshul gyis mtha' dpyad pas don bsdu ba la
NK120(e)001:9513: pa'i 'grel pa'o //// gsum / brjod bya'i lus ngos bzung ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa /
NK120(e)001:9514: yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'i sgo nas mtha' dpyad pa /
NK120(e)001:9515: sdom pa gsum nyams su len tshul bsdus te bstan pa'i sgo nas mjug bsdu ba'o //
NK120(e)001:9516: dang po brjod bya'i lus ngos bzung ba'i sgo nas mdor bstan pa ni /
NK120(e)001:9517: de lta'i sdom gsum gang zag rgyud gcig la //
NK120(e)001:9518: rang ldog ma 'dres dgag dgos yongs su rdzogs //
NK120(e)001:9519: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yon tan yar ldan pas //
NK120(e)001:9520: gnad kyis mi 'gal dus skabs gang gtsor spyod //
NK120(e)001:9522: da ni de lta'i so byang sngags kyi sdom pa
NK120(e)001:9523: gsuma po de rim par nod pa'i gang zaga gi
NK120(e)001:9524: rgyud gciga la 'gal med du nyams su len tshul
NK120(e)001:9525: gyi mtha' dpyad pas don bsdu ba'i tshul bshad par
NK120(e)001:9526: bya ste / de la mdo rgyud dgongs 'grel dang
NK120(e)001:9527: bcas pa'i don la shes rab gsum gyis slob pa
NK120(e)001:9528: zad mi shes pa mnga' ba gsar rnying gi mkhas
NK120(e)001:9529: grub du ma'i dgongs pa rma med pa nyid gzhung
NK120(e)001:9530: 'dir bkod pa'i don ngos bzung ba ste /
NK120(e)001:9531: sdom pa gsum po de rang ranga gi ldoga pa ma 'dresa pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9532: dagga bya dang dgosa pa yongas su rdzogas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9533: sdo ma pa 'og ma'i ngo bo gong mar gansa 'gyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9534: 'og ma'i yona tan gong mar yara ldana gyi tshul yod pasa dang /
NK120(e)001:9535: rnam pa 'gal bar snang yang ganda kyis mi 'agla ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9536: dusa dang skabas ganga du gong 'og gang gtso bora
NK120(e)001:9537: spyod dgos pa'i tshul te rnam pa drug po 'di
NK120(e)001:9538: ni kun mkhyen klong chen pa'i bsam gtan ngal gso
NK120(e)001:9539: las / nyan thos byang chub sems dang rig pa 'dzin //
NK120(e)001:9540: sdom pa gsum po dag dang mi 'gal bar //
NK120(e)001:9541: rang rgyud sdom zhing gzhan phan ci 'grub dang //
NK120(e)001:9542: cir snang dag pa'i lam du bsgyur bar bya //
NK120(e)001:9543: zhes pa'i don 'grel ba shing rta rnam dag tu 'chad pa ni /
NK120(e)001:9546: gang zag gcig gi rgyud la gsum ldan du bsrung ba la /
NK120(e)001:9551: sdom pa gsum gnad kyis mi 'gal ba /
NK120(e)001:9552: dus skabs kyi gtso bor gang 'gyur du bya ba dang drug go //
NK120(e)001:9553: zhes gsungs pa dang dgongs pa gcig go //
NK120(e)001:9554: gnyis pa yan lag rgyas par bshad pa'i sgo nas
NK120(e)001:9555: mtha' dpyad pa la nang gses don tshan drug tu
NK120(e)001:9556: yod pa las / dang po sdom gsum rang ldog ma 'dres pa'i tshul ni /
NK120(e)001:9557: de yang blang yul bsam pa cho ga rnams //
NK120(e)001:9558: so sor nges phyir rang ldog ma 'dres yin //
NK120(e)001:9560: sdom pa gsum po de yang /
NK120(e)001:9562: gang gis len pa'i bsam pa /
NK120(e)001:9563: ji ltar len pa'i cho ga rnams tha dad pa'i sgo nas /
NK120(e)001:9564: ji srid du blangs pa'i dus kyang so sora ngesa pa'i phyir na /
NK120(e)001:9565: ngo bo gnas 'gyur yang rang rang gi ldooga pa
NK120(e)001:9566: la gzhi mthun pa mi srid pas ma 'dresa par
NK120(e)001:9568: thob pa ma nyams par so sor gnas pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:9569: de yang yin te so thar ni ji srid 'tsho'i bar dang /
NK120(e)001:9570: byang sdom ni snying po byang chub kyi bar du khas blangs kyi /
NK120(e)001:9571: sngags sdom thob dus de dang de nyams rkyen dang gtong rgyur ma bshad pas /
NK120(e)001:9572: dper na bsam pa sems bskyed kyis zin pas cho
NK120(e)001:9573: ga nyan thos kyi lugs ltar blangs pa'i theg chen
NK120(e)001:9574: so thar ram nyan thos kyi dge slong gi sdom
NK120(e)001:9575: pa nyid slar sems bskyed blangs pas der gnas 'gyur
NK120(e)001:9576: ba'i rgyud kyi so thar gyi sdom pa gang yin
NK120(e)001:9577: kyang rung ste / de la kun slong byang chub sems kyi ldog pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9578: sdom pa'i ldog pa gnyis yod pa las snga ma tshe 'phos pa'i dus su mi gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:9579: de byang sems kyi sdom pa'i gtong rgyu ma yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:9580: phyi ma sdom pa khas blangs pa'i dus kyi ldog cha ni gtong ste /
NK120(e)001:9581: ji srid 'tsho'i mtha' can yin pa'i phyir /
NK120(e)001:9582: de ltar yang rab dbye las /
NK120(e)001:9583: theg chen so sor thar yin yang //
NK120(e)001:9584: dge slong la sogs sdom pa yi //
NK120(e)001:9585: ldog pa shi ba'i tshe na gtong //
NK120(e)001:9586: byang chub sems kyi ldog pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9589: gnyis pa dgag dgos yongs rdzogs ni /
NK120(e)001:9590: dgag bya nyon mongs dgos pa mi 'ching bar //
NK120(e)001:9591: rang rang lam gyi ngos nas yongs su rdzogs //
NK120(e)001:9592: spong bsgyur lam du byed pa so so yang //
NK120(e)001:9593: nyon mongs rang mtshan spong bar mkhas rnams mthun //
NK120(e)001:9595: sdom pa gsum kas dagga bya rang rgyud kyi nyon mongas pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9596: des kun nas bslangs pa'i mi dge ba sdom par gcig ste /
NK120(e)001:9598: chos gang zhig dngos dang brgyud nas kun tu 'dod
NK120(e)001:9599: chags pa'i rgyur 'gyur gyi kun tu 'dod chags dang
NK120(e)001:9600: bral bar mi 'gyur ba 'di ni chos ma yin
NK120(e)001:9602: ston pa'i bstan pa ma yin par shes par gyis shig /
NK120(e)001:9603: chos gang zhig dngos dang brgyud nas kun tu 'dod
NK120(e)001:9604: chags dang bral ba'i rgyur 'gyur gyi kun tu 'dod
NK120(e)001:9605: chags kyi rgyur mi 'gyur ba 'di ni chos yin
NK120(e)001:9607: ston pa'i bstan pa yin par shes par byos shig /
NK120(e)001:9608: zhes pa la sogs pa gsungs so //
NK120(e)001:9609: dgosa pa nyon mongs pa des rang rgyud mi 'chinga bar yang mtshungs te /
NK120(e)001:9610: mi tshangs spyod lta bu nyan thos pas mi spyod pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9611: gong ma gnyis kyi thabs kyis zin pas spyad pa
NK120(e)001:9612: gnyis ka 'dod pa'i dri mas ma gos par 'dra
NK120(e)001:9613: bas rnam pa mi 'dra yang rar ranga gi lam
NK120(e)001:9614: gyi ngosa nasa dgag dgos kyi yon tan yongas su
NK120(e)001:9615: rdzogas pa ste / nyan thos pas bden gnyis rdza
NK120(e)001:9616: sa yod du bltas nas so thar gyis nyon mongs
NK120(e)001:9618: byang chub sems dpa' rang bzhin med par shes nas chos nyid du bsgyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9619: gsang sngags pas de ye shes kyi rang bzhin du
NK120(e)001:9620: bltas te lam du byed pa'i tshul soo so ba
NK120(e)001:9621: ltar snang yanga 'ching byed kyi nyona moongs rang matshana
NK120(e)001:9622: pa rnams sponga bar makhasa pa rnams mthuna te /
NK120(e)001:9623: dper na dug spong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9625: sngags kyis btab ste bza' ba gsum kas kyang dug
NK120(e)001:9626: gis mi gnod pa'i dgos pa sgrub par gcig pa
NK120(e)001:9627: bzhin no // gsum pa ngo bo gnas 'gyur ni /
NK120(e)001:9628: so thar kun slong sems bskyed kyis zin na //
NK120(e)001:9629: nyes spyod sdom pa zhes bya'i tshul khrims yin //
NK120(e)001:9630: dbang thob rdo rje 'dzin pa'i sdom par 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:9631: de phyir ngo bo gnas 'gyur yin no zhes //
NK120(e)001:9632: 'bum phrag lnga pa'i lung gis gsal bar grub //
NK120(e)001:9634: nyon mongs rang ga mas kun nas bslangs pa'i sgo
NK120(e)001:9635: gsum gyi las kyis 'khor bar 'ching bas de nyid
NK120(e)001:9636: shes rab dang snying rje phyogs gcig gis bzung nas
NK120(e)001:9637: nyes spyod spong ba'i sdom pa la zhugs pa na
NK120(e)001:9639: mthar thug thar pa'i rgyur 'gyur ba'i soo thara de
NK120(e)001:9640: nyid kuna slong semas bskyed dang shes rab chen po
NK120(e)001:9641: gnyis kyis zina nasa gzhan don gyi bya ba la
NK120(e)001:9642: zhugs na byang chub chen por grol ba'i rgyur 'gyur
NK120(e)001:9643: ba byang chub sems dpa'i nyes spyod sdoma pa zhesa
NK120(e)001:9644: bya ba'i tshul khrimsa yina la /
NK120(e)001:9645: de nyid kyang dabnga thob cing thabs shes chen pos
NK120(e)001:9646: yongs su zin pa ni bla na med pa'i byang
NK120(e)001:9647: chub chen por 'bad rtsol med par lhun gyis grub
NK120(e)001:9648: pa'i rgyur rdo rje 'dzina pa'i sdom para 'gyur ba
NK120(e)001:9649: de'i phyir 'og ma gnyis kyi skabs su rang don
NK120(e)001:9650: yid byed tha mal snang zhen re yod pa btang
NK120(e)001:9651: nas gzhan gnod gzhir bcas spong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9652: gzhan phan gzhir bcas sgrub pa'i sems pa gnyis sngags
NK120(e)001:9653: sdom gyi ngo bora gansa 'gyur ba yina no zhesa
NK120(e)001:9654: 'buma phrag lnga pa'i lung gisa gasla bar grub ste
NK120(e)001:9656: rdo yi rigs kyi bre brag zhig /
NK120(e)001:9657: ces pa la sogs pa sngar drangs pa ltar ram /
NK120(e)001:9658: yang na gsang ba spyod pa'i rgyud las /
NK120(e)001:9659: dper na rdo las zangs su 'gyur //
NK120(e)001:9660: zangs las gser gyi rnam pa ste //
NK120(e)001:9661: zangs kyi dus na rdo med la //
NK120(e)001:9662: gser du gyur pas zangs mi snang //
NK120(e)001:9663: rig 'dzin nang gi dge slong la //
NK120(e)001:9664: so sor thar dang byang chub sems //
NK120(e)001:9665: gnyis po gnas pa nyid du ni //
NK120(e)001:9666: sangs rgyas nyid kyis ma gsungs so //
NK120(e)001:9667: zhes pa ltar sngags sdom thob ste thabs shes khyad
NK120(e)001:9668: par can gyi ye shes rgyud la skyes na 'og
NK120(e)001:9669: ma gnyis kyi dman sems dang /
NK120(e)001:9670: tha mal snang zhen gyi ldog cha de dus mi gnas la /
NK120(e)001:9671: sdom pa'i ngo bo ni rigs lnga spyi'i rnam snang
NK120(e)001:9672: gi dam tshig tu gnas 'gyur bas tha dad pa
NK120(e)001:9673: med do // bzhi pa yon tan yar ldan ni /
NK120(e)001:9674: 'jig rten rnal 'byor rnal 'byor blo khyad kyis //
NK120(e)001:9675: gong ma gong mas gnod phyir 'og ma yi //
NK120(e)001:9676: yon tan yar ldan 'og ma zin gyis gnon //
NK120(e)001:9679: bslab gsum gyi nyams len cung zad rgyud la 'byor pa'i rnal 'byor pa dang /
NK120(e)001:9680: de yang thabs shes khyad par can gyis zin pa'i
NK120(e)001:9681: rnal 'byor pa rnams blo na 'phar ba'i khyad par
NK120(e)001:9682: gyis gonga ma gonga mas 'og ma 'og ma rnams
NK120(e)001:9683: kyi rgyud kyi dman sems dang /
NK120(e)001:9684: snang zhen la sogs pa la gnod cing spong ba'i phyir dang /
NK120(e)001:9685: 'oga ma'i sdom pa bsrungs pa yi yona tan gong
NK120(e)001:9686: ma'i sdom pa'i ngang du yara ldan gyi tshul gyis
NK120(e)001:9687: 'oga ma zila gyis gnona pa'i phyir te /
NK120(e)001:9689: bla med mchog gi dam tshig tu //
NK120(e)001:9690: 'dul ba'i dbang gis tshul khrims dang //
NK120(e)001:9691: ji snyed sdom pa bsam yas pa //
NK120(e)001:9692: ma lus kun 'dus rnam par dag /
NK120(e)001:9694: lnga pa gnad kyis mi 'gal ba ni //
NK120(e)001:9695: 'du shes gsum gyis 'khrig na rnal 'byor de //
NK120(e)001:9696: yul bsam sbyor ba mthar thug ma tshang bas //
NK120(e)001:9697: rmi lam ji bzhin gnad kyis 'gal mi srid //
NK120(e)001:9699: sdom pa 'og ma gnyis gong mar 'dus pa mi
NK120(e)001:9700: 'thad de so thar gyi pham bzhi 'chab bcas spong
NK120(e)001:9701: ba dang / byang sems kyi sems can 'tshe ba
NK120(e)001:9702: cha bcas las ldog nas gzhan la phan 'dogs pa
NK120(e)001:9703: de sngags sdom gyi spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig
NK120(e)001:9704: lnga dang dngos su 'gal ba'i phyir snyam na /
NK120(e)001:9705: rnam pa 'gal ba ltar snang yang /
NK120(e)001:9706: pham pa bzhi'i nang tshan mi tshangs spyod lta bu
NK120(e)001:9707: la mtshon na 'du shes gsuma gyi sgo nas las
NK120(e)001:9708: rgya bsten pa'i tshe 'khriga spyod kyi rnam pa ltar
NK120(e)001:9709: snang na'ang / rnal 'byor pa de la yul gyi
NK120(e)001:9710: 'du shes rang mtshan pa de log nas yab yum
NK120(e)001:9711: lha'i 'du shes su gnas 'gyur bas yul gyi yan
NK120(e)001:9713: srid pa rang mtshan pa de bde chen chos kyi
NK120(e)001:9714: 'du shes su gnas 'gyur bas bsam pa'i yan lag
NK120(e)001:9715: ma tshang la / chags pas bya ba'i sbyor ba
NK120(e)001:9716: de byed pa sdom pa'i thabs mkhas kyis zin pas
NK120(e)001:9717: sbyor ba'i yan lag ma tshang ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9718: mthar thug thig le 'phos pas bde ba'i sim pa
NK120(e)001:9719: bdag gir byed pa de chags pa'i ro ye shes
NK120(e)001:9720: su bsgyur zhing thig le 'dzag med du 'ching ba'i
NK120(e)001:9721: phyir mathara thug gi yan lag ma tshang basa na
NK120(e)001:9722: / chos thams cad sems nyid rang snang du shes
NK120(e)001:9723: pas rmi lam gyi gnas skabs na bya ba byas
NK120(e)001:9724: pa ji bzhina du ganda kyisa 'agla ba ni mi
NK120(e)001:9726: ma chags pa la chags pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9727: chags pa nyid na chags pa med //
NK120(e)001:9728: de ni tshangs mchog rgyal po ste //
NK120(e)001:9729: shin tu chags pa chen po yin //
NK120(e)001:9731: ye nas skye med de bzhin nyid //
NK120(e)001:9732: sgyu mar snang ba mig yor tshul //
NK120(e)001:9733: sbyor sgrol bya ba kun byas kyang //
NK120(e)001:9734: rdul cha tsam yang byas pa med //
NK120(e)001:9736: drug pa gnas skabs gang gtsor spyod pa ni /
NK120(e)001:9737: sdig to mi dge'i phyogs dang tshogs pa'i gseb /
NK120(e)001:9738: 'og ma gtsor byed 'dod pas dben pa dang //
NK120(e)001:9739: spyod pa'i dus dang dben par gsang sngags spyad //
NK120(e)001:9740: nang ma 'doms na ma 'dres yongs rdzogs bsrung //
NK120(e)001:9741: 'doms na dgag dgos brtsi zhes mkhas rnams bzhed //
NK120(e)001:9742: las dang po dang rnal 'byor grub thob dang //
NK120(e)001:9743: thams cad mkhyen pa'i spyod pa gang yin pa //
NK120(e)001:9744: dus tshod 'brel bar dgos zhes dus 'khor bshad //
NK120(e)001:9746: sdiga to mi dge ba'i phyogsa rang bzhin gyi kha na ma tho ba rnams dang /
NK120(e)001:9747: tshogas pa mang po'i gseba tu las dang po pa rnams lta ci smos /
NK120(e)001:9748: rang rgyud la nyes pas mi gos pa'i rnal 'byor
NK120(e)001:9749: pa rnams kyis kyang gdul bya'i rgyud chud mi za
NK120(e)001:9750: ba'i phyir 'oga ma nyan thos kyi lugs gtso bora
NK120(e)001:9752: phyi ru nyan thos spyod pa skyongs //
NK120(e)001:9753: nang du 'dus pa'i don la dga' //
NK120(e)001:9756: phyi ltar lag len mdo sde'i lugs su spyad //
NK120(e)001:9757: rgyu 'bras spang blang zhib pa'i dgos pa yod //
NK120(e)001:9759: yang byang chub sems dpa' rang 'doda yid la byed
NK120(e)001:9760: pasa dbeen pa na gzhan don du 'gyur nges pa'i
NK120(e)001:9761: lus ngag gi mi dge ba bdun gnang ba dang
NK120(e)001:9762: / gsang sngags thun mong ma yin pa'i spyod pa
NK120(e)001:9763: spyad pa'i dus dang dben para ni gsang sngags kyi
NK120(e)001:9764: spyod pa rnams spyad na 'og ma rnams dang 'gal
NK120(e)001:9765: ba ltar snang yang ltung ba'i gzugs brnyan tsam las
NK120(e)001:9766: don la nyes pa med par ma zad dgos pa
NK120(e)001:9767: / dang ldan te / slob dpon chen pos /
NK120(e)001:9768: nang ltar gsang sngags thun mong lugs su spyad //
NK120(e)001:9769: bskyed rdzogs don dang 'brel ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK120(e)001:9770: gsang ba gsang chen a ti'i lugs su spyad //
NK120(e)001:9771: tshe gcig 'od skur grol ba'i dgos pa yod //
NK120(e)001:9774: 'di la sdig to mi dge'i phyogs //
NK120(e)001:9775: phal cher nyan thos lugs bzhin bsrung //
NK120(e)001:9776: 'dod pas dben pa'i ltung ba dga' //
NK120(e)001:9777: byang chub sems dpa'i lugs bzhin bsrung //
NK120(e)001:9779: gnyis ka mthun rnams 'bad pas bsrung //
NK120(e)001:9781: theg chen so sor thar la gnang //
NK120(e)001:9783: sdom pa gsum ka nang ma 'domas pa ste mthun
NK120(e)001:9784: par gyur na gzhan mi dad par gyur pa'i cha
NK120(e)001:9785: la sogs pa spang blang gi gnas thams cad so
NK120(e)001:9786: sor ma 'dresa par yongas su rdzogas par bsrunga bar
NK120(e)001:9787: bya zhing / nang 'domas pa ste gcig gi spang
NK120(e)001:9788: byar bshad pa gcig gi bsrung byar song nas 'gal
NK120(e)001:9789: bar gyur na rang rgyud kyi dagga bya nyon mongs
NK120(e)001:9791: dgosa pa mi 'ching ba gnyis gang du tshang ba
NK120(e)001:9792: brtsisa nas gang du tshang ba de spyad par bya
NK120(e)001:9793: dgos so zhesa makhasa pa rnams bzheda de /
NK120(e)001:9794: mi dge ba dang nyes pa skye ba gang yang 'gog cing /
NK120(e)001:9795: dge ba dang yon tan bskyed na gang la yang bslab par bya dgos pas /
NK120(e)001:9796: spyir btang dang dmigs bsal gyi gnad shes pa gal che ba'i phyir ro //
NK120(e)001:9797: de yang gsum ldan rdo rje 'dzin pas spyod pa
NK120(e)001:9798: kha na ma tho ba med cing dus tshod dang
NK120(e)001:9799: 'brel bar spyod dgos pas gnas skabs so so'i blang
NK120(e)001:9800: dor kyang shes par bya ste /
NK120(e)001:9801: lasa dang po pas so thar gyi dgag bya dang
NK120(e)001:9802: byang sngags kyi rtsa ba dang yan lag gi ltung
NK120(e)001:9803: ba rnams gtso bor bsrung ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9804: de yang sngags sam ting 'dzin gyis chang gi ro bsgyur ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9805: dug zhi ba la sogs pa'i drod ma thob pa de srid du las dang po pa zhes bya'o //
NK120(e)001:9806: brtan pa thob nas blo na 'phar ba'i rim pa
NK120(e)001:9807: ltar bskyed rdzogs kyi rnal 'byor la gnas pa'i sgo
NK120(e)001:9808: nas dam rdzas khyad par can brten pa sogs sngags
NK120(e)001:9809: nang rgyud kyi spyod pa thun mong ba dang /
NK120(e)001:9810: bskyed rdzogs la goms pa'i 'bras bu gnas skabs grub
NK120(e)001:9811: pa thob pa na blang dor med pa'i spyod pa
NK120(e)001:9812: dang / mthar thug gi 'bras bu thamsa cad mkhyen
NK120(e)001:9813: pa'i ye shes mngon du gyur pa'i tshe na gzhan
NK120(e)001:9814: la phan pa'i spyod pa kho na gang yina pa
NK120(e)001:9815: de dang de dag dus tshod dang 'brela ba spyod
NK120(e)001:9816: dgosa zhesa dus 'khor las bashada de /
NK120(e)001:9818: de'i phyir las dang po pas rnal 'byor pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:9819: rnal 'byor pas grub pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:9820: grub pas thams cad mkhyen pa'i bya ba mi bya'o //
NK120(e)001:9822: gsum pa sdom pa gsum nyams su len tshul bsdus te bstan pa'i sgo nas mjug bsdu ba ni /
NK120(e)001:9823: yon tan gzhi rten so thar gang nus steng //
NK120(e)001:9824: bya chub sems bskyed sngags kyi yan lag yin //
NK120(e)001:9825: smin byed dbang thob sdom gsum mig ltar bsrung //
NK120(e)001:9826: gdan gsum lha ru shes pa'i bskyed rim dang //
NK120(e)001:9827: mtshan bcas mtshan ma med pa'i rdzogs rim bsgom //
NK120(e)001:9828: nye rgyu'i spyod pas rim bzhin mtshams sbyar nas //
NK120(e)001:9829: 'adi'am 'chi kha dang ni bar do ru //
NK120(e)001:9830: rang bzhin sprul pa'i zhing du rdzogs 'tshang rgya //
NK120(e)001:9832: nyan thos dang thun mong ba'i lam du 'khor ba
NK120(e)001:9833: la skyo shas dang nges 'byung gis kun nas bslangs
NK120(e)001:9834: te yoona tan thams cad kyi gzhi rten spong ba
NK120(e)001:9835: bzhi'am bdun ldan gyi so sor thara pa rigs bdun
NK120(e)001:9836: gyi sdom pa ganga nus blangs la lus ngag nyes
NK120(e)001:9837: spyod las ldog par bya zhing /
NK120(e)001:9838: de'i steng du mtha' yas pa'i sems can thams cad
NK120(e)001:9839: kyi don du byang chub thob 'dod kyi bsam pas
NK120(e)001:9840: sems bskyed kyi sdom pa blangs na /
NK120(e)001:9841: de gnyis gsang sngagsa kyi sdom pa'i yan lag tu 'gyur ba yina la /
NK120(e)001:9842: de yang sems can thams cad gdod ma nas rnam
NK120(e)001:9843: par dag kyang de ltar ma rtogs pas sdug bsngal
NK120(e)001:9844: rgyu 'bras kyis gzir ba la bzod phod pa'i snying
NK120(e)001:9845: stobs drag pos / kun nas bslangs te smin byed
NK120(e)001:9846: kyi dabnga la brten nas rig pa 'dzin pa'i sdom
NK120(e)001:9847: pa rgyud la thob par byas nas sdom pa gsuma
NK120(e)001:9848: po de'i bslab bya rnams dgag dgos kyi gnad shes
NK120(e)001:9849: pa'i sgo nas miga gi 'bras bu ltar gces spras
NK120(e)001:9850: kyis bsrunga bar bya zhing sbyang gzhi sbyang byed ngo
NK120(e)001:9851: 'phrod pa'i sgo nas gadna gsuma lha ru shesa pa'i
NK120(e)001:9852: lta ba dang ma bral bar bskyed rim zab mo
NK120(e)001:9854: rtsa rlung thig le la dngos su gnad du bsnun
NK120(e)001:9855: pas lam matshana bacasa kyi rdzogs rim thabs lam steng
NK120(e)001:9857: de thams cad kyi rgyas gdab tu gyur pa matshana ma med pa'i rdzogsa rim bsgom zhing /
NK120(e)001:9858: goms pa na zag pa med pa'i 'bras bu la
NK120(e)001:9859: myur du sbyor ba'i nye rgyu'i spyod pasa rima pa
NK120(e)001:9860: bzhina matshamas sbyar nas dbang po rab tshe 'di zung
NK120(e)001:9862: 'bring 'chi kha 'od gsal las zung 'jug gi skur ldang ba dang ni /
NK120(e)001:9863: tha ma srid pa bar do ru chos nyid kyi
NK120(e)001:9864: bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis ranga bzhina sprul pa sku'i
NK120(e)001:9865: zhing du rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i rigs
NK120(e)001:9866: lnga'i sangs rgyas kyi zhal mthong zhing dbang bskur la
NK120(e)001:9867: byang chub tu lung bstan te dbugs dbyung ba thob
NK120(e)001:9868: nas mngon par rdzogas par 'tshang rgya ba yin no
NK120(e)001:9870: sdom gsum spyir dpyad pa'i rim par phye ba ste lnga pa'o //
NK120(e)001:9872: sngom pa gsuma gyi bsrung bya nyams su len tshul
NK120(e)001:9873: gyi gnad spyir dpyad pa'i rima para phye ba ste
NK120(e)001:9874: le'u lnga pa'i rnam par bshad pa'o //
NK120(e)001:9875: rtsa ba'i gsum pa bshad pa mthar phyin pa'i bya ba la lnga /
NK120(e)001:9876: dang po rtsom pa'i rgyu brtse ba'i snying rje chen
NK120(e)001:9877: po thugs rgyud la ji ltar 'khrungs pa'i tshul ni
NK120(e)001:9878: / deng sang ma sbyangs mu cor smra ba brgyas //
NK120(e)001:9879: rang gi ye shes rdul tsam ma rtogs par //
NK120(e)001:9880: rang bzo'i cho gas rmongs rnams tshim pa'i dus //
NK120(e)001:9881: skyabs de bsam gyin snying nas mchi ma dku //
NK120(e)001:9883: denga sanga gsung rabs dgongs 'grel dang bcas pa la
NK120(e)001:9884: thos bsam gyis legs par ma sbyangsa shing blun po
NK120(e)001:9885: mkhas rlom can gzhan la mu cora smra ba brgya
NK120(e)001:9886: phrag du mas / sgom pa nyams len gyi sgo
NK120(e)001:9887: nas ranga gi gnas lugs kyi ye shes rdul phran
NK120(e)001:9888: gyi cha shas tsam yang ma rtogsa para ranga bzosa
NK120(e)001:9889: bslad pa'i cho gasa rigs mthun rmongsa pa rnams dga'
NK120(e)001:9890: ba bskyed cing tshim pa'i dus 'dir /
NK120(e)001:9891: rang gzhan gnyis ka brlag pa'i skyabsa gnas de 'dra
NK120(e)001:9892: ba la bsten pa'i snyigs dus kyi skye bo 'di
NK120(e)001:9893: rnams kye ma kye hud snying re rje bsam gyin
NK120(e)001:9894: skyes bu dam pa rnams ni snying nas mya ngan
NK120(e)001:9895: gyi mchi ma dku bar 'os pa'i gnas su gyur
NK120(e)001:9896: pa yin no // gnyis pa 'di ltar rtsom dgos pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK120(e)001:9897: mdo sngags lam rnams mu med 'gro ba'i phyir //
NK120(e)001:9898: tshang la ma nor lam 'di rgyal bas gsungs //
NK120(e)001:9899: gangs can 'di na de dag phyogs rer 'dzin //
NK120(e)001:9900: gcig tu sems kyang sdom gsum ming tsam lus //
NK120(e)001:9902: mdo sngagsa lam rim rnams ni mthar yas shig mu
NK120(e)001:9903: meda pa'i 'gro ba rnams kyi khams dbang dang mthun
NK120(e)001:9904: par de dag thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen pa'i
NK120(e)001:9906: gang zag gcig 'tshang rgya ba'i thabs tshanga la ma nor ba'i lam 'di rgyal basa gsungas mod /
NK120(e)001:9907: 'on kyang gangas can 'di na mdo sngags gnyis 'gal
NK120(e)001:9908: lo zhes blun po spyi brtol can dee dag gis
NK120(e)001:9909: ni me chu ltar 'gal 'du'i phung por mthong nas
NK120(e)001:9911: mkhas pa rnam dpyod dang ldan pa gcig tu bsdu
NK120(e)001:9912: bar semsa pa dag gis kyang bshad yams kyi sa
NK120(e)001:9913: bcad pa tsam las sdom pa gsuma gyi bslab bya
NK120(e)001:9914: gong 'og mi 'gal bar shes dgos pa rnams ni
NK120(e)001:9916: gsum pa ji ltar brtsams pa'i tshul ni //
NK120(e)001:9917: 'di ni mkhas grub du ma'i legs bshad las //
NK120(e)001:9918: sgrims pa'i blo yis phyogs gcig dag tu bkod //
NK120(e)001:9919: de phyir nongs pa'i dri ma med snyam rlom //
NK120(e)001:9921: tshul de ltar mthong nas bstan bcos 'dira ni rang
NK120(e)001:9922: bzo dang phyogs ris spangs te mdo rgyud kyi don
NK120(e)001:9923: ji lta ba bzhin du gtan la 'bebs par byed
NK120(e)001:9924: pa'i makhasa grub du ma'i legas par bshad pa lasa
NK120(e)001:9925: / ji skad bstan pa rnams sgrimsa po'i blo yisa
NK120(e)001:9926: brtags shing dpyad pa'i sgo nas mdo rgyud man ngag
NK120(e)001:9927: rnams dang mi 'gal bar phyogsa gciga dag tu bkoda
NK120(e)001:9928: / pa yin pas / rgyu mtshan de yi phyir
NK120(e)001:9929: na ma rtogs pa dang log par rtogs pa'i dbang
NK120(e)001:9930: gis nyes par bshad pa sogs kyi nongsa pa'i dri
NK120(e)001:9931: ma cha tsam med do snyam du rlom pa yin
NK120(e)001:9932: pas na lam mchog 'di nyid kyi rjes su 'jug
NK120(e)001:9933: pa'i skal bzang gi gdul bya rnams snying nas yid
NK120(e)001:9934: ches pa'i nor skal du bzung bar mdzod cig ces
NK120(e)001:9936: bzhi pa des thob pa'i dge ba bsngo ba ni /
NK120(e)001:9937: dge des kun bzang go 'phang myur thob shog /
NK120(e)001:9939: mdo sngags chos tshul rgya mtsho tshang la ma nor
NK120(e)001:9940: ba skal bzang kun tu dga' ba'i 'jug ngogs gcig
NK120(e)001:9941: pur gyur pa sdom gsum rnam par nges pa'i bstan
NK120(e)001:9942: bcos ngo mtshar ba 'di nyid brtsams pa las byung
NK120(e)001:9943: ba'i bsod nams kyi phung po mkha' mthar gtugs pa'i
NK120(e)001:9944: dge tshogs desa mkha' khyab kyi 'gro ba thams cad
NK120(e)001:9945: sku lnga ye shes lnga dang 'du 'bral med par
NK120(e)001:9946: rang byung gdod ma'i sangs rgyas kun tu bazanga po'i
NK120(e)001:9947: go 'aphanga myur du thob par shoga cig ces so
NK120(e)001:9948: // mthar bstan bcos ji ltar brtsams pa'i mdzad byang smos pa ni /
NK120(e)001:9949: ces sdom gsum rnam nges tshig gis rim par phye
NK120(e)001:9950: ba 'di gangs ri'i phreng bas bskor ba'i yul ljongs
NK120(e)001:9951: lho phyogs kyi rgyud du byung ba nges par 'byung
NK120(e)001:9952: ba'i bsam pa can mnga' ris kyi pan+di ta pad+ma
NK120(e)001:9953: dbang gi rgyal pos bkod pa /
NK120(e)001:9954: phyogs dus thams cad du rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK120(e)001:9955: po'i bstan pa bya ba byed nus par gyur cig
NK120(e)001:9957: de skad ces sdom pa gsum rnam par ngesa pa
NK120(e)001:9958: zhes bya ba'i bstan bcos 'di nyid mdzad pa po'i
NK120(e)001:9960: gangs can pa'i lam ston thu mi sam+b+ho tas /
NK120(e)001:9961: yi ge'i khungs nas ming byung ste //
NK120(e)001:9962: ming gi khungs nas tshig byung la //
NK120(e)001:9963: tshig gis don rnams ston par byed //
NK120(e)001:9967: tshig 'dus pa las don gyi rnam grangs rnams ston pa las /
NK120(e)001:9968: 'dir tshig gi sgo nas bstan pa'i gzhung tshogs le'u
NK120(e)001:9969: rima par phye ba lnga'i bdag nyid can gyi gzhung
NK120(e)001:9970: bzang po tshig nyung la don bsdus pa lung rig
NK120(e)001:9971: man ngag du ma'i bang mdzod du gyur pa 'di
NK120(e)001:9972: nyid bar chad med par brtsams pa mthar phyin pa'i
NK120(e)001:9973: skabs su babs pa na bar snang gi lha rnams
NK120(e)001:9974: kyis mngon par shes pa'i legs so'i me tog gi
NK120(e)001:9975: char bsnyil ba dang bcas yongs su grub pa yin
NK120(e)001:9976: la / bstan bcos mdzad pa po'i mtshan dang /
NK120(e)001:9977: gang du mdzad pa'i gnas kyi khyad par ni bsil
NK120(e)001:9978: ldan gangsa ri'i phreng basa yongs su bskora ba'i bod
NK120(e)001:9979: kyi yul ljongsa las bye brag lho phyogsa kyi rgyud
NK120(e)001:9980: mnga' ris glo bo ma thang du byung ba yon
NK120(e)001:9981: tan gyi khyad par shes rab dang snying rjes srid
NK120(e)001:9982: zhi'i mtha' gnyis las ngesa par 'byung ba'i bla na
NK120(e)001:9983: med pa'i byang chub don gnyer gyi bsam pa bzang
NK120(e)001:9985: sbyor ba gzhan don sgrub pa'i thabs la mkhas pa
NK120(e)001:9986: can rig pa'i gnas chen lnga dang gnas phran lnga
NK120(e)001:9987: rnams thugs su chud pa'i mang'a risa kyi pan+di ta
NK120(e)001:9988: pad+ma dabnga gi rgyal po rdo rje grags pa rgyal
NK120(e)001:9989: mtshan dpal bzang posa gsung rab dgongs 'grel dang bcas
NK120(e)001:9990: pa'i don ji lta ba bzhin du bkoda par mdzad
NK120(e)001:9991: pa 'di ni thar 'dod kyi gang zag rnams nas
NK120(e)001:9992: spyi bo'i rgyan du blangs par 'os pa kho na
NK120(e)001:9994: gang zhig rgyal ba'i bstan pa 'ba' zhig gis //
NK120(e)001:9995: dbang byas rnam g.yeng med yid can gyis bshad //
NK120(e)001:9996: thar pa thob pa'i lam dang rjes mthun pa //
NK120(e)001:9997: de yang drang srong bka' bzhin spyi bos blangs //
NK120(e)001:9999: de ltar brtsams pa'i dge ba ci yod pa des
NK120(e)001:10000: phyogsa bcu dang dus gsum gyis bsdus pa'i 'jig rten
NK120(e)001:10001: gyi khams thamsa cad du mdo sngags rgyal pa'i bstan
NK120(e)001:10002: pa yin no cog spyi dang /
NK120(e)001:10003: khyad par theg pa kun gyi rtse mor son pa
NK120(e)001:10004: ranga bzhina rdzogsa pa chen po a ti yo ga'i
NK120(e)001:10005: bstan pa la bshad sgrub kyi sgo nas bya ba
NK120(e)001:10006: rlabs po che byed nus para gyur ciga ces smon
NK120(e)001:10007: lam du mdzad pa ni bsngo ba rnams kyi nang
NK120(e)001:10008: nas mchog tu gyur pa ste /
NK120(e)001:10009: smon lam thams cad kyang dam pa'i chos yongs su
NK120(e)001:10010: 'dzin par bsngosa na der 'du bar gsungs ba'i phyir
NK120(e)001:10012: rgyal ba kun gyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
NK120(e)001:10013: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
NK120(e)001:10014: bzang po spyod pa rnam par sbyong pa yang //
NK120(e)001:10015: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyod par shog /
NK120(e)001:10016: ces gsungs pa dang tshul mthun pa yin no //
NK120(e)001:10018: de ltar rnam 'dren bzhi pa'i ring lugs mchog /
NK120(e)001:10019: thog mthar bar dge'i lam gyi srol phyes nas //
NK120(e)001:10020: kun khyab yid bzhin nor bu'i gter kha zhig /
NK120(e)001:10021: thang mar brdal 'di khri srong khyod min su //
NK120(e)001:10022: thog mar dge ba sgo gsum nyes spyod sdom //
NK120(e)001:10023: bar du dge ba gzhan phan gzhir bcas bsgrub //
NK120(e)001:10024: tha mar dge ba don gnyis lhun grub kyi //
NK120(e)001:10025: rgyal sar dbugs chen 'byin la bslu ba med //
NK120(e)001:10026: rmongs pa bdag kyang de lta'i tshul shes nas //
NK120(e)001:10027: khyod kyi lam bzang byi dor cung bgyis pa //
NK120(e)001:10028: 'di las lam bzang nor ba med pa'i rgyun //
NK120(e)001:10029: rnam 'dren lnga pa'i bar du gsal gyur cig /
NK120(e)001:10030: tshul 'dir 'chad nyan sgom sgrub zab mo'i srol //
NK120(e)001:10031: lnga ba do'i mthar yang nub med slar gsal nas //
NK120(e)001:10032: 'jig rten phan bder spyod pa'i skal bzang gis //
NK120(e)001:10033: zhing rnams kun khyab bkra shis dpal 'bar shog /
NK120(e)001:10034: de ltar sdom gsum rnam par nges pa'i gzhung 'di
NK120(e)001:10035: la 'dren pa bka' drin mtshungs med o rgyan chos
NK120(e)001:10036: 'byor rgya mtsho'i sku drung nas rang lo bcu gnyis
NK120(e)001:10037: par rdzogs chen dpal sprul 'jigs med chos kyi dbang
NK120(e)001:10038: po'i zhal rgyun gtso bor byas pa'i smin khrid zhib
NK120(e)001:10040: rang nyid nas de ma thag tu bris pa'i brjed
NK120(e)001:10041: zin 'bru 'grel lta bu zhig yod pa la phyis
NK120(e)001:10042: su zhib par bltas pa na brjod bya'i don la
NK120(e)001:10043: nor 'khrul mi 'dug kyang rjod byed tshig tshogs mang
NK120(e)001:10044: nyung ci rigs pas skabs 'gar zlos skyon lta bu
NK120(e)001:10045: dang / skabs rer 'bru gnyer ma thub pa sogs khongs snyoms pa zhig byung mi 'dug cing /
NK120(e)001:10046: spyir yang skabs der rang nyid lo na phra zhing
NK120(e)001:10047: sbyangs stobs kyi shes yon zhan pa sogs kyis blta
NK120(e)001:10048: go chod pa khyer bde don tshang zhig kyang byung
NK120(e)001:10049: mi 'dug pas na phyin chad yig rgyun mi 'phel
NK120(e)001:10050: bar bya sems kho na'i ngang gzhan rkyen 'du 'dzi
NK120(e)001:10051: mang pos yengs te rim lus su gyur /
NK120(e)001:10052: phyis su rang ltos slob tshogs bla sprul kha shas
NK120(e)001:10053: na rang re'i 'bru 'grel 'di la blta bde don
NK120(e)001:10054: tshang zhig nges par mtha' skyong yod pa zhes yang
NK120(e)001:10055: yang dran bskul byed mkhan kha shas shig byung ba
NK120(e)001:10056: dang / da lta snga 'gyur bka' ma'i phrin chog
NK120(e)001:10057: rgyab chos bcas spar 'debs skabs su sdom 'grel 'di
NK120(e)001:10058: yang sdebs su tshud na rmongs pa rang 'dra 'ga'
NK120(e)001:10059: la cung zad phan thogs yong rgyu'i re ba bcas
NK120(e)001:10060: dang / te / lha rigs sh+aakya'i dge bsnyen rnal
NK120(e)001:10061: 'byor spyod pa 'jigs bral ye shes rdo rjes rang
NK120(e)001:10062: lo brgyad cu gya gcig pa shing byi hor zla
NK120(e)001:10063: bcu pa'i shes rab kyi cha la nub phyogs dga'
NK120(e)001:10064: ba 'khyil ba'i ljongs su bskyod sdong skabs zhib mor
NK120(e)001:10065: dpyad pa'i sgo nas sbyar ba las /
NK120(e)001:10066: yi ge pa ni rang gi gam du nye bar
NK120(e)001:10067: gnas pa blo gsal bsod nams nor bu nas rtsom
NK120(e)001:10068: gzhi'i zin bris ci rigs par btab cing /
NK120(e)001:10069: yongs su rdzogs par sngon dag'i bag chags bzang po
NK120(e)001:10070: las 'phro mthud pa la mi zhum pa rang slob
NK120(e)001:10071: mon gyi sngags btsun kun bzang dbang 'dus kyis bgyis
NK120(e)001:10072: pa'o // 'dis kyang mchog gsang pad+ma'i ring lugs nam
NK120(e)001:10073: yang mi nyams par gong nas gong du 'phel zhing
NK120(e)001:10074: rgyas te rtag khyab lhun grub 'byung ba'i cha rkyen
